{"department_text": "Movies, Music & Games", "nr_products": 493283, "catid": 82, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/musical-instruments-accessories-sound-recording/b/ref=sd_allcat_mi/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=11091801", "text": "Musical Instruments", "description_title": "Amazon.com's Musical Instruments Store", "keyword_count": {"musical instruments store": 2, "instruments": 6, "amazoncom": 3, "musical instruments": 5, "musical": 6, "store": 5}, "description_wc": 277, "description_text": "Welcome to the Musical Instruments Store at Amazon.com. From stage to studio, this is your source for the gear you need to perform your best--whether you\u2019re a beginner or a seasoned musician. Browse our selection of guitars, keyboards, basses, amps, drums, stringed instruments, band & orchestra, DJ gear, and more to get set up with the perfect instrument. Check out the latest recording equipment, from microphones to monitors and audio interfaces to DAW software. Take care of your live sound needs with power amps, speakers, and cables galore. Pick up some pro lighting effects for your next gig. Or how about some fun kids\u2019 musical instruments to get \u2018em started at a young age? Whatever your goal--outfitting a venue, recording a rock & roll masterpiece, DJing parties, learning violin--Amazon has you covered. Check out top deals, gift ideas, best-selling gear, and featured brands such as Fender, Gibson, Line 6, Pearl, M-Audio, Avid, Shure Microphones, Zildjian, Sabian, Peavey, Epiphone, Yamaha, Casio, and hundreds more. Take advantage of Amazon Prime shipping, financing with the Amazon.com Store Card, and other special offers. Browse our special stores, such as the Beginner Store for students and those just starting out, or the Musical Instruments Outlet, featuring huge markdowns on all kinds of gear and equipment. Need accessories for your instrument? No problem\u2014pick up some strings, sticks, reeds, picks, stands, tuners, or anything else you might need from our huge selection. And, as with all things Amazon.com, check out customer reviews of musical instruments to help make your choice. Whatever your musical needs, you\u2019ll find it here in the Musical Instruments Store. Start making some music today!", "parent_text": "Movies, Music & Games", "parent_catid": 8, "keyword_density": {"musical instruments store": "2.2", "instruments": "2.2", "amazoncom": "1.1", "musical instruments": "3.6", "musical": "2.2", "store": "1.8"}, "department_id": 8},
{"department_text": "Movies, Music & Games", "nr_products": 654479, "catid": 83, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Entertainment-Collectibles/b/ref=sd_allcat_entcol/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=5088769011", "text": "Entertainment Collectibles", "description_title": "Entertainment Collectibles at Amazon.com", "keyword_count": {"collectibles": 9, "entertainment collectibles": 4}, "description_wc": 167, "description_text": "Welcome to the Entertainment Collectibles Store featuring music, movie, TV, and theater memorabilia, collectibles, and autographs from the past and present. The Entertainment Collectibles store covers many genres with Amazon Marketplace sellers offering a unique selection of autographed items and collectible memorabilia. If you are looking to build your collection of music memorabilia, movie collectibles, TV collectibles, theater memorabilia, or want to find a unique gift for an avid collector, then the new Entertainment Collectibles Store has the unique selection that you are looking for. The store focuses on authenticated collectibles and memorabilia, such as autographs authenticated by PSA/DNA, R.E.A.L. and Autograph Pros. Whichever artists, actors, actresses, are your favorite, you should be able to find them in our giant selection of autographed photos, posters, prints, trading cards, musical instruments, props, wardrobe, and other memorabilia, and collectibles. The store will continue to grow, so whether you are adding to your collection or buying something as a gift, find it at the new Amazon Entertainment Collectibles Store.", "parent_text": "Movies, Music & Games", "parent_catid": 8, "keyword_density": {"collectibles": "5.4", "entertainment collectibles": "4.8"}, "department_id": 8},
{"department_text": "Movies, Music & Games", "nr_products": 201028, "catid": 84, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/computer-video-games-hardware-accessories/b/ref=sd_allcat_cvg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=468642", "text": "Video Games", "description_title": "Video Games from Amazon.com", "keyword_count": {"video": 6, "amazoncom": 3, "video games": 5, "games": 9}, "description_wc": 227, "description_text": "Amazon\u2019s Video Games store is your entertainment hub for everything related to Video Games. The store features thousands of games at great prices and allows you to shop by gaming platform, bestsellers, new and future releases, bonus offers, price, deals, genre, ESRB rating, and more. You can shop for every type of game you may be looking for, including Xbox 360 , PlayStation 3 , PlayStation 4 , Nintendo Wii and Wii U, Nintendo 3DS, PlayStation Vita, Digital, Free-to-Play, Kindle Fire, PC and Mac, Nintendo DS, and much more. When you\u2019re looking to join in on the hottest new video game developments online, there\u2019s no better place to be than Amazon.com. Our new & future releases section features the latest games and newest pre-order options. Its streamlined, hassle-free pages are perfect for locating new video games in seconds, so you\u2019ll be at the forefront of all the action and right in line with even the most hardcore gaming aficionados. No matter which gaming system you use, Amazon.com offers the latest updates and releases on new video games. For bonus offers and everyday savings on a wide selection of games and accessories, visit our Deals Store . Don\u2019t forget to trade in the games you\u2019ve already finished for Amazon.com gift cards in the Video Games Trade-In Store .", "parent_text": "Movies, Music & Games", "parent_catid": 8, "keyword_density": {"games": "4.1", "amazoncom": "1.4", "video games": "4.5", "video": "2.7"}, "department_id": 8},
