{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 0, "catid": 97, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Laptops-Tablets/b/ref=sd_allcat_lapnet/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2956501011", "text": " Laptops & Tablets", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Laptops, Ultrabooks & Tablets at Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Laptops-Tablets/b/ref=sd_allcat_lapnet/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2956501011", "keyword_count": {}, "description_wc": 328, "description_text": "Nowadays, it\u2019s all about portability. More and more of us have left behind the bulky desktop PC for these smaller, more mobile (and these days just as powerful) counterparts. Still haven\u2019t made the leap? Amazon is the perfect one-stop shop for a new laptop, tablet, or Ultrabook. With brands like Acer, Apple, ASUS, Dell, HP, Kindle Fire HD, Lenovo, Samsung, Sony, and Toshiba, you\u2019re sure to end up with a great machine. On the laptop front, you\u2019ll find all the standard styles, whether you\u2019re looking for a PC, Mac, Chromebook, Netbook, touchscreen laptop, Ultrabook, or more. Check out laptop best sellers, peruse our best deals, check out our helpful buying guides, and more\u2014you\u2019ll find just the right laptop model for you. If you\u2019re looking for a powerful, ultra-portable laptop, an Ultrabook may be just the right choice. An Ultrabook is a high-end subnotebook, outfitted with a low-power Intel processor, solid-state drive, and other technologies to give you a featherweight form-factor without losing performance or battery life. If you\u2019re unsure of which Ultrabook would suit your needs, our Ultrabook Buying Guide might be a good place to start. Or perhaps you\u2019re after a tablet? Tablet computing is increasingly popular, and it\u2019s no wonder why. These flat, touchscreen devices let you casually surf the web, enjoy music and video, play games, download and use apps (tablet speak for applications), read eBooks, and so much more. Our Tablet Buying Guide can help you find the right tablet for your needs, or you can check out best sellers, browse by brand, and more to do your research. You can also check out our selection of 2-in-1, aka convertible, machines, which combine a tablet and laptop in one. So whether you\u2019re looking for a laptop, Ultrabook, or tablet\u2014or even some combination of the above\u2014you\u2019ve come to the right place.", "parent_text": "Electronics & Computers", "parent_catid": 9, "keyword_density": {}, "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 0, "catid": 98, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Desktops/b/ref=sd_allcat_deskserv/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=4972214011", "text": "Desktops & Monitors", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Desktop Computers & Monitors at Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Desktops/b/ref=sd_allcat_deskserv/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=4972214011", "keyword_count": {"desktop computers": 4, "desktop": 5}, "description_wc": 268, "description_text": "Desktop computers are far from dead. Avid gamers, media professionals, or just home users looking for serious expandability all still look to desktop computers to suit their needs, and there are plenty of great machines available. Check out the best in desktop computers here at Amazon, from brands like Acer, Alienware, Apple, ASUS, CyberpowerPC, CybertronPC, Dell, Gateway, HP, iBUYPOWER, Lenovo, Sony, and Toshiba. You can check out our Desktop Buying Guide to find out a bit more about the right machine for you. Maybe you\u2019re looking for a newer all-in-one PC, where the monitor and CPU are a single unit, saving you all kinds of space in setting it up. Or maybe you\u2019re after the latest and greatest gaming PC--a good gaming PC is a cut above the average machine, with enhanced graphics, processing power, a supercharged cooling system, and other features to keep it at peak performance. Whether it\u2019s a gaming PC or any other type, you\u2019ll be covered here. Shop by price, brand, and other criteria such as desktop computers with a specific processor type (AMD or Intel). Check out best sellers, new releases, top rated and most gifted machines, and more. Once you\u2019ve picked out your machine you\u2019ll need to pick a monitor. Amazon has you covered there as well. Look for a monitor by size, check out monitor best sellers, choose between LCD and LED monitor types, and more. Whether you\u2019re after a massive high-definition monitor (for that gaming PC rig) or something a bit more modest, you\u2019ll find it here.", "parent_text": "Electronics & Computers", "parent_catid": 9, "keyword_density": {"desktop computers": "3.0", "desktop": "1.9"}, "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 0, "catid": 99, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Computer-Accessories/b/ref=sd_allcat_compaccess/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2956536011", "text": "Computer Accessories & Peripherals", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Computer Accessories at Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Computer-Accessories/b/ref=sd_allcat_compaccess/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2956536011", "keyword_count": {"computer": 6, "accessories": 7, "computer accessories": 4}, "description_wc": 241, "description_text": "Looking for an external hard drive to expand your storage, a router to set up your own network, or just a more comfortable keyboard and mouse? Amazon\u2019s Computer Accessories Store has all these and more. You\u2019re sure to find what you need in our broad selection of computer accessories and peripherals, including flash memory cards and USB drives, wired and wireless PC headsets, cables, and laptop bags, batteries, and cases. Check out our best sellers, top-rated computer accessories, and helpful customer reviews. We have accessories for every need and every computer, Mac or PC, from compact, high-speed SDHC and microSD flash memory cards to full-featured peripherals like wired and wireless keyboards, mice, headsets, and microphones designed for business, gaming, and home computing. If you\u2019re tough on your devices, don\u2019t miss our selection of rugged and spill-resistant accessories. Does your home or office network need a boost? Take a look at our selection of AC and N Wi-Fi routers. If it\u2019s deals you want, look no further. We have big discounts on every kind of computer accessory. Or maybe you just need more cables for all your gadgets. We\u2019ll keep you connected and in sync with USB, Ethernet, SATA, Lightning cables and more. If you\u2019re always on the go, protect and power your laptop and accessories with our bags, cases, batteries, and chargers--all in Amazon\u2019s Computer Accessories Store.", "parent_text": "Electronics & Computers", "parent_catid": 9, "keyword_density": {"computer": "2.5", "accessories": "2.9", "computer accessories": "3.3"}, "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 0, "catid": 100, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/PC-Parts-Components/b/ref=sd_allcat_components/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=193870011", "text": "Computer Parts & Components", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Computer Parts and Components from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/PC-Parts-Components/b/ref=sd_allcat_components/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=193870011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "computer parts": 5, "computer": 11, "components": 4, "computer parts and components": 1}, "description_wc": 315, "description_text": "If you\u2019re looking to repair, build, or upgrade your computer, you can find the components and computer parts you need at Amazon.com. We have a wide variety of computer parts and components, so whether you\u2019re trying to build a computer from the ground up or you just need to replace a few things for optimal performance, you can find what you need. Our hard disk drives and solid state drives come in a wide variety of capacities to hold all of your games, music, movies, and TV shows without a problem., and our high-performance sound cards and graphics cards can help you create the ultimate entertainment experience with crisp pictures and life-like sounds. For those who want to build their own tower, we carry the computer parts and hardware to get you started. We have a great selection of computer cases and chasses in metal or plastic, with USB 3.0 capabilities, windowed side panels, and amazing designs. We also have reliable and fast processors from some of the top manufacturers, including Intel, AMD, Corsair, Kingston, Crucial for Memory, and more. If you\u2019re shopping for computer parts on a budget, try filtering our processors, SSDs, or other components by price, by used or refurbished models, and even by discount to see some of the most affordable options available. For a faster computer experience, we carry many different memory modules to boost your RAM. Increasing your memory by one to 16 gigabytes can significantly improve your multitasking abilities so you can go between video chatting, playing games, listening to music and more without your computer getting bogged down by all the open applications. We even have an assortment of ergonomic, purpose-built, and other input devices to give you more control over your user interface. Find the components and computer parts you need to repair, build, or upgrade your computer at Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Electronics & Computers", "parent_catid": 9, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.6", "computer parts": "3.2", "computer": "3.5", "components": "1.3", "computer parts and components": "1.3"}, "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 258273, "catid": 101, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/design-download-business-education-software/b/ref=sd_allcat_sw/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=229534", "text": "Software", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Welcome to the Software Store at Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/design-download-business-education-software/b/ref=sd_allcat_sw/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=229534", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 5, "software store": 4, "software": 20}, "description_wc": 252, "description_text": "The Amazon.com Software Store is the ideal online destination for shopping computer software. Whether you own a Mac or PC, the Amazon.com Software Store has the selection to meet all your software needs. Search software by title, browse by category, and compare software programs until you find exactly the software you\u2019re looking for. If you are building a library of software programs for your home and office, the Amazon.com Software Store has you covered. Shop top Microsoft productivity titles such as Microsoft Office, Microsoft Word, Windows XP, Windows Vista, or recent and new versions like Windows 7 and Windows 8. Or if you are looking to better protect your computer and personal information, shop computer security and antivirus titles from trusted brands like McAfee, Norton, and BitDefender. In the market for photo software, video software, or design software? The Amazon.com Software Store offers a great selection from leading brands such as Adobe and Autodesk, with top titles including Photoshop Elements, InDesign, and Sketchbook Pro. You can also manage and optimize your videos with movie software or DVD software, or even harness your musical creativity with recording software. If you are looking to download software directly to your Mac or PC, you\u2019ve come to the right place. Amazon.com offers a growing collection of top software programs available for instant download to a computer, making the experience of shopping for software online more convenient than ever. Find all the latest software deals including straight price discounts, gift cards with purchase, and more.", "parent_text": "Electronics & Computers", "parent_catid": 9, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "2.0", "software store": "3.2", "software": "7.9"}, "department_id": 9},
