{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 1782250, "catid": 109, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Patio-Lawn-Garden/b/ref=sd_allcat_lp/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2972638011", "text": "Patio, Lawn & Garden", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Lawn Equipment from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Patio-Lawn-Garden/b/ref=sd_allcat_lp/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2972638011", "keyword_count": {"lawn equipment from amazoncom": 1, "lawn": 7, "lawn equipment": 5, "amazoncom": 4}, "description_wc": 313, "description_text": "No matter what the weather is like, your garden and lawn is a great place to relax and take a break from your busy life. Amazon.com carries all sort of lawn equipment to make sure that the time you spend in your front or back yard is as comfortable and inviting as possible. We have a wide variety of lawn equipment to help you with any landscaping and gardening chores. Mowers, trimmers and blowers can make keeping lawns neat and tidy, conveying an extremely welcoming and open environment. Useful watering tools, like heavy-duty hoses and spray nozzles are essential for making sure that all of your garden flowers and veggies get the moisture they need. We also have lawn equipment to help with your gardening, such as pruning shears, spades and germination trays. Once you\u2019ve polished and perfected your front and back yard, it\u2019s time to host a barbeque, and Amazon.com carries everything you need to throw a great outdoor party. You can find propane, natural gas, and charcoal burning grills easily among our outdoor cooking supplies. For serious eats, try special smokers and fryers built especially for outdoor use to give your barbeque unique and unforgettable flavor. We also have the tongs, spatulas, grill scrapers and other outdoor cooking accessories to make grilling fun. Take advantage of the selection of lawn equipment Amazon.com has to help you entertain for your outdoor party. Patio chairs, swinging benches and even hammocks can make it easy to relax and enjoy the peace of your garden. When it gets cold, we have many different styles of outdoor heaters to keep you and your guests warm and cozy. When it gets warmer outside, our pool supplies will help you cool down and keep you ready for a season of wet summer fun. Prepare for the changing seasons with the diverse lawn equipment from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "parent_catid": 10, "keyword_density": {"lawn equipment": "3.2", "lawn": "2.2", "lawn equipment from amazoncom": "1.3", "amazoncom": "1.3"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 57780, "catid": 110, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Art/b/ref=sd_allcat_fine_art/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=6685269011", "text": "Fine Art", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Fine Art at Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Art/b/ref=sd_allcat_fine_art/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=6685269011", "keyword_count": {"art": 22, "fine art": 5}, "description_wc": 152, "description_text": "Welcome to our new Fine Art store featuring paintings, drawings, mixed media works, photography and art prints. From new artists to famous artists the Fine Art store features artworks and paintings for sale from a multitude of periods and styles including: Pop art, Abstract art, Modern art, Contemporary art, and much more. We focus on highlighting a wide variety of artists, painters, Contemporary artists, Renaissance artists, Modern and Post-Modern artists; find an artist that fits your style in our Fine Arts store. The Fine Arts store features many types of artwork including: canvas prints, abstract paintings, oil paintings, drawings, photography, mixed media works, and collages to add to your home, art gallery, professional workspace or other. As we continue to grow our collections of artworks, the Fine Arts store is sure to have something for everybody whether you are an experienced collector or looking to find your first piece of art.", "parent_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "parent_catid": 10, "keyword_density": {"art": "14.5", "fine art": "6.6"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 1653130, "catid": 111, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Arts-Crafts-Sewing/b/ref=sd_allcat_sch/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2617941011", "text": "Arts, Crafts & Sewing", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Arts and Crafts from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Arts-Crafts-Sewing/b/ref=sd_allcat_sch/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2617941011", "keyword_count": {"arts": 8, "crafts": 9, "amazoncom": 4, "arts and crafts": 7}, "description_wc": 325, "description_text": "Creating something beautiful or useful out with your own two hands is one of life\u2019s truly rewarding experiences. The feeling of accomplishment and time well spent has had people coming back to arts and crafts throughout history. Today, there are more tools and supplies than ever before to enable you to realize your vision. Whether you\u2019re introducing a curious youngster to arts and crafts for the first time, or if you\u2019ve been steeped in it your whole life, there\u2019s a project waiting for you. The Arts, Crafts, & Sewing Store at Amazon.com is your gateway to a world of unlimited creativity. We offer a huge variety of materials, tools, and supplies for arts and crafts of every discipline. From basics like paper and glue to advanced, computer-controlled equipment for professionals, Amazon.com has the arts and crafts supplies you need to get the most out of your creative hobby. To make it easier to browse our large selection, we provide helpful sorting and filtering tools. You can choose to view items of a certain color, material, or size. Narrowing your choices to the most relevant products is one way we help save you time. Choosing products you know and trust is important, which is why at Amazon.com, we carry top arts and crafts brands such as Martha Stewart Crafts, Brother, Fiskars, and dozens more. Additionally, our user reviews from other customers who have purchased the item you\u2019re interested in can often help you decide whether or not a product is right for you. We\u2019re proud of our customer service at Amazon.com, and we want to give you the best arts and crafts shopping experience we can, by offering conveniences like Free Shipping on many popular products. Whether you\u2019re looking for a new creative way to express yourself, or simply want to expand your repertoire of DIY projects, there\u2019s something for you in the world of arts and crafts.", "parent_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "parent_catid": 10, "keyword_density": {"arts": "2.5", "amazoncom": "1.2", "arts and crafts": "6.5", "crafts": "2.8"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 683815, "catid": 112, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/pet-supplies-dog-cat-food-bed-toy/b/ref=sd_allcat_ps/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2619533011", "text": "Pet Supplies", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Pet Supplies from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/pet-supplies-dog-cat-food-bed-toy/b/ref=sd_allcat_ps/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2619533011", "keyword_count": {"pet": 20, "pet supplies": 6, "pet supplies from amazoncom": 1, "supplies": 7}, "description_wc": 343, "description_text": "Puppies, rabbits, kittens, parrots, rodents, lizards, fish, and other pets all have one thing in common: their humans love them. If you\u2019re bringing home a new pet, or if you\u2019re browsing for something new for an old family friend, we have all the pet supplies you need to ensure your pet\u2019s health and longevity. We have all the pet supplies and food you could need to ensure your critter\u2019s health. If your new little family member eats pellets, kibble, flakes, or veggies, we have what they love. We carry pet food from some of the most trusted names in pet nutrition, including Purina, Kaytee, Fancy Feast, and much more. Nutrition for pets is just as important as it is for us humans; their attitude and energy levels can drastically improve when they\u2019re getting the right vitamins, minerals, and proteins they need. The next step is to ensure your pet\u2019s hygiene. We carry cage liners for a variety of small pets and birds. They\u2019re much easier to deal with than traditional shredded newspaper and sawdust options, because these pet supplies are built to be especially absorptive. We also have kitty litter for cats, training supplies for dogs, and a wide variety of filters for fish. Whether your pet scurries, swims or squawks, make sure they have a clean environment to thrive in. Once you\u2019ve taken care of all the necessary pet supplies, it\u2019s time to get down to the fun part. Pet toys can make spending time with your furry, scaly, or feathered friend even more enjoyable than it already is. There are a variety of toys to enrich caged pets, and there are also balls, climbing structures, and chew toys for larger animals. If you filter your search for pet supplies by price, you can see the most affordable pet toys first, so you can afford to treat your pet to some extra love. Live your life to the fullest, and ensure your pets can do the same with the pet supplies from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "parent_catid": 10, "keyword_density": {"pet": "5.8", "pet supplies": "3.5", "pet supplies from amazoncom": "1.2", "supplies": "2.0"}, "department_id": 10},
