u2019re an aficionado of red wines, we have just the selection for you, from dry red wine to sweet red wine across multiple varieties. Browse through many varieties of red wines, such as Cabernet Sauvignon, Pinot Noir, Merlot, Malbec, Sangiovese, Syrah, Zinfandel, Cabernet Franc, Tempranillo, and Greneche. Or, if you can\u2019t get enough of delicious white wines, we have a broad selection to choose from whether you prefer a dry white wine or sweet white wine. Browse through many varieties of white wines, such as Chardonnay, Moscato, Pinot Grigio, Pinot Gris, Riesling, Sauvignon Blanc, Semillon, and Viognier. We\u2019ve got great sparkling wine and dessert wine, too, which are perfect for special occasions.", "parent_text": "Beauty, Health & Grocery", "parent_catid": 11, "keyword_density": {"wine": "12.4"}, "department_id": 11},
