{"department_text": "Sports & Outdoors", "nr_products": 13332672, "catid": 156, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Sports-Collectibles/b/ref=sd_allcat_sprt_cllct/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=3250697011", "text": "Sports Collectibles", "description_title": "Sports Collectibles at Amazon.com", "keyword_count": {"sports collectibles": 8, "sports": 16}, "description_wc": 291, "description_text": "Welcome to our new Sports Collectibles store featuring sports memorabilia and sports collectibles from past, current and future stars from all major sport leagues and events including: Major League Baseball (MLB), National Football League (NFL), National Basketball Association (NBA), National Hockey League (NHL), Major League Soccer (MLS), NCAA, and Olympics. If you are looking to build your collection of sports collectibles and sports memorabilia or want to find a unique gift for an avid collector that will surprise them, our new store has the unique selection of sports memorabilia and sports collectibles that you are looking for. We focus on authentic sports collectibles and sports memorabilia, such as autographs and game-used jerseys authenticated by Ace Authentic, Frameworth, Highland Mint, Icon Sports Memorabilia, James Spence Authentication, MeiGray Group, MLB Players Alumni Association, Mounted Memories, NFL Players Inc., Panini Authentic, PSA/DNA, Steiner Sports, Topps, Tristar Authentic, and Upper Deck Authenticated. For the trading card collectors, we focus on having a large selection of wax packs and boxes, factory complete sets and single cards graded by Beckett Grading Services and Professional Sports Authenticator (PSA). As we continue to grow our selection, the Amazon Sports Collectibles Store is sure to have something for everybody. Whichever teams or players are your favorite, you should be able to find them amongst our giant selection of Authentic Game Used Merchandise, Autographed Jerseys, Balls, Bats, Shoes, Photos, Helmets, Trading cards, Other Sports Memorabilia and Sports Collectibles. Our new store will also have supplies such as display cases, ball cubes and card protectors, so whether you are adding to your collection, organizing your collection, or buying something as a gift, let the new Amazon Marketplace Sports Collectibles store help you find it.", "parent_text": "Sports & Outdoors", "parent_catid": 14, "keyword_density": {"sports collectibles": "5.6", "sports": "5.6"}, "department_id": 14},
{"department_text": "Sports & Outdoors", "nr_products": 101618, "catid": 157, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Golf-Sports-Outdoors/b/ref=sd_allcat_golf/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=3410851", "text": "Golf", "description_title": "Golf Equipment from Amazon.com", "keyword_count": {"golf": 11, "golf equipment from amazoncom": 2, "golf equipment": 5}, "description_wc": 328, "description_text": "Feeling a cool breeze against your face as you pull back and swing at a golf ball is a relaxing, almost meditative experience. Thanks to quality golf equipment from Amazon.com, you can enjoy the rich landscape of a grassy course and maybe even hit a few eagles. Or you can leave the wildlife alone and try harder to get in on the green. Golf clubs are number one on our list of golf equipment essentials, so we offer a wide variety of clubs for your needs. If you\u2019re looking for the right iron, wood or putter, you\u2019re in luck; you can select specific drivers to make short work of your quest for the perfect club. If you\u2019re not looking for individual clubs, you can also choose from our complete sets to get everything you need to go out to the driving range. When you don\u2019t have time to drive to the range, we can help you set up a variety of training options so you can practice while you\u2019re at home. Take a break after work with our practice putting greens and try to sink a few balls before dinner. Our golf nets can be hooked up in your back yard or garage so you can swing away and keep the birds and neighbors\u2019 windows safe. Among our collection of golf equipment, you\u2019ll find a variety of swing trainers so you can build up your core muscles and hone your tempo and lag. When you finally have time to visit the course but the weather isn\u2019t behaving, we have the solution for you. Specially made golf umbrellas, golf hats, and other golf equipment can make you comfortable in any weather. Our polo and other golf shirts are breezy enough that hot, summer days won\u2019t be a problem. With quality training and golf equipment from Amazon.com, the days of evicting birds from their nests will be a thing of the past.", "parent_text": "Sports & Outdoors", "parent_catid": 14, "keyword_density": {"golf": "3.4", "golf equipment": "3.0", "golf equipment from amazoncom": "2.4"}, "department_id": 14},
{"department_text": "Sports & Outdoors", "nr_products": 0, "catid": 158, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/sporting-goods/b/ref=sd_allcat_sg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=3375251", "text": "All Sports & Outdoors", "description_title": "The Amazon Sports & Outdoors Store", "keyword_count": {"amazon": 3, "amazon sports outdoors store": 2, "store": 5, "sports": 7}, "description_wc": 126, "description_text": "The Amazon Sports & Outdoors Store is the leading online retailer of sporting goods and outdoor equipment. We feature specialty stores in popular categories like Exercise & Fitness, Golf, Skiing & Snowboarding, Cycling, Hunting & Fishing, Camping & Hiking, and Boating & Watersports. But because as an online retailer we enjoy the advantage of \"unlimited\" shelf space, we also feature stores -- and a wide selection of products -- for smaller categories like Skateboarding, Surfing, Paintball & Airsoft, Racquet Sports, and Team Sports. If you're a sports fan check out our Fan Shop. And if you consider yourself a hard-charging athlete check out our new Amazon Athlete store. No matter your sports passion or skill level, we're confident you'll find what you're looking for in the Amazon Sports & Outdoors Store", "parent_text": "Sports & Outdoors", "parent_catid": 14, "keyword_density": {"amazon": "2.4", "amazon sports outdoors store": "6.3", "store": "4.0", "sports": "5.6"}, "department_id": 14},
{"department_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "nr_products": 0, "catid": 159, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/automotive-auto-truck-replacements-parts/b/ref=sd_allcat_apa/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=15684181", "text": "Automotive Parts & Accessories", "description_title": "More about Auto Parts and Accessories", "keyword_count": {"auto": 17, "parts and accessories": 3, "parts": 18, "auto parts": 12}, "description_wc": 252, "description_text": "The world of auto parts includes everything from performance parts to car care to tools and equipment for cars, trucks and even RVs. Amazon.com Automotive Parts and Accessories store presents this huge world of automotive products an organized online store with a number of refinements, so you can find the auto parts you need. For example, the Green Automotive section contains earth-friendly auto parts. Replacement Parts showcases auto parts to keep your car or truck in top shape. Interior auto parts , exterior auto parts and car care auto parts let you update and care for your ride. Our auto parts even include everything from wheel and tire care products to new rims and wheels. There are even gift ideas for the enthusiast. Amazon.com Automotive also has a helpful Part Finder tool that allows customers to find and filter products that fit their vehicle. You can browse through products with this tool, or even use it to filter down specific array of products. Browse the site and discover auto parts that make winter less stressful, parts and accessories for your RV, tools that help diagnose what\u2019s wrong, as well as parts to fix what ails your vehicle. You can even shop for auto parts by trusted name brands or find auto parts for specific vehicle brands like Chevrolet , Ford , or Ferrari . Even better, Amazon\u2019s Automotive Parts and Accessories store lets you shop for auto parts in one location from the comfort of your home or garage.", "parent_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "parent_catid": 15, "keyword_