{"department_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "nr_products": 313068, "catid": 160, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Tools-Equipment-Automotive/b/ref=sd_allcat_ate/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=15706941", "text": "Automotive Tools & Equipment", "description_title": "More about Automotive Tools", "keyword_count": {"automotive": 7, "tools": 11, "automotive tools": 5}, "description_wc": 168, "description_text": "To take care of your vehicle, you are going to need a wide number of automotive tools. Fortunately, Amazon.com Automotive houses a wide selection of automotive tools that you can use to fix and enhance your car, truck, ATV, or RV. Our selection goes above and beyond our diagnostic and scanner tools . Our automotive tools allow users to truly understand problems that are occurring with their vehicle, and then fix them. The automotive tool selection includes body repair tools , brake repair tools , drive train tools , garage and shop tools , impact wrenches , and so much more. Our automotive tools provide auto owners the ability to work independently on their car, allowing them to save money. These automotive tools act as the perfect complimentary purchase to any other performance or replacement part purchase that you make on our store. Since these tools are shipped quickly, you can save yourself a trip down to the store and get started working on your vehicles right away.", "parent_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "parent_catid": 15, "keyword_density": {"automotive": "4.3", "tools": "6.8", "automotive tools": "6.2"}, "department_id": 15},
