{"department_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "nr_products": 194958, "catid": 162, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/b/ref=sd_allcat_wt/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=15706571", "text": "Tires & Wheels", "description_title": "More about Tires, Rims, and Wheels", "keyword_count": {"tires": 11, "wheels": 4, "tires rims and wheels": 2, "tires rims": 3, "rims": 5}, "description_wc": 229, "description_text": "Amazon.com Automotive has a great selection of tires, rims, and wheels for your vehicle. Our wide selection of rims and tires allows any car enthusiast to quickly find and replace their current wheels, or improve their current vehicle. Our website allows customers to browse through a wide variety of tires, rims, or wheels based on need. For example, we have tires for trailers , commercial trucks , SUVs , RVs , and more. Our tire selection allows you to browse and find the correct products for whatever purpose. Our selection includes all-season tires , off-roading tires , performance tires , and more. We even have tires for motorcycles and ATVs . Our rims and tires don\u2019t come alone, either. Our pages have all the necessary tire accessories , wheel and rim accessories, and tire and wheel repair tools that you may need. This will allow you to purchase the necessary equipment to do tasks such as diagnose your wheel alignment and balancing. You can even find kits for rim and tire installation , so you can do it yourself and enhance your vehicle, whether it is a car, truck, or ATV, year round for every season. With Amazon.com\u2019s Part Finder tool you can find the perfect rim and tires that fit your vehicle. You can shop for tires, rims, and wheels confidently online at Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "parent_catid": 15, "keyword_density": {"tires": "5.0", "wheels": "1.8", "tires rims and wheels": "3.7", "tires rims": "2.7", "rims": "2.3"}, "department_id": 15},
{"department_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "nr_products": 1057774, "catid": 163, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Motorcycle-ATV-Automotive/b/ref=sd_allcat_matv/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=346333011", "text": "Motorcycle & Powersports", "description_title": "More about Motorcycle and Powersports Parts", "keyword_count": {"powersports parts": 5, "parts": 16, "motorcycle": 14}, "description_wc": 224, "description_text": "Amazon.com has a great selection of motorcycle parts and powersports parts. Find motorcycle parts for your bike\u2019s motor , body , braking system , or drive train . Discover replacement or performance exhaust systems , and replacement or upgraded lighting in our motorcycle parts selection. You can also find a wide variety of ATV and powersports parts, including replacement or performance items. Motorcycle helmets and protective gear are popular items. Flip-up, full face, open face and off-road motorcycle helmets are featured from the industry\u2019s top names. You can even find replacement shields for motorcycle helmets. Choose from a large selection of jackets, pants, gloves and jerseys for yourself and a friend, and choose many other new motorcycle parts and accessories to match your new gear. Need gift ideas or looking for bargains? There\u2019s a motorcycle parts gift guide and an outlet for motorcycle parts on the site. Battery chargers and helmets are very popular motorcycle parts gifts. We also host a wide selection of ATV and powersports parts that are easy to gift. Shop for motorcycle parts based on customer review, price, brand, or shipping option. You can also search by the best selling motorcycle parts and powersports parts. It\u2019s easy to find the right motorcycle parts when you shop for motorcycle parts and powersports parts on Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "parent_catid": 15, "keyword_density": {"powersports parts": "4.6", "parts": "7.3", "motorcycle": "6.4"}, "department_id": 15},
