{"department_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "nr_products": 253842, "catid": 165, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Lab-Scientific-Supplies/b/ref=sd_allcat_ind_lab/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=317970011", "text": "Lab & Scientific", "description_title": "About Lab Equipment", "keyword_count": {"lab equipment": 4, "equipment": 7, "lab": 17}, "description_wc": 269, "description_text": "Lab Equipment includes a wide variety of laboratory supplies such as meters, microscopes, and purification systems that are used to facilitate scientific and educational processes. Researchers, educators, and hobbyists use lab equipment such as lab furnaces, microscopes, shakers, hot plates, and stirrers to assist in testing, measuring, inspecting, and data gathering. Microscopes, used to enhance the resolution of an object or image, are commonly used lab equipment, found in many biology, chemistry, and learning labs. Other laboratory equipment, such as furnaces, are used for heating applications that require a range of high temperatures. They heat to high temperatures evenly and maintain consistent temperatures, while providing an environment free of undesirable contaminants and moisture. Autoclaves are also commonly used laboratory supplies that assist in sterilization applications. Additional lab supplies include desiccators, which are seal-able enclosures used to protect contents from atmospheric moisture. A centrifuge is used to spin fluids of different densities to separate various parts, commonly blood and DNA samples. Laboratory equipment, such as lab baths and accessories, are used to assist with common lab operations. An electrophoresis apparatus is designed to run multiple groups of student samples at the same time. Lab supplies can be made from a wide variety of material types, selected for their application abilities such as temperature, water, or chemical resistance. Some lab supplies are designed to meet specific health, safety, and environmental standards. Lab equipment commonly operates with electrical or battery-powered sources, and may come with a warranty. Laboratory equipment is widely used in education, lab research, biology, metallurgy, engineering, chemistry, manufacturing, and in the medical, forensic science, and veterinary industries.", "parent_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "parent_catid": 15, "keyword_density": {"lab equipment": "3.0", "equipment": "2.6", "lab": "6.3"}, "department_id": 15},
{"department_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "nr_products": 106722, "catid": 166, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/b/ref=sd_allcat_ind_jan/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=317971011", "text": "Janitorial", "description_title": "Janitorial Supplies", "keyword_count": {"supplies": 7, "janitorial supplies": 4, "janitorial": 7}, "description_wc": 243, "description_text": "Janitorial supplies are used to clean and maintain work and home environments. Commercial cleaning supplies and supplies used by homeowners include general cleaning supplies, equipment & fixtures, personal care items, and waste receptacles & liners. Janitorial supply products commonly include business essentials that are routinely re-stocked, such as all-purpose cleaners, bathroom cleaners, disinfectants, and disposal wipes. Janitor-housekeeping carts can have various material types, shelving, handle types, capacity, dimensions, colors, and the ability to hold trash bags or other waste-collection containers. Janitorial supply products include personal care items, such as facial tissues, hand soap, paper towels, sanitizers, and toilet paper. Janitorial supplies also include equipment & fixtures, such as baby-changing tables, carpet sweepers, floor polishers, hand dryers, paper towel dispensers, soap & lotion dispensers, toilet bowls, toilet paper dispensers, toilet seat dispensers, and urinals. Personal care items, such as facial tissues, hand soap, paper towels, sanitizers, and toilet paper are commonly used janitorial supplies. Janitorial supply products also include maintenance products, such as waste receptacles & liners. A trash can, recycling container, rollout trash can, and commercial trash bin are commonly used Rubbermaid Commercial Products. These Rubbermaid Commercial Products come in a variety of capacities, shapes, dimensions, materials, and colors. Smoking receptacles include an array of products used to contain cigarette waste. Smoking receptacles come in many capacities, types, dimensions, and material types. Janitorial supplies, used by professionals and in private applications, are necessary to maintain and clean work areas and provide personal care.", "parent_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "parent_catid": 15, "keyword_density": {"supplies": "2.9", "janitorial supplies": "3.3", "janitorial": "2.9"}, "department_id": 15},
{"department_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "nr_products": 638882, "catid": 167, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/b/ref=sd_allcat_ind_saf/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=318135011", "text": "Safety", "description_title": "Safety Supplies", "keyword_count": {"safety supplies": 3, "supplies": 4, "safety": 16}, "description_wc": 308, "description_text": "Safety supplies come in a variety of forms, including safety signs, personal protective equipment, and a wide array of other safety equipment. Safety supplies are used to mark an area, or to help protect persons from potentially hazardous conditions. Lock out tag out, sometimes referred to as lockout tagout (LO/TO), are safety procedures that use safety devices to help keep areas safe. Lock out tag out devices use color, warning labels or tags, and a physical barrier to temporarily prohibit machine operation or power activation, and reduce accidents, during maintenance or repair. Safety signs, or warning signs such as \u201cExit\u201d, \u201cDanger\u201d, or \u201cCaution\u201d, are used to display messaging and inform people of important circumstances. Personal protective equipment is anything from reflective chest coverings to hardhats, or Geiger counters & radiation detectors, used to detect the presence of ionizing radiation, to emergency response, first aid supplies, and eye wash units. Fire alarms and fire extinguishers are also used in safety. Additional safety products include: gloves, safety glasses, ear protection, hardhats, coveralls, fire-resistant clothing, rainwater & chemical splash apparel, and lab coats. Hazardous storage cabinets, and hazardous storage cans are safety equipment. Glove options include; cleanroom gloves, controlled environment gloves, cryogenic gloves, cut-resistant gloves, disposable gloves, and work gloves. Flags are a type of safety sign that come in a variety of colors, shapes, dimensions, and may have a magnetic, quick disconnect, or threaded hex base type. Flags can also come with reflective markings and lighting. Floor markers come in various types of adhesive tape, colors, markings (such as stripes, arrows, or words), and widths that can be used to mark an area. Safety mirrors are used as personal protective equipment. Safety supplies are used in construction sites, work sites, high-traffic areas, and in home applications. Safety equipment can meet various safety standards.", "parent_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "parent_catid": 15, "keyword_density": {"safety supplies": "2.0", "supplies": "1.3", "safety": "5.3"}, "department_id": 15},
{"department_text": "Movies, Music & Games", "nr_products": 23888, "catid": 168, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_11091801_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A11091801%2Cn%3A%2111965861%2Cn%3A11971241&bbn=11965861&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833355&rnid=11965861", "text": "Guitars", "description_title": "Guitars from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/musical-instruments-accessories-sound-recording/b/ref=sd_allcat_mi/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=11091801", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "guitars": 9}, "description_wc": 378, "description_text": "There\u2019s nothing like new gear to help you get excited about making music. Guitars that want to be picked up and played will motivate you to learn licks faster, write riffs better, and become a more creative musician. If you\u2019re fingering your first chords, or recording your follow up album, your guitars and amps should inspire you to practice and play at your best. From dreadnoughts to parlors, you\u2019ll find acoustic guitars in a huge variety of styles at Amazon.com. We carry popular brands like Martin, Taylor, and Takamine, so no matter what look and feel you\u2019re going for, there\u2019s an acoustic to suit your style. Our product filters can help you track down the perfect instrument. Browse guitars by brand, layout, and even top, back, or neck woods. For warm, folky sounds, many players prefer mahogany, while maple has a brighter, punchy tone. From Chuck Berry to Jack white, electric guitar has been the backbone of rock and roll for decades. Legendary guitars like the Gibson Les Paul and Fender Stratocaster have appeared on countless #1 records, and remain a popular choice today. The variety of options for electric guitars is practically endless. Humbuckers, single coils, Floyd Rose tremolos, and dozens of other features mean there\u2019s an instrument fit for every player. We make it easy to find guitars you\u2019re interested in. Choose the brands, features, and colors you\u2019re interested in, and we\u2019ll show you guitars that match your criteria. All the amplifiers and accessories you need to get the most out of your tone are available at Amazon.com. Our range of amp selection, from 5-watt practice amps and all-tube amps to 100-watt full stacks and everything in between, will have you strumming and shredding to your heart\u2019s content. Whether you\u2019re after a gritty, British tone, or a clean and sparkly American shimmer, we\u2019ve got amps from popular brands like Marshall, Vox, and Fender to help you find the perfect sound. For new guitar players and old pros alike, the excitement of trying out new gear can motivate you creatively and technically. Explore your tone, style, and imagination with guitars and guitar accessories that make you want to grow as a player.", "parent_text": "Musical Instruments", "parent_catid": 82, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.5", "guitars": "2.4"}, "department_id": 8},
