{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 746365, "catid": 183, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_502394_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A502394%2Cn%3A172435&bbn=502394&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833357&rnid=502394", "text": "Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Accessories for Camera and Video", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Camera-Photo-Film-Canon-Sony/b/ref=sd_allcat_p/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=502394", "keyword_count": {"camera": 1, "video": 2, "accessories": 1}, "description_wc": 176, "description_text": "Amazon.com carries accessories to meet the needs of every level of photographer and videographer, from basic point and shoot users to professional level shooters. From bags to tripods, flashes to battery chargers, there is an accessory to fit every demand. Need to protect that expensive DSLR during that family vacation on the lake? Check out our selection of waterproof shells and capture all the fun on the water without worry. Want to take your photos and videos to the next level? Amazons wide range of lighting, tripods, microphones and studio software can get you the professional results you are looking for. When it comes to ways to tote your gear, our selection of slings, backpacks, model specific cases and messenger-style bags offer every level of protection and organization. Whatever the accessory, including rain protection, filters, remotes, light boxes and light meters, Amazon.com has the brands, selection and prices every shutterbug wants. Need help finding the right accessory for your camera? Our featured accessory categories make it easy to find the item you are looking for.", "parent_text": "Camera, Photo & Video", "parent_catid": 89, "keyword_density": {"camera": "0.6", "video": "1.1", "accessories": "0.6"}, "department_id": 9},
