{"nr_products": 445, "catid": 220, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_5088769011_nr_n_31?rh=n%3A4991425011%2Cn%3A%214991426011%2Cn%3A5088769011%2Cn%3A5263624011&bbn=5088769011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833382&rnid=5088769011", "text": "Wardrobe Items", "description_wc": 0, "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Entertainment-Collectibles/b/ref=sd_allcat_entcol/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=5088769011", "parent_text": "Entertainment Collectibles", "parent_catid": 83, "department_text": "Movies, Music & Games", "department_id": 8},
{"department_text": "Movies, Music & Games", "nr_products": 15936, "catid": 221, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_468642_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A468642%2Cn%3A%2111846801%2Cn%3A14210751&bbn=11846801&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833356&rnid=11846801", "text": "PlayStation 3", "description_title": "PlayStation 3 from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/computer-video-games-hardware-accessories/b/ref=sd_allcat_cvg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=468642", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "playstation 3": 8, "3": 11}, "description_wc": 342, "description_text": "The Sony PlayStation 3 is one of the most advanced gaming consoles ever produced. Cutting edge 3D graphics, 5.1 surround digital audio, fully integrated wireless networking, and a dozen other features make it a popular choice among gamers. The PlayStation 3 can do more than just play video games, too. With a Blu-Ray player and hard disk drives up to 500GB, this console is a complete home entertainment unit, capable of playing HD movies, streaming media content from your home computer, and even browsing the internet. At Amazon.com, we offer a complete line of PlayStation 3 consoles, games, and accessories to satisfy gamers, movie watchers, and media streamers alike. You\u2019ll find bestselling PlayStation 3 classics, new releases, and hard to find titles from popular developers like AcTiVision, Ubisoft, and Square Enix across all genres, from FPS to RPGs. To find PlayStation 3 games that you\u2019re interested in, you can use our fast and easy product filters. Choose the developers, genres, ESRB ratings, and release dates you want to browse, and we\u2019ll automatically create a list of games that meet your criteria. If you\u2019re looking to pick up accessories and add-ons for your PS3, you can browse our selection of PlayStation 3 controllers, keyboards, remotes, and more. The original Sony Dualshock controller is a time tested and well-loved peripheral. You\u2019ll find Dualshock and Sixaxis controllers in a wide variety of colors, including brilliant white, satin reds and blues, and even metallic silver and gold. If you\u2019re shopping for your first PlayStation 3, you\u2019ll find a wide selection of consoles to choose from, including Slim models with hard drive space ranging from 160 to 500GB. Many new games are downloadable, so larger hard drives are a must-have for avid gamers. The Sony PlayStation 3 is more than a simple gaming console. The PS3 is an all-in-one entertainment hub for games, movies, and more. Amazon.com carries the consoles, games, and accessories you need to enjoy one of the most popular gaming consoles.", "parent_text": "Video Games", "parent_catid": 84, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.6", "playstation 3": "4.7", "3": "3.2"}, "department_id": 8},
{"department_text": "Movies, Music & Games", "nr_products": 2230, "catid": 222, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_468642_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A468642%2Cn%3A%2111846801%2Cn%3A6469269011&bbn=11846801&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833356&rnid=11846801", "text": "Xbox One", "description_title": "Xbox One from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/computer-video-games-hardware-accessories/b/ref=sd_allcat_cvg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=468642", "keyword_count": {"xbox": 12, "amazoncom": 2, "xbox one": 10, "one": 12}, "description_wc": 356, "description_text": "Microsoft\u2019s Xbox One is the latest offering in the Xbox family of gaming and entertainment consoles. Designed to be an all in one entertainment system, the Xbox One combines cutting edge gaming, media streaming, internet connectivity, and television integration. At Amazon.com, we offer a variety of Xbox One consoles, games, and accessories. Featuring an 8 core AMD processor with a 12 core GPU, 8 gb of RAM, and 500 gb of storage space, the Xbox One is a formidable machine. Fully integrated wireless internet makes it easier than ever to connect to Xbox Live, and play games online with your friends all over the world. The Xbox One can also connect with your television service, and offers an enhanced programming guide, as well as real time updates to fantasy sports leagues, right as the action is happening. The initial offering of Xbox One games includes franchise favorites, as well as a selection of new properties sure to get gamers excited. The latest iteration of the Call of Duty series promises an even more realistic and detailed warfare experience, with improvements to the graphics, gameplay, and online capabilities millions of gamers love. Sports fans are eagerly anticipating next generation releases from the Madden and NBA2K series. You can burn rubber and shave seconds off your lap time with Forza 5, which puts you behind the wheel of exotic super cars from around the world, and challenges you to stay cool while you push the limits of your vehicle on one of dozens of famous racetracks around the world. Other highly anticipated releases include Titan Fall, The Division, Ryse, Destiny, Watch Dogs, Final Fantasy XV, andand Dead Island 3, which promises even more zombie smashing mayhem. We also offer a full range of Xbox One accessories, including controllers, headsets, and protective skins. Shopping online at Amazon.com makes it easy to find the Xbox One accessories you need, and our selection is growing all the time. The Xbox One sets a new standard in home entertainment consoles. From cutting edge gaming, to steaming movies and music, the Xbox One is the only piece of hardware you\u2019ll need.", "parent_text": "Video Games", "parent_catid": 84, "keyword_density": {"one": "3.4", "amazoncom": "0.6", "xbox one": "5.6", "xbox": "3.4"}, "department_id": 8},
{"department_text": "Movies, Music & Games", "nr_products": 22632, "catid": 223, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_468642_nr_n_3?rh=n%3A468642%2Cn%3A%2111846801%2Cn%3A14220161&bbn=11846801&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833356&rnid=11846801", "text": "Xbox 360", "description_title": "Xbox 360 Games from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/computer-video-games-hardware-accessories/b/ref=sd_allcat_cvg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=468642", "keyword_count": {"xbox 360": 11, "amazoncom": 2, "xbox 360 games": 9, "xbox": 12}, "description_wc": 288, "description_text": "Test your mettle against close friends and fierce rivals with Microsoft\u2019s remarkable advanced gaming platform and Xbox 360 games. Amazon.com is your online source for the best deals on Xbox 360 games and accessories, along with Xbox LIVE time and Microsoft Points that will keep you at the front lines of gaming and ahead of the competition. Take the first leap toward building your system at the Consoles Store before you build your collection of Xbox 360 games. You\u2019ll find dozens of Xbox 360 consoles sold individually, bundled with Kinect , in various colors, and equipped with different hard drive capacities, so you can match your gaming platform to your personality and Xbox 360 games. If you\u2019re looking to enhance your existing console and how you interact with your Xbox 360 games, peek in the Accessories Store, where you\u2019ll find everything you need to jumpstart the action. Accessory kits, headsets, controllers, fitness accessories, skins, faceplates, batteries, and purchasable networking points allow you to customize your console for a whole new level of gaming possibilities. These products will make the Xbox 360 your go-to device for gaming and media. We pride ourselves on delivering the best selection of Xbox 360 games, along with an expansive array of consoles and accessories. Find action, flying, racing, strategy, and adventure Xbox 360 games and browse Xbox 360 games by rating, genre, and release date to share the next must-have release with family, friends, coworkers, and other gamers in your life. With this Microsoft console, you\u2019ll experience the camaraderie of online gaming and exclusive Xbox 360 games you won\u2019t find anywhere else. Compare your progress with like-minded gamers with bundles and accessories from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Video Games", "parent_catid": 84, "keyword_density": {"xbox 360": "7.7", "xbox": "4.2", "amazoncom": "0.7", "xbox 360 games": "9.4"}, "department_id": 8},
{"department_text": "Movies, Music & Games", "nr_products": 14921, "catid": 224, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_468642_nr_n_4?rh=n%3A468642%2Cn%3A%2111846801%2Cn%3A14218901&bbn=11846801&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833356&rnid=11846801", "text": "Wii", "description_title": "Wii Games from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/computer-video-games-hardware-accessories/b/ref=sd_allcat_cvg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=468642", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 3, "wii games": 8, "wii": 15}, "description_wc": 273, "description_text": "New Wii games for everyone\u2019s favorite white console guarantee a good time for players of all levels of experience. When both newbies and experts find promise in the Wii\u2019s unique platform and the vast selection of innovative Wii games, you know you\u2019ve stumbled onto a gem among systems. Whether you\u2019re in the market for new Wii games or the console itself, Amazon.com offers all the gadgets, gizmos, and info you need to get moving with your own Wii Remote. While the Wii\u2019s bright white design may have first caught the world\u2019s attention, you\u2019ll also find striking black and red versions via the Console Guide . Amazon.com carries a variety of Wii bundles that consolidate your shopping list into one convenient package, so you can spend less time online and more time playing Wii games. Looking for your very own home fitness system? Wii Fitness Accessories include Wii Fit wrist straps, belts, boxing gloves, push-up bars, and aerobic steps and sporty Wii games to go with them. These products will get your heart pumping and your mind racing by turning your Wii into a virtual fitness center. Take an hour or two from your day to delve into exhilarating Wii games. Groove out with Just Dance 4 , follow the hobbits in LEGO Lord of the Rings, and revisit your favorite plumbers in Super Mario Bros. We pride ourselves in bringing the newest Wii games and hardware to your computer and doorstep as quickly as possible. More than just a gaming system, the transformative Wii games and consoles at Amazon.com give new definition to having fun.", "parent_text": "Video Games", "parent_catid": 84, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "1.1", "wii games": "5.9", "wii": "5.5"}, "department_id": 8},
{"department_text": "Movies, Music & Games", "nr_products": 2281, "catid": 225, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_468642_nr_n_5?rh=n%3A468642%2Cn%3A%2111846801%2Cn%3A3075112011&bbn=11846801&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833356&rnid=11846801", "text": "Wii U", "description_title": "Wii U Games from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/computer-video-games-hardware-accessories/b/ref=sd_allcat_cvg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=468642", "keyword_count": {"u": 60, "wii u games": 6, "games": 11, "wii u": 10, "wii u games from amazoncom": 2}, "description_wc": 333, "description_text": "The next generation of Nintendo is finally here. You can welcome this new bundle of joy to your home with the long-awaited Wii U games from Amazon.com. The new touch-screen built within the controller allows for a whole new way to experience Nintendo games and interact with your surroundings. We have a wide variety of Wii U games to choose from. If there are Wii U games coming up that you have to have, many of our titles are available for pre-order, so whether you\u2019re buying Wii U games as a gift or for yourself, you can ensure you get your copy. When you hear about Mario Kart 8, or the new characters that have been announced for the upcoming Super Smash Brothers, you\u2019ll be glad we\u2019re offering you the option. The Wii U is already seeing a resurgence of some of the most popular Nintendo games. If you loved hurling plant-people at monsters before, the new installation of Pikmin, with better graphics and plenty of surprises could be a great choice for you. If you miss the long, sunny days spent grass-slashing and breaking pottery in a hunt for wild rupees, the high-definition remake of Zelda: The Windwaker could be the Wii U game for you. There are also many exciting Wii U games coming out from a variety of other developers. Activision\u2019s popular Call of Duty: Black Ops II offers everything you need to run through rough terrain, snipe enemies and deftly achieve demanding objectives. Since the Wii U is Nintendo\u2019s next generation gaming system, new games are coming out all the time, and you can find racing games, first-person shooters, fighting games and much more with fantastic graphics and touch-screen enhanced gameplay. Since the Wii U is so new, it has a lot to look forward to. You can experience all the best moments of this gaming system\u2019s life with the Wii U games from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Video Games", "parent_catid": 84, "keyword_density": {"games": "3.3", "wii u games": "5.4", "u": "18.0", "wii u": "6.0", "wii u games from amazoncom": "3.0"}, "department_id": 8},
