{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 1011, "catid": 240, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1266092011_nr_n_6?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A1266092011%2Cn%3A281056&bbn=1266092011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833358&rnid=1266092011", "text": "Home Theater Systems", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Home Theater from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Televisions-Video/b/ref=sd_allcat_tv/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=1266092011", "keyword_count": {"home": 11, "amazoncom": 2, "theater": 10, "home theater": 9}, "description_wc": 314, "description_text": "Home theater systems allow movie lovers to recreate the movie theater experience at home. Instead of standing in long lines to buy tickets, you can watch the latest films and television shows from the comfort of your living room. Whether you need a system for a small apartment or looking to outfit a large entertainment room, you'll find the best home theater system for you at Amazon.com. When putting together a home theater system, you want to use the very best components available. We have home theater speakers and other home entertainment accessories made by the top companies in the industry such as Sony, Samsung, Panasonic, and LG. Get complete systems that include a television, surround sound speakers, remote controls, and iPod or iPhone dock. If you already have a system, we offer a good selection of individual parts that allow you to buy only what you need as well as tools and supplies to help you maintain your system. The products you will find in our online store have the features you want in home theater systems such as HDMI ports, powerful wattage (from 50w to 1kW systems), multiple channels, Internet or satellite radio, and Smart TVs. Many of these home theater systems are Energy Star certified, so you save money on your energy bills. We even have wireless systems that make setting up a true surround sound experience a breeze. Whether you are buying home theater systems for yourself or as a gift to someone else, you'll find the equipment you want made by brands you know, love, and trust. No matter your budget, there are home theater systems available in the price range you're looking for. Fast shipping means your purchase will arrive at your front door right on time. For the best value and selection, choose Amazon.com as the place to shop for home theater systems.", "parent_text": "TV & Video", "parent_catid": 87, "keyword_density": {"home": "3.5", "amazoncom": "0.6", "theater": "3.2", "home theater": "5.8"}, "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 6, "catid": 241, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1266092011_nr_n_7?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A1266092011%2Cn%3A2632816011&bbn=1266092011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833358&rnid=1266092011", "text": "Installation Services", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "TV Installation from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Televisions-Video/b/ref=sd_allcat_tv/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=1266092011", "keyword_count": {"tv": 12, "tv installation": 5, "amazoncom": 2}, "description_wc": 311, "description_text": "Catch all your favorite shows and enjoy the freedom and break from wrestling with your television by connecting with local TV installation providers for quick and hassle-free setup. Whether you\u2019ve got a wall-mounted or on-stand television, Amazon.com wide selection of TV installation services will have your TV set up in no time. From basic to premium services, choose from a variety of options to have your electronics set up and displayed professionally. Including both the expert services and mount itself, all you need to do is provide the TV. With a simple click of the mouse, we will contact professional servicers on your behalf, who will in turn schedule a TV installation appointment with you based on the size and type of your television. Easily filter through services by brands, customer rating, price, and keyword for the best TV installation for your home, budget, and TV. Basic services will mount and install your TV, while more extensive services will take care of concealing wires in the wall or with wire moulding. You can even read service reviews from other customers like you right on the page to see how well they really hold up in real life. We also feature a variety of televisions, accessories, and extras to make your home theater even better. From large flat-screen TVs and sleek Blu-ray players to popular Roku streaming devices, projectors, and powerful speaker systems, it\u2019s easy to enhance any movie, soundtrack, or video game. And if you\u2019re interested in mounting your TV yourself, we offer several wall mounting kits and tools to keep you effective, empowered, and safe when you want to enjoy the satisfaction of a little DIY. Get your new TV up on the wall sooner with TV installation services from Amazon.com and you\u2019ll be sure to catch all your favorite shows.", "parent_text": "TV & Video", "parent_catid": 87, "keyword_density": {"tv": "3.9", "tv installation": "3.2", "amazoncom": "0.6"}, "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 32141, "catid": 242, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1266092011_nr_n_8?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A1266092011%2Cn%3A1286610011&bbn=1266092011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833358&rnid=1266092011", "text": "Projection Screens", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Projector Screens from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Televisions-Video/b/ref=sd_allcat_tv/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=1266092011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "projector": 8}, "description_wc": 313, "description_text": "Keep your employees from falling asleep by showing a vivid presentation on a high-quality projector screen. Watching home films or hit movies on a projector screen is also a wonderful way to bond with your family and friends. Choosing a projector screen might seem a bit intimidating, but Amazon.com works hard to make the entire process easy. You don't have to head to your local electronics store to find dependable brands like Epson, Mustang, and MGM. Whether you're looking for a modern HD projector, a traditional overhead projector, or a reliable LCD projector, we can help you find exactly what you need from the brands that you trust. There are many different supplies designed to enhance the experience you have with your video projection screen. A mount ensures that your projection screen remains in an upright position during use, while spare bulbs allow you to replace old ones when they need it and watch each movie in clear, vibrant color. We also carry cords to connect the projector screen to your laptop, making it easy to wow your boss or client with large graphics during your next business presentation. You don't have to be confined to your living room or conference hall when you use a projector screen. We have several different models that work well outside, allowing you to enjoy an exciting film as you lounge in the grass or wade across the pool. An outdoor screen also makes it easy for you to share memorable moments with a large group of people during a wedding, school function, or birthday party. You don't have to travel to the theater to enjoy watching crisp, colorful graphics expand across a large backdrop. A video projection screen makes an excellent addition to any family room or conference area, and Amazon.com carries a variety of brands and models for all budgets.", "parent_text": "TV & Video", "parent_catid": 87, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.6", "projector": "2.6"}, "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 16254, "catid": 243, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1266092011_nr_n_9?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A1266092011%2Cn%3A300334&bbn=1266092011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833358&rnid=1266092011", "text": "Projectors", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Projectors from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Televisions-Video/b/ref=sd_allcat_tv/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=1266092011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 1, "projectors": 3}, "description_wc": 324, "description_text": "Cinephiles will love to see their favorite film in a format that gives its wide-screen spectacle justice with one of these video projectors. When your television isn't big enough, purchasing a projector will give you the opportunity to watch a movie or show in high definition on your wall. You can even bring it out to your backyard for a bit of summertime movie watching. As you search through the various projector reviews, you'll see brand names like Epson, Sony, and BenO offering projection equipment that is both moderately priced and ready to provide you with the high-definition viewing you crave. Set it up in your living room, dim the lights and splash the sights of your favorite show, sporting event, or movie across your wall. Choose a projector that not only works in the dark, but can also be used in some low lighting situations. Of course, some movie fans can bring the movie theater experience anywhere in their home. Remodel your bonus room into your own theater, complete with movie seats, a projector and a screen to get the best out of your viewing experience. Connect your cable box, streaming device, or video game system to your projector and entertain yourself with a large viewing experience in the comfort of your own home. Some of the best projectors can also be used outside. If you want to have a nighttime barbecue while replicating the drive-in experience, use a projector to play one of your favorite movies for your friends and family. It's a fun way to experience your cinematic treats while enjoying the outdoors. At Amazon.com, you'll find plenty of projectors of all stripes, so you can choose the right one for your home entertainment needs. With shipping options that'll bring your projector to you within a few days, you're only a few clicks from taking your movie viewing to the next level.", "parent_text": "TV & Video", "parent_catid": 87, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.3", "projectors": "0.9"}, "department_id": 9},
