USB port so you can transfer files from your computer to watch or listen to on your television. For the tech-savvy household, media players are a way to consolidate your devices while adding to your library of shows to watch and music to listen to. Whichever media player you're looking for, Amazon.com will have one shipped to you in a matter of days. Find the right one for your budget, space, and needs and you'll be ready to expand your media library with a single device. Stream movies, music or television shows to your TV with one of these players.", "parent_text": "TV & Video", "parent_catid": 87, "keyword_density": {"media": "3.8", "amazoncom": "0.3", "media players": "3.8", "players": "2.2"}, "department_id": 9},
{"nr_products": 281897, "catid": 246, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1266092011_nr_n_12?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A1266092011%2Cn%3A3230976011&bbn=1266092011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833358&rnid=1266092011", "text": "Television Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_wc": 0, "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Televisions-Video/b/ref=sd_allcat_tv/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=1266092011", "parent_text": "TV & Video", "parent_catid": 87, "department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 4662, "catid": 247, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1266092011_nr_n_13?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A1266092011%2Cn%3A172659&bbn=1266092011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833358&rnid=1266092011", "text": "Televisions", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "TVs from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Televisions-Video/b/ref=sd_allcat_tv/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=1266092011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "tvs": 4}, "description_wc": 352, "description_text": "The TV is the centerpiece of your home's entertainment center. As a place to gather with friend or family to watch the news, sports, a favorite television series, or blockbuster movie, you're going to want a TV with optimum sound and picture quality. When you come home from a long day at work, sitting in front of the television and watching your favorite program is a common way to end your day. TVs from all brands, including Samsung, VIZIO, and Toshiba, offer you the basics, with outputs for your cable or satellite subscription, as well as options for all of your gaming needs. It'll be a cinch to watch the news or your favorite sitcom from the comfort of your own couch. Of course, if you're a sports fan, you're going to want the best TV to watch your favorite games. Some of the flat-screen TVs offer an experience that'll make you feel like you're at your team's stadium. The high-definition TVs bring a crystal clear screen and optimal sound so you can catch every strike out or kick off. Hook it up with your streaming device and you can have entire seasons of NBA or MLB action in HD quality. Read the TV reviews on Amazon.com to discover the best set for your needs. If you're looking for a device with premium picture and sound, check out some of the LED or LCD sets to really take your viewing to the next level. Not only will it make every pixel count, these LED or LCD screens go great with your digital devices, such as your Blu-Ray player. Plug in that player and sit in awe as your favorite movie plays out as it was meant to be seen in stunning high definition. When you're looking for a new TV at a great price and the convenience of shipment right to your door, Amazon.com is the place for you. You'll find a wide array of TVs that will not only fit your needs, but your budget as well.", "parent_text": "TV & Video", "parent_catid": 87, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.6", "tvs": "1.1"}, "department_id": 9},
