{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 1011, "catid": 252, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_667846011_nr_n_3?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A667846011%2Cn%3A281056&bbn=667846011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833358&rnid=667846011", "text": "Home Theater Systems", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Home Theater from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Home-Audio-Electronics/b/ref=sd_allcat_hat/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=667846011", "keyword_count": {"home": 11, "amazoncom": 2, "theater": 10, "home theater": 9}, "description_wc": 314, "description_text": "Home theater systems allow movie lovers to recreate the movie theater experience at home. Instead of standing in long lines to buy tickets, you can watch the latest films and television shows from the comfort of your living room. Whether you need a system for a small apartment or looking to outfit a large entertainment room, you'll find the best home theater system for you at Amazon.com. When putting together a home theater system, you want to use the very best components available. We have home theater speakers and other home entertainment accessories made by the top companies in the industry such as Sony, Samsung, Panasonic, and LG. Get complete systems that include a television, surround sound speakers, remote controls, and iPod or iPhone dock. If you already have a system, we offer a good selection of individual parts that allow you to buy only what you need as well as tools and supplies to help you maintain your system. The products you will find in our online store have the features you want in home theater systems such as HDMI ports, powerful wattage (from 50w to 1kW systems), multiple channels, Internet or satellite radio, and Smart TVs. Many of these home theater systems are Energy Star certified, so you save money on your energy bills. We even have wireless systems that make setting up a true surround sound experience a breeze. Whether you are buying home theater systems for yourself or as a gift to someone else, you'll find the equipment you want made by brands you know, love, and trust. No matter your budget, there are home theater systems available in the price range you're looking for. Fast shipping means your purchase will arrive at your front door right on time. For the best value and selection, choose Amazon.com as the place to shop for home theater systems.", "parent_text": "Home Audio & Theater", "parent_catid": 88, "keyword_density": {"home": "3.5", "amazoncom": "0.6", "theater": "3.2", "home theater": "5.8"}, "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 369, "catid": 253, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_667846011_nr_n_4?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A667846011%2Cn%3A322215011&bbn=667846011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833358&rnid=667846011", "text": "Multiroom Digital Music Systems", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Music Streaming from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Home-Audio-Electronics/b/ref=sd_allcat_hat/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=667846011", "keyword_count": {"streaming": 7, "music streaming": 6, "music": 12, "amazoncom": 1}, "description_wc": 322, "description_text": "When you are shopping for a multiroom music system, what music streaming device you choose makes a large impact on the quality of your listening experience. Whether you want a wireless model, Bluetooth capabilities, or a music-streaming player small enough to carry with you, you can use our site's convenient search and filter options to browse through our catalog and find a device that fits your needs and your budget. We have a variety of music streaming players that have built-in Wi-Fi, giving you the freedom to take your music with you wherever there is a wireless Internet connection. We also have a wide selection of Bluetooth-enabled devices, from full stereo systems to compact devices designed for areas with limited space. Whether you are looking for a weather-resistant outdoor speaker system, a video and music streaming box that includes a remote and keyboard, or an all-in-one player with integrated speakers that lets you play different tracks in different rooms of your home, you can browse, search, and select music streaming equipment from top brands like Roku, Apple, Sonos, Netgear, Sling Media, and more. We also offer media streaming devices, including projectors and tuners that feature a variety of convenient functions, including alarms, AM/FM and HD radio capabilities, and LCD displays. If you are looking for equipment that has modern functionality but vintage-appeal, we have options featuring classic finishes designed to mimic the wood construction of old-school music players. Your personality and style should be reflected in your music-streaming player, which gives you all of the modern conveniences of digital music. Whether you want a device for personal listening or want to play music through your entire house, you can shop for the audiophile in your life, all from the comfort of your own home. Amazon.com has what you need to bring music to every area in your home and yard.", "parent_text": "Home Audio & Theater", "parent_catid": 88, "keyword_density": {"streaming": "2.2", "music streaming": "3.7", "music": "3.7", "amazoncom": "0.3"}, "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 1933, "catid": 254, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_667846011_nr_n_5?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A667846011%2Cn%3A172521&bbn=667846011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833358&rnid=667846011", "text": "Portable DVD Players", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Portable DVD Players from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Home-Audio-Electronics/b/ref=sd_allcat_hat/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=667846011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 1, "portable dvd players": 4, "portable dvd": 8}, "description_wc": 322, "description_text": "Whether you travel often for work or are going on a trip for fun, bring a portable DVD player with you to pass the time while you're on a plane or a train. Bring your favorite movies along with you and watch them by yourself or with a friend. These portable DVD players come in a compact size that can fit nicely in your book bag or suitcase. When searching for the best portable DVD player, you'll find devices from Sony, Sylvania, and Phillips that come with screens anywhere from seven to nine inches in size. The best of these portable DVD players feature a high definition screen that'll bring out a high-quality picture from your disc. With your portable DVD player, you can watch you movie on your lap or at a desk. While at home, the player is small enough to fit nicely on your desk or shelf. Some of the devices even have a USB port so you can transfer music or video files onto the player from your computer. You'll also find portable DVD players with a swivel design that lets you move the device's screen to face you. It's great for when you want to view a movie without anyone else seeing what you're watching. There's also a jack on the side so you can plug in your headphones and view your movie or TV show without bothering those around you. Some portable DVD players even have audio options, allowing you to customize the sound settings on your device. After you've found the right portable DVD player for you, make your order right here on Amazon.com. You'll find plenty of shipping options that'll get your device to your home within a few days. Once you have it, you'll be set to entertain yourself on that long flight or train ride for work or play.", "parent_text": "Home Audio & Theater", "parent_catid": 88, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.3", "portable dvd players": "3.7", "portable dvd": "5.0"}, "department_id": 9},
{"nr_products": 4736, "catid": 255, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_667846011_nr_n_6?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A667846011%2Cn%3A3236445011&bbn=667846011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833358&rnid=667846011", "text": "Radios", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_wc": 0, "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Home-Audio-Electronics/b/ref=sd_allcat_hat/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=667846011", "parent_text": "Home Audio & Theater", "parent_catid": 88, "department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "department_id": 9},
