{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 544, "catid": 257, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_667846011_nr_n_8?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A667846011%2Cn%3A11973981&bbn=667846011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833358&rnid=667846011", "text": "Turntable Cartridges & Needles", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Turntable Cartridges from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Home-Audio-Electronics/b/ref=sd_allcat_hat/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=667846011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "cartridges": 9, "turntable": 11, "turntable cartridges": 5}, "description_wc": 321, "description_text": "Whether you are getting ready for a stellar DJ performance or a private party at home with friends, you will need a good turntable cartridge to ensure you get the best quality music from your audio equipment. Cartridges hold the needle in a traditional turntable and the magnet in more modern versions, transmitting sound to your speakers. High-quality turntable cartridges may or may not include needles or magnets. The stylus on modern magnet-driven turntables allows for high-quality sound with less concern about scratching potentially rare vinyl albums. Many DJs prefer the sound of more traditional turntable cartridges, and not all cartridges will work on all turntable systems. Amazon.com carries a wide selection of available cartridges from companies such as Audio Technica, Panasonic, and Shure so that you can easily find the right piece for your needs. The tone arm mount is also a major consideration when replacing turntable cartridges. Modern systems typically have a half-inch mount, which has become standard in the industry. Longer mounts may not work with specific turntables, and incorrect cartridges could lead to potential damage. Choosing the right arm mount length can help minimize the risks to your records. Force gauges and other accessories can also help prevent damage from regular turntable use. Modern features have made turntable cartridges far more advanced than earlier versions. Styluses have begun to replace needles, and special guards protect your records from damage. Headshell wires are often easily replaced using only a small screwdriver, allowing you to get the most out of your cartridge and ensure that it lasts for some time with regular maintenance. Many units are designed to work with specific equipment, creating powerful sounds when employed in combination with their sister parts. Amazon.com allows you to shop for turntable cartridges and other musical accessories or instruments from the comfort of your own home. Save both time and money with inexpensive and fast shipping options.", "parent_text": "Home Audio & Theater", "parent_catid": 88, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.6", "cartridges": "2.8", "turntable": "3.4", "turntable cartridges": "3.1"}, "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 8317, "catid": 258, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_502394_nr_n_4?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A502394%2Cn%3A7161070011&bbn=502394&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833357&rnid=502394", "text": "Film Photography", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Film Photography Equipment from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Camera-Photo-Film-Canon-Sony/b/ref=sd_allcat_p/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=502394", "keyword_count": {"film photography": 7, "equipment": 7, "amazoncom": 2, "film photography equipment from amazoncom": 1, "film photography equipment": 6, "film": 18}, "description_wc": 369, "description_text": "If you miss the tactile pleasure and art of taking physical photos, developed commercially or in your own private darkroom, or you\u2019d like to be able to pass a tangible print between family and friends, the film photography equipment from Amazon.com can help you capture precious moments on real film. From instant photo films to analog cameras, we have a wide variety of film photography equipment to choose from. Our film cameras come in a selection of formats, sizes, designs, and more. Find tidy point-and-shoot film cameras, waterproof cameras you can use in the rain, and even high-quality SLR cameras for crystal clear landscapes, portraits, family pictures, and many other shots. If you\u2019re planning a party, barbecue, wedding reception, or other big event, we also offer disposable cameras to place around tables, counters, and more to inspire guests to take fun commemorative pictures of the big day. Once you\u2019ve picked out your camera, we also have a great selection of film among our camera and film photography equipment. You can find all of the standard sizes of film to fit any camera, including 35mm and instant film. Instant film cameras, including Fujifilm Instax and Polaroid models, can be incredibly fun for parties or for kids. Take a picture, wait a few minutes for it to develop, and you can have the fun, immediate gratification of a physical photo. You can find packs of multiple film rolls so you can always have enough to record trips, parties, family visits, and more. We even carry film from some of the most popular film photography equipment brands, including Fuji, Kodak, Impossible, and many others. You can also find a great selection of darkroom equipment for film photography as well. Slide viewers are extremely convenient ways to look at your negatives in detail without having to develop them first. We carry many smaller models with 2 x 2-inch displays that you can carry around wherever you go to show negatives to clients, family members, and more. We also carry many developing solutions, red bulbs, and other crucial film photography equipment to set up your very own darkroom. You can find quality film photography equipment at Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Camera, Photo & Video", "parent_catid": 89, "keyword_density": {"film photography": "3.8", "equipment": "1.9", "amazoncom": "0.5", "film photography equipment from amazoncom": "1.4", "film photography equipment": "4.9", "film": "4.9"}, "department_id": 9},
