{"department_text": "Sports & Outdoors", "nr_products": 7047, "catid": 385, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_3403201_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A3375251%2Cn%3A%213375301%2Cn%3A3403201%2Cn%3A1265458011&bbn=3403201&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833258&rnid=3403201", "text": "Bikes", "description_title": "Bikes from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/cycling-bikes-bicycles-bike-sale/b/ref=sd_allcat_bike/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=3403201", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "bikes": 6}, "description_wc": 293, "description_text": "Riding a bike is a great way to relieve stress and take a little time to yourself. Flying through the parks, the woods, and your neighborhood in the fresh air can be a wonderful escape from your daily stresses and worries. Amazon.com offers a wide variety of bikes for you to choose from to help you enjoy the outdoors even more. For the urban dwellers, we have a variety of general-use models built to endure city streets, dirt paths in the park, and craggy suburban sidewalks. Our hybrid bikes are ideal for all common terrain, and many even come with bike racks attached so you can carry your bags with you without having to wear a sweaty backpack. Comfort bikes are built with cushioned saddles and are great for casual bicycle riders. We also have a variety of purpose-built bicycles for all sorts of sports, hobbies, and functions. Mountain bikes usually come with bigger tires with a lot of traction so they won\u2019t slip or tumble when you\u2019re cycling through a forest path. They can also come with shock absorbers for more treacherous terrain. BMX bikes are smaller and lighter so you can jump, grind, and flip to your heart\u2019s content. We even have unicycles for hobbyists looking for a challenge. Our specialty bicycles come in a variety for many applications. Recumbent bikes offer an alternative riding position for those that need a more ergonomic ride. Electric bicycles are idea for those who want to commute to work with a little added boost and efficiency. Electric models have a battery-powered motor that can assist with pedaling and add a few miles-per-hour to your pedaling speed. Find the right bike to fit your needs from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Cycling", "parent_catid": 151, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.7", "bikes": "2.0"}, "department_id": 14},
