{"department_text": "Sports & Outdoors", "nr_products": 4012, "catid": 387, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_3403201_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A3375251%2Cn%3A%213375301%2Cn%3A3403201%2Cn%3A2346793011&bbn=3403201&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833258&rnid=3403201", "text": "Kids' Bikes & Accessories", "description_title": "Balance Bikes from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/cycling-bikes-bicycles-bike-sale/b/ref=sd_allcat_bike/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=3403201", "keyword_count": {"balance": 8, "amazoncom": 2, "bikes": 11, "balance bikes from amazoncom": 1, "balance bikes": 6}, "description_wc": 287, "description_text": "Encourage early development of motor skills like balance, direction, and movement with balance bikes and watch your little tyke take off in a cloud of dust. From no-pedal balance bikes to attachable bike trainers to grownup mountain bikes, Amazon.com\u2019s large collection of kids\u2019 bikes and accessories will have everything you need from the first ride. Shop and filter through thousands of kids\u2019 bikes by age, type, brand, price, and more for the most appropriate model for your kid. Great for young children, balance bikes help them learn balance and steering. Without any pedals, gears, chains, or training wheels, balance bikes are available in wood and metal and a variety of different colors, themes, sizes, and more for different tastes and personalities. Size and shape depends on the age and height of your child so be sure to take measurements before purchase for a comfortable and exhilarating ride. Or if they aren\u2019t ready for their own, you can attach a long push handle to the back to help protect and guide your child. We also carry a variety of training bikes for kids of all ages and levels if your child is ready to leave balance bikes behind and get a \u201cbig kid\u201d one. From the classic tricycles to pink Barbie beginner models with removable training wheels to blue youth mountain bikes, find the perfect seat for your child as they grow up. Keep them protected with safety gear like helmets and pads to cushions the falls and trips that are bound to happen with any kind of learning. Savor childhood with balance bikes from Amazon.com; they say you never forget how to ride a bike and they\u2019ll never forget you teaching them well.", "parent_text": "Cycling", "parent_catid": 151, "keyword_density": {"bikes": "3.8", "amazoncom": "0.7", "balance": "2.8", "balance bikes from amazoncom": "1.4", "balance bikes": "4.2"}, "department_id": 14},
