{"department_text": "Sports & Outdoors", "nr_products": 14863, "catid": 389, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_3403201_nr_n_4?rh=n%3A3375251%2Cn%3A%213375301%2Cn%3A3403201%2Cn%3A6389156011&bbn=3403201&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833258&rnid=3403201", "text": "Wheels & Accessories", "description_title": "Bicycle Wheels from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/cycling-bikes-bicycles-bike-sale/b/ref=sd_allcat_bike/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=3403201", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 1, "wheels": 13, "bicycle wheels": 9}, "description_wc": 303, "description_text": "Your bicycle wheels have a significant effect on the overall ride quality, stiffness, and comfort of your bike. From cruiser wheels built for relaxing to racing wheels designed to squeeze every ounce of efficiency and speed out of your bike, there\u2019s a set of wheels for every riding style. For casual riders, relatively lightweight, slightly stiff aluminum bicycle wheels will provide a good balance of affordability, comfort, and performance. While aluminum is more rigid and slightly less forgiving than steel, it\u2019s much lighter, which can reduce pedaling effort. Supple, wider profile bicycle wheels and tires provide a more forgiving, supple ride. While stiffness is good for speed and handling, your bike ride will be more comfortable and relaxing with more forgiving bicycle wheels and tires. Regular commuters and riders who like to get where they\u2019re going quickly and confidently might prefer narrower, stiffer bicycle wheels that increase performance because they\u2019re supple enough to absorb the impact from an accidental bump or pothole now and again. Purpose-built road bikes typically have a lower riding position, which encourages a more powerful posture and leg position. Bicycle wheels designed to transfer that power effectively to the road can help you become faster and more confident on the road. Road racing, triathlon, and sprint racing bicycle wheels are extra stiff, aerodynamic, and made from materials like carbon fiber for maximum speed and handling. In a competition, fractions of a second count, so it\u2019s important to get as much performance as possible from your wheels and tires. At Amazon.com, you\u2019ll find high performance bicycle wheels from popular brands like Shimano, Zipp, and Mavic. Cruise to the beach on a sunny Sunday or shave another second off your sprint time with bicycle wheels that are right for your riding style and equipment.", "parent_text": "Cycling", "parent_catid": 151, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.3", "wheels": "4.3", "bicycle wheels": "5.9"}, "department_id": 14},
