{"department_text": "Sports & Outdoors", "nr_products": 133663, "catid": 395, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_3421331_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A3375251%2Cn%3A%213375301%2Cn%3A3421331%2Cn%3A3397331&bbn=3421331&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833257&rnid=3421331", "text": "Boating", "description_title": "Boating Supplies from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Boating-Water-Sports-Outdoors/b/ref=sd_allcat_btwt/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=3421331", "keyword_count": {"boating supplies": 7}, "description_wc": 317, "description_text": "Make sure you\u2019re ready to head out on the water whenever the weather is right by stocking up on boating supplies to keep you fishing, skiing, and sailing all year long. To keep your boat running smoothly and efficiently all season long, we offer a range of engine maintenance and repair parts for inboard and outboard engines. It\u2019s important to have backup engine components and other crucial boating supplies on board whenever you cast off. For smaller fishing boats, simple parts like fuel filters and impellers can be replaced quickly and easily with a few simple tools. Keep spare boating supplies for engine work, such as fuel lines and oil filters handy, so you\u2019re ready to take advantage of every sunny weekend. Safety and operational equipment are important boating supplies for large and small vessels alike. Most areas require the use of life vests or personal flotation devices, so make sure you\u2019ve got enough for your whole crew. Many products have detailed descriptions of their certifications and intended use, so you can be sure the vests you\u2019re interested in are appropriate for your boat. You\u2019ll also find an array of navigation equipment, electronics, and charts to help you cruise your favorite waterways safely. You can organize your boating supplies effectively with a variety of specially designed storage containers for boats. Dry bags are an effective way to keep items you bring on board from getting wet. Cell phones, wallets, and food can be stored in the hold without worry about moisture creeping in. If you tow your boat, browse our selection of boating supplies for trailers. You\u2019ll find replacement lights and indicators, telescoping wheels, hub kits, and more. No matter what kind of boat you operate, keeping it well stocked with boating supplies will ensure you can head out for a relaxing day on the water whenever you\u2019d like.", "parent_text": "Boating & Water Sports", "parent_catid": 153, "keyword_density": {"boating supplies": "4.4"}, "department_id": 14},
