{"department_text": "Sports & Outdoors", "nr_products": 36933, "catid": 412, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_706814011_nr_n_4?rh=n%3A3375251%2Cn%3A%213375301%2Cn%3A706814011%2Cn%3A2342470011&bbn=706814011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833258&rnid=706814011", "text": "Skiing", "description_title": "Ski Gear from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/outdoor-gear/b/ref=sd_allcat_outrec/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=706814011", "keyword_count": {"ski gear": 5, "ski": 11, "ski gear from amazoncom": 2, "gear": 10}, "description_wc": 294, "description_text": "Whether you\u2019re ready to hit the slopes this weekend or are stocking up for next season\u2019s snow, having the right ski gear makes all the difference in your performance on the mountain. You can keep warm, safe, and comfortable while you take on that fresh powder or those icy moguls with the ski gear from Amazon.com Downhill, cross-country, telemark, or backcountry; whatever type of skiing you are into, we have the gear for it. Check out our Ski Gear store to find the latest skis, poles, bindings, and boots that fit your ski preference, style, and budget. We feature top brands like Atomic, Black Diamond, and Thule, so you can plan your ski trips in excitement and anticipation, knowing you are getting high-quality products. You\u2019ll find all the gear for skiing that you need to keep warm, comfortable, safe, and swooshing down the slopes. Stay safe on the slopes with properly fitting, comfortable helmets for kids and adult to protect your head from tree debris, ice, and falls. You can also find the right pair of goggles to shield your eyes from sun glare, ice crystals without the dreaded goggle fog-up. Find all the gear you need to stay warm and insulated: tactical hoods, waterproof jackets, pants, beanies, and long johns so you don\u2019t go numb halfway down the mountain. Quickly search and filter your results by featured brands, average customer review, condition, and price to find the best gear. Is fresh powder predicted soon? Have your ski gear delivered straight to your door with a variety of affordable and easy shipping options. Make your next ski trip great with the right ski gear from Amazon.com, your 24/7 online gear shop. Always open for your convenience.", "parent_text": "Outdoor Gear", "parent_catid": 149, "keyword_density": {"ski gear": "3.4", "ski gear from amazoncom": "2.7", "ski": "3.7", "gear": "3.4"}, "department_id": 14},
{"department_text": "Sports & Outdoors", "nr_products": 29162, "catid": 413, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_706814011_nr_n_5?rh=n%3A3375251%2Cn%3A%213375301%2Cn%3A706814011%2Cn%3A2342471011&bbn=706814011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833258&rnid=706814011", "text": "Snowboarding", "description_title": "Snowboarding Gear from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/outdoor-gear/b/ref=sd_allcat_outrec/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=706814011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 1, "snowboarding gear": 5, "gear": 6}, "description_wc": 278, "description_text": "Be ready to hit fresh powder next time it snows with all the right snowboarding gear, whether your board needs a new coat of wax or your bindings need to be tightened. Crushing it on the mountain means being prepared at home to face anything. Stock up on the snowboarding gear you need now and be the first one out there every time. In all different sizes, styles, and colors, Amazon.com has all the gear and tools your need. Whether you\u2019re looking for a freestyle or free ride board, men\u2019s or women\u2019s boots, or a new pair of bindings, check out our Snowboarding Gear Shop to find the latest snowboard, boots, bindings, and stomp pads that fit your personality and your budget. With top brands like DC, Nike, Columbia, and Santa Cruz, rest assured knowing you\u2019re getting high-quality products. Made to last in adverse conditions and treatment, protective snowboarding gear can is crucial to keep you safe on the mountain. You can find all the helmets, goggles, and protective clothing to protect you and ensure your performance isn\u2019t hampered by conditions or injury. Check out our selection of helmets with sturdy straps to protect yourself from falling debris, ice, and wipe-outs. The right pair of goggles can protect your eyes from the wind, ice crystals, snow glare, and keep your vision clear from fogging up. Keep insulated from head to two with waterproof jackets and pants, gloves, hats, face masks, and socks. With our wide selection of snowboarding gear, we\u2019ll have what you need, so you\u2019ll be able to perform well and stay comfortable and safe on the mountain.", "parent_text": "Outdoor Gear", "parent_catid": 149, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.4", "snowboarding gear": "3.6", "gear": "2.2"}, "department_id": 14},
{"nr_products": 3173, "catid": 414, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_3403201_nr_n_6?rh=n%3A3375251%2Cn%3A%213375301%2Cn%3A3403201%2Cn%3A6389528011&bbn=3403201&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833258&rnid=3403201", "text": "Pedals & Cleats", "description_wc": 0, "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/cycling-bikes-bicycles-bike-sale/b/ref=sd_allcat_bike/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=3403201", "parent_text": "Cycling", "parent_catid": 151, "department_text": "Sports & Outdoors", "department_id": 14},
{"department_text": "Sports & Outdoors", "nr_products": 5947, "catid": 415, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_3403201_nr_n_7?rh=n%3A3375251%2Cn%3A%213375301%2Cn%3A3403201%2Cn%3A6389202011&bbn=3403201&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833258&rnid=3403201", "text": "Helmets", "description_title": "Bike Helmets from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/cycling-bikes-bicycles-bike-sale/b/ref=sd_allcat_bike/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=3403201", "keyword_count": {"helmets": 9, "bike": 10, "bike helmets": 7, "bike helmets from amazoncom": 2}, "description_wc": 326, "description_text": "Biking is a great way to experience the outdoors and have fun while exercising. But like every other outdoor activity, you need the proper safety equipment to fully enjoy it. The bike helmets from Amazon.com provide the perfect protection for everyone from kids to adults to freely bike without a worry. You can find a wide variety of bike helmets for all the head sizes you need. Kids will love looking through the many designs we carry. They can choose their own helmet with cartoons, animals, dinosaurs, and much more printed on them, which will inspire them to go outside and exercise even more. Because we carry a variety of design made especially for boys and for girls, your child won\u2019t feel shy choosing the bike helmet they truly want and you can feel secure in finding a properly fitting helmet for your child. Our adult bike helmets may not have cartoons and puppies printed on them, but they are purpose-built for any type of biking. The aerodynamic designs could help you shave precious minutes off of your race or commute. Many models come with removable visors and adjustable fitting straps, so you can change your fit and your helmet to suit any weather. Our bike helmets are very lightweight, so you won\u2019t feel weighed down wearing them, but they still offer great protection on the road. Among our specialty bike helmets, we have many BMX helmets for extreme protection as you run off ramps and attempt flips. These helmets provide full-head coverage, just like a motorcycle helmet, ensuring that even your jaw, ears, and chin will be fully padded in case of a tumble. Our racing bike helmets are made with breathability in mind, so they\u2019re ideal for long bike trips or for riders who are prone to getting overheated. Keep your head protected and enjoy peace of mind on your rides with the quality, durable bike helmets from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Cycling", "parent_catid": 151, "keyword_density": {"helmets": "2.8", "bike": "3.1", "bike helmets": "4.3", "bike helmets from amazoncom": "2.5"}, "department_id": 14},
{"nr_products": 954, "catid": 416, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_3403201_nr_n_8?rh=n%3A3375251%2Cn%3A%213375301%2Cn%3A3403201%2Cn%3A1265463011&bbn=3403201&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833258&rnid=3403201", "text": "Protective Gear", "description_wc": 0, "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/cycling-bikes-bicycles-bike-sale/b/ref=sd_allcat_bike/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=3403201", "parent_text": "Cycling", "parent_catid": 151, "department_text": "Sports & Outdoors", "department_id": 14},
{"department_text": "Sports & Outdoors", "nr_products": 36155, "catid": 417, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_3403201_nr_n_9?rh=n%3A3375251%2Cn%3A%213375301%2Cn%3A3403201%2Cn%3A2371051011&bbn=3403201&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833258&rnid=3403201", "text": "Clothing", "description_title": "Cycling Clothing from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/cycling-bikes-bicycles-bike-sale/b/ref=sd_allcat_bike/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=3403201", "keyword_count": {"cycling clothing": 6, "amazoncom": 3, "cycling clothing from amazoncom": 1, "clothing": 7}, "description_wc": 303, "description_text": "Tuning up your ride means more than adding essentials to your bike: it also means finding the best cycling clothing to get you from Point A to B. You might have a souped-up bike that's ready to hit the streets, and make sure your bike clothing can keep up on the ride.Amazon.com is here to help you get your threads pedal perfect. We know sporting the right cycling clothing may vary from season to season, but our variety of apparel and accessories for men, women, boys, and girls ensures everyone will find practical, technical fits optimized for difficult conditions. From padded bike shorts and pants to insulated gloves to reflective vests, you'll find cycling clothing to keep you cool in warm months and comfortable during cold months, even if you have to splash across flooded train tracks or pedal through a freezing downpour. We offer a variety of cycling clothing comforts like compression shorts, moisture-wicking tops, blister-preventing socks, and sun-protectant gloves from quality brands like Pearl iZUMi, Canari Cyclewear, Zoic, and more. It\u2019s easy to top off a bike-ready outfit with a cap or moisture-wicking headband for added protection. If you want to beat the heat or conquer snowy conditions, the right cycling clothing can make all the difference. Amazon.com offers a range of protective gear, including sun sleeves and arm warmers, jackets, tights, vests, and even jerseys with SPF protection. When you search by our color filters, you can coordinate your ensemble with your bike. You can even gear up using our handy price and discount filters, so you can stick to your budget without sacrifice. It\u2019s time to hit the road for some quality time with your bike. Thanks to cycling clothing from Amazon.com, you can keep going mile after mile.", "parent_text": "Cycling", "parent_catid": 151, "keyword_density": {"cycling clothing": "4.0", "amazoncom": "1.0", "cycling clothing from amazoncom": "1.3", "clothing": "2.3"}, "department_id": 14},
{"department_text": "Sports & Outdoors", "nr_products": 2018, "catid": 418, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_3403201_nr_n_10?rh=n%3A3375251%2Cn%3A%213375301%2Cn%3A3403201%2Cn%3A3404251&bbn=3403201&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833258&rnid=3403201", "text": "Footwear", "description_title": "Cycling Shoes from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/cycling-bikes-bicycles-bike-sale/b/ref=sd_allcat_bike/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=3403201", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "cycling": 7, "shoes": 11, "cycling shoes": 6, "cycling shoes from amazoncom": 1}, "description_wc": 321, "description_text": "Riding a bike with your boots or sneakers isn\u2019t ideal. Boots are too heavy and bulky, so they end up getting scuffed against the sides of your bicycle, and sneakers don\u2019t offer the right support. Amazon.com offers a variety of cycling shoes to make sure you have the right equipment to keep the power in your pedal. Cycling shoes have the benefit of stiffer soles, so they\u2019re easy to slide into foot holsters. They also enhance the comfort of your feet on long rides because they don\u2019t bend as much and don\u2019t put all of the pressure on the balls of your feet. Many of our models even lock onto special pedals as well, so they\u2019re ideal for longer trips and adventures. We also offer many cycling shoes that are purpose-built for specific applications. Shoes for road bikes are stiffer than most and offer lightweight, breathable designs so that when you\u2019re pedaling down the raceway, your feet can stay cool. Mountain bike cycling shoes are not quite as stiff, but they still offer much more support than regular sneakers. They also come with enough traction, so if you decide to get off of your bike in the middle of the woods, they still offer support and balance for a short hike. Casual cycling shoes are great all-around shoes. They aren\u2019t quite as stiff as mountain bike shoes, but they\u2019re enough to make your commute much more comfortable on your feet. Because they\u2019re built to be general-use shoes, they\u2019re also ideal for walking around streets, offices, and coffee shops between bike trips. That way you won\u2019t have to bring an extra pair of shoes to work when you commute. Every sport needs the proper equipment, and bicycling is no different. When you select cycling shoes from Amazon.com, you can see the difference they make to your ride.", "parent_text": "Cycling", "parent_catid": 151, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.6", "cycling": "2.2", "shoes": "3.4", "cycling shoes": "3.7", "cycling shoes from amazoncom": "1.2"}, "department_id": 14},
{"nr_products": 30032, "catid": 419, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_3403201_nr_n_11?rh=n%3A3375251%2Cn%3A%213375301%2Cn%3A3403201%2Cn%3A6389203011&bbn=3403201&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833258&rnid=3403201", "text": "Hydration", "description_wc": 0, "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/cycling-bikes-bicycles-bike-sale/b/ref=sd_allcat_bike/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=3403201", "parent_text": "Cycling", "parent_catid": 151, "department_text": "Sports & Outdoors", "department_id": 14},
{"department_text": "Sports & Outdoors", "nr_products": 20142, "catid": 420, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_3403201_nr_n_12?rh=n%3A3375251%2Cn%3A%213375301%2Cn%3A3403201%2Cn%3A3403211&bbn=3403201&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833258&rnid=3403201", "text": "Accessories", "description_title": "Bike Gear from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/cycling-bikes-bicycles-bike-sale/b/ref=sd_allcat_bike/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=3403201", "keyword_count": {"bike gear": 6, "amazoncom": 2, "bike": 17, "bike gear from amazoncom": 1}, "description_wc": 357, "description_text": "It\u2019s taken forever, but you\u2019ve finally picked the perfect bike. It might suit all your commuting needs or it might just take you cruising around town. Either way, now you face a bigger dilemma: what kind of bike gear should you add to accelerate your ride? Amazon.com is here to help you pick the optimal options to soup up your bike ride. If you\u2019re racing across city streets to arrive at your desk on time, bike gear like lights, bike bells, horns, mirrors, racks, and panniers can help get you there safely with less stress on your mind and fewer burdens on your back. Fenders offer a dryer ride in unpredictable rains, so you can even cycle in your work clothes. For heavy-duty road racing, you might be on the lookout for bike gear like cyclocomputers, GPS units, stashable bike pumps, moisture-wicking bike gloves, and water bottle cages. To help you avoid the discomfort of long rides, we even offer a selection of personal care products, handy bike pack accessories. And if you need to do a little repair on the go, we offer replacement valve caps and other accessories to help maximize performance. For training in the off-season or for warming up pre-race, we also offer bike trainers in our wide selection of bike gear. You might be ready to tool around town on your new cruiser or hybrid bike, so we offer baskets perfect for stowing your stuff. When you need to rest, our selection of bike locks will help keep your bike secure. If you need to zoom around but have a lot to carry, we even offer convenient bike trailers. Because you\u2019ve got a lot of miles to cover, we know you want your bike gear should be the best quality, so we offer brands like Kryptonite, Topeak, Pearl iZUMi, and more. Plus, we offer convenient price and discount filters so you can pedal according to your budget. Tuning up your ride is every cyclist\u2019s rite of passage. With bike gear from Amazon.com, we\u2019ll help you find the smooth ride of your dreams.", "parent_text": "Cycling", "parent_catid": 151, "keyword_density": {"bike gear": "3.4", "amazoncom": "0.6", "bike": "4.8", "bike gear from amazoncom": "1.1"}, "department_id": 14},
{"department_text": "Sports & Outdoors", "nr_products": 5213, "catid": 421, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_3403201_nr_n_13?rh=n%3A3375251%2Cn%3A%213375301%2Cn%3A3403201%2Cn%3A6389515011&bbn=3403201&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833258&rnid=3403201", "text": "Bike Racks & Bags", "description_title": "Bike Racks from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/cycling-bikes-bicycles-bike-sale/b/ref=sd_allcat_bike/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=3403201", "keyword_count": {"bike racks": 4, "amazoncom": 4, "bike racks from amazoncom": 1, "racks": 5, "bike": 9}, "description_wc": 306, "description_text": "If you\u2019ve ever tried biking to work or through a mountain pass with a backpack on, you know it can rattle your belongings, and make you overheat very quickly. Bike racks and bags from Amazon.com offer a convenient way to stow and carry food, tools, rain gear and other long ride necessities with you. We have a variety of sturdy bike racks to make your commute and outdoor adventures much more practical and enjoyable. Installing our racks can increase your mobile storage space, freeing your hands and pockets from burden. They\u2019re also durable enough to withstand the constant jolting and bumping of mountain biking, so you can bring a healthy supply of extra energy bars, water, and emergency kits onto the mountain trails with ease. Our rack-top bags fit perfectly on bike racks to hold your belongings. Commuters will love keeping an extra shirt and shoes in their bag, so they can change before going into work. They're durable enough to withstand jolting and longer bike tours, so you can bring extra water, bars and emergency supplies with you when bike touring. Our bike rack bags have many pockets and compartments, so it\u2019s easy to organize all of your things. If you need a new bike rack bag soon, Amazon.com offers a variety of shipping options to speed up your delivery. Amazon.com also offers a variety of other front panniers and handlebar accessories to add additional cargo to your ride. Some bags offer clear display pockets, so they provide a great way to use your phone's GPS applications while you ride. Or, add a classic basket to your front handlebars for a nostalgic nod to old fashioned bike-riding fun. Bike racks from Amazon.com offer an effective storage solution to bring your essentials with you on all your bicycling rides", "parent_text": "Cycling", "parent_catid": 151, "keyword_density": {"bike racks": "2.6", "amazoncom": "1.3", "bike racks from amazoncom": "1.3", "racks": "1.6", "bike": "2.9"}, "department_id": 14},
