{"department_text": "Sports & Outdoors", "nr_products": 10852, "catid": 475, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_3410851_nr_n_12?rh=n%3A3375251%2Cn%3A%213375301%2Cn%3A3410851%2Cn%3A2371053011&bbn=3410851&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833256&rnid=3410851", "text": "Clothing", "description_title": "Golf Clothes from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Golf-Sports-Outdoors/b/ref=sd_allcat_golf/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=3410851", "keyword_count": {"golf clothes": 7, "amazoncom": 1, "golf": 9}, "description_wc": 315, "description_text": "Look good and stay comfortable on and off the course with golf clothes designed to help you perform your best, from the tee box to the putting green. At Amazon.com, you\u2019ll find golf clothes for men and women from top brands like Nike, Callaway, and Oakley. Whether you\u2019re after the laidback, comfortable look that Rory McIlroy brings to the course or a more classic Greg Normal style, we offer golf pants, shirts, outerwear, and accessories to help you channel your favorite pros and maybe even capture some of their power and precision. Shorts and pants for men and women should be comfortable, flex adequately with your swing, and regulate temperature well over an 18-hole walk. Golf clothes made with technical fabrics provide extra stretch and moisture-wicking properties, so even if you\u2019re playing in the balmy Florida heat, you can stay cool and dry on the course. We also offer skirts and dresses made with similar high-performance materials. Shirts and outerwear are available in a variety of styles for all seasons. Upper body range of motion is crucial to a consistent swing, so golf clothes are specially designed to let you move freely and comfortably no matter what club you\u2019re playing. Short and long-sleeve shirts, rainproof zip ups, and fleece jackets will get you out on the course in any weather. Our selection of hats, visors, and other accessories can help you complete your look, and our convenient product filters can help you quickly find golf clothes you\u2019re interested in. Simply choose brands, colors, and materials you want, and we\u2019ll display products that fit your criteria. Scratch golfers and new players alike understand the benefit of golf clothes designed and constructed to combine comfort and performance on the course. The range of styles and brands available means there\u2019s golf clothes for every player and budget.", "parent_text": "Golf", "parent_catid": 157, "keyword_density": {"golf": "2.9", "amazoncom": "0.3", "golf clothes": "4.4"}, "department_id": 14},
