{"department_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "nr_products": 29296, "catid": 490, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A15684181%2Cn%3A%2115690151%2Cn%3A15706571%2Cn%3A353609011&bbn=15706571&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833218&rnid=15706571", "text": "Tires", "description_title": "Tires from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/b/ref=sd_allcat_wt/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=15706571", "keyword_count": {"tires": 14}, "description_wc": 309, "description_text": "Tires enable your vehicle's on-road performance to be the best it can be. The type of car tires you select will have an important impact on your ability to drive your car smoothly and safely in various weather conditions and locations. Tires are ring-shaped casings filled with wires and cords, and they slip around your car's wheel rims in order to protect them and keep you on the road. Modern car tires are pneumatic and constructed out of natural and synthetic rubbers, fabric, wire, carbon black, and a variety of chemical compounds. The treads of tires are important for traction, and their bodies hold compressed air that creates a protective inflatable cushion for each wheel, designed to protect against wear and tear. When it comes to choosing the right car tires for your vehicle, the treads are one of the most important features to consider because they are the parts of tires that come into contact with the road's surface. Tread patterns are made up of grooves designed to channel away water, lugs that contact the road surface, voids that allow lugs to shed water, and sipes (valleys across the tire) that are designed to prevent hydroplaning, so you'll want to examine all of these aspects when selecting your tires. Selecting car tires essentially comes down to where and when you'll be driving. You can select from high-performance tires, mud and snow tires, and specialized tires that match the year, make, and model of your car thanks to Amazon's Part Finder. You'll be able to get the perfect set of car tires that are the best fit for your vehicle and that match your price and style requirements. Our website's advanced search features make it easy to find car tires for almost any vehicle currently on the road.", "parent_text": "Tires & Wheels", "parent_catid": 162, "keyword_density": {"tires": "4.5"}, "department_id": 15},
