{"department_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "nr_products": 5691, "catid": 495, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_5?rh=n%3A15684181%2Cn%3A%2115690151%2Cn%3A15706571%2Cn%3A15706911&bbn=15706571&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833218&rnid=15706571", "text": "Spacers", "description_title": "Wheel Spacers from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/b/ref=sd_allcat_wt/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=15706571", "keyword_count": {"wheel": 16, "spacers": 10, "amazoncom": 1, "wheel spacers": 9}, "description_wc": 330, "description_text": "A set of wheel spacers can help you mount your wheels and tires in the optimal position to clear brake parts, fill out wheel wells, and accommodate wider tires for superior grip. For lifted trucks and SUVs, large wheels can provide extra ground clearance for better off-roading, but without the proper wheel spacing, steering precision and handling stability can be compromised. A set of wheel spacers will effectively set your wheel hubs further apart, so you can equip wider tires and increase your footprint. Wheel spacers can improve fitment on any vehicle. Proper backspacing places your wheels in the correct position within the wheel well, which has a dramatic effect on performance and aesthetics. Wheel spacers can modify backspacing to accommodate wider tires for better traction, or simply to create a custom wide stance. To find wheel spacers that will fit your hubs properly, you can use our helpful Part Finder. Enter the year, make, and model car or truck you drive, and we\u2019ll automatically generate a list of compatible parts. On or off the road, it\u2019s important to install aftermarket car parts made from durable, weather resistant materials that will stand up to whatever you put them through. Wheel spacers made from billet aluminum, steel, and other advanced alloys are often powder or enamel coated for extra durability. Most wheel spacers have detailed descriptions of their construction materials, dimensions, and features, so you can be sure to find a set of spacers that are as tough as the stock components on your vehicle. At Amazon.com, we offer a full range of drivetrain components for performance cars, off-road trucks, and family vehicles. You\u2019ll find wheel spacers, brake parts, transmission repair parts, and a host of other equipment, all together in one convenient place. Best of all, we can ship everything you need straight to your door. Install a set of wheel spacers to achieve perfect backspacing, and enjoy the performance benefits of wider set tires.", "parent_text": "Tires & Wheels", "parent_catid": 162, "keyword_density": {"wheel": "4.8", "spacers": "3.0", "amazoncom": "0.3", "wheel spacers": "5.5"}, "department_id": 15},
