{"nr_products": 10281, "catid": 531, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_3?rh=n%3A15684181%2Cn%3A%2115690151%2Cn%3A346333011%2Cn%3A404702011&bbn=346333011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833217&rnid=346333011", "text": "Fluids & Maintenance", "description_wc": 0, "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Motorcycle-ATV-Automotive/b/ref=sd_allcat_matv/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=346333011", "parent_text": "Motorcycle & Powersports", "parent_catid": 163, "department_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "department_id": 15},
{"department_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "nr_products": 110832, "catid": 532, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_4?rh=n%3A15684181%2Cn%3A%2115690151%2Cn%3A346333011%2Cn%3A404632011&bbn=346333011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833217&rnid=346333011", "text": "Accessories", "description_title": "Motorcycle Accessories from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Motorcycle-ATV-Automotive/b/ref=sd_allcat_matv/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=346333011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 3, "motorcycle accessories": 7, "motorcycle": 8}, "description_wc": 345, "description_text": "On or off the road, you\u2019ll enjoy your rides more often with a few helpful motorcycle accessories designed to make riding, storage, and maintenance easier and more convenient. You\u2019ll find all the motorcycle accessories you need for street bikes and cruisers at Amazon.com. If you\u2019ve got a road trip planned with another motorcyclist or a passenger, consider electronic communications equipment to make it easier to talk to your companions. Hands free headsets make it easy to clearly speak to passengers and other bikers, even over the roar of a big V-Twin. Pack more gear along for the ride with motorcycle accessories designed to increase cargo area. Saddlebags, cargo racks, and tie downs will help you safely distribute the load, so you won\u2019t have to leave anything behind. Off-road riders can hit the trails with motorcycle accessories designed for safety, stability, and durability. Keep track of your ride with an enduro computer, and get at-a-glance information about speed, revs, total ride time, and engine temperature. Loading up your ATVs and motocross bikes doesn\u2019t have to be a tricky enterprise. Loading ramps let you ride your off-roader right into the back of a pickup truck or trailer, so there\u2019s no awkward, dangerous lifting. You\u2019ll also find motorcycle accessories to help you navigate the trail safely. Winches, tool kits, and fuel containers of all kinds are available to be delivered straight to your door from Amazon.com. Most bikers don\u2019t brave the weather on two wheels all year round. If you store your motorcycle in a garage over the winter, browse our selection of motorcycle accessories for storage and maintenance. Universal and custom fit bike covers will keep dirt, dust, and moisture off your bike, so it\u2019ll be ready to roll in the spring time. To keep your battery in good condition, hook up a trickle charger to prevent a slow drain while you\u2019re not riding. Make riding as convenient and enjoyable s possible with motorcycle accessories for storage, maintenance, and performance from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Motorcycle & Powersports", "parent_catid": 163, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.9", "motorcycle accessories": "4.1", "motorcycle": "2.3"}, "department_id": 15},
{"department_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "nr_products": 128678, "catid": 533, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_16310091_nr_n_5?rh=n%3A16310091%2Cn%3A%2116310161%2Cn%3A6054382011&bbn=16310161&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833213&rnid=16310161", "text": "Food Service Equipment & Supplies", "description_title": "Food Service & Restaurant Supplies", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/industrial-scientific-supplies/b/ref=sd_allcat_ind_sup/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=16310091", "keyword_count": {"food": 7, "restaurant supplies": 3, "food service": 2, "supplies": 9, "restaurant": 17}, "description_wc": 230, "description_text": "Restaurant supplies and equipment include a wide variety of restaurant supply products that are used in commercial and residential kitchens, and carried by restaurant supply stores. Essential kitchen supply products commonly include kitchen utensils, commercial cookware, and commercial bakeware. Restaurant equipment is used to prepare and transport food and dishes used in restaurant supply environments. Restaurant equipment and kitchen supplies include janitorial equipment, racks and shelving, and bulk food storage products, used to store food. Kitchen supplies also include food serving items. Tabletop restaurant supply products, such as restaurant dining room supplies, are used to set tables, and serve and display food. Food service disposables are used to replenish kitchen supplies for everyday serving. Kitchen supplies consist of commercial bakeware, such as racks, baking sheets, and braising torches, which are common products in a restaurant supply business. Commercial stovetops, sinks, dishwashers, pizza ovens, and refrigeration products are a central component of restaurant supplies. Specific restaurant equipment, such as bar equipment and supply, or concession and vending restaurant supply products, may also be used. Restaurant supply products include food service disposables, such as gloves, plates, and utensils, and items used to support cleaning and maintaining kitchens, restaurants, and other facilities that use restaurant supplies. Restaurant equipment can include other types of specific restaurant supply equipment, such as bar equipment and other kitchen supply accessories, such as coffee and espresso kitchen supplies.", "parent_text": "Industrial Supplies", "parent_catid": 164, "keyword_density": {"food": "3.0", "restaurant supplies": "2.6", "restaurant": "7.4", "supplies": "3.9", "food service": "1.7"}, "department_id": 15},
