{"department_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "nr_products": 146, "catid": 553, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_15706941_nr_n_29?rh=n%3A15684181%2Cn%3A%2115690151%2Cn%3A15706941%2Cn%3A15709061&bbn=15706941&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833214&rnid=15706941", "text": "Strut Compressors", "description_title": "Strut Spring Compressor from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Tools-Equipment-Automotive/b/ref=sd_allcat_ate/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=15706941", "keyword_count": {"compressor": 12, "spring": 10, "strut": 20, "strut spring": 7, "amazoncom": 1, "strut spring compressor": 6}, "description_wc": 300, "description_text": "Purchasing the perfect strut spring compressor is important for keeping you safe while you change the struts on your vehicle. Designed to aid in the replacement of strut cartridges and assembly components, a strut compressor will safely compress your vehicle's door springs for easy removal and installation of the new springs. Depending on the strut spring compressor, built-in detent pins allow you to lock the door's springs securely into place for a safer installation process. With the right strut compressor, you can adjust the handle to fit a variety of strut spring sizes, decreasing the mounting interference for quick installation. Strut compressors provide you with a variety of uses, whether it is for the replacement of a strut tube, bent strut, damaged spindle, or shock absorber, without the need of other clamps or devices. Additionally, the strut spring compressor features a heavy-duty steel construction for long-lasting durability against weathering. Offering low strut compressors prices for budget-conscious consumers, Amazon.com provides you with a wide variety of strut spring compressors to help keep your vehicle's tune up quick and easy, decreasing the risk of you becoming injured during the strut installation process. The filtering options on the left side of the page allow you to choose between shipping options, reviews, brands, prices, new arrivals, sellers, and discounts to help narrow your search for the perfect strut spring compressor. Whether you need to change the struts on your vehicle or simply wish to purchase a strut compressor for \"just in case\" situations, buying the right strut compressor can help keep the installation process quick and efficient. Greatly decreasing the mounting interference, a strut spring compressor will help keep you safe while you are replacing the struts and assembly components, diminishing the chances of you being injured.", "parent_text": "Automotive Tools & Equipment", "parent_catid": 160, "keyword_density": {"compressor": "4.0", "spring": "3.3", "strut": "6.7", "strut spring": "4.7", "amazoncom": "0.3", "strut spring compressor": "6.0"}, "department_id": 15},
{"nr_products": 1814, "catid": 554, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_15706941_nr_n_30?rh=n%3A15684181%2Cn%3A%2115690151%2Cn%3A15706941%2Cn%3A15709071&bbn=15706941&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833214&rnid=15706941", "text": "Thread Repair Kits", "description_wc": 0, "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Tools-Equipment-Automotive/b/ref=sd_allcat_ate/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=15706941", "parent_text": "Automotive Tools & Equipment", "parent_catid": 160, "department_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "department_id": 15},
{"nr_products": 14664, "catid": 555, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_15706941_nr_n_31?rh=n%3A15684181%2Cn%3A%2115690151%2Cn%3A15706941%2Cn%3A15709111&bbn=15706941&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833214&rnid=15706941", "text": "Tire & Wheel Tools", "description_wc": 0, "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Tools-Equipment-Automotive/b/ref=sd_allcat_ate/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=15706941", "parent_text": "Automotive Tools & Equipment", "parent_catid": 160, "department_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "department_id": 15},
{"department_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "nr_products": 919, "catid": 556, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_15706941_nr_n_32?rh=n%3A15684181%2Cn%3A%2115690151%2Cn%3A15706941%2Cn%3A155346011&bbn=15706941&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833214&rnid=15706941", "text": "Tire Air Compressors & Inflators", "description_title": "Air Compressor from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Tools-Equipment-Automotive/b/ref=sd_allcat_ate/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=15706941", "keyword_count": {"air compressor": 6, "amazoncom": 1, "compressor": 9, "air": 10}, "description_wc": 292, "description_text": "One of the most useful and versatile tools that you will ever own is an air compressor. More than just a tire inflator, it can be used to power your spray gun, nail gun, power wrench, and so much more. When shopping for an air compressor or tire inflator, you will notice that there are two standard types of air compressors on the market: piston-type compressors and portable compressors. The most common is the portable compressor, although the piston type is usually found in a commercial-garage setting or in the home garage of someone who does a lot of automotive repairs. The piston-type air compressor or tire inflator has a tank that is used to store compressed air. The motor will shut off whenever the tank is full, and restart whenever the pressure inside the tank drops. The portable air compressor is small, compact, and perfect for use as a tire inflator. It doesn't have a storage tank, and runs continually to provide air for inflating tires, sports equipment, pool floats, and so forth, or for powering smaller spray guns and other small air tools. Choosing the right unit for your needs is important. If you will use it as a basic tire inflator, then you will be fine going with a portable unit that you can store in the trunk of your car and that probably plugs into the opening for your cigarette lighter. One thing to pay special attention to is the horsepower rating of the unit. This can range from 1.5 HP to 7 HP. The more horsepower the unit offers, the bigger the jobs it can handle. You can find a top-notch tire inflator or air compressor from trusted brands when shopping Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Automotive Tools & Equipment", "parent_catid": 160, "keyword_density": {"air compressor": "4.1", "amazoncom": "0.3", "air": "3.4", "compressor": "3.1"}, "department_id": 15},
