{"department_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "nr_products": 14502, "catid": 561, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_15706941_nr_n_37?rh=n%3A15684181%2Cn%3A%2115690151%2Cn%3A15706941%2Cn%3A13400481&bbn=15706941&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833214&rnid=15706941", "text": "Welding Tools", "description_title": "Welding Supplies from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Tools-Equipment-Automotive/b/ref=sd_allcat_ate/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=15706941", "keyword_count": {"welding supplies": 4, "amazoncom": 2, "welding": 18}, "description_wc": 323, "description_text": "Welding is a precise job that requires the correct materials and equipment to achieve great results. Whether you need welding accessories for MIG, TIG, or stick welding, you\u2019ll find a wide variety of raw materials, wire, safety equipment, and tools to help you get the job done right every time. The most common type of welding for home shops is metal inert gas, or MIG welding. This process uses inert gas to shield the steel being welded, and is generally considered a high-speed method that\u2019s easy to learn. MIG welding is very useful for joining thin steel, and is somewhat resistant to contaminates and dirty surfaces. At Amazon.com, we offer a complete line of MIG welding supplies and equipment, ranging from welders to masks to wire and electrical components. Many small MIG welders are highly portable, so you can pack them up and bring them wherever you need to go. For highly precise welds, many professionals prefer tungsten inert gas, or TIG welding. This process is much slower than MIG or stick welding, but produces the \u201ccleanest\u201d welds, and is therefore popular in aerospace and performance automotive applications. TIG welding can join many different types of metal, including steel, stainless steel, copper, aluminum, and dozens of alloys in nearly any thickness, so it\u2019s a particularly useful method. Since TIG welding requires pristine surfaces to join metals, it\u2019s important you have the correct welding supplies including wire brushes, gas flow meters, nozzles, and wire feeders to ensure a quality weld. Stick welding is one of the oldest arc welding methods, and has been in use around the world for decades. It is a versatile process that requires no shielding gas, so fewer welding supplies are needed. Stick welding does, however, require more clean up on the finished weld to ensure longevity. You\u2019ll find all the welding supplies you need for MIG, TIG, stick, and gas welding at Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Automotive Tools & Equipment", "parent_catid": 160, "keyword_density": {"welding supplies": "2.5", "amazoncom": "0.6", "welding": "5.6"}, "department_id": 15},
{"nr_products": 88, "catid": 562, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_15706941_nr_n_38?rh=n%3A15684181%2Cn%3A%2115690151%2Cn%3A15706941%2Cn%3A15709221&bbn=15706941&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833214&rnid=15706941", "text": "Windshield Wiper Tools", "description_wc": 0, "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Tools-Equipment-Automotive/b/ref=sd_allcat_ate/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=15706941", "parent_text": "Automotive Tools & Equipment", "parent_catid": 160, "department_text": "Automotive & Industrial", "department_id": 15},
{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 208864, "catid": 563, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_165793011_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A165793011%2Cn%3A%21165795011%2Cn%3A165993011&bbn=165795011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=165795011", "text": "Action Figures & Statues", "description_title": "Action Figures from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/toys/b/ref=sd_allcat_tg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165793011", "keyword_count": {"action": 8, "amazoncom": 2, "action figures": 4}, "description_wc": 288, "description_text": "There\u2019s nothing quite as symbolic of childhood as an action figure. Whether you\u2019re looking for your child\u2019s favorite movie characters, dinosaurs, superheroes or collectable figurines, we have the perfect toys for you. Amazon.com carries the latest items from Marvel Comics, Disney, Transformers, Star Wars, Power Rangers, WWE, Halo and more. Watch as your child plays through epic battles of good versus evil with the hottest new action figures. It\u2019s a great and active way to play. Running around the kitchen or backyard holding a Thor action figure over their head, acting out an action-packed chase between a plastic T. rex and a stegosaurus, and setting up elaborate battlegrounds with toy soldiers will keep your little one busy for hours. But not all of our action figures are so action-packed, we also carry a wide variety of farm animals, Mr. Potato Heads, Disney Princesses, Calico Critters and more peaceful toys. Browse through our playsets and you\u2019ll find the perfect stage for your child\u2019s imagination to blossom. From pirate ships to fantasy castles, doll houses to whimsical tree houses, we carry something for every child. Don\u2019t be surprised when you browse through our toys and find gifts for yourself. We have plastic replicas of some of your favorite movie and television props. We even have a selection of household items themed after classic characters, spaceships and relics. Our highly detailed action figures are also perfect for adorning a playful grown-up\u2019s office. There are no toys as sturdy or as versatile as action figures. Whether you need a gift for a rambunctious son, a playful daughter, or yourself, you\u2019re sure to find what you\u2019re looking for on Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Toys & Games", "parent_catid": 130, "keyword_density": {"action": "2.8", "amazoncom": "0.7", "action figures": "2.8"}, "department_id": 12},
{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 98964, "catid": 564, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_165793011_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A165793011%2Cn%3A%21165795011%2Cn%3A166057011&bbn=165795011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=165795011", "text": "Arts & Crafts", "description_title": "Crafts for Kids from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/toys/b/ref=sd_allcat_tg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165793011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 1, "kids": 8, "crafts for kids": 4, "crafts": 6}, "description_wc": 321, "description_text": "Keep your kids engaged while building motor skills and encouraging creativity and imagination with a host of crafts for kids that are perfect for rainy afternoons indoors. From drawing and painting, to sculpting and beading, to coloring and stamping, our wide variety of different crafts for kids will entertain and inspire your kids. Search and filter your results by category, featured characters, gender, interest, price, and more to narrow down your selection and make choosing the right kid\u2019s crafts easier. Shop craft kits and supplies from top brands like Crayola, Play-Doh, and Roseart with your kids online, and make it easy to compare similar products and features. Our convenient, affordable, and quick shipping options, mean you can get the kid\u2019s crafts you\u2019re interested in delivered straight to your door right when you want them. At Amazon.com, you\u2019ll find a wide selection of beads, clay and dough, drawing and painting supplies, fuse beads, molding and sculpting sticks, stickers, scissors, and other crafts for kids. Hands on materials inspire children to be creative and think critically while the have fun playing, and being imaginative with their craft projects. You can salvage a rainy afternoon stuck inside the house by having a few kid\u2019s craft projects ready to go. Let your future fashion designer scribble all over magazines, coloring books, and scratch paper. Or, you can paint still-life portraits, Martian landscapes, and underwater creatures with adjustable height standing easels, smocks, and bright colors, and even make fuzzy creatures out of a variety of pipe cleaners, and hide them around the house for friends to find. For days when lots of kids will be stopping by, you can set up a friendship bracelet station, or break out the sticker pads for hours of creative entertainment. Crafts for kids will inspire your children to be creative and explore their artistic side, and teach them what imagination is all about.", "parent_text": "Toys & Games", "parent_catid": 130, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.3", "kids": "2.5", "crafts for kids": "3.7", "crafts": "1.9"}, "department_id": 12},
{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 124285, "catid": 565, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_165793011_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A165793011%2Cn%3A%21165795011%2Cn%3A196601011&bbn=165795011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=165795011", "text": "Baby & Toddler Toys", "description_title": "Infant Toys from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/toys/b/ref=sd_allcat_tg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165793011", "keyword_count": {"infant toys from amazoncom": 2, "infant": 9, "infant toys": 6, "toys": 10}, "description_wc": 311, "description_text": "Experts say that play is the best way to learn, and now with the quality infant toys from Amazon.com, you can make sure your kids get all the educational playtime they need during their most developmental stages. Musical and sound-making infant toys are popular and fun. They can come with a variety of buttons, pulleys and other features to make the toys roar, squeak, chirp, and more. Our musical toddler toys are great for providing a beat that your child can dance to when they\u2019re energetic. Others play softer lullabies that can be used to soothe them to sleep, and when they do, we have all the plush and stuffed animals your infant or toddler could want to cuddle up with. Stacking and nesting infant toys can help your little one develop valuable motor skills and pattern recognition. On many models, your child will be encouraged to stack their pieces in order from large to small, or based on shape and color. They\u2019ll be absorbed in their game, trying to sort out all the brightly colored pieces in order to complete the puzzle. If you\u2019re puzzling over how to find affordable toys, try filtering your search by price to see the most budget-friendly toddler and infant toys we have available. Many infants, and even some toddlers, love to put their toys, clothes or random found objects in their mouths. For that, we carry many different sizes and styles of teethers. These infant toys are especially designed to be safe and comforting for your baby to chew on. You can choose from a variety of materials, so if your baby prefers softer chewing materials like fluid-filled plastics, we have just the items for them. Infants and toddlers learn at quick speeds, and now you can give them a little more inspiration with infant toys from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Toys & Games", "parent_catid": 130, "keyword_density": {"infant toys": "3.9", "infant": "2.9", "infant toys from amazoncom": "2.6", "toys": "3.2"}, "department_id": 12},
{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 78241, "catid": 566, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A165796011%2Cn%3A%21165797011%2Cn%3A2402554011&bbn=165797011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833288&rnid=165797011", "text": "Apparel & Accessories", "description_title": "Baby Clothes from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/baby-car-seats-strollers-bedding/b/ref=sd_allcat_ba/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165796011", "keyword_count": {"baby clothes": 7, "baby": 11, "amazoncom": 4, "baby clothes from amazoncom": 1}, "description_wc": 307, "description_text": "Dressing up your little one should offer convenience and comfort, so Amazon.com has combed the wide world of baby clothes to offer soft, playful, and totally kid-friendly threads worth loving. From bodysuits and rompers to dresses and suits sets, we offer baby clothes for all sorts of little ones. With our easy-to-browse search categories for baby girls, baby boys, and unisex baby clothes, choosing the right wardrobe for your mini marvel is quick and painless. You can narrow your search by size, silhouette style, and even by price. And because we know that comfort and convenience is premium for baby, we've gathered quality baby clothes from name brands like Absorba, Zutano, Calvin Klein, and many more. We feature handy baby clothes categories so you can choose from sets or separates. You can doll up your little lady with dress sets that come complete with diaper covers and crochet headbands, or you can sharpen your little man's look with a one-piece romper complete with pull-on elastic waistband pants. And because you might want to take your little one to the pool for some summer fun, we've even got swim sets complete with diaper seams. From ruffles to rough-and-tumble, Amazon.com offers baby clothing suited for your preferences, whether it's a twirl-worthy tutu, an adventure-ready tee, a novelty bodysuit, a classic puff-sleeve top, or an organic fabric. If your baby clothes don't exactly fit your needs, you can easily return them with our free shipping and free returns on eligible items. Lap necks, snap closures, and elastic waistbands all add ease to your life?shopping at Amazon.com offers another convenience. Thanks to the wide selection of baby clothes from Amazon.com, snapping a little one into comfort is as easy as the click of a button.", "parent_text": "Baby", "parent_catid": 131, "keyword_density": {"baby clothes": "4.6", "baby": "3.6", "amazoncom": "1.3", "baby clothes from amazoncom": "1.3"}, "department_id": 12},
