{"department_text": "Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry", "nr_products": 25782, "catid": 569, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_672123011_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A672123011%2Cn%3A%21672124011%2Cn%3A679217011&bbn=672124011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833285&rnid=672124011", "text": "Girls", "description_title": "Girls' Shoes from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/shoes-men-women-kids-baby/b/ref=sd_allcat_shoe/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=672123011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "girls": 7, "shoes": 14, "girls shoes": 6}, "description_wc": 327, "description_text": "Whether your little girl wants to spend the day at the beach, an outdoor garden party, or on a nature hike, we've got all kinds of adorable and durable girls' sandals to keep her comfortable and cute all day long. Amazon.com takes steps to keep your girl clad in the kicks she craves. Our featured categories of girls' shoes are designed to put a spring in her step, whether you're looking for ballet flats, sandals, mary janes, running shoes, or crib shoes. We are passionate about helping you save time and money in outfitting your girl, so we provide handy filters to easily browse all of our designs for girls' shoes. From athletic shoes, boots, clogs and mules to crib shoes and first walkers all the way to flats, loafers, outdoor, oxfords, sandals, slippers, sneakers, and uniform and school shoes; you can make sure she's appropriately shod for the occasion. Because we strive to provide you with quality designs in all of our girls' shoes, we feature a wealth of brands, including outdoor favorites KEEN and crocs, athletic favorites New Balance and Merrell, and classics from Robeez by Stride Rite. And because color and design can matter as much as the brand, we also offer a girls' shoes color filter so you can pick those tie-dyed mules or pink mary janes your mini maven's been talking about. We know time is as precious as the shoes on your little one's feet, so closures matter too. Using our handy girls' shoes search toolbar, you can quickly browse for lace-ups, buckles, or adjustable closures. Plus, you can narrow your search by size and shoe width, so getting the shoes on her feet is as easy as getting her into her favorite tutu or tee. She'll need a great pair of shoes at every stage of her life, and Amazon.com is here to help with our wide selection of comfortable girls' shoes.", "parent_text": "Shoes", "parent_catid": 139, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.6", "girls": "2.1", "shoes": "4.3", "girls shoes": "3.7"}, "department_id": 13},
{"department_text": "Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry", "nr_products": 17924, "catid": 570, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_672123011_nr_n_3?rh=n%3A672123011%2Cn%3A%21672124011%2Cn%3A679182011&bbn=672124011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833285&rnid=672124011", "text": "Boys", "description_title": "Boys\u2019 Shoes from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/shoes-men-women-kids-baby/b/ref=sd_allcat_shoe/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=672123011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "boys shoes": 6, "shoes": 9}, "description_wc": 306, "description_text": "Whether they\u2019re running after the bus, walking to friends\u2019 houses, or playing sports, stock up on a variety of boys\u2019 shoes for all sorts of different occasions and events. From slip-on sandals for home and colorful sneakers for school to insulated boots for the winter and comfortable loafers for lounging, Amazon.com\u2019s large selection of boys\u2019 shoes has all the shoe types your kids could want. Featuring sizes and widths for infants, toddlers, little, and big kids, our products are sorted into convenient categories that make browsing simple and easy. With free shipping and free returns on eligible items, you can have your new shoes delivered to your door step with just a single click. Comfortable and sturdy, we carry a wide range of boys\u2019 shoes that satisfy all needs and preferences. Able to withstand the wear and tear of growing up, you can choose from casual sneakers, clogs, loafers, and slippers or more formal and specialty athletics and outdoor, boots, oxfords, and dress shoes. With our wallet-friendly options, you can find several pairs of boys\u2019 shoes at home for whatever occasion and event may arise. Whether it\u2019s their first step or their first game, choosing the right pair is easy whether they need laces, hook-and-loop, slip-on, and another kind of closure type. Featuring popular brands, characters, movies, and themes, you can find all of your kids\u2019 favorites at our Boys\u2019 Shoes Store, from Mickey and all his friends to The Hulk, Batman, Lego, Thomas the Engine, and more. Other characters and fun designs make it easy to personalize their shoes even more. With well-known brands like KEEN, Crocs, New Balance, and Stride Rite, save time and money by shopping from home. Rain, snow, sleet, or shine, the right boys\u2019 shoes are just a click away on Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Shoes", "parent_catid": 139, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.7", "boys shoes": "3.9", "shoes": "2.9"}, "department_id": 13},
{"department_text": "Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry", "nr_products": 0, "catid": 571, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_672123011_nr_n_4?rh=n%3A672123011%2Cn%3A%21672124011%2Cn%3A15743631&bbn=672124011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833285&rnid=672124011", "text": "Handbags", "description_title": "Handbags from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/shoes-men-women-kids-baby/b/ref=sd_allcat_shoe/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=672123011", "keyword_count": {"handbags from amazoncom": 1, "handbags": 6}, "description_wc": 370, "description_text": "The ideal handbag can add a pop of color to a neutral top or can dress up a casual look. Outfit-making handbags can set the tone for an entire wardrobe, yet are versatile enough to wear every day. With the right color, shape, and pockets you're looking for, the perfect handbag can be equal parts convenient and stylish--that's why the Amazon Handbag Store carries a wide variety of shapes, sizes, colors, and brands so you can find the perfect fit. We offer a unique, vibrant, and versatile assortment of designer handbags, including clutches, wristlets, cross-body bags, shoulder bags, elegant evening bags, and fun-and-functional top-handle bags. Not sure what kind of bag you want? Browse the latest picks from your favorite designers, like Rebecca Minkoff, Kate Spade New York, and more. Headed out for the night? Easily dress-up your formal wear with an iridescent and studded evening bag. Need something for day-to-day life? Check out structured totes or sporty messenger bags. You don't have to choose between a luxe and practical leather shoulder bag or a flirty clutch?you can have both, thanks to our array of affordable handbags. Need a roomy interior? Check out our range of top-handle and shoulder bags. A slouchy hobo might be just what you seek for those casual and on-trend occasions. What about a simple, sleek design? Simply choose a wristlet or cross-body bag with a chain-link strap for an in-the-know look. We know the interior of quality handbags often matters just as much as what's on the outside. That's why our offerings allow you a visual peek inside your selection while also offering reliable dimensions. These features allow you to rely on our selection of handbags for coordinating lining and the right amount of pocket space. And, if your new handbag doesn't work out, you can return it using our free returns on eligible items. When you find that perfect-for-you handbag, it can be timeless. From party-ready clutches and evening bags to day-perfect totes and shoulder bags, browse our sure-to-please selection of long-lasting handbags from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Shoes", "parent_catid": 139, "keyword_density": {"handbags from amazoncom": "0.8", "handbags": "1.6"}, "department_id": 13},
