{"department_text": "Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry", "nr_products": 52180, "catid": 576, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_15743631_nr_n_3?rh=n%3A672123011%2Cn%3A%21672124011%2Cn%3A15743631%2Cn%3A3421075011&bbn=15743631&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833285&rnid=15743631", "text": "Shoulder Bags", "description_title": "Shoulder Bags from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Handbags-Accessories-Clothing/b/ref=sd_allcat_bags/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=15743631", "keyword_count": {"shoulder": 11, "shoulder bags": 6, "amazoncom": 1}, "description_wc": 301, "description_text": "When you\u2019re on the go, you want your shoulder bag to keep everything in place and stay firmly on your shoulder. Whether you prefer zipper or turn-lock closures, at Amazon.com, we think you should have the best in go-to shoulder bags that match your tastes and stand up to your everyday routine. From the iconic baguette and slouch hobo bag to elegant satchels and practical totes, we\u2019ve curated a selection of structured shoulder bags designed to fit your needs. Selecting the right strap and the right shape for the right occasion take can be a fun process and we want your search for exclusive, ergonomically-friendly shoulder bags to be convenient and enjoyable. With our filterable selection of color palettes that speak to your unique sense of fashion and a search feature that allows you to find visually similar items, we want you to help you quickly choose the best stow-and-go option for you. Even better, if you find your new shoulder bag doesn\u2019t fit your needs, you can return it with free returns on eligible items. You can even filter our selection of shoulder bags by designer brands, including Michael Kors, Guess, and Vera Bradley. Maybe you want to go beyond color and choose a textured design. From faux-ostrich skin to laser cuts to lace and beyond, our range of shoulder bags includes classic looks and vibrant accessory centerpieces. It\u2019s as easy to go for a stand-out, free-spirited bag as it is to shoulder a neutral-hued bag. Whether you want a roomy satchel or tote for a casual afternoon outing or you want a baguette under your arm for a polished look, our wide selection of shoulder bags takes the stressful weight of shopping right off your shoulders.", "parent_text": "Handbags", "parent_catid": 140, "keyword_density": {"shoulder": "3.7", "shoulder bags": "4.0", "amazoncom": "0.3"}, "department_id": 13},
