{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 27307, "catid": 601, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_165793011_nr_n_3?rh=n%3A165793011%2Cn%3A%21165795011%2Cn%3A166092011&bbn=165795011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=165795011", "text": "Building Toys", "description_title": "Building Sets from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/toys/b/ref=sd_allcat_tg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165793011", "keyword_count": {"building": 13, "amazoncom": 2, "building sets from amazoncom": 1, "building sets": 7, "sets": 8}, "description_wc": 289, "description_text": "Introduced early in life, the love of learning can last for years and years. The building sets from Amazon.com help girls and boys learn how to set goals, plan ahead and overcome challenges. You\u2019ll be amazed at the things kids can think of and then create using even the simplest building blocks. From advanced LEGO sets to larger and simpler DUPLO blocks and Megabloks, we have something perfect for every age level. Build castles, pillboxes, racecars, barns and more. Building sets never get old, you can always take old creations apart and keep building and rebuilding an infinite possibility of machines, buildings and vehicles. If you want a little more direction, Amazon.com offers plenty of specific building sets to recreate the Space Needle, the Empire State Building, the Guggenheim Museum, Frank Lloyd Wright\u2019s Fallingwater, and more. It\u2019s a great way to study modern architectural design and engineering while having a blast. The completed building sets of local land marks look great on office desks or at home. We have building sets for almost anything you can imagine, including Ferris wheels, roller coasters, the White House, Transformers, spooky graveyards and scenes from your favorite adventure movies. Our Tegu blocks also make a great office desk toy to help you decompress before or after difficult meetings. These building blocks are made with just magnets and high-quality natural woods; they\u2019ll look beautiful lying around when they\u2019re not in use. Building sets can begin a lifelong hobby of construction and engineering. They help you develop reasoning and planning skills that are invaluable to your daily life. If you\u2019re looking for a way to spend more time with your kids, building sets could be the perfect solution.", "parent_text": "Toys & Games", "parent_catid": 130, "keyword_density": {"building": "4.5", "amazoncom": "0.7", "building sets": "4.8", "building sets from amazoncom": "1.4", "sets": "2.8"}, "department_id": 12},
{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 105756, "catid": 602, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_165793011_nr_n_4?rh=n%3A165793011%2Cn%3A%21165795011%2Cn%3A166118011&bbn=165795011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=165795011", "text": "Dolls & Accessories", "description_title": "Dolls & Accessories from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/toys/b/ref=sd_allcat_tg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165793011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 3, "accessories": 1, "dolls": 3}, "description_wc": 317, "description_text": "Every woman can remember her favorite doll growing up. Whether it was a floppy Raggedy Ann, an elaborately dressed fashion doll, or a soft and squeezable baby doll, they make lasting impressions on young girls. Give the girl in your life a doll she will think of happily in the years to come. Doctor and teacher play sets make the perfect gift for a young girl. They provide positive role models for girls who are not into playing dress-up and taking care of babies. A teacher play set can even inspire girls to become better students and to have a growing respect for their academic life. Let your little one listen to your heart beat with her stethoscope, check your blood pressure or test your reflexes; you never know where these skills may lead. Our baby dolls are perfect for the toddlers who want to be just like their mom. We have babies that walk, giggle, change clothes, drink from a bottle and more to make your little girl feel like she\u2019s taking care of the real thing. The strollers, bassinets and different outfits on Amazon.com make the experience complete. We also have a wide variety of fashion dolls from Barbie, Monster High, Disney, Winx and more. Browse Amazon.com\u2019s lists of different fashion sets and accessories. They\u2019ll provide countless hours of mix-and-match dress-up fun for your little girl. If you\u2019re looking for the beautiful and book-smart Belle from Disney Princesses, or the fearless Katniss Everdeen, we have all of your girl\u2019s favorite characters. For added fun, our doll houses and playsets provide new stages for your dolls to play. Whether your girl is headstrong and wild or gentle and sweet, there\u2019s a doll out there that\u2019s the perfect fit for her. Let Amazon.com help you create precious memories for the little girl in your life.", "parent_text": "Toys & Games", "parent_catid": 130, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.9", "accessories": "0.3", "dolls": "0.9"}, "department_id": 12},
{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 151531, "catid": 603, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_165793011_nr_n_5?rh=n%3A165793011%2Cn%3A%21165795011%2Cn%3A166316011&bbn=165795011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=165795011", "text": "Dress Up & Pretend Play", "description_title": "Dress Up & Pretend Play from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/toys/b/ref=sd_allcat_tg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165793011", "keyword_count": {"play": 2, "dress": 8, "amazoncom": 1}, "description_wc": 303, "description_text": "Playing dress-up and make-believe are essential parts of childhood. They stretch the imagination, teach story-telling and social skills, and they're often great exercise. Now you can make your kids\u2019 fantasy world all the more real with the costumes and dress-up supplies from Amazon.com. The imaginary bad guys, dragons and bandits won\u2019t stand a chance with our arsenal of plastic swords, pistols, bows and arrows, shields, and superhero costumes. Watch you girl or boy\u2019s confidence grow as they don the mask of their favorite hero. We have costumes and dress-up accessories from your favorite movies and TV shows, including The Avengers, Star Wars, Sesame Street and more. We also have gowns and dresses for little girls to look like cherished Disney Princesses. Complete with our wigs and tiaras, your girl will never want to take off her royal attire. Playing dress-up in a sparkling princess dress creates the perfect opportunity to lift your girl and dance with her while she\u2019s still young enough to be picked up. Our accessories are fun for all occasions, or even when there\u2019s no occasion at all. See how much fun boys and girls will have trying on an assortment of mustaches, glasses, hats and hair-dos. But not all of our costumes and dress-up items are for kids; we also carry a wide variety of grown-up costumes for themed parties, Halloween and general silliness. If you\u2019re planning a birthday party, going to a themed dance or you simply want to have more fun with the kids at home, take a look at all the exciting dress-up items and accessories we have to offer. Be honest, wouldn\u2019t wearing a sparkling tiara or bushy black mustache make walking the dog a little more fun?", "parent_text": "Toys & Games", "parent_catid": 130, "keyword_density": {"play": "0.7", "dress": "2.6", "amazoncom": "0.3"}, "department_id": 12},
{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 173342, "catid": 604, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_165793011_nr_n_6?rh=n%3A165793011%2Cn%3A%21165795011%2Cn%3A166164011&bbn=165795011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=165795011", "text": "Electronics for Kids", "description_title": "Electronics for Kids from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/toys/b/ref=sd_allcat_tg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165793011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 1, "kids": 7, "electronics for kids": 5}, "description_wc": 284, "description_text": "It\u2019s no secret that technology is taking part in more and more aspects of our lives. Give you child a leg up on learning new technologies with fun and educational electronics for kids. We have simple toys for preschoolers and a wide selection of electronics for kids a little more mature. Our Vtech InnoTabs and LeapFrog LeapPads imitate popular tablet computers so your kids can feel tech-savvy. There are a vast number of educational games so boys and girls can solve math problems, learn plant and animal names, and solve a variety of other puzzles with their favorite characters from Pixar, Nickelodeon, Disney and more. Browse our electronics for kids and you\u2019ll find a digital camera perfectly suited to your child\u2019s personality. Watch as they become photographer in the making, taking snapshots of the family pet, house plants, friends and siblings. It\u2019s easy to upload the pictures onto your computer and then onto social media outlets so relatives hundreds of miles away can witness your boy or girl\u2019s masterpieces. Check out our Spy Net gear and walkie talkie radio systems to inspire a new interest of espionage and collusion in your little ones. These electronics for kids are perfect for the James Bond or Sherlock Holmes of the family. Planning objectives, looking for clues, writing covert messages in invisible ink and speaking through a voice scrambler will become your boy or girl\u2019s passion for weeks, if not months. With every technology in the world upgrading so rapidly, it\u2019s important for your kids to get a head start. Luckily, with Amazon.com\u2019s electronics for kids, we\u2019ve made it as easy and fun as possible to learn.", "parent_text": "Toys & Games", "parent_catid": 130, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.4", "kids": "2.5", "electronics for kids": "5.3"}, "department_id": 12},
{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 410307, "catid": 605, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_165793011_nr_n_7?rh=n%3A165793011%2Cn%3A%21165795011%2Cn%3A166220011&bbn=165795011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=165795011", "text": "Games", "description_title": "Games from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/toys/b/ref=sd_allcat_tg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165793011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "games": 13}, "description_wc": 348, "description_text": "Playing board games is an easy and fun way for the whole family to spend time together. Childhood is short, so it\u2019s important to spend time with your kids while they\u2019re still young. At Amazon.com we carry a wide variety of board games to play with your family and friends. We carry Fibber, Uno, Jenga, Spot It, The Sneaky Snacky Squirrel Game and a number of other board games that kids love. You won\u2019t need to beg your kids to stop watching TV or playing video games when you have our fun family games. They\u2019ll be begging you and all their friends to play along. For literary families, check out our collection of word-based board games, including Scrabble, Bananagrams, Boggle, Mad Gab, Scattergories and more. They also help you retain a wider vocabulary, so you can show off your word-smithing even when you\u2019re not playing. But not all of our games are for young kids. We also carry a huge selection of card games perfect for older kids, teens and adults. Cards against Humanity, Fluxx, Apples to Apples, Forbidden Island, and Munchkin Deluxe are all here in one easy-to-browse location for your convenience. If you\u2019re more into trading card games, we also have Magic: the Gathering, Pok\u00e9mon cards, Yu-Gi-Oh! and much more. They say playing games involving strategy and planning can help your brain stay as you age. Expand your mind with board games like Chess, Shogi, and Go. Shogi, also known as Japanese Chess, is a fun variation for fans of the western style of Chess. Many of the pieces move similarly, but with added pieces and extra rules, it\u2019s a fun way to re-inspire your old hobbies. Life\u2019s too short not to take a breather and have some fun. With creative board games like Telestrations and The Game of Things, you\u2019re bound to learn something new about your friends and family. Browse Amazon.com\u2019s wide selection of board games and you won\u2019t be disappointed in what you find.", "parent_text": "Toys & Games", "parent_catid": 130, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.6", "games": "3.7"}, "department_id": 12},
{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 252357, "catid": 606, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_165793011_nr_n_8?rh=n%3A165793011%2Cn%3A%21165795011%2Cn%3A3226142011&bbn=165795011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=165795011", "text": "Grown-Up Toys", "description_title": "Grown-Up Toys from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/toys/b/ref=sd_allcat_tg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165793011", "keyword_count": {"grown": 6, "amazoncom": 2, "grown up toys": 5}, "description_wc": 287, "description_text": "Fart machines, political toilet paper and fake poop; this is what being a grown-up is all about. Those long childhood days of eating broccoli because you had to, dreaming of a better life filled with waterslides, and staring longingly into candy shops are over. You\u2019ve paid your dues, now welcome to adulthood. You\u2019re free. Our grown-up toys, gags and novelties are sure to help you make up for lost time. Stink bombs, shocking gum, fake poop, all the things your mother never let you have are here for your enjoyment. We carry just about every gag and prank you can imagine, from exploding cigarettes to a remote control for your significant other. Just make sure that what you choose to do with your new grown-up toys isn\u2019t technically a misdemeanor. If you\u2019re not a fan of humor at another\u2019s expense, we also have a wide variety of board games and other grown-up toys. From tamer games like The Game of Things and Loaded Questions to something a little more risqu\u00e9, we have something for everybody. But games and jokes aren\u2019t the extent of our grown-up toys. With high quality vinyl collector dolls and figurines, Amazon.com is the perfect place to find a gift for the comic and movie fans on your gift list. Our figurines include favorite characters from Where the Wild Things Are, Dragon Ball Z, Marvel Comics, DC Comics, classic horror movies, The Hunger Games and even The Munsters. Whether you\u2019re grasping at your lost days of childhood or planning a hilarious night of drinks and Cards against Humanity, Amazon.com has all the grown-up toys you need to pull it off.", "parent_text": "Toys & Games", "parent_catid": 130, "keyword_density": {"grown": "2.1", "amazoncom": "0.7", "grown up toys": "5.2"}, "department_id": 12},
{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 237041, "catid": 607, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_165793011_nr_n_9?rh=n%3A165793011%2Cn%3A%21165795011%2Cn%3A276729011&bbn=165795011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=165795011", "text": "Hobbies", "description_title": "Hobbies from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/toys/b/ref=sd_allcat_tg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165793011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "hobbies": 7}, "description_wc": 327, "description_text": "Coin collecting, model train building, slot car racing and rocket-launching can be very relaxing and rewarding hobbies. At Amazon.com, we carry all the supplies and kits you need to start a new and fulfilling pastime. Driving RC cars, planes and helicopters inspire hours of play outdoors, and the world of collecting is a great place to meet others who share your hobbies. For collectors of baseball cards, Magic the Gathering cards, paper money, vintage photographs, postcards and manuscript rejection slips, we carry every size of plastic binder slips you could need. They\u2019re perfectly clear and sturdy so your treasures stay easy-to-see and protected. Whether you\u2019re just drawn to the esthetics of coins or you just plain love money, we also carry a variety of coin collecting supplies to make sure your Buffalo Nickel stays penned in and safe. Browse our die-cast vehicle collection and you\u2019ll find aircrafts, excavators, military vehicles, Harley Davidson models and more. Or if you need a little more horse-power from your hobbies, check out our radio controlled vehicles. Our wide selection of RC vehicles includes helicopters, cars, planes, boats, motorcycles and more. Driving and flying RC vehicles are the perfect hobbies for young racing enthusiasts. Bring your vehicles to a skate park and see how many jumps and flips you can perform with them. But once you sign for all the supplies you need for your hobbies, what\u2019s there to look forward to in the mail? Now you can replay the experience of receiving your Amazon.com packages again and again with our model UPS and USPS vehicles. Relive the excitement and anticipation whenever you need a pick-me-up with our highly detailed mail trucks. Immersing yourself in your hobbies is a great way to unwind after a long work day. Hobbies can even open new worlds for you, like meeting fellow enthusiasts, developing common pastimes with loved ones, and even inspiring new careers.", "parent_text": "Toys & Games", "parent_catid": 130, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.6", "hobbies": "2.1"}, "department_id": 12},
{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 108320, "catid": 608, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_165793011_nr_n_10?rh=n%3A165793011%2Cn%3A%21165795011%2Cn%3A166210011&bbn=165795011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=165795011", "text": "Kids' Furniture, D\u00e9cor & Storage", "description_title": "Kids\u2019 Furniture from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/toys/b/ref=sd_allcat_tg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165793011", "keyword_count": {"kids furniture from amazoncom": 1, "amazoncom": 2, "kids": 9, "furniture": 7, "kids furniture": 6}, "description_wc": 286, "description_text": "Fun and durable, the right kids' furniture will create a comfortable and engaging environment for your child to live and grow. Whether it's time to play dress-up and pretend or time to ride off to sleepy town, find the right kids' furniture from Amazon.com that can withstand the rough-and-tumble of growing children. Sorted into categories like chairs, nightstands, armoires, and dressers, you can filter through our large selection of kids' furniture and decor by material, color, brands, price, and more to narrow down your choice. Turn your child's bedroom into their own little world with personalized kids' furniture fit for little bodies and young minds. Featuring popular characters, brands, themes, and interests, our wide array of furniture for kids can create any environment you want. Pamper your little princess with pink, purple, pastel colors with their own Disney Princess themed hamper, dresser, vanity, and canopy bed. Let your kid be the superhero of his room with Superman, Batman, and Spiderman desks, flip sofas, and beds. And don't forget to teach organization with various storage chests, trunks, drawers, and bins for any stray toys, clothes, books, and shoes. Take furnishings and decoration one step further with kids' room decor from the floor to the walls and ceiling. Add whimsical wall stickers and decals as temporary decoration, easily applied and removed for growing tastes. Changing curtains, rugs, and lighting can easily set different tones and moods without having to replace large kids' furniture items. The ceiling's the limit with what you can create. From themed bunk beds to appealing kids' activity tables to colorful bookcases, give them a space of their own with Amazon.com, your one-stop shop for kids' furniture.", "parent_text": "Toys & Games", "parent_catid": 130, "keyword_density": {"kids furniture": "4.2", "kids furniture from amazoncom": "1.4", "amazoncom": "0.7", "kids": "3.1", "furniture": "2.4"}, "department_id": 12},
{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 82669, "catid": 609, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_165793011_nr_n_11?rh=n%3A165793011%2Cn%3A%21165795011%2Cn%3A166269011&bbn=165795011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=165795011", "text": "Learning & Education", "description_title": "Learning & Education Toys from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/toys/b/ref=sd_allcat_tg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165793011", "keyword_count": {"toys from amazoncom": 1, "amazoncom": 2, "education": 7, "learning": 4, "toys": 6}, "description_wc": 357, "description_text": "Instilling a love for learning and exploration early in a child\u2019s life is crucial for a bright future. Education is important to instill confidence and problem-solving skills in your boy or girl. With the educational toys from Amazon.com, we make it easy for you to give your kids a fun and encouraging learning experience. We provide everything they need for their academic futures. (Glasses, beards, and pocket protectors not included.) It\u2019s been said that many young adults can\u2019t find Iraq or Indonesia on a map of the world. Now you can put your kids ahead of the class with the educational toys at Amazon.com. Our spinning globes, motorized solar systems, and space theater planetariums will help you and your child get a better picture of our place in the universe. We also carry high-quality microscopes and telescopes for the little picture and big picture students. Our selection of microscope slides gives your child a peek into the secret lives of algae, starch, fungus, synthetic fibers, and more. Onions make great microscope slides; you\u2019ll be able to see the individual cells that make up the skin and roots. Our collection of scientific educational toys also includes many science experiments to grow crystals, build your own robot, make volcanoes, and construct complex electronic circuit boards. Magnetic poetry and journals are perfect educational toys for your future liberal arts major. Creating refrigerator haiku and recording them in brightly colored lock-and-key journals make reading and writing tons of fun. A high literacy rate is extremely important in learning how to express yourself well, and communicate effectively with everyone around you. The best thing about learning how to write well with our educational toys is that you\u2019ll never be bored; with just a pen and paper, you can create whole new universes, epic battles, romance stories, philosophical theses, and infinite other possibilities just by knowing how to use your mind. Whether your child is a future Einstein or Galileo, we have all the educational toys they could need to begin their academic journey. The only thing we don\u2019t offer is the diploma.", "parent_text": "Toys & Games", "parent_catid": 130, "keyword_density": {"toys from amazoncom": "0.8", "amazoncom": "0.6", "education": "2.0", "learning": "1.1", "toys": "1.7"}, "department_id": 12},
{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 95627, "catid": 610, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_165793011_nr_n_12?rh=n%3A165793011%2Cn%3A%21165795011%2Cn%3A166027011&bbn=165795011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=165795011", "text": "Novelty & Gag Toys", "description_title": "Novelty Toys from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/toys/b/ref=sd_allcat_tg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165793011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "novelty toys from amazoncom": 1}, "description_wc": 299, "description_text": "Laughter is the best medicine, and the doctor is in. Crack up your friends, and yourself, with the wide array of gags and novelty toys from Amazon.com. From fart whistles to rubber chickens \u2013 the pinnacle of humor technology \u2013 we have the perfect gear for the budding comedian. Who wouldn\u2019t be surprised to find their prescription bottles or toilet seat staring back at them? Our googly-eyes are perfect for turning any household objects into surprising and hilarious gags. Put them on the tip jar at work and watch the gratuities pour in, or on your child\u2019s night-light to make bedtime a little more fun. Our USB Pet Rocks are the perfect gags for your desk. They will confuse anyone who walks by your desk. When they ask what it does, keep the jokes going by simply telling them it does everything a regular pet rock does, only online. Floating eyeballs are also great for sneaking into a co-worker\u2019s coffee. If that's not enough office havoc for you, we have some gags that might be up your alley. The Devil Drive USB Flash Drive, a cunning piece of demonic fun, plugs in to laptops and desktop computers to cause a world of frustration. Programmable to ranges between 5 and 15 seconds, it toggles the caps lock key, types out random strings of words and garbage text on its own, and makes the mouse-cursor go wild. Just be sure whoever you prank has a good sense of humor and forgives people easily. No matter what level of prank or gag you\u2019re looking for, light-hearted or fiendish, Amazon.com has what you\u2019re looking for. Who knows, the right gags might even inspire a career change. What is the deal with airline food, anyways?", "parent_text": "Toys & Games", "parent_catid": 130, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.7", "novelty toys from amazoncom": "1.3"}, "department_id": 12},
{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 141921, "catid": 611, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_165793011_nr_n_13?rh=n%3A165793011%2Cn%3A%21165795011%2Cn%3A1266203011&bbn=165795011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=165795011", "text": "Party Supplies", "description_title": "Party Supplies from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/toys/b/ref=sd_allcat_tg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165793011", "keyword_count": {"party": 18, "amazoncom": 1, "party supplies": 8}, "description_wc": 322, "description_text": "A lot goes into planning and pulling off a fun, memorable party. From birthdays, to baby and wedding showers, to graduation celebrations, there\u2019s no end to the special occasions that deserve to be celebrated with a party, which means you\u2019ll need a steady source of party supplies to help make every event go smoothly. At Amazon.com, you\u2019ll find a wide variety of party supplies to make your next event go off without a hitch. Decorations, invitations, party favors, and tableware are all available in a range of styles and themes appropriate for any occasion. Liven up your party with balloons, streamers, banners, and other decorations, all matched to the theme and occasion you\u2019re after. You can use our helpful product filters to find party supplies that complement the look and feel of your celebration. Choose the colors, styles, themes, and even brands you\u2019re interested in, and we\u2019ll create a list of products that fit your criteria. No party is complete without games and activities, which is why we offer a full range of party supplies to help you organize fun group events for your guests. Classic kids\u2019 party games are great for younger party goers, and more mature adult games will keep their parents occupied for hours. If you\u2019re planning a fiesta, make sure you browse our selection of pi\u00f1atas. You can make party planning fast and easy with complete kits of party supplies, available in coordinated colors and themes. Paper plates and cups, napkins, tablecloths, and decorations pre-selected and packaged together make choosing party supplies a breeze. For planning kids\u2019 birthdays, graduation parties, or baby showers, these coordinated kits save time, and make hosting a fantastic party easier than ever. Throw the party of the year with fun and functional party supplies. For kids and adults alike, decorative party supplies that complement the occasion can be a memorable addition to your celebration.", "parent_text": "Toys & Games", "parent_catid": 130, "keyword_density": {"party": "5.6", "amazoncom": "0.3", "party supplies": "5.0"}, "department_id": 12},
{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 67217, "catid": 612, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_165793011_nr_n_14?rh=n%3A165793011%2Cn%3A%21165795011%2Cn%3A166359011&bbn=165795011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=165795011", "text": "Puzzles", "description_title": "Puzzles from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/toys/b/ref=sd_allcat_tg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165793011", "keyword_count": {"puzzles": 11, "amazoncom": 1}, "description_wc": 303, "description_text": "Solving puzzles and brain teasers are important activities to teach kids to work hard at solving complex problems. At Amazon.com, we carry a wide selection of jigsaw puzzles, brain teasers, pegged puzzles, mazes, and more. Solving Jigsaw puzzles is also a great activity to do with your kids while you talk. Our brain teasers include tangram puzzles, ball mazes, wooden interlocking puzzles, and a variety of other mind bogglers and conundrums. Traditional Rubik\u2019s Cubes too easy for you? Challenge yourself with puzzles ranging from 4x4x4 to 7x7x7 cubes. Not mathematically adept? The world\u2019s biggest crossword puzzle is a perfect gift for the word-smith of the family. We also carry a wide variety of 3-D puzzles. We have models of the New York skyline, the Whitehouse, the Chrysler Building, the London Tower Bridge, Cinderella\u2019s Castle, and much more for the homesick, the travelers, and the wishful thinkers. We even have 3-D puzzles of skulls and dinosaur skeletons which make perfect desk ornaments for students of the natural sciences. Completing Sudoku puzzles provides excellent exercise for your brain. Our wide selection of Sudoku sets, including electronic sets, wooden sets, cubes, and even toilet paper, ensures hours and hours of playing time wherever you go. Having trouble solving that tile? I\u2019ll give you a hint: it\u2019s a number between one and nine. We even have large-print booklets and thick Sudoku collections that make perfect coffee-table books. Whether you\u2019re trying to stretch your brain capacity or spending some leisure time with your loved ones, we have something for you. It doesn\u2019t matter if you\u2019re vying to beat the Rubik\u2019s Cube world record, or you\u2019ve never penciled-in a Sudoku puzzle in your life, we have puzzles and brain teasers for every level.", "parent_text": "Toys & Games", "parent_catid": 130, "keyword_density": {"puzzles": "3.6", "amazoncom": "0.3"}, "department_id": 12},
{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 77293, "catid": 613, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_165793011_nr_n_15?rh=n%3A165793011%2Cn%3A%21165795011%2Cn%3A166420011&bbn=165795011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=165795011", "text": "Sports & Outdoor Play", "description_title": "Sports & Outdoor Play from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/toys/b/ref=sd_allcat_tg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165793011", "keyword_count": {"play": 3, "outdoor": 6, "amazoncom": 2, "sports": 1}, "description_wc": 295, "description_text": "It\u2019s crucial to learn to enjoy exercise at an early age. It supports a healthy life style and helps develop sportsmanship and confidence. What, with TV and computers taking more and more of our time, it\u2019s nice to be able to go outside with some outdoor toys from Amazon.com and rediscover the joys of parks and playgrounds. Our bikes, tricycles, scooters, and other ride-ons make the perfect outdoor toys to inspire healthy hobbies. We carry fun styles, colors, and shapes so younger kids can feel cool on their new wheels. Don\u2019t forget the helmets, elbow pads, knee pads, and gloves to make sure biking and playing outside stays harmless and fun. You, a few friends, foam-blasting outdoor toys, and a local playground are the only ingredients needed for an epic all-out war. Since the darts and rockets are made of foam, they\u2019re safe and fun for kids too. If you don\u2019t already have a foam blaster at your office, consider getting one. They\u2019re great for blasting away at the sales staff from the safety of your cubicle. Once you and the kids have worked up a sweat, why not cool down with our sprinklers, kiddie pools, and other water-based outdoor toys? We have everything you need to cool down in style from geyser blast sprinklers and Super Soakers, to inner tubes and inflatable whales. Our beach-balls and sand buckets are great for the beach. Remember how fun it used to be to run around outside with your friends? Well, what\u2019s changed? The outdoor toys from Amazon.com will help you reconnect with your inner wild-child. So put on your sunscreen, tighten your laces, and check out the outdoor toys we have to offer.", "parent_text": "Toys & Games", "parent_catid": 130, "keyword_density": {"play": "1.0", "outdoor": "2.0", "amazoncom": "0.7", "sports": "0.3"}, "department_id": 12},
{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 154830, "catid": 614, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_165793011_nr_n_16?rh=n%3A165793011%2Cn%3A%21165795011%2Cn%3A166461011&bbn=165795011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=165795011", "text": "Stuffed Animals & Plush", "description_title": "Stuffed Animals from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/toys/b/ref=sd_allcat_tg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165793011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 1, "stuffed animals": 4, "stuffed": 5}, "description_wc": 238, "description_text": "Do you remember cuddling up with your favorite stuffed animals, listening to a goodnight story or the rain patter softly against the windowpanes? A good stuffed animal means comfort; it means long, peaceful nights and slow, warm days at home. At Amazon.com, we appreciate the special role stuffed animals play in all of our lives from infancy all the way to your 60th anniversary. When you browse our teddy bears, you\u2019re really browsing for a companion to cuddle and watch movies with. Browse our teddy bears, and you\u2019ll come across a mate whose personality resounds with yours. Dopey bears, droopy bears, shaggy bears, white bears, brown bears, bears that look like primped poodles, and squashed little bears with a hump in their back; you\u2019ll find these and more in our collection of stuffed animals. Also check out our selection of plushies that turn from pets into pillows. They\u2019re perfect for cuddling up and going to bed with during a reading of Goodnight Moon, or Where the Wild Things Are. We have quite the menagerie, including monkeys, moose, bears, zebras, ladybugs, and dragons. We even carry favorite characters from children\u2019s books like Clifford the Big Red Dog. There\u2019s nothing that\u2019s more fun to unwrap during the holidays or on a birthday than big, cozy stuffed animals. Browse our assortment today for the perfect gift, and the perfect friend, for your loved ones.", "parent_text": "Toys & Games", "parent_catid": 130, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.4", "stuffed animals": "3.4", "stuffed": "2.1"}, "department_id": 12},
{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 52648, "catid": 615, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_165793011_nr_n_17?rh=n%3A165793011%2Cn%3A%21165795011%2Cn%3A256994011&bbn=165795011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=165795011", "text": "Tricycles, Scooters & Wagons", "description_title": "Kids\u2019 Bikes from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/toys/b/ref=sd_allcat_tg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165793011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "kids": 9, "kids bikes from amazoncom": 1, "kids bikes": 5}, "description_wc": 318, "description_text": "Watch your kids zoom off into the sunset with their first kids\u2019 bikes and ride-on toys they\u2019ll remember forever. Amazon.com\u2019s large selection of kids\u2019 bikes, trikes, and other ride-on toys will have your little ones zipping around indoors and out. From classic red wagons, to electronic Jeeps, balanced scooters, and learning tricycles, easily find the best kids\u2019 bike for your child by age range, gender, featured brands, interests, price, and more. With several affordable and fast shipping options, have it delivered straight to your door and put money saved towards a family vacation fund. Perfect for riding around the neighborhood, park, or block, tricycles are a great stepping stone for \u201cgrown up\u201d kids\u2019 bikes they aren\u2019t ready for yet. Low to the ground and stable, tricycles have easy-to-grip handles, good turning, and heavy traction wheels that keep your kid in control at all times. Or try a balance bike or tricycle that will grow with your child, featuring handle attachments, extendable columns, and combination models. With different wheel and frame sizes available, it\u2019s easy to sort through our Kids\u2019 Bikes store for what works best for your kids, from their first steps to their first mountain bike. Don\u2019t forget to keep a variety of helmets, knee pads, and other safety gear available for any trip. We also offer various wagons, scooters, and other ride-on toys that are fun to play with while safe enough for young children. From basic ride-on toys to electronic toys and lightweight scooters, there are many different ways to let your kids play around. Play cops and robbers with a replica police pedal car, lean back with big wheel riders, or race friends with low scoot seats. Indulge in fun kids\u2019 bikes from Amazon.com now and watch them grow\u2014next thing you know, they\u2019ll be asking for the keys to the car.", "parent_text": "Toys & Games", "parent_catid": 130, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.6", "kids": "2.8", "kids bikes from amazoncom": "1.3", "kids bikes": "3.1"}, "department_id": 12},
{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 93338, "catid": 616, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_165793011_nr_n_18?rh=n%3A165793011%2Cn%3A%21165795011%2Cn%3A166508011&bbn=165795011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=165795011", "text": "Toy Remote Control & Play Vehicles", "description_title": "Play Vehicles and Remote Control from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/toys/b/ref=sd_allcat_tg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165793011", "keyword_count": {"control": 1, "amazoncom": 1, "vehicles": 6}, "description_wc": 317, "description_text": "Since the invention of the first internal combustion engine in 1807, self-propelled vehicles have captured the imaginations of people all around the world. Whether you\u2019re into engineering, design, or break-neck speeds, modern vehicles are marvels of human endeavor. With the die-cast and RC vehicles from Amazon.com, you can appreciate the culmination of hundreds of years\u2019 worth of discovery and invention in the palm of your hand. Our die-cast models are perfect for kids and collectors alike. Browse our seemingly endless supply of Hot Wheels. They fit perfectly into our many Hot Wheels race courses, jumps, and looping tracks for endless fun. Collectors will be happy to find a wide variety of highly-detailed cars, trucks, planes, industrial vehicles, and much more waiting for them in our online store. If you\u2019re in the market for something with a little more 'oomph,' check out our RC cars and trucks. These high-octane machines will have everyone at the park uttering oohs and ahhs. Do tricks, flips, and jumps with our collection of RC vehicles from Mattel, Kid Galaxy, Air Hogs, Maisto, and more. Or leave the road behind altogether with our RC helicopters and planes. Relive the excitement of World War I dogfights with our old-fashioned propeller planes. Do a barrel role! Learn how to do all sorts of tricks with our model planes. Airlift action figures out of the sandbox with our RC helicopters to prepare for a career in rescue services. Our Air Swimmers, RC zeppelins shaped like sharks and other fish, are perfect for kids just learning how to control RC vehicles. Whether you want a model to place on a shelf, looking pretty and shiny for years to come, or an RC vehicle to zoom around the block, we have something for you. Browse our toy selection today and you might just find the thrill of your life.", "parent_text": "Toys & Games", "parent_catid": 130, "keyword_density": {"control": "0.3", "amazoncom": "0.3", "vehicles": "1.9"}, "department_id": 12},
{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 124285, "catid": 617, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A165796011%2Cn%3A%21165797011%2Cn%3A196601011&bbn=165797011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833288&rnid=165797011", "text": "Baby & Toddler Toys", "description_title": "Infant Toys from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/baby-car-seats-strollers-bedding/b/ref=sd_allcat_ba/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165796011", "keyword_count": {"infant toys from amazoncom": 2, "infant": 9, "infant toys": 6, "toys": 10}, "description_wc": 311, "description_text": "Experts say that play is the best way to learn, and now with the quality infant toys from Amazon.com, you can make sure your kids get all the educational playtime they need during their most developmental stages. Musical and sound-making infant toys are popular and fun. They can come with a variety of buttons, pulleys and other features to make the toys roar, squeak, chirp, and more. Our musical toddler toys are great for providing a beat that your child can dance to when they\u2019re energetic. Others play softer lullabies that can be used to soothe them to sleep, and when they do, we have all the plush and stuffed animals your infant or toddler could want to cuddle up with. Stacking and nesting infant toys can help your little one develop valuable motor skills and pattern recognition. On many models, your child will be encouraged to stack their pieces in order from large to small, or based on shape and color. They\u2019ll be absorbed in their game, trying to sort out all the brightly colored pieces in order to complete the puzzle. If you\u2019re puzzling over how to find affordable toys, try filtering your search by price to see the most budget-friendly toddler and infant toys we have available. Many infants, and even some toddlers, love to put their toys, clothes or random found objects in their mouths. For that, we carry many different sizes and styles of teethers. These infant toys are especially designed to be safe and comforting for your baby to chew on. You can choose from a variety of materials, so if your baby prefers softer chewing materials like fluid-filled plastics, we have just the items for them. Infants and toddlers learn at quick speeds, and now you can give them a little more inspiration with infant toys from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Baby", "parent_catid": 131, "keyword_density": {"infant toys": "3.9", "infant": "2.9", "infant toys from amazoncom": "2.6", "toys": "3.2"}, "department_id": 12},
{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 3258, "catid": 618, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A165796011%2Cn%3A%21165797011%2Cn%3A405369011&bbn=165797011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833288&rnid=165797011", "text": "Baby Stationery", "description_title": "Baby Stationery from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/baby-car-seats-strollers-bedding/b/ref=sd_allcat_ba/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165796011", "keyword_count": {"baby": 11, "baby stationery": 6, "amazoncom": 4, "baby stationery from amazoncom": 1}, "description_wc": 292, "description_text": "Whether you\u2019re ready to tell the world you\u2019re expecting a wee one or are already drafting the invitations for baby\u2019s first birthday bash, the right baby stationery can set the mood you want for your birth announcements, baby showers, family parties, and birthdays. At Amazon.com, we feature many different birth announcement and invitation styles, designs, and looks to match your personality. From balloon embellishments and adorable animals to classic, clean lines and photo cards, easily filter through our collection of birth announcements and baby shower invitations by shipping options, customer review, brands, and more to easily refine your search. Or browse hundreds of choices for what stands out to you. You can even filter by price and discount for wallet-friendly baby stationery that won\u2019t break the bank. If the shower is over and the gift wrap has all been thrown away, you can find the perfect thank you cards on Amazon.com\u2019s Baby Stationery Store. Our selection of thank you cards comes in all shapes, sizes, themes, and interests. From pink butterflies and classic patterns to baby clothes laundry lines and diaper shapes, we offer a variety of styles so you can personalize them to your own tastes and preferences. From colorful, sweet invitations and announcements to baby shower games and new mommy advice cards, find the baby stationery you want on Amazon.com. We feature a variety of birth announcements, invitations, and thank you cards ready for whatever event you\u2019re planning. And with many affordable and convenient shipping options, it\u2019s easier than ever to have the baby stationery you want delivered straight to your door. With the right baby stationery from Amazon.com, you can be ready and stress-free for showers, announcements, and thank yous.", "parent_text": "Baby", "parent_catid": 131, "keyword_density": {"baby": "3.8", "baby stationery": "4.1", "amazoncom": "1.4", "baby stationery from amazoncom": "1.4"}, "department_id": 12},
