{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 2075, "catid": 627, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_11?rh=n%3A165796011%2Cn%3A%21165797011%2Cn%3A166887011&bbn=165797011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833288&rnid=165797011", "text": "Potty Training", "description_title": "Potty Training from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/baby-car-seats-strollers-bedding/b/ref=sd_allcat_ba/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=165796011", "keyword_count": {"potty training": 7, "potty": 9, "training": 10, "amazoncom": 3}, "description_wc": 320, "description_text": "If it's time to start the transition to potty training, look to Amazon.com for all your baby essentials to ease the change. From packs of night-time training pants and disposable potty liners to step-up stools and cushioned seats, we feature a wide selection of potty training supplies that make it easier on you and your little ones. Sorted into convenient categories like seat covers, step stools, travel potties, training pants, and potties and seats, all your potty training necessities are just a click away. With well-known brands like Pampers, Arm & Hammer, and Fisher-Price, it's easy to shop for all your favorites from the comfort of your home. Great for babies of all sizes and ages, Amazon.com's variety of potty training supplies will help keep your bathroom clean and ready for whatever is to come. With detailed product descriptions, large photos, and many options to choose from, easily filter by customer rating, shipping options, featured brands, and more to quickly refine your search. You can also filter by price and discount for wallet- and baby-friendly choices. With your baby and the earth in mind, we also offer natural and organic products. No matter where you are with potty training, make sure to stock up on extra supplies, so you are never left high and dry at a critical time. We bring you quality and trusted products designed to hold up to the wear-and-tear of growing up. Character