{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 23, "catid": 634, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_471306_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A468642%2Cn%3A%2144263011%2Cn%3A471306%2Cn%3A6427814011&bbn=471306&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=11846801", "text": "PlayStation 4", "description_title": "PlayStation 4 from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Kids-Family/b/ref=sd_allcat_cvg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=471306", "keyword_count": {"playstation": 7, "amazoncom": 3, "playstation 4": 4, "4": 10}, "description_wc": 378, "description_text": "The long-awaited release of the PlayStation 4 is at hand. Amazon.com carries PlayStation 4 consoles, games, and accessories to ensure you can experience the new generation of Sony\u2019s popular gaming system at its best. We have a variety of PlayStation 4 bundles to choose from. Standard editions include a console along with a wireless controller, while special bundles can also come with a new game and a gift card for $10 off your first year of PlayStation Plus, so you can start enjoying the benefits of membership right away. The PS4 will be able to play Blu-ray and DVDs and connect to a variety of online content, including a game store where you can download games directly to the PS4\u2019s 500GB hard drive. This time it features sharing capabilities to show your game-playing highlights on social media channels, as well as compatibility with the handheld PlayStation Vita console so you can play your favorite PS4 games remotely, and much more. Amazon.com offers a great selection of PS4 games to choose from, made by some of the most popular game companies out there. Previous PlayStations have been known for their popular RPGs and adventure games, and the PS4 is breaking ground by hosting long awaited sequels, such as Final Fantasy XV, Assassin\u2019s Creed IV: Black Flag, Oddworld: New \u2018n\u2019 Tasty, and Kingdom Hearts III, which include rich casts of characters, fun puzzles, and jaw-dropping cinematic sequences. Some of the most popular first-person shooters are also rushing out on the market with exciting new installations, including Call of Duty and Battlefield, so you can blitz into war zones to fight a vast array of enemies while accomplishing objectives. Other highly anticipated releases include Killzone Shadow Fall, Infamous Second Son, Knack, Destiny, Watch Dogs, Drive Club, and The Order: 1886. Sports lovers will also find the games they\u2019re looking for on the new PS4. A new generation of turf-thrashing, court-dominating sports games will come with all the action you\u2019ve learned to love on previous systems, but with better graphics, updated player rankings, and more. You can find everything you\u2019ll need to enjoy the next generation of gaming technology, including the PlayStation 4 console, games, and accessories, at Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Video Games for Kids", "parent_catid": 134, "keyword_density": {"playstation": "1.9", "amazoncom": "0.8", "playstation 4": "2.1", "4": "2.6"}, "department_id": 12},
{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 1319, "catid": 635, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_471306_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A468642%2Cn%3A%2144263011%2Cn%3A471306%2Cn%3A14210751&bbn=471306&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=11846801", "text": "PlayStation 3", "description_title": "PlayStation 3 from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Kids-Family/b/ref=sd_allcat_cvg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=471306", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "playstation 3": 8, "3": 11}, "description_wc": 342, "description_text": "The Sony PlayStation 3 is one of the most advanced gaming consoles ever produced. Cutting edge 3D graphics, 5.1 surround digital audio, fully integrated wireless networking, and a dozen other features make it a popular choice among gamers. The PlayStation 3 can do more than just play video games, too. With a Blu-Ray player and hard disk drives up to 500GB, this console is a complete home entertainment unit, capable of playing HD movies, streaming media content from your home computer, and even browsing the internet. At Amazon.com, we offer a complete line of PlayStation 3 consoles, games, and accessories to satisfy gamers, movie watchers, and media streamers alike. You\u2019ll find bestselling PlayStation 3 classics, new releases, and hard to find titles from popular developers like AcTiVision, Ubisoft, and Square Enix across all genres, from FPS to RPGs. To find PlayStation 3 games that you\u2019re interested in, you can use our fast and easy product filters. Choose the developers, genres, ESRB ratings, and release dates you want to browse, and we\u2019ll automatically create a list of games that meet your criteria. If you\u2019re looking to pick up accessories and add-ons for your PS3, you can browse our selection of PlayStation 3 controllers, keyboards, remotes, and more. The original Sony Dualshock controller is a time tested and well-loved peripheral. You\u2019ll find Dualshock and Sixaxis controllers in a wide variety of colors, including brilliant white, satin reds and blues, and even metallic silver and gold. If you\u2019re shopping for your first PlayStation 3, you\u2019ll find a wide selection of consoles to choose from, including Slim models with hard drive space ranging from 160 to 500GB. Many new games are downloadable, so larger hard drives are a must-have for avid gamers. The Sony PlayStation 3 is more than a simple gaming console. The PS3 is an all-in-one entertainment hub for games, movies, and more. Amazon.com carries the consoles, games, and accessories you need to enjoy one of the most popular gaming consoles.", "parent_text": "Video Games for Kids", "parent_catid": 134, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.6", "playstation 3": "4.7", "3": "3.2"}, "department_id": 12},
