{"department_text": "Toys, Kids & Baby", "nr_products": 59, "catid": 639, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_471306_nr_n_5?rh=n%3A468642%2Cn%3A%2144263011%2Cn%3A471306%2Cn%3A3075112011&bbn=471306&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=11846801", "text": "Wii U", "description_title": "Wii U Games from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Kids-Family/b/ref=sd_allcat_cvg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=471306", "keyword_count": {"u": 60, "wii u games": 6, "games": 11, "wii u": 10, "wii u games from amazoncom": 2}, "description_wc": 333, "description_text": "The next generation of Nintendo is finally here. You can welcome this new bundle of joy to your home with the long-awaited Wii U games from Amazon.com. The new touch-screen built within the controller allows for a whole new way to experience Nintendo games and interact with your surroundings. We have a wide variety of Wii U games to choose from. If there are Wii U games coming up that you have to have, many of our titles are available for pre-order, so whether you\u2019re buying Wii U games as a gift or for yourself, you can ensure you get your copy. When you hear about Mario Kart 8, or the new characters that have been announced for the upcoming Super Smash Brothers, you\u2019ll be glad we\u2019re offering you the option. The Wii U is already seeing a resurgence of some of the most popular Nintendo games. If you loved hurling plant-people at monsters before, the new installation of Pikmin, with better graphics and plenty of surprises could be a great choice for you. If you miss the long, sunny days spent grass-slashing and breaking pottery in a hunt for wild rupees, the high-definition remake of Zelda: The Windwaker could be the Wii U game for you. There are also many exciting Wii U games coming out from a variety of other developers. Activision\u2019s popular Call of Duty: Black Ops II offers everything you need to run through rough terrain, snipe enemies and deftly achieve demanding objectives. Since the Wii U is Nintendo\u2019s next generation gaming system, new games are coming out all the time, and you can find racing games, first-person shooters, fighting games and much more with fantastic graphics and touch-screen enhanced gameplay. Since the Wii U is so new, it has a lot to look forward to. You can experience all the best moments of this gaming system\u2019s life with the Wii U games from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Video Games for Kids", "parent_catid": 134, "keyword_density": {"games": "3.3", "wii u games": "5.4", "u": "18.0", "wii u": "6.0", "wii u games from amazoncom": "3.0"}, "department_id": 12},
