{"department_text": "Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry", "nr_products": 48647, "catid": 651, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1036592_nr_n_3?rh=n%3A1036592%2Cn%3A%211036682%2Cn%3A1040666&bbn=1036682&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833285&rnid=1036682", "text": "Boys", "description_title": "Boys\u2019 Clothing from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/clothing-accessories-men-women-kids/b/ref=sd_allcat_apr/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=1036592", "keyword_count": {"boys": 7, "boys clothing": 6, "amazoncom": 2}, "description_wc": 340, "description_text": "Whether you\u2019re looking for lightweight, activewear for your boy for running and playing, or straight-leg chinos and button-down shirts for an upcoming special event, Amazon.com carries boys\u2019 clothing for your choice of season, occasion, and function. Our selection of boys\u2019 clothing includes a wide variety of boys\u2019 tops for you to choose from. We offer a large selection of T-shirts that are perfect for a growing boy\u2019s wardrobe, including comfortable, and breathable styles great for sports, school, and casual events. The crisp collars of our polo shirts can add a touch of maturity, and they\u2019re easy to layer under cardigans or over long-sleeved T-shirts for added warmth. Our Boys\u2019 Clothing Store also offers a wide selection of button-down and dress shirts for your little guy to wear during formal occasions. You can also combine an open button-down shirt over a T-shirt for a playful, light-hearted look. Once you\u2019ve picked out tops for your little guy, you can also shop for bottoms. We carry many pants, shorts, and activewear among our boys\u2019 clothing. You can choose from durable and long-lasting blue jeans for a relaxed look, cargo pants for an adventurous and outdoorsy look, and chinos for a versatile look that can go with formal and casual apparel. For bright and sunny afternoons, we also have many brilliantly colored, durable shorts to inspire play and fun. Our activewear can also ensure that your little guy will stay comfortable during sports and outdoor activities. We also have a variety of boys\u2019 clothing to suit any kind of weather. If your boy loves to cool off during the summer by doing cannonballs into pools or leaping into the waves of the ocean, we have a range of swim trunks fit for several occasions. Our sweaters and coats can help your little guy stay toasty and warm during breezy evenings and chilly nights. It\u2019s easy to find boys\u2019 clothing in a range of colors, styles, and brands at Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Clothing", "parent_catid": 138, "keyword_density": {"boys": "2.1", "boys clothing": "3.5", "amazoncom": "0.6"}, "department_id": 13},
{"department_text": "Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry", "nr_products": 78402, "catid": 652, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1036592_nr_n_4?rh=n%3A1036592%2Cn%3A%211036682%2Cn%3A2402554011&bbn=1036682&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833285&rnid=1036682", "text": "Baby", "description_title": "Baby Clothes from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/clothing-accessories-men-women-kids/b/ref=sd_allcat_apr/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=1036592", "keyword_count": {"baby clothes": 7, "baby": 11, "amazoncom": 4, "baby clothes from amazoncom": 1}, "description_wc": 307, "description_text": "Dressing up your little one should offer convenience and comfort, so Amazon.com has combed the wide world of baby clothes to offer soft, playful, and totally kid-friendly threads worth loving. From bodysuits and rompers to dresses and suits sets, we offer baby clothes for all sorts of little ones. With our easy-to-browse search categories for baby girls, baby boys, and unisex baby clothes, choosing the right wardrobe for your mini marvel is quick and painless. You can narrow your search by size, silhouette style, and even by price. And because we know that comfort and convenience is premium for baby, we've gathered quality baby clothes from name brands like Absorba, Zutano, Calvin Klein, and many more. We feature handy baby clothes categories so you can choose from sets or separates. You can doll up your little lady with dress sets that come complete with diaper covers and crochet headbands, or you can sharpen your little man's look with a one-piece romper complete with pull-on elastic waistband pants. And because you might want to take your little one to the pool for some summer fun, we've even got swim sets complete with diaper seams. From ruffles to rough-and-tumble, Amazon.com offers baby clothing suited for your preferences, whether it's a twirl-worthy tutu, an adventure-ready tee, a novelty bodysuit, a classic puff-sleeve top, or an organic fabric. If your baby clothes don't exactly fit your needs, you can easily return them with our free shipping and free returns on eligible items. Lap necks, snap closures, and elastic waistbands all add ease to your life?shopping at Amazon.com offers another convenience. Thanks to the wide selection of baby clothes from Amazon.com, snapping a little one into comfort is as easy as the click of a button.", "parent_text": "Clothing", "parent_catid": 138, "keyword_density": {"baby clothes": "4.6", "baby": "3.6", "amazoncom": "1.3", "baby clothes from amazoncom": "1.3"}, "department_id": 13},
