terior of quality handbags often matters just as much as what's on the outside. That's why our offerings allow you a visual peek inside your selection while also offering reliable dimensions. These features allow you to rely on our selection of handbags for coordinating lining and the right amount of pocket space. And, if your new handbag doesn't work out, you can return it using our free returns on eligible items. When you find that perfect-for-you handbag, it can be timeless. From party-ready clutches and evening bags to day-perfect totes and shoulder bags, browse our sure-to-please selection of long-lasting handbags from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Clothing", "parent_catid": 138, "keyword_density": {"handbags from amazoncom": "0.8", "handbags": "1.6"}, "department_id": 13},
