{"department_text": "Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry", "nr_products": 200976, "catid": 675, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_3367581_nr_n_8?rh=n%3A3367581%2Cn%3A%213880591%2Cn%3A3888431&bbn=3880591&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833286&rnid=3880591", "text": "Accessories", "description_title": "Jewelry Accessories from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/jewelry/b/ref=sd_allcat_jewelry/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=3367581", "keyword_count": {"jewelry accessories from amazoncom": 1, "amazoncom": 2, "jewelry accessories": 6, "jewelry": 19, "accessories": 7}, "description_wc": 315, "description_text": "Protect your fashion investments with jewelry accessories like jewelry boxes, cleaners, and other storage to make your jewelry continue to sparkle on you and in the box. From jewelry boxes and organizers to cleaning and care products to gem testers and balances, Amazon.com has all the jewelry accessories you need to safely store, maintain, and display your collection. Featuring popular brands and designers like Household Essentials, Blitz USA, 1928 Jewelry, and Lori Bonn, you can rest assured knowing you\u2019re getting high quality and sought-after products, and with our convenient free shipping and return options on eligible items, it\u2019s easy to exchange if you get another jewelry organizing brainstorm. One of the most important jewelry accessories is a jewelry box, or a jewelry armoire, curio, or other mode of storage. Whether you want a warm wooden box with multiple pull drawers and compartments, a hanging jewelry organizer for all your necklaces, a back-of-the-door mirror cabinet, or a handsome standing armoire, you have many options to keep your jewelry well-organized and protected. If you travel often and need to bring your accessories with you, use travel-safe holders and organizers that keep your jewelry from moving and falling out. Small pouches and gift bags also make it easy to move a few small items around, or as present holders to friends and family. We carry other jewelry accessories such as cleaning supplies, polishing cloths, ultrasonic cleaners, sprays, solutions, and brushes for all types of jewelry to remove dirt, scratches, and other effects of daily wear. For diamonds and other precious metals and gems, you\u2019ll find we carry the specialized jewelry accessories and cleaners for good care and maintenance of your precious jewelry. Whether you wear jewelry all the time or just for special occasions, jewelry accessories from Amazon.com will make your bracelets, necklaces, earrings, and other pieces last longer.", "parent_text": "Jewelry", "parent_catid": 143, "keyword_density": {"accessories": "2.2", "jewelry": "6.0", "amazoncom": "0.6", "jewelry accessories from amazoncom": "1.3", "jewelry accessories": "3.8"}, "department_id": 13},
