 treat to your mornings without taking up much time. If you\u2019re always in a rush in the morning and need quick breakfast foods to take on the go, cereal and breakfast bars could be ideal to fill up in the morning. Breakfast bars feature crunchy nuts, sweet chunks of chocolate, chewy oats, real fruit and berry pieces, and more to give you a burst of energy when you need it. They pack easily, so you can keep a few in your office, purse, and glove compartment for quick bites whenever and wherever you need it. Stay full, energized, and healthy with breakfast foods from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Natural & Organic", "parent_catid": 125, "keyword_density": {"breakfast": "3.2", "breakfast foods from amazoncom": "2.3", "breakfast foods": "3.5"}, "department_id": 11},
