{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 143717, "catid": 685, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_2617941011_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A2617941011%2Cn%3A%212617942011%2Cn%3A2747968011&bbn=2617942011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833318&rnid=2617942011", "text": "Art Supplies", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Art Supplies from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Arts-Crafts-Sewing/b/ref=sd_allcat_sch/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2617941011", "keyword_count": {"art supplies": 4, "amazoncom": 2, "art": 10}, "description_wc": 332, "description_text": "Kurt Vonnegut said that practicing an art-- no matter how well or badly--is a way to make your soul grow. Whether you\u2019re a professional illustrator or a novice painter, you\u2019re looking for the art supplies your soul needs to gain a few inches. Anyone can begin to be an artist and our art supply selection is sure to get your creative juices flowing. Look through our selection of pens, including Sakura micron pens which are increasingly popular among cartoonists and illustrators. Pencils come in every variety of hardness, from the hardest lead, 9H, to the softest, 9B, and everything in between. Charcoal is also a fun medium to work in if you like getting your hands dirty. Charcoal lines look rugged and bold, making portraits and landscapes look dramatic. Every different tool has a different effect on the picture and on your audience. Amazon.com\u2019s Art Supply Store also carries a veritable rainbow of paint colors and varieties. Watercolors are a great paint for beginners and students. They\u2019re easy to mix, dry quickly, and are easily cleaned up if spilled on the table. Acrylics are great for quick-drying, bright pictures, and oils are ideal for capturing color depth and texture. We have just about every brush you could need in our art supplies, including assorted packs of brushes for the prolific painter. We even have your needs for easels, paper and notebooks covered. Our real-canvas easels come pre-stretched into frames or in un-primed rolls if you want to fit it over unconventional frame sizes. Watercolor paper, drawing paper, newspaper stock, sketch pads, Bristol board and more can be found in our art supplies. For artists on the go, we have a variety of Moleskine notebooks. Our shipping options ensure hassle-free shipping for larger items. When your soul needs a little exercise, Amazon.com is here for you. Our art supplies will keep you creating and stretching your imagination for a long time to come.", "parent_text": "Arts, Crafts & Sewing", "parent_catid": 111, "keyword_density": {"art": "3.0", "amazoncom": "0.6", "art supplies": "2.4"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 344492, "catid": 686, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_2617941011_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A2617941011%2Cn%3A%212617942011%2Cn%3A12896081&bbn=2617942011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833318&rnid=2617942011", "text": "Beading & Jewelry-Making", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Beading Supplies from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Arts-Crafts-Sewing/b/ref=sd_allcat_sch/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2617941011", "keyword_count": {"supplies": 7, "amazoncom": 2, "beading": 7, "beading supplies": 6, "beading supplies from amazoncom": 1}, "description_wc": 369, "description_text": "Have you ever been browsing for earrings and necklaces and thought: \u201cI could make that?\u201d Our beading supplies can inspire you to do just that. Stringing beads stretches your creativity in a constructive way, and leaves you with beautiful, personalized fashion accessories. Make your own unique fashion accessories you\u2019ll be proud to show off. Create necklaces, anklets, bracelets, earrings, and much more with the beading supplies from Amazon.com. Our beading supplies come in a wide assortment of colors, shapes, sizes and materials. If you\u2019re not sure what kind of jewelry you want to make, we have big kits of supplies full of a wide variety of starting materials. You can also buy packs of specific styles of beads in case you already have a creative plan for your beading project. Choose from Czech glass beads, Tibetan prayer beads, a variety of pendants, gold-plated rondelles, and much more. Everything you need to make earrings of all styles is here for you in our Beads & Jewelry-Making Store. We have hooks of all styles and materials, including silver-plated, gold-plated and even surgical steel hooks for sensitive ears. Our filter-by-price feature assures that you can find what you need without going over-budget. We want to make it as easy for you to get the beading supplies you need as possible, that way you can spend more time creating wearable art. Our assortment of charms is ideal for making unique bracelets and necklaces. We have glass and metal charms that fit perfectly with popular Pandora, Biagi, Troll and Chamilia charm bracelets. Get fun charms in the shapes of frogs, teddy bears, ducks, words and cows in beautiful colors. For the avid hobby-jeweler, larger lots of 50-100 glass beads makes for less re-ordering. Take advantage of our convenient shipping options to get your order delivered quickly and securely. Whether you\u2019re planning a unique party activity or you sell your creations at craft fairs, we have quality beading supplies for all skill levels. Making your own jewelry can be a great idea for gifts as well--lavish your talent on your friends and loved ones with the beautiful beading supplies available from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Arts, Crafts & Sewing", "parent_catid": 111, "keyword_density": {"supplies": "1.9", "amazoncom": "0.5", "beading": "1.9", "beading supplies": "3.3", "beading supplies from amazoncom": "1.1"}, "department_id": 10},
