{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 191, "catid": 690, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_2617941011_nr_n_5?rh=n%3A2617941011%2Cn%3A%212617942011%2Cn%3A262680011&bbn=2617942011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833318&rnid=2617942011", "text": "Fabric Care", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Fabric Care from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Arts-Crafts-Sewing/b/ref=sd_allcat_sch/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2617941011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "care": 9, "fabric": 12, "fabric care": 5}, "description_wc": 331, "description_text": "Does it ever seem like you need an advanced degree in textiles to properly care for the fabrics that make up your clothes, blankets, and furniture? It can seem like rocket science sometimes, but choosing the right fabric care products will help you tackle every textile, whether it\u2019s cotton, wool, or something you might be likely to find on a NASA spacesuit. For textiles that wrinkle easily, or stubbornly resist ironing, starch and starch alternatives are can make big jobs a lot easier. Starching fabrics is especially important for quilters, who need their elements to be carefully measured and matched. For dark colors, traditional spray starch can sometimes leave flaky white residue, so many people have come to rely on starch alternatives. You can learn more about fabric care products like these by reading user reviews written by people who have purchased the exact items you\u2019re interested in. We also offer a wide selection of fabric care products designed to give your textiles a certain degree of water resistance. Some products restore water resistance to synthetic fabrics that were designed to be waterproof, but have lost some of the effectiveness over time. Other products can make materials like cotton and wool more resistant to water. Waterproofing products can be applied to clothing, or used to pretreat fabric before you construct a garment. Technical fabrics are an amazing boon to garments like rain jackets and running shoes, but it can be tricky to care for them without compromising their waterproof or insulating qualities. At Amazon.com, we offer a wide range products for fabric care specifically designed to clean and care for your specialized technical fabrics. You\u2019ll find products that can remove odors and stains safely, while preserving the technical qualities of your garment. Whether it\u2019s a silk blouse, a pair of waterproof boots, or a wedding quilt, you can find the diverse fabric care products you need to improve the look and longevity of your fabrics at Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Arts, Crafts & Sewing", "parent_catid": 111, "keyword_density": {"fabric care": "3.0", "amazoncom": "0.6", "fabric": "3.6", "care": "2.7"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 4786, "catid": 691, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_2617941011_nr_n_6?rh=n%3A2617941011%2Cn%3A%212617942011%2Cn%3A12896841&bbn=2617942011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833318&rnid=2617942011", "text": "Fabric Painting & Dyeing", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Fabric Dye from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Arts-Crafts-Sewing/b/ref=sd_allcat_sch/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2617941011", "keyword_count": {"dye": 14, "amazoncom": 2, "fabric dye": 7, "fabric": 10}, "description_wc": 342, "description_text": "For thousands of years, people have created beautiful and unique cloth and apparel by dyeing fabric with natural pigments. From the dyed flax seeds found in prehistoric caves to the 1960s tie-dye revivals, adding rich vibrant color livens up our fabric and gets us in touch with a time-honored handicraft. Fabric dyes are easier to use than ever, and they can be found in more colors than the rainbow. At Amazon.com, we offer a wide variety of fabric dyes for every kind of project, from all-purpose dyes suitable for art projects and casual use, to more professional and permanent products. Different dyes have very different applications, so we\u2019ve made it easy to find suitable materials with our convenient filters. You can search for fabric dyes suitable for use with specific materials like cotton or polyester, or you can specify features like permanent, or fiber reactive dye. The right fabric dye applicator can make a big difference in the appearance and quality of your finished product. Whether you need daubers, sponges, markers, or brushes, you\u2019ll find the tools you need at Amazon.com. For group projects, or particularly prolific crafters, we offer applicators and brushes in affordable bulk quantities. Many of these products are eligible for Free Shipping, so you can get the fabric dye and supplies you need delivered straight to your door. Are you interested in sharing your hobby with new people? Complete kits of fabric dyes, applicators, and patterns are a fun and easy way to introduce adults and children alike to an exciting and creative art. All types of kits are available, from simple sets of fabric markers, to groovy tie dye kits, to more advanced versions complete with applicators and fixatives. Color your world with eye-catching and attractive custom materials for craft projects and clothing. Whether you want to follow in the footsteps of thousands of years of tradition, or simply want to add a splash of color to your life, fabric dyes are ideal for adding vibrancy to all your textile projects.", "parent_text": "Arts, Crafts & Sewing", "parent_catid": 111, "keyword_density": {"dye": "4.1", "amazoncom": "0.6", "fabric dye": "4.1", "fabric": "2.9"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 60754, "catid": 692, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_2617941011_nr_n_7?rh=n%3A2617941011%2Cn%3A%212617942011%2Cn%3A12897011&bbn=2617942011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833318&rnid=2617942011", "text": "Furniture & Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Art Furniture from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Arts-Crafts-Sewing/b/ref=sd_allcat_sch/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2617941011", "keyword_count": {"art furniture": 6, "amazoncom": 3, "art": 10, "furniture": 8}, "description_wc": 315, "description_text": "You don\u2019t have to be the only artist in the park with an old, rickety easel any longer. Purpose-built art furniture takes some of the stress out of your process by ensuring an efficient, functional workspace. Anyone who\u2019s ever tried to make the best of an improvised drafting table or sewing cabinet knows the value of well-designed furniture for arts and crafts. At Amazon.com, we offer dozens of styles and brands suitable for everyone from kids to professionals. Are you searching for an ideal drawing surface for a drafting project, or other large-format illustration work? Take a look at our inventory of drawing tables. Whether you\u2019re interested in high-end art furniture, or portable surfaces meant for designers on the go, Amazon.com has plenty of options to suit your needs. Aesthetics are important when it comes to furniture for art projects, which is why we offer a multitude of materials, styles and finishes. Browse our selection of portable art furniture for painters and find the perfect set up for your work. Lightweight aluminum easels are great for portability, while wooden varieties have a certain classic look that can be inspiring. We also offer a range of art furniture for children, to help inspire the peque\u00f1o Picasso in the family. It\u2019s never too early to set your kids up with a great creative space with art furniture and accessories. At Amazon.com, we\u2019re proud of our great customer service. We want to make sure your experience shopping for the art furniture and supplies you need is quick and easy, so you can spend more time creating. Helpful brand and price filtering options, convenient shipping, and low prices on the products you\u2019re looking for are all ways we want to make your life easier. We\u2019re excited to be a part of the creation of your next masterpiece.", "parent_text": "Arts, Crafts & Sewing", "parent_catid": 111, "keyword_density": {"art": "3.2", "amazoncom": "1.0", "art furniture": "3.8", "furniture": "2.5"}, "department_id": 10},
