{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 296, "catid": 696, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_2617941011_nr_n_11?rh=n%3A2617941011%2Cn%3A%212617942011%2Cn%3A12898411&bbn=2617942011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833318&rnid=2617942011", "text": "Photography", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Photography Supplies from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Arts-Crafts-Sewing/b/ref=sd_allcat_sch/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2617941011", "keyword_count": {"supplies": 7, "photography": 9, "photography supplies": 5, "photography supplies from amazoncom": 1}, "description_wc": 340, "description_text": "Becoming a photographer takes a lot more than just slinging a DSLR camera around your neck. Let your passion for photography and your eye for composition be fully developed with the help of quality photography supplies. With adequate supplies, you can print, transfer, and retouch photos to turn your snapshots into gallery-worthy works of art. You can find a wide variety of photography supplies to help you make the most of your upcoming projects. Photo coloring kits can add an artful touch to colored or black and white photography, drawing the attention of the viewer dramatically to the subject matter. We have a nice selection of supplies for photography coloring, including photo oil paints, oil pencils, and sheets of gelatin film to color your photographs. Each has their own benefits and techniques, so browse the customer reviews to see how others have enjoyed these photography supplies to get ideas on creative applications. Our photo paper is great for printing out quality prints easily from your home computer. Why would you pay high retail costs for someone else\u2019s artwork when you can cheaply print your own masterpieces right on your desktop. With a simple frame, your home office could become a photographer\u2019s studio, and if you filter you search for photography supplies by price, the transformation can be quite affordable. Once you get your creative juices flowing and photo paper just isn\u2019t cutting it for you anymore, we have just the thing. Our transfer sheets let you print out intricate designs from your computer and then transfer them from the sheets to a variety of surfaces. Some transfer sheets are made for cloth and other textiles, while some adhere better to smooth, hard surfaces. You can use them to personalize your laptop, desk and much more. If you have an SD memory card full of photos, but nothing to do with them, we have just the answer. The photography supplies from Amazon.com make it easy to print and hang your photography to show off to the world.", "parent_text": "Arts, Crafts & Sewing", "parent_catid": 111, "keyword_density": {"supplies": "2.1", "photography": "2.6", "photography supplies": "2.9", "photography supplies from amazoncom": "1.2"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 3177, "catid": 697, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_2617941011_nr_n_12?rh=n%3A2617941011%2Cn%3A%212617942011%2Cn%3A12898451&bbn=2617942011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833318&rnid=2617942011", "text": "Printmaking", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Printmaking Materials from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Arts-Crafts-Sewing/b/ref=sd_allcat_sch/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2617941011", "keyword_count": {"printmaking materials from amazoncom": 1, "printmaking": 12, "amazoncom": 3, "materials": 5, "printmaking materials": 4}, "description_wc": 324, "description_text": "Printmaking traces its origins back to the unique hand-carved seals, impressions, and simple charcoal rubbings of prehistory. Early printmaking culture and serialized artwork has its roots in woodcuts and early metal engravings, while newer technologies like lithography revolutionized the art world in the 18th and 19th centuries. Today, printmaking is more accessible and affordable than ever, keeping the tradition alive and well. At Amazon.com, we offer printmaking materials for projects big and small. You\u2019ll find heat presses and screens suitable for creating custom designed clothing, fine art, posters, and more. Heat transfer presses are an affordable way to get started producing retail quantities of t-shirts and other clothing. Entry level printmaking presses have thermostat-regulated temperature controls, and precise timers, which will help ensure consistent, quality results. Inks and emulsions for printmaking are available in a wide variety of colors, finishes, and quantities. For smaller jobs, we offer variety packs and starter sets of ink that work well for most basic printmaking projects. Specialty inks for fabrics, metals, and other materials are also available. You can use our product filters to quickly find the right ink for your project. Simply enter the colors, brands, and keywords you\u2019re interested in, and we\u2019ll show you printmaking materials that meet your criteria. At Amazon.com, you\u2019ll find all the printmaking materials and equipment you need to get the job done right. We offer brayers, heat guns, squeegees, and other tools to help you produce quality, long lasting work. Whether you prefer to work with paper, cotton, glass, or something even more exotic, you can get all the printmaking supplies you need delivered straight to your door. Some products are eligible for Free Shipping, so you\u2019ll get everything you need delivered at no additional cost. Whether your printmaking technique is traditional or cutting edge, the right printmaking materials from Amazon.com will help you create quality, long lasting work for years to come.", "parent_text": "Arts, Crafts & Sewing", "parent_catid": 111, "keyword_density": {"printmaking": "3.7", "amazoncom": "0.9", "printmaking materials from amazoncom": "1.2", "printmaking materials": "2.5", "materials": "1.5"}, "department_id": 10},
