o matter what dog supplies you are looking for, you\u2019ll find all your dog supply needs here at Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Pet Supplies", "parent_catid": 112, "keyword_density": {"supplies": "2.8", "amazoncom": "0.4", "dog": "14.3", "dog supplies": "4.8"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 50788, "catid": 705, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_2619533011_nr_n_3?rh=n%3A2619533011%2Cn%3A%212619534011%2Cn%3A2975446011&bbn=2619534011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833318&rnid=2619534011", "text": "Fish & Aquatic Pets", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Aquarium Supplies from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/pet-supplies-dog-cat-food-bed-toy/b/ref=sd_allcat_ps/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2619533011", "keyword_count": {"aquarium supplies from amazoncom": 1, "amazoncom": 2, "aquarium supplies": 6, "aquarium": 10, "supplies": 7}, "description_wc": 306, "description_text": "Looking to dive into aquatics upkeep? With an ocean of options available, selecting aquarium supplies from Amazon.com is as easy as the butterfly stroke. We\u2019ve cast a wide net to bring you a versatile selection of aquariums and fish tanks, starter kits, food, pumps and filters, d\u00e9cor, and lights. Your fish may not get to choose how to decorate its new pad, but at Amazon.com you\u2019ll find an array of tanks and aquariums fit for your aquatic companions from quality brands like Penn-Plax, Pure Aquatic, MarineLand, and more. For every inch of fish you add to the tank, one gallon of water should also be added. The range of tanks, fish bowls, breeding tanks, stands, hoods, and starter kits we offer can assist you in selecting properly sized aquarium supplies for your water dweller. Creating the right ecosystem sometimes requires additional aquarium supplies like filters, substrate, and other health supplies. Keep your aquatic pal healthy by choosing from our selection of healthy food and placing it in one of our regulated automatic feeders. Fish naturally produce toxins, so adding a layer of substrate to the tank helps clean those toxins and lends to a balanced nitrogen cycle. Adding pumps and filters, whether you choose from fluidized, canister, power or wet or dry filters, also boosts longevity. Topping these essentials off with other aquarium supplies like cleaners, test kits, hydrometers, heaters, thermometers, and water treatment kits ensures the reduction of harmful elements in your aquarium. Incorporating d\u00e9cor into your fish\u2019s habitat can provide both aesthetic and health benefits. Our range of aquarium supplies includes LED and other lights that nurture aquarium plants and animals who need light for food. Building the perfect tank ensures healthy fish and a pleasant environment. Our selection of aquarium supplies offers a deep sea of delight.", "parent_text": "Pet Supplies", "parent_catid": 112, "keyword_density": {"aquarium supplies from amazoncom": "1.3", "amazoncom": "0.7", "aquarium supplies": "3.9", "aquarium": "3.3", "supplies": "2.3"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 14830, "catid": 706, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_2619533011_nr_n_4?rh=n%3A2619533011%2Cn%3A%212619534011%2Cn%3A2975481011&bbn=2619534011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833318&rnid=2619534011", "text": "Horses", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Horse Supplies from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/pet-supplies-dog-cat-food-bed-toy/b/ref=sd_allcat_ps/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2619533011", "keyword_count": {"supplies": 7, "horse": 15, "horse supplies": 5, "horse supplies from amazoncom": 2}, "description_wc": 332, "description_text": "Cantering through fields, mesas, and country roads with your pony or horse can be one of the most invigorating experiences in life. With the horse supplies from Amazon.com, you can ensure that your travelling companion enjoys a long and healthy life, and that you two can experience more of the world together. You can find all the supplies for your horse that you need in our Horse Supplies Store. We carry a large selection of quality horse feeding supplies to give your horse companions nutritious meals to keep them going. We have plastic bins, metal buckets and even slow-feeding hay nets to make it easy to give your horse the proper food and water. When you want to show your appreciation and make your equine friend\u2019s day a little brighter, we carry an assortment of treats and salt-licks to reward your loyal animal. To ensure your horse\u2019s utmost health, we also carry a number of horse supplies made especially to deal with common parasites and p. We carry de-wormers that come in tasty pellets to mix in with your horse\u2019s regular feed, and tubes of paste that are flavored like apples and other treats to make them easy to administer. If pesky flies trouble your pony, , we have an assortment of fly masks, traps, and sprays to make your riding companion as comfortable as they can be. Once their health and food are all taken care of, it\u2019s time for grooming. With the right brush, brushing your horse\u2019s mane and coat can be a very relaxing, meditative experience for you and your horse. Grooming time is a time to bond, so it\u2019s important to make it comfortable and enjoyable for the both of you. If you need your horse supplies soon, we offer a variety of quick shipping options to get you your brushes, shampoos, and treats fast. Take good care of your trusted horse companion with the horse supplies from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Pet Supplies", "parent_catid": 112, "keyword_density": {"supplies": "2.1", "horse": "4.5", "horse supplies from amazoncom": "2.4", "horse supplies": "3.0"}, "department_id": 10},
{"nr_products": 367, "catid": 707, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_2619533011_nr_n_5?rh=n%3A2619533011%2Cn%3A%212619534011%2Cn%3A2975497011&bbn=2619534011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833318&rnid=2619534011", "text": "Insects", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_wc": 0, "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/pet-supplies-dog-cat-food-bed-toy/b/ref=sd_allcat_ps/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2619533011", "parent_text": "Pet Supplies", "parent_catid": 112, "department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 12030, "catid": 708, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_2619533011_nr_n_6?rh=n%3A2619533011%2Cn%3A%212619534011%2Cn%3A2975504011&bbn=2619534011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833318&rnid=2619534011", "text": "Reptiles & Amphibians", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Reptile Supplies from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/pet-supplies-dog-cat-food-bed-toy/b/ref=sd_allcat_ps/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2619533011", "keyword_count": {"supplies": 7, "reptile": 11, "amazoncom": 1, "reptile supplies": 6}, "description_wc": 328, "description_text": "Basic reptile care varies greatly between species, so it\u2019s important to make sure you\u2019ve got all the reptile supplies you need to keep your pets healthy and happy. Habitats, food, shelter, and environmental conditions are all important considerations when it comes to taking good care of your reptiles. At Amazon.com, you\u2019ll find terrariums in a wide variety of shapes and sizes. While some lizards and snakes prefer enclosures with greater vertical height to accommodate objects to climb on, other reptiles need wider habitats with extra room for water and rocks. You can use our product filters to find reptile supplies suited to your pet. Choose the type of product, brands, and features you\u2019re interested in, and we\u2019ll display products that meet your criteria. Certain reptiles need frequent exposure to UV light to ensure healthy calcium levels and bone growth. We offer a range of UV and non-UV lamps for your terrarium in different intensities, sizes, and colors, so you can be sure your pet is living in an environment with just the right amount of \u201csun.\u201d Other reptile lighting supplies are also available, including timers, voltage regulators, and mounting accessories. To learn more about certain products, read user reviews written by other people who have purchased the specific reptile supplies you\u2019re interested in. To maintain proper temperature and humidity in your terrarium, use accurate thermometers, hygrometers, and heat lamps. Temperature related reptile supplies should be appropriately paired to the size of your enclosure to ensure a consistent environment. You can also use an automatic thermostat to help maintain a specific temperature easily. Paired with other important reptile supplies like heat lamps and moisture regulators, you can create an authentic jungle environment for your pet. Lizards, turtles, and snakes are sensitive creatures that need a specific, controlled environment to thrive. Make sure you\u2019re equipped with all the reptile supplies you need to provide a comfortable and healthy habitat for your pet.", "parent_text": "Pet Supplies", "parent_catid": 112, "keyword_density": {"supplies": "2.1", "reptile": "3.4", "amazoncom": "0.3", "reptile supplies": "3.7"}, "department_id": 10},
