l animal needs -- pet grooming products, pet carriers, pet treats, pet leashes -- Amazon Pets is your very own pets supplies store. And, with our subscribe-and-save program, you can get free automatic delivery and get 15% off eligible pet supplies. Set your delivery schedule, receive 15% off pet supplies and start receiving pet supplies at your doorstep.", "parent_text": "Pet Supplies", "parent_catid": 112, "keyword_density": {"small": "4.5", "supplies": "2.6", "small animal": "8.2", "small animal supplies": "2.2", "animal": "4.5"}, "department_id": 10},
