ing straps, lift tables, pallet trucks, pallets, platform trucks, roller stands, service carts, tie-downs, and winches, hoists, and pulleys. And for reaching those second floor and elevated building situations, don't show up without a reliable stepladder, extension ladder, emergency ladder, telescoping ladder, or multiple ladders, and for longer term jobs, some sturdy scaffolding. In the same way that using weak materials or unhelpful tools is a sure step towards disaster, using a less-than-dependable brand is a bad idea. Shop top brands like 2x4basics, 3M, Cramer, Filtrete, Honeywell, JET, Kidde, Louisville Ladder, Lux, Magna Cart, and Werner and start building with a leg already up. You'll also find a wide range of deals and special offers on building materials and supplies in the Value Center. There won't be a building job in the world you'll back down from finishing.", "parent_text": "Home Improvement", "parent_catid": 114, "keyword_density": {"building": "2.3", "supplies": "0.9", "building supplies": "0.6"}, "department_id": 10},
