{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 778135, "catid": 716, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_228013_nr_n_6?rh=n%3A228013%2Cn%3A%21468240%2Cn%3A228899&bbn=468240&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833317&rnid=468240", "text": "Painting Supplies & Wall Treatments", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Painting Supplies from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Tools-and-Home-Improvement/b/ref=sd_allcat_hi2/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=228013", "keyword_count": {"painting supplies from amazoncom": 2, "supplies": 6, "amazoncom": 3, "painting supplies": 5, "painting": 8}, "description_wc": 304, "description_text": "Whether you\u2019re getting a home ready to sell, or you\u2019re redecorating your own home, re-painting can make dramatic changes to the look and feel of a house. Brighten up your kitchen rich, warm hues, or paint the master bathroom with cool blues to add a calming mood. The painting supplies from Amazon.com can help you color your world and freshen your space. In our Painting Supplies & Wall Treatments Store, we have a wide selection of paints, stains, and varnishes for you to choose from. Dark stains for wooden furniture, cabinetry, banisters and windowsills can add a great accent to bright rooms. We have buckets of paint in every color of the rainbow, and small bottles of touch-up paint if you just need to spot-fix a ding or scuff on your walls. Many of our painting supplies are eligible for Free Shipping, saving you a bundle on shipping costs. Brushes, rollers and more can also be found at Amazon.com. Our paintbrushes come in nylon, polyester, or foam tips for a variety of jobs. Paint thinners, like turpentine and acetone, are available for easy brush-cleaning when the day\u2019s work is over. You can filter our brushes, rollers, and other paint supplies by price, allowing you to stay on your painting budget. If you\u2019re looking for wall treatments other than painting supplies, our wallpapers comes in many patterns and colors. Choose from elegant, Victorian wallpapers to wild zebra stripes. We also carry a variety of wall stencils to get intricate designs imprinted on your bedroom walls. Even beginning painters can get great results with the simple stenciling instructions on our products. No matter if your painting job is big or small, you can freshen up your walls and your world with the wall treatments and painting supplies from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Home Improvement", "parent_catid": 114, "keyword_density": {"painting supplies from amazoncom": "2.6", "supplies": "2.0", "amazoncom": "1.0", "painting supplies": "3.3", "painting": "2.6"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 1054656, "catid": 717, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_228013_nr_n_7?rh=n%3A228013%2Cn%3A%21468240%2Cn%3A328182011&bbn=468240&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833317&rnid=468240", "text": "Power & Hand Tools", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Power & Hand Tools", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Tools-and-Home-Improvement/b/ref=sd_allcat_hi2/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=228013", "keyword_count": {"tools": 20, "power hand tools": 2, "hand tools": 4, "power": 6, "hand": 6}, "description_wc": 415, "description_text": "Contractors, woodworkers, dry-wallers, builders, plumbers, roofers, and DIY enthusiasts all share one thing: they know that the right tool helps to get a job done right the first time. Having reliable tools held or plugged in creates an environment where work gets done quickly and safely and lets you attempt everything from simply hammering a nail to building a house. And having the right tool means picking out a tool from the right brand, a brand that understands your tool needs. At Amazon.com's Power & Hand Tools Store we have an unbeatable selection of power and hand tool brands, a list that includes top brands such as Bear Grylls Survival Knives, Black & Decker, Bosch, Delta, Denali, DEWALT, Dremel, Fein, Festool, Fluke, Hitachi, JET, Leatherman, Makita, Milwaukee, Porter-Cable, Rockwell Jawhorse, Stanley, and more. These brands have become trusted over time because of their expertise in a wide variety of power and hand tools. Within this long list of brands, you'll be able to find tools for all tasks, starting with the essential power tools for big projects, tools like drills, grinders, rotary tools, routers, saws, sanders, and shears and cordless drills, cordless saws, cordless impact drivers, cordless screwdrivers, and cordless nailers and staplers, and then moving into air tools such as air compressors, nailers, staplers, power sprayers, impact wrenches, sanders, and grinders. And if you're building a bookshelf or doing fine woodworking, you'll want to be sure you have the proper woodworking tools: measuring and layout tools, cutting tools, shaping tools, assembly, finishing tools, and project planning tools. You'll want to stock up on hand tools, multitools, knives, clamps, and wrenches because they come in handy in such a wide range of spots--job sites, camping, around-the-house emergencies, and more. While Amazon.com's Power & Hand Tools Store is focused on tools, tools can't work alone without the right accessories and support and safety products. Round out your workshop and tool collection with batteries, calipers, chargers, chalk lines, clamps, drill bits, dust collectors and air cleaners, ear protection, eye protection, fire extinguishers, gloves, jigs, hardhats, kneepads, levels, line lasers, marking tools, measuring wheels, mobile bases, router bits, rulers, saw blades, scanners and testers, stands, tape measures, tool storage, welding helmets, and workbenches. You'll also find a wide range of deals and special offers on building materials and supplies in the Value Center. Before long, you'll have the right tool and accessory any time you want it.", "parent_text": "Home Improvement", "parent_catid": 114, "keyword_density": {"hand tools": "1.9", "power hand tools": "1.4", "tools": "4.8", "power": "1.4", "hand": "1.4"}, "department_id": 10},
