{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 462149, "catid": 722, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_328182011_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A228013%2Cn%3A%21468240%2Cn%3A328182011%2Cn%3A551238&bbn=328182011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833318&rnid=328182011", "text": "Hand Tools", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Hand Tools", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Power-Tools-and-Hand-Tools/b/ref=sd_allcat_hi/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=328182011", "keyword_count": {"tools": 8, "hand tools": 6, "hand": 8}, "description_wc": 351, "description_text": "There are situations and jobs that lend themselves to plugging in a power tool, but then there are those situations and jobs that demand a little more concentration and fine workmanship, those moments where you need to be able to have more feel for what you're doing, and those activities where you can't be lugging around heavy machinery, not to mention an extension cord or battery pack. At these times, having the right hand tool near at hand makes all the difference. When it comes to precise equipment that doesn't have an outside power source, Amazon.com's Hand Tools Store offers a vast selection. If looking for a stud or doing other testing, there are electrical testers, multi testers, stud finders, moisture meters, and distance estimators that can save you time as well as chalk lines, line lasers, levels, marking tools, measuring wheels, rulers, and tape measures to promote accuracy. There is also an incredible assortment of clamps to keep materials and more in place: angle clamps, bar and pipe clamps, C-clamps, edge clamps, spreader clamps, spring clamps, and vertical glue-press clamps. Hand tools are essential if you enjoy outdoor adventuring, too (even if the outdoors is only the forest in your backyard), with multitools and multitool accessories and folded knives, fixed blade knives, utility knives, blades, knife sets, and flashlights to keep the wild from getting worrisome. Don't forget the classic hand tools, either, the chisels, hammers, pliers, screwdrivers, sockets and socket sets, tool sets, tool bags, and wrenches that form the crucial core of any tool collection. These hand tools, both contemporary and classic, share a certain trait. The best hand tools are made by the best brands, dependable brands such as Black & Decker, Bessey, Bucket Boss, Dorcy, Fluke, Gear Wrench, Gerber Bear Grylls Knives, Irwin, Klein, Leatherman, MagLite, SOG Specialty Knives, Smith & Wesson, Stanley, Streamlight, and Wenger Swiss Army Knives. You'll also find a wide range of deals and special offers on building materials and supplies in the Value Center. With good hand tools, you're prepared for any task.", "parent_text": "Power & Hand Tools", "parent_catid": 115, "keyword_density": {"hand tools": "3.4", "tools": "2.3", "hand": "2.3"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 41530, "catid": 723, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_328182011_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A228013%2Cn%3A%21468240%2Cn%3A328182011%2Cn%3A553244&bbn=328182011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833318&rnid=328182011", "text": "Measuring & Layout Tools", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Measuring Tools from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Power-Tools-and-Hand-Tools/b/ref=sd_allcat_hi/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=328182011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "tools": 11, "measuring tools": 9}, "description_wc": 336, "description_text": "Whether you\u2019re working on a new home layout, an expanded deck, or a simple tool shed for the backyard, it\u2019s easy to plan your projects with precision and skill with Amazon.com\u2019s selection of measuring tools. From basic tape measurers and levels to handy multi-meters and laser distance measurers, and everything in between, we carry an assortment of layout and measuring tools that will make planning, drafting, and executing your dreams easier and quicker. And with several convenient and affordable shipping options to choose from, you can have the measuring tools, layout helpers, and other essentials delivered in time for your next build session. Great for DIYers, hobbyists, professional, and contractors, our selection of measuring tools has the gear to help grow your plans in the right shape. Easily browse for the measuring tools that you need, or filter by type, featured brands, shipping option, condition, and other attributes to further refine your search. You can also filter by price and discount for wallet-friendly measuring tools that don\u2019t sacrifice quality, or shop the most popular, customer-recommended products with our sort by function. Featuring well-known brands like CH Hanson, HM Digital, and Neiko, we include product reviews and ratings right on the page so you can read tips, recommendations, and suggestions from other customers about how well our measuring tools hold up during use. Ideal for small- and large-scale projects at home, in the office, or at your own construction site, measuring tools will help you get the job done right, no matter how complex your plans are. With so many tools to choose from, you can easily keep your angles accurate, voltages on target, studs in the pocket, and measurements precise when putting in wood floors, installing cabinets to the nursery, or planning a sculpted garden. They say \u201cmeasure twice, cut once,\u201d and with the measuring tools, power tools, and home improvement supplies from Amazon.com, you\u2019ll be well-equipped to measure as often as you need to.", "parent_text": "Power & Hand Tools", "parent_catid": 115, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.6", "tools": "3.3", "measuring tools": "5.4"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 422756, "catid": 724, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_328182011_nr_n_3?rh=n%3A228013%2Cn%3A%21468240%2Cn%3A328182011%2Cn%3A552262&bbn=328182011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833318&rnid=328182011", "text": "Power Tool Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Power Tool Accessories", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Power-Tools-and-Hand-Tools/b/ref=sd_allcat_hi/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=328182011", "keyword_count": {"tool": 6, "power tool accessories": 3, "accessories": 13, "power": 4}, "description_wc": 359, "description_text": "The phrase \"always accessorize\" may seem to be a better fit with a fashion magazine than a job site. But the array of accessories within Amazon.com's Power Tool Accessories Store can turn your singular drill into a multifunction machine, keep your saw from ripping wood the wrong way, smooth materials down or stand them up, and help ensure that the job can be worked on until it's done, even if a battery runs out of juice. You accessory package should start with the basics--because the right basics are key to building. These must-haves include blades such as band saw blades, circular saw blades, jig saw blades, planer knives, and table saw blades, as well as boring bits, countersink bits, drill bit sets, hole saws, jigs, SDS-shank bits, self-feed bits, spade bits, and twist bits, and Phillips-tip bits, slotted-tip bits, square-tip bits, and Torx-tip bits. After the basics, bulk up on specialized accessories, including router accessories like router bits, collets, door and window bits, tables, and templates, sander accessories like belts, detail sander paper, discs, sheets, and sleeves, and circular saw accessories, lathe accessories, miter saw accessories, table saw accessories, and gauges and lubricants. Amazon.com's Power Tool Accessories Store also has accessories that keep the power flowing and light the night when needed: battery packs, chargers, converters, cordless tool batteries, radio chargers, and work lights. If you need to add a steadying influence look for workbenches, portable workbenches, miter saw stands, router tables, and table saw stands, and if you need to keep everything together browse the selection of brad nails, collated nails, collated screws, framing nails, roofing nails, and staples. Whatever accessories best round out your tool collection, stick to the brands that are known for providing consistent products, brands such as Bench Dog, Bosch, DEWALT, Drill Doctor, Dremel, Fein, Festool, Freud, Irwin, Kreg, Makita, Milwaukee, Porter-Cable, and Rockwell Jawhorse. You'll also find a wide range of deals and special offers on building materials and supplies in the Value Center. Once you have the right power tool accessories in place, no job can slow you down.", "parent_text": "Power & Hand Tools", "parent_catid": 115, "keyword_density": {"tool": "1.7", "power tool accessories": "2.5", "accessories": "3.6", "power": "1.1"}, "department_id": 10},
