{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 296548, "catid": 729, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_495224_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A228013%2Cn%3A%21468240%2Cn%3A495224%2Cn%3A5486428011&bbn=495224&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833318&rnid=495224", "text": "Ceiling Lights", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Ceiling Lights from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/lighting-and-ceiling-fans/b/ref=sd_allcat_llf/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=495224", "keyword_count": {"lights": 12, "ceiling": 10, "amazoncom": 3, "ceiling lights from amazoncom": 2, "ceiling lights": 5}, "description_wc": 349, "description_text": "The French author Victor Hugo once said \u201cto love beauty is to see light.\u201d Why not increase the love and see the beauty of your home by adding new sources of lighting in your space? Brighten up any room with chandeliers, pendant lights, flush-mounted lights, and other ceiling lights from Amazon.com. A beautiful ceiling light can bring out the color and texture of your interior decorating scheme and make your space warm, bright, and inviting. Chandeliers can be fun and eccentric or sophisticated and subtle. You can find chandeliers in a wide variety of designs that will make a great room or hall feel like a sparkling ballroom or can give a dining room a romantic air for an intimate dinner. What could more elegant than a Tiffany chandelier to hang in your bedroom or studio? Amazon.com offers a variety of secure shipping options, so you can get your ceiling lights on time and all in one piece. Pendant lights can add color and excitement to rooms without taking up too much room. Perfect for studies, office, and peaceful restaurant tables, pendant lights can offer a spot of light right where you need it, or warm the room with their glow. Glass pendants shine light through stained or blown glass to add rich hues to your home. Our filter-by-price feature conveniently lets you browse the most affordable ceiling lights. For lower ceilings, you can find the perfect fit for your space with flush-mount ceiling lights. They don\u2019t hang down from the ceilings like chandeliers and pendants do, they\u2019re short but effective lights that lay flush against your ceiling. They\u2019re perfect for patios and porch lights, because many of the designs are closed, meaning these attractive lights won\u2019t attract moths and bugs. We also have ceiling light designs especially made for kids\u2019 rooms that are decorated with bright colors and themes. Don\u2019t strain your eyes in the dark when you can shed a little light in your space. Bring out the beauty of your home with the ceiling lights from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Lamps & Light Fixtures", "parent_catid": 116, "keyword_density": {"lights": "3.4", "ceiling": "2.9", "ceiling lights from amazoncom": "2.3", "amazoncom": "0.9", "ceiling lights": "2.9"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 7670, "catid": 730, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_495224_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A228013%2Cn%3A%21468240%2Cn%3A495224%2Cn%3A5772192011&bbn=495224&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833318&rnid=495224", "text": "Commercial Lighting", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Commercial Lighting from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/lighting-and-ceiling-fans/b/ref=sd_allcat_llf/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=495224", "keyword_count": {"commercial lighting": 7, "amazoncom": 3, "lighting": 10}, "description_wc": 313, "description_text": "Are you tired of flickering, inadequate fluorescent lighting? Upgrading outdated commercial lighting can have a dramatic impact on the overall look and feel of a workspace or retail area. If you\u2019ve changed one too many bad ballasts, or if you get to design new commercial lighting plan from scratch, there are dozens of bright, energy-efficient fixtures to choose from. Commercial lighting in outdoor areas is important for safety and comfort, especially for locations with plenty of foot traffic. For businesses that want to create inviting outdoor areas for customers, adequate lighting is crucial to ensure a professional and appealing space. Suitable lighting is just as important for non-retail outdoor businesses. Ensuring that all work areas are adequately lighted can increase productivity and safety. Shopping online at Amazon.com for your outdoor commercial lighting is a fast and easy way to compare dozens of products in order to find the ideal solution for your space. Commercial lighting includes some often overlooked elements, such as emergency and exit signage. Choosing dependable emergency lights is a must, and at Amazon.com, we feature a wide variety of brands and styles, so there\u2019s something for every project and budget. Lighted exit signs are often subject to specific safety regulations. Detailed product descriptions on many items can help you determine which exit signs meet the regulatory standards you\u2019re working within. New advances in LED technology have carried over into commercial lighting. LED\u2019s are a fantastic way to reduce energy consumption, especially for fixtures that are on most or all of the time. Additionally, LED bulbs tend to last significantly longer than conventional incandescent or fluorescent bulbs, so you\u2019ll spend less time performing maintenance. Adequate commercial lighting helps create a safe and pleasant environment for workers and customers. Choose dependable, suitable fixtures from Amazon.com and ensure an efficient, comfortable work space, indoors and outdoors.", "parent_text": "Lamps & Light Fixtures", "parent_catid": 116, "keyword_density": {"commercial lighting": "4.5", "amazoncom": "1.0", "lighting": "3.2"}, "department_id": 10},
