{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 68806, "catid": 733, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_495224_nr_n_5?rh=n%3A228013%2Cn%3A%21468240%2Cn%3A495224%2Cn%3A3736531&bbn=495224&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833318&rnid=495224", "text": "Novelty Lighting", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Novelty Lights from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/lighting-and-ceiling-fans/b/ref=sd_allcat_llf/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=495224", "keyword_count": {"novelty lights": 6, "lights": 12, "amazoncom": 1, "novelty": 8}, "description_wc": 317, "description_text": "Lighting has the power to invigorate and energize us, to lift our mood, to soothe our nerves, and it even affects our health. Lowered lights can make us feel calm and relaxed, colored lights can inspire fun and adventure, and sparkling lights set the mood for dancing. Amazon.com has all the novelty lights you could need to adjust the mood of your room. Disco balls will leave you tapping your toes for Saturday night. These novelty lights are great for getting parties going with their bright colors and reflections, so don your white suit and slick shoes, and get ready to turn the beat around. Everyone will feel like hot stuff on the dance floor with the lights low and your disco ball sparkling. Many of our novelty lights are eligible for Free Shipping, so you\u2019ll have more in the budget for DJs and disco boots. Lava lamps are great for setting a whole different mood. When you want to relax and take a mini-break at your desk, there\u2019s nothing better than these novelty lamps. Just the view of them, their colors slowly floating up and down the glass, can give you a nostalgic trip to the 1970s. Now you can even filter your search by discount and see what deals will pop up. Fiber optic lights can be fun novelty lights to bring to dance parties around the world. Going to a darkened, dance floor, raising your hands with these colorful lights in them will make you create a dream-like, human light show. If you\u2019re looking for something that fits your budget, you can filter by price to see the most affordable novelty lights first. It\u2019ll ensure that you don\u2019t go over budget. Put a little novelty in your life and light up your space for work or play in a fun way with the novelty lights from Amazon.", "parent_text": "Lamps & Light Fixtures", "parent_catid": 116, "keyword_density": {"novelty lights": "3.8", "lights": "3.8", "amazoncom": "0.3", "novelty": "2.5"}, "department_id": 10},
