{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 167427, "catid": 735, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_495224_nr_n_7?rh=n%3A228013%2Cn%3A%21468240%2Cn%3A495224%2Cn%3A5486429011&bbn=495224&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833318&rnid=495224", "text": "Wall Lights", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Wall Lights from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/lighting-and-ceiling-fans/b/ref=sd_allcat_llf/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=495224", "keyword_count": {"wall lights from amazoncom": 1, "wall": 7, "wall lights": 5, "lights": 10}, "description_wc": 322, "description_text": "If you\u2019re looking for a light fixture that can add depth to rooms without taking up any floor space, we may have the answer for you. Wall lights can add subtle accents to architectural features, or draw the eye to hanging artworks and pictures. Browse our lights to see if there\u2019s something in your style. We have many elegant wall lights for the sophisticated shopper, like candelabras and many sconces. Candelabras look like candles, but use light bulbs so you can keep the romantic ambience without the fire hazard. Lining your hall with candelabras will make you feel like a Victorian-era noble in his or her estate. Our sconces come in a variety of styles that can also add a touch of class and worldly charm. Swinging arm wall lights are great when you want lights that can be adjusted and moved without taking up floor or desk space. They swing out on a simple but sturdy hinge easily. Our wall-mounted reading lights can add a final touch of comfort to your bedroom. Those who read in bed before going to sleep will appreciate such an easy-to-reach lamp, so they can turn off the light without getting out of bed. We also have a variety of night lights for kids so they can drift off peacefully into sleep. Wallchieres are decorative wall lights that diffuse or shine light upwards. They can add unique accents to bedrooms and doorways by providing a torch-like light. Put two in your master bedroom to dramatically frame your bed, or on either side of a special painting or work of art to draw special attention to it. We also have a wide variety of other picture and display lights to give your precious artworks the attention they deserve. The wall lights from Amazon.com offer a space-saving lighting solution that can add sparkle and brilliance to your home d\u00e9cor.", "parent_text": "Lamps & Light Fixtures", "parent_catid": 116, "keyword_density": {"wall lights from amazoncom": "1.2", "wall": "2.2", "wall lights": "3.1", "lights": "3.1"}, "department_id": 10},
