{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 11109, "catid": 740, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_511228_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A228013%2Cn%3A%21468240%2Cn%3A511228%2Cn%3A4621633011&bbn=511228&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833317&rnid=511228", "text": "Address Numbers & Plaques", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Address Numbers from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Hardware-Locks-and-Fasteners/b/ref=sd_allcat_hdw/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=511228", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "address numbers": 6, "address": 8}, "description_wc": 282, "description_text": "Part of making a new house into a home is adding your own personal touches and creating an aesthetic that reflects who you are. Small details like address numbers can go a long way in establishing an inviting atmosphere. Address plaques are often the first thing people look at, so make a great first impression with a set of stylish and appealing address numbers. If you\u2019re in the process of doing a major remodel, it\u2019s important to make sure finishing pieces match the overall aesthetic of your project. At Amazon.com, we offer a large selection of address numbers and plaques in many popular styles, so finding the perfect match for your house is simple. You can filter the products you see by color, brand, and price to quickly narrow down your choices. Shopping online with Amazon.com is a fast and convenient way to get the address number you want delivered right to your door. We make it easy to search for specific items that might be hard to find, such as lighted or solar powered address numbers. If you\u2019re having trouble deciding if a product is right for you, take a look at our helpful user reviews. You can find out how happy other customers are with the address numbers you\u2019re interested in, or if the product suits the specific needs of the project you\u2019re working on. Giving your home an appealing, fresh look can be as simple as adding details like stylish address numbers. Whether you\u2019re a new homeowner, or have lived in your house your whole life, it can be simple to spruce up the look of your home with a few affordable tweaks.", "parent_text": "Hardware", "parent_catid": 118, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.7", "address numbers": "4.3", "address": "2.8"}, "department_id": 10},
