lity and performance of a MagLite, but don\u2019t need something so large, browse our selection of mini MagLites that feature the same durable materials and construction in small, pocket-sized packages. Our selection of flashlights features dozens of fantastic products, so you can narrow your search quickly with our helpful product filters. Simply choose the bulb type, brand, special features, and battery style you\u2019re interested in, and we\u2019ll create a list of products that meet your criteria. Most flashlights feature detailed info about their performance, construction materials, battery life, and weight, so you\u2019ll be sure to find a flashlight that works well for you. From power outages, to making repairs in dimly lit areas, there are countless uses for a reliable flashlight.", "parent_text": "Hardware", "parent_catid": 118, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.3", "flashlights": "2.6"}, "department_id": 10},
