{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 623030, "catid": 750, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_511228_nr_n_10?rh=n%3A228013%2Cn%3A%21468240%2Cn%3A511228%2Cn%3A511332&bbn=511228&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833317&rnid=511228", "text": "Nails, Screws & Fasteners", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Fasteners from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Hardware-Locks-and-Fasteners/b/ref=sd_allcat_hdw/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=511228", "keyword_count": {"fasteners from amazoncom": 1, "amazoncom": 2, "fasteners": 6}, "description_wc": 339, "description_text": "Sometimes it can seem like everything in your home decides to fall apart at the same time. With the proper fasteners, keeping everything where it should be won\u2019t be a problem. Everything from cords and wires to photo frames and drywall can be put in its place easily. At Amazon.com, we have fasteners of all sorts, shapes, and sizes. Our wide variety of bolts, screws, and nails means you can find exactly what you need for your next DIY project. Whether you\u2019re building a new table, birdhouse or scale-model catapult, the right sized bolts and nails are crucial. We even have especially made picture hangers, so there\u2019s no need to constantly straighten painting that hang by a single nail. If you\u2019re on a tight schedule, our different shipping options mean you can get your fasteners as quickly as you need them. Zip ties and cable ties are very affordable fasteners. Bind and organize just about everything with these versatile items. Cable ties are extremely useful for a variety of projects, like organizing network cables and computer desks, sorting items at your workbench, and more. Our snaps are great for keeping keys, access cards, and other small objects from getting lost. To make it easier for friends, family, baby-sitters, or dog-walkers to come into your home, use a snap to hide your keys in a secret location. Liquid fasteners are ideal for decorating and fixing broken objects. You can find trusted brands like Gorilla Glue, Franklin International, Quakehold!, and more to help you with your home improvement projects. You can make your own refrigerator magnets by gluing a small, magnetic disk to the back of any object. Or try this: make your own kissing salt and pepper shakers by gluing small magnets on the insides of the shakers. Things fall apart. If you\u2019re going crazy with all the repairs and remodeling you have to do around the house, we\u2019re here to help. Keep it together with the fasteners from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Hardware", "parent_catid": 118, "keyword_density": {"fasteners from amazoncom": "0.9", "amazoncom": "0.6", "fasteners": "1.8"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 13405, "catid": 751, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_511228_nr_n_11?rh=n%3A228013%2Cn%3A%21468240%2Cn%3A511228%2Cn%3A511378&bbn=511228&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833317&rnid=511228", "text": "Padlocks & Hasps", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Padlocks from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Hardware-Locks-and-Fasteners/b/ref=sd_allcat_hdw/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=511228", "keyword_count": {"padlocks": 6, "amazoncom": 2, "padlocks from amazoncom": 1}, "description_wc": 258, "description_text": "There\u2019s nothing better than a reliable padlock--whether it\u2019s for your bike, school locker, or shed--to keep your valuable property safe and secure. Take the proper precautions with your belongings by locking them up with a padlock from Amazon.com. Keyed padlocks are great security solutions. There\u2019s no combination to forget; all you have to remember your key. Our heavy-duty, keyed padlocks are ideal for tool boxes, gates and fences, and storage containers. You can even filter your search by price to view the most affordable padlocks first so you won\u2019t go over your budget. Interested in going key-free? Combination padlocks are opened simply by remembering a string of numbers you choose yourself. They\u2019re ideal for gym lockers or cabinets when you don\u2019t want to carry a bunch of keys. There are even alphabetical combination locks that allow you to choose a word that\u2019s easy to remember and help you unlock quickly. Cable locks are ideal for bicyclists. When you\u2019re at work, or even while your bike waits outside the coffee shop, give yourself the peace of mind that your bicycle is safe and secure. They can also be used to secure strollers outside when walking into crowded stores and restaurants. Many of our padlocks and cable locks are eligible for Free Shipping, meaning you don\u2019t have to budget for extra delivery fees. Guard your time and serenity as well as your belongings. With the padlocks from Amazon.com, you can keep your peace of mind and relax.", "parent_text": "Hardware", "parent_catid": 118, "keyword_density": {"padlocks": "2.3", "amazoncom": "0.8", "padlocks from amazoncom": "1.2"}, "department_id": 10},
