what you need. We offer a selection divided into body, eyes, face, feet, hands and nails, lips, maternity, sets, and sun care products. If you have normal, dry, oily, a combination, or sensitive skin, you can use our handy skin type filters to select the products best suited for you. We also offer a handy skin-care attribute filter, so you can find everything from alcohol free, anti-aging, exfoliating, moisturizing, oil-free, purifying, and sunscreen-included skin care products. With quality brands like Olay, L\u2019Oreal Paris, Burt\u2019s Bees, Dove, The Body Shop, and more, you can shop for your favorite radiant skin care products right from home. From clinical-strength sunscreen to beaded eye masks, you can find skin care products from Amazon.com that are ready to rejuvenate your outer layers, protect them from harsh elements, and keep them soft and comfortable.", "parent_text": "All Beauty", "parent_catid": 120, "keyword_density": {"care products": "5.5", "skin care": "5.5", "amazoncom": "0.5", "products": "3.0", "skin": "4.4", "skin care products": "7.4", "skin care products from amazoncom": "1.4", "care": "3.3"}, "department_id": 11},
