{"department_text": "Beauty, Health & Grocery", "nr_products": 15385, "catid": 769, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_16310101_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A16310101%2Cn%3A%2116310211%2Cn%3A16310251&bbn=16310211&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833316&rnid=16310211", "text": "Breakfast Foods", "description_title": "Breakfast Foods from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/grocery-breakfast-foods-snacks-organic/b/ref=sd_allcat_gro/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=16310101", "keyword_count": {"breakfast": 11, "breakfast foods from amazoncom": 2, "breakfast foods": 6}, "description_wc": 341, "description_text": "Make sure you have great-tasting and high-energy breakfast foods from Amazon.com to fuel up for long meetings, busy schedules, and extended workouts. From cereals and breakfast bars to instant drinks and pastries, we have a wide variety of breakfast foods to choose from. A popular option, cereal is a universally loved breakfast option that millions of people start their mornings with every day. We carry a great selection of cereals from favorite brands such as Kellogg\u2019s, General Mills, Post, and Nature\u2019s Path, sure to provide spoonful after spoonful of crisp and crunchy flavor. Or if you\u2019re looking for something warm, hot oatmeal can be just the thing to give you a boost of energy to start the day off right. Granola can be added to anything from milk to yogurt cups, providing a sweet, fiber-filled addition to your breakfast. You can even select gluten-free, sugar-free, nonfat, low-carb, kosher, certified organic, low-fat, free trade, vegan, low-sodium options, and much more. For something a little warmer and sweeter, we offer a complete selection of delicious breakfast foods like pastries and cakes to satisfy any craving in the morning. With our variety of pancake and waffle mixes, you can whip up quick and easy weekend breakfast foods for brunch for your family. Toaster pastries from Pop-Tarts, Nature\u2019s Path, Glutino, and others can add a sweet treat to your mornings without taking up much time. If you\u2019re always in a rush in the morning and need quick breakfast foods to take on the go, cereal and breakfast bars could be ideal to fill up in the morning. Breakfast bars feature crunchy nuts, sweet chunks of chocolate, chewy oats, real fruit and berry pieces, and more to give you a burst of energy when you need it. They pack easily, so you can keep a few in your office, purse, and glove compartment for quick bites whenever and wherever you need it. Stay full, energized, and healthy with breakfast foods from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Grocery & Gourmet Food", "parent_catid": 124, "keyword_density": {"breakfast": "3.2", "breakfast foods from amazoncom": "2.3", "breakfast foods": "3.5"}, "department_id": 11},
{"nr_products": 80766, "catid": 770, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_16310101_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A16310101%2Cn%3A%2116310211%2Cn%3A16322461&bbn=16310211&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833316&rnid=16310211", "text": "Candy & Chocolate", "description_wc": 0, "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/grocery-breakfast-foods-snacks-organic/b/ref=sd_allcat_gro/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=16310101", "parent_text": "Grocery & Gourmet Food", "parent_catid": 124, "department_text": "Beauty, Health & Grocery", "department_id": 11},
{"department_text": "Beauty, Health & Grocery", "nr_products": 198291, "catid": 771, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_16310101_nr_n_3?rh=n%3A16310101%2Cn%3A%2116310211%2Cn%3A6461478011&bbn=16310211&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833316&rnid=16310211", "text": "Canned, Dry & Packaged Foods", "description_title": "Pantry Staples from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/grocery-breakfast-foods-snacks-organic/b/ref=sd_allcat_gro/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=16310101", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 1, "pantry staples": 8}, "description_wc": 355, "description_text": "From canned foods and packaged meals to your favorite seasonings and cooking supplies, no kitchen is complete without the basic pantry staples to enhance meals, get you through a busy week, or be the start of your next baking project. Every chef, cook, and baker needs a well-stocked kitchen to quickly whip up a fast meal or decadent dessert. With your favorite pantry staples in the cabinet and ready to use, you\u2019ll never be at a loss in the kitchen again. From afternoon snacks to Sunday brunches, make sure you\u2019re stocked with the canned sauces, dried noodles and rice, extra condiments, and basic oils and vinegars for any meal. You can even save up to 15% and receive free shipping on regularly scheduled deliveries of your preferred products through Subscribe & Save, so you\u2019ll never run out again. Featuring a wide selection of pantry staples from top brands like Nature\u2019s Way, Nutiva, Betty Crocker, and Honeyville Farms, it\u2019s never been easier to get the non-perishable foods you want. We offer a range of pantry staples from dinner basics and starters like pasta and beans to delicious and nutritious snacks like peanut butter and canned tuna fish. Simply filter by type, specialty, brand, average customer rating, shipping option, and price, or use our handy sort options to quickly refine your search to the pantry staples that best match your preferences. Allergic to soy or working with a gluten-free diet? Shop our specialty stores, including Gluten-Free, Kosher, Sugar-Free, Nonfat, Certified Organic, and GMO-Free, for pantry staples and products that easily fit your needs. Sorted into convenient categories that are easy to browse and shop, our Pantry Staples Store has everything you need to restock your kitchen after moving or refill a few missing ingredients. Jarred and canned foods are great for nights when you forget to thaw meat or plan a meal, while condiments, relishes, seasonings, and marinades can jumpstart your next dinner party. At Amazon.com, you can quickly find and cross off all the pantry staples you need off your grocery list with just one visit.", "parent_text": "Grocery & Gourmet Food", "parent_catid": 124, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.3", "pantry staples": "4.5"}, "department_id": 11},
