{"department_text": "Beauty, Health & Grocery", "nr_products": 87697, "catid": 774, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_16310101_nr_n_6?rh=n%3A16310101%2Cn%3A%2116310211%2Cn%3A16322721&bbn=16310211&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833316&rnid=16310211", "text": "Snack Foods", "description_title": "Snack Foods from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/grocery-breakfast-foods-snacks-organic/b/ref=sd_allcat_gro/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=16310101", "keyword_count": {"snack foods from amazoncom": 1, "amazoncom": 2, "snack": 11, "foods": 7, "snack foods": 6}, "description_wc": 363, "description_text": "From offering hungry partygoers bite-sized bites for those between-conversation pauses to giving little ones healthy options while out at the park or the zoo, snack foods can feed everyone. When you\u2019re in a pinch between lunch and dinner and need something to tide you over, you can grab everything from healthy fruit snacks to sweet cookies and savory and salty chips. Amazon.com offers a wide selection of snack foods to give you a little pick-me up when you need it most. Whether you\u2019re not in the mood to cook or are out and need to boost your blood sugar, you can choose snack foods in a whole variety of flavors and types. Our selection includes everything from applesauce, fruit cups, breadsticks, chips and crisps, cookies, crackers, dried fruit and raisins, fruit leather, fruit snacks, granola and trail mix bars, ice cream cones and toppings, jerky and dried meats, nuts and seeds, party mix, popcorn, pork rinds, pretzels, pudding and gelatin, puffed snacks, rice cakes, rice crackers, salsas, dips, and spreads, trail mix, wasabi peas, and more. When you crave snack foods but have special dietary needs, you might prefer a variety of specialty options. We offer everything from gluten-free, kosher, low-fat, sugar-free, vegan, nonfat, vegetarian, certified organic, and many more options. With quality brands like Nature Valley, Frito-Lay, Navitas Naturals, Popchips and Annie's Homegrown, you can shop for crispy, crunchy, and delicious options right from home. We even offer Subscribe & Save options to help you save 15% on eligible purchases, give you free shipping, and provide you with regularly scheduled deliveries of your favorite snack foods. As if our wide selection wasn\u2019t enough, our Recipe Center can help you discover quick and tasty recipes for dinner, desserts, snacks, and more. Plus, you can expand your search and browse our selection of beverages, coffee, breakfast foods, baking products, snacks, candy, baby food, pantry staples, gifts, and fresh flowers, and check off everything on your list thanks to our selection of groceries under $10. With snack foods from Amazon.com, you can bite into sweet, savory, and completely delicious pick-me ups of your choice.", "parent_text": "Grocery & Gourmet Food", "parent_catid": 124, "keyword_density": {"snack foods from amazoncom": "1.1", "snack": "3.0", "amazoncom": "0.6", "foods": "1.9", "snack foods": "3.3"}, "department_id": 11},
{"department_text": "Beauty, Health & Grocery", "nr_products": 6679, "catid": 775, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_16310101_nr_n_7?rh=n%3A16310101%2Cn%3A%2116310211%2Cn%3A16323111&bbn=16310211&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833316&rnid=16310211", "text": "Baby Foods", "description_title": "Baby Food from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/grocery-breakfast-foods-snacks-organic/b/ref=sd_allcat_gro/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=16310101", "keyword_count": {"food": 14, "baby food": 9, "amazoncom": 2, "baby": 17}, "description_wc": 374, "description_text": "Make sure your little ones are getting the right nutrients, foods, and nourishment they need to grow up strong. Amazon.com\u2019s selection of baby food can offer your baby the vitamins and minerals they need. To ensure that your little one gets what they need, we have a wide variety of baby food to choose from. From pureed fruit and vegetable baby food packed with vital nutrients to organic infant formula packed with extras, baby food is an important part of your baby\u2019s diet, supplying the protein, iron, and vitamin B they need. We even have completely earth-friendly, organic, and natural food options for added health benefits. When you\u2019re ready to move on to cup or bottle feeding, you can find a wide selection of great liquid options for your baby as well. A staple for many parents, formula contains many of the same nutrients as natural milk and is available in creamy, tasty mixtures perfect for small bodies. Juices made from real fruits can be a healthy snack or in-between meal for your little one. To make drinking their juices and formula easier, we also offer a great selection of bottles and sippy cups in our Baby Feeding Store. We also feature the brands of baby food you know and love, including Gerber, Earth\u2019s Best, Plum Organics, and more. We feature a variety of baby snack foods as well, so when you\u2019re on the go, you can always have something ready for when your baby gets hungry. Check out our great selection of baby food in pouches\u2014a new way to take baby food out wherever you might want to adventure with baby. Convenient and mess-free, baby food in pouches is travel-ready and perfect for on-the-go, busy lifestyles. From biscuits and crackers to fruit pouches and cereals, we also have many sweet flavors that kids love. Our selection of snack foods are made specifically with infants and young children in mind, so you can find the snack foods for baby that don\u2019t have hard edges like big people\u2019s snacks do. Whatever your little ones crave, you can find great tasting baby food in a variety of flavors and textures at Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Grocery & Gourmet Food", "parent_catid": 124, "keyword_density": {"food": "3.7", "baby food": "4.8", "amazoncom": "0.5", "baby": "4.5"}, "department_id": 11},
{"department_text": "Beauty, Health & Grocery", "nr_products": 7722, "catid": 776, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_16310101_nr_n_8?rh=n%3A16310101%2Cn%3A%2116310211%2Cn%3A2983386011&bbn=16310211&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833316&rnid=16310211", "text": "Wine", "description_title": "Wine", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/grocery-breakfast-foods-snacks-organic/b/ref=sd_allcat_gro/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=16310101", "keyword_count": {"wine": 48}, "description_wc": 388, "description_text": "Amazon Wine is an ideal place to buy wine online, offering a vast selection of wines from iconic brands to enthusiast favorites. Learn about wine by hearing directly from the winemaker about winemaking techniques, wine tasting notes, vineyard details, and wine pairing suggestions. Become a wine connoisseur of your own right by discovering the best wine for your taste preferences, whether it\u2019s dry wines or sweet wines, and by reading wine reviews by other customers. Use our simple filters to sort by type, such as red wine, white wine, ros\u00e8 wine, sparkling wine, and dessert wine. Also, narrow down your choices by wine rating or price, to help you buy the perfect wine for any occasion, whether you are looking for a fine wine or an everyday wine. Examine wine labels online to help you make perfect food and wine pairings or just read wine quotes directly from the winemaker. In our wine store, you can browse through different regions to discover wines from California, Washington, Oregon, and more. Featured wine country regions include Napa Valley, Sonoma, Paso Robles, Walla Walla, Red Mountain, and Willamette Valley. Wine gifts are a popular crowd pleaser during the holidays, and Amazon\u2019s wide selection of wine bottles and gift accessories can help you create wonderful combinations for wine gift baskets that will be loved by friends and family members alike. Or you can choose a unique wine bottle from your favorite vintage to stock your loved ones wine cellars and wine racks. You can also browse our selection of wine glasses, wine openers, wine books, glass markers and more to add something extra special. If you\u2019re an aficionado of red wines, we have just the selection for you, from dry red wine to sweet red wine across multiple varieties. Browse through many varieties of red wines, such as Cabernet Sauvignon, Pinot Noir, Merlot, Malbec, Sangiovese, Syrah, Zinfandel, Cabernet Franc, Tempranillo, and Greneche. Or, if you can\u2019t get enough of delicious white wines, we have a broad selection to choose from whether you prefer a dry white wine or sweet white wine. Browse through many varieties of white wines, such as Chardonnay, Moscato, Pinot Grigio, Pinot Gris, Riesling, Sauvignon Blanc, Semillon, and Viognier. We\u2019ve got great sparkling wine and dessert wine, too, which are perfect for special occasions.", "parent_text": "Grocery & Gourmet Food", "parent_catid": 124, "keyword_density": {"wine": "12.4"}, "department_id": 11},
