s, Popchips and Annie's Homegrown, you can shop for crispy, crunchy, and delicious options right from home. We even offer Subscribe & Save options to help you save 15% on eligible purchases, give you free shipping, and provide you with regularly scheduled deliveries of your favorite snack foods. As if our wide selection wasn\u2019t enough, our Recipe Center can help you discover quick and tasty recipes for dinner, desserts, snacks, and more. Plus, you can expand your search and browse our selection of beverages, coffee, breakfast foods, baking products, snacks, candy, baby food, pantry staples, gifts, and fresh flowers, and check off everything on your list thanks to our selection of groceries under $10. With snack foods from Amazon.com, you can bite into sweet, savory, and completely delicious pick-me ups of your choice.", "parent_text": "Natural & Organic", "parent_catid": 125, "keyword_density": {"snack foods from amazoncom": "1.1", "snack": "3.0", "amazoncom": "0.6", "foods": "1.9", "snack foods": "3.3"}, "department_id": 11},
{"department_text": "Beauty, Health & Grocery", "nr_products": 1536, "catid": 779, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_51537011_nr_n_7?rh=n%3A16310101%2Cn%3A%2151536011%2Cn%3A51537011%2Cn%3A16323111&bbn=51537011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833288&rnid=16310211", "text": "Baby Foods", "description_title": "Baby Food from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Natural-Organic-Grocery/b/ref=sd_allcat_nto/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=51537011", "keyword_count": {"food": 14, "baby food": 9, "amazoncom": 2, "baby": 17}, "description_wc": 374, "description_text": "Make sure your little ones are getting the right nutrients, foods, and nourishment they need to grow up strong. Amazon.com\u2019s selection of baby food can offer your baby the vitamins and minerals they need. To ensure that your little one gets what they need, we have a wide variety of baby food to choose from. From pureed fruit and vegetable baby food packed with vital nutrients to organic infant formula packed with extras, baby food is an important part of your baby\u2019s diet, supplying the protein, iron, and vitamin B they need. We even have completely earth-friendly, organic, and natural food options for added health benefits. When you\u2019re ready to move on to cup or bottle feeding, you can find a wide selection of great liquid options for your baby as well. A staple for many parents, formula contains many of the same nutrients as natural milk and is available in creamy, tasty mixtures perfect for small bodies. Juices made from real fruits can be a healthy snack or in-between meal for your little one. To make drinking their juices and formula easier, we also offer a great selection of bottles and sippy cups in our Baby Feeding Store. We also feature the brands of baby food you know and love, including Gerber, Earth\u2019s Best, Plum Organics, and more. We feature a variety of baby snack foods as well, so when you\u2019re on the go, you can always have something ready for when your baby gets hungry. Check out our great selection of baby food in pouches\u2014a new way to take baby food out wherever you might want to adventure with baby. Convenient and mess-free, baby food in pouches is travel-ready and perfect for on-the-go, busy lifestyles. From biscuits and crackers to fruit pouches and cereals, we also have many sweet flavors that kids love. Our selection of snack foods are made specifically with infants and young children in mind, so you can find the snack foods for baby that don\u2019t have hard edges like big people\u2019s snacks do. Whatever your little ones crave, you can find great tasting baby food in a variety of flavors and textures at Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Natural & Organic", "parent_catid": 125, "keyword_density": {"food": "3.7", "baby food": "4.8", "amazoncom": "0.5", "baby": "4.5"}, "department_id": 11},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 269688, "catid": 780, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1057792_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%2113900811%2Cn%3A%211063496%2Cn%3A%21251263011%2Cn%3A1057792%2Cn%3A1063236&bbn=1057792&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833320&rnid=1057792", "text": "Bath", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Bathroom Supplies from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/bedding-bath-sheets-towels/b/ref=sd_allcat_bb/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=1057792", "keyword_count": {"bathroom": 17, "amazoncom": 2, "bathroom supplies": 6}, "description_wc": 306, "description_text": "Whether you are stocking your new bathroom after a move or simply improving the usability of your existing bathroom, Amazon.com has the bathroom supplies you need. Our bathroom supplies help you clear up clutter in the bathroom and decorate it to your tastes. From scales to shower caddies, you'll find everything you need to make your bathroom as useful as possible for every member of your family. Looking for a wide selection of bathroom supplies and accessories to jazz up your decor? Add a new shower curtain, a bath rug, or coordinated bath linens to your bathroom to give it a new look and feel. We pride ourselves on offering a wide range of colors and styles to help you achieve the look you want, whether that be sophisticated or whimsical. Extend the utility of your bathroom by choosing from our selection of scales, or change out your showerhead for one that has the extra features you need. Wastebaskets, handheld showers, shower treads, drain stoppers, and plungers are other bathroom supplies that can help you make the most out of this often-overlooked room. You can also find bath fixtures in brass, bronze, chrome, nickel and other materials. If your bathroom is in need of better organization, we offer shower caddies, bathroom shelves, soap dispensers, towel racks, medicine cabinets and cosmetic organizers to help you create a place for everything. These products can help you get organized, so you can find what you need quickly and easily while in the bathroom. You and your family spend countless hours in the bathroom, so choose bathroom supplies and accessories that will make your time spent there as enjoyable and useful as possible. With the wide range of bathroom supplies available at Amazon.com, you are sure to find just the right products for all of your bathroom needs.", "parent_text": "Bedding & Bath", "parent_catid": 107, "keyword_density": {"bathroom": "5.6", "amazoncom": "0.7", "bathroom supplies": "3.9"}, "department_id": 10},
