{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 238703, "catid": 790, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_2972638011_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A2972638011%2Cn%3A%213238155011%2Cn%3A4619352011&bbn=3238155011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833320&rnid=3238155011", "text": "Farm & Ranch", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Farm Supplies from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Patio-Lawn-Garden/b/ref=sd_allcat_lp/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2972638011", "keyword_count": {"farm": 7, "farm supplies": 4, "amazoncom": 2, "supplies": 9}, "description_wc": 292, "description_text": "Working in the fields and among livestock can be extremely rewarding and satisfying. You may revel in digging for some hard work, but sometimes you need a little help from reliable farm supplies. Amazon.com offers all sorts of farming equipment, supplies, feed, and chemicals to make your work a little more fruitful. The first thing on many farmers\u2019 minds is pests. From poisons and mosquito dunks to natural bug repellants and flea traps, we carry a wide variety of pest control supplies. For bigger jobs, we offer chemical sprayers with a locking lid and a hand pump so you can properly spray with an even coating. You can also find a big selection of soils, fertilizers, mulches, and other farm supplies to help grow a fresh and plentiful harvest. You\u2019ll also find a large variety of farm supplies for keeping livestock big and healthy. We carry many bags of feed for all sorts of animals. From special goat pellets to grit for chicks and chickens, you\u2019ll find everything you need to feed every size, age, and species of livestock, including horses. Plastic buckets, bucket-holding wire frames, and watering supplies can make the process of feeding your animals quick and convenient. We even have beekeeping supplies for hobby or professional-level apiarists. For serious agriculturalists, we have mechanical and heavy-duty farm equipment and supplies to help you get even the biggest jobs done. Generators will give you a reliable and plentiful power source for operating power tools, machinery, and other electronic devices. We also carry vibrating plates and rammers to pack down soil, tiller rakes to make quick work of rough soil, and much more. Amazon.com carries all sorts of farm supplies to help you during the toughest seasons.", "parent_text": "Patio, Lawn & Garden", "parent_catid": 109, "keyword_density": {"farm": "2.4", "farm supplies": "2.7", "amazoncom": "0.7", "supplies": "3.1"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 308040, "catid": 791, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_2972638011_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A2972638011%2Cn%3A%213238155011%2Cn%3A3610851&bbn=3238155011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833320&rnid=3238155011", "text": "Gardening", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Gardening from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Patio-Lawn-Garden/b/ref=sd_allcat_lp/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2972638011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 3, "gardening": 8}, "description_wc": 304, "description_text": "Anyone can be a gardener, with or without a green thumb. With the right gardening and gardening supplies, it doesn\u2019t have to be a jungle out there anymore. It\u2019s easy to step up your gardening game with all the necessary gardening tools and supplies from Amazon.com. From pruners, shears, and other tools to seeds, bulbs, and plants, you can take control of your yard and let it bloom bright. Whether you have specific flowers, plants, trees, or herbs in mind, we offer a large variety of all things green, orange, red, blue, sweet, and more. A good yard or garden needs the right gardening tools to work it into shape. You can find tools, accessories, carts, bins, containers, and other supplies for gardening, as well as well-known brands and featured sellers at Amazon.com. Our selection of shovels, tool sets, forks, hoes, shears, and trowels makes it easy to get into the garden groove. Plus, you can keep everything hydrated with our large selection of watering equipment, including everything from extendable hoses and faucets to watering cans and irrigation kits. When you have a full arsenal of tools in your toolshed or garage, you can get down in the mud quickly without too much mess. To help you start your dream garden, we offer live potted plants, bulbs, and seeds. Our soils, fertilizers, mulches, and germination equipment will help everything grow healthy and strong. Plus, it\u2019s easy to protect your plants and flowers with covers and containers during the winter or other inclement weather. We\u2019ll help you save time with our category filters, so you can find plant containers, gardening accessories, and more by color, price, and brand. Whatever you need to make your garden grow, you can find it in the wide selection of gardening supplies available at Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Patio, Lawn & Garden", "parent_catid": 109, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "1.0", "gardening": "2.6"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 11346, "catid": 792, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_2972638011_nr_n_3?rh=n%3A2972638011%2Cn%3A%213238155011%2Cn%3A552808&bbn=3238155011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833320&rnid=3238155011", "text": "Generators & Portable Power", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Power Up Your Generator Knowledge", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Patio-Lawn-Garden/b/ref=sd_allcat_lp/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2972638011", "keyword_count": {"generator": 1, "power": 1}, "description_wc": 32, "description_text": "Before you buy, learn more about generators , including the difference between portable and standby . Plus, download our worksheet and figure out how much power you need. \u203a Check out the guide", "parent_text": "Patio, Lawn & Garden", "parent_catid": 109, "keyword_density": {"power": "3.3", "generator": "3.3"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 38196, "catid": 793, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_2972638011_nr_n_4?rh=n%3A2972638011%2Cn%3A%213238155011%2Cn%3A553760&bbn=3238155011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833320&rnid=3238155011", "text": "Grills & Outdoor Cooking", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Grilling Supplies from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Patio-Lawn-Garden/b/ref=sd_allcat_lp/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2972638011", "keyword_count": {"grilling supplies from amazoncom": 2, "grilling supplies": 3, "grilling": 7, "supplies": 4}, "description_wc": 306, "description_text": "When the weather gets warmer and the skies clear, it\u2019s a perfect time to relax with a barbeque, and when the skies get cloudy and the cold wind blows, that\u2019s also the perfect time to warm yourself up with some barbeque. Grilling season can last all year thanks to quality grilling supplies from Amazon.com We feature a wide variety of grilling supplies, including the grills themselves. We have many propane, natural gas, and electric-powered grills so you can choose the one that best suits your purposes. Classic charcoal burning grills offer that traditional smoky flavor you grew up with, while our gas and electric grills provide a flavorless heat source, letting your marinades and barbeque sauces take center stage. Wire brushes can also help keep old flavors of last week\u2019s dinner from changing the flavor of your burgers and corn on the cob. For more advanced barbeque masters, we offer smokers, fryers, and Dutch ovens to complete your meat-making arsenal. Smokers come in a variety of shapes and use many different heat sources. You\u2019ll have a lot of fun experimenting with different smoked meats, cheeses, peppers, and more. Dutch ovens are as versatile as any other piece of cooking hardware out there, and can simplify cooking stews, roasts, chilies, and much more. They\u2019re ideal one-pot cookers, which saves on clean-up afterwards. If you\u2019re already happy with your grilling and barbequing setup, we have a variety of grilling accessories and supplies to go with it. We carry everything from essential heavy-duty spatulas, tongs, and forks to high-tech meat thermometers that help you grill the perfect steaks every time. We even have metal or disposable skewers perfect for grilling shrimp, veggies and even marshmallows. Any season is barbeque season thanks to quality grilling supplies from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Patio, Lawn & Garden", "parent_catid": 109, "keyword_density": {"grilling supplies from amazoncom": "2.6", "grilling": "2.3", "grilling supplies": "2.0", "supplies": "1.3"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 286916, "catid": 794, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_2972638011_nr_n_5?rh=n%3A2972638011%2Cn%3A%213238155011%2Cn%3A551242&bbn=3238155011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833320&rnid=3238155011", "text": "Mowers & Outdoor Power Tools", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Landscaping Tools from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Patio-Lawn-Garden/b/ref=sd_allcat_lp/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2972638011", "keyword_count": {"landscaping": 8, "amazoncom": 2, "landscaping tools from amazoncom": 1, "landscaping tools": 6}, "description_wc": 328, "description_text": "Your lawn and your garden are extensions of your home, and should get the same care and grooming that the rest of your home does. Now landscaping work doesn\u2019t have to require back-breaking labor. With the right landscaping tools from Amazon.com, you can mow, blow, saw, and prune to your heart\u2019s content without breaking a sweat. We have all sorts of landscaping tools to help you out with your lawn work. In our collection of lawn mowers, you\u2019ll definitely find something suited just for your needs. Everything from ride-on models, gas-powered push lawn mowers, and hand-powered push reel lawn mowers are here for you to browse. To clip and snip edgings, hedges and more, we even carry an assortment of string trimmer and hedge trimmers to make adding the finishing touches to your garden a breeze. If you like to do everything by hand, you can do that too with our handheld landscaping tools, such as shears, shovels, rakes and more. Every season has its own specific lawn care needs. Whether you need to remove dead leaves, falling maple seeds, or inches of snow, we have the landscaping tools for you. Our leaf blowers can make short work of clearing your driveway and walkways from basic debris. And when the weather gets chilly, our snow throwers can save your back from the hours it\u2019ll take to shovel out your car. For more serious landscaping jobs that require skill and precision, you can find the right landscaping tools here. With our large arsenal of gas- and battery-powered chainsaw and electric pruners will help you clear your yard of obtrusive branches and trees. Pressure washers can help you clean outdoor tiles grout, remove road scum from your car, and even whisk off dirt from fences and windows if you know the right psi for the job. The reliable landscaping tools at Amazon.com can help you make short work of your projects.", "parent_text": "Patio, Lawn & Garden", "parent_catid": 109, "keyword_density": {"landscaping": "2.4", "amazoncom": "0.6", "landscaping tools": "3.7", "landscaping tools from amazoncom": "1.2"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 687397, "catid": 795, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_2972638011_nr_n_6?rh=n%3A2972638011%2Cn%3A%213238155011%2Cn%3A553788&bbn=3238155011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833320&rnid=3238155011", "text": "Outdoor D\u00e9cor", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Outdoor D\u00e9cor from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Patio-Lawn-Garden/b/ref=sd_allcat_lp/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2972638011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 1, "outdoor": 9, "d": 70, "cor": 7, "outdoor d cor": 6}, "description_wc": 310, "description_text": "Are you the kind of person who makes the most of spring and summer, and spends as much time as you can enjoying your yard? Be sure you\u2019ve got all the outdoor d\u00e9cor you need to transform your yard into a fun, fair weather outdoor living area. Show your true colors with flags and flag poles from Amazon.com. From national pride to sports loyalty, you\u2019ll find a range of flags to fly over your outdoor living area. There won\u2019t be any question about who the biggest Packers fan on the block once you raise your 3x5 helmet flag over your backyard. If you want to send a different message to your neighbors, we offer a variety of pirate flags that add a distinct swashbuckling element to your outdoor d\u00e9cor. Wind chimes will add soothing sights and sounds to your outdoor d\u00e9cor. Wood, glass, and metal chimes each have a distinct tone and appearance, so there\u2019s a version to suit every preference. Most chimes are tuned to specific intervals in order to produce a pleasing, coherent sound. You\u2019ll find high pitches and low pitches, familiar melodies, and exotic, eastern inspired tunes. We offer a variety of garden sculptures and statues to add a bit of dimension to your outdoor d\u00e9cor. From classics like gnomes and flamingos to contemporary pieces like reflective spheres and suncatchers, you can spruce up your garden any way you\u2019d like. Use our convenient product filters to quickly find sculptures that you like. Choose materials, colors, and features you\u2019re interested in, and we\u2019ll display outdoor d\u00e9cor products that fit your criteria. Create an inviting and comfortable atmosphere in your yard by choosing outdoor d\u00e9cor that suits your style. Functional and decorative details can have a big impact on the livability of your outdoor spaces.", "parent_text": "Patio, Lawn & Garden", "parent_catid": 109, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.3", "outdoor": "2.9", "outdoor d cor": "5.8", "d": "22.6", "cor": "2.3"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 7248, "catid": 796, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_2972638011_nr_n_7?rh=n%3A2972638011%2Cn%3A%213238155011%2Cn%3A14107611&bbn=3238155011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833320&rnid=3238155011", "text": "Outdoor Heaters & Fire Pits", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "CobraCo Fire Pits", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Patio-Lawn-Garden/b/ref=sd_allcat_lp/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2972638011", "keyword_count": {"cobraco fire pits": 1}, "description_wc": 7, "description_text": "Save 25% on CobraCo Fire Pits .", "parent_text": "Patio, Lawn & Garden", "parent_catid": 109, "keyword_density": {"cobraco fire pits": "50.0"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 2833, "catid": 797, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_2972638011_nr_n_8?rh=n%3A2972638011%2Cn%3A%213238155011%2Cn%3A13400641&bbn=3238155011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833320&rnid=3238155011", "text": "Outdoor Storage", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Outdoor Storage Containers from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Patio-Lawn-Garden/b/ref=sd_allcat_lp/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2972638011", "keyword_count": {"outdoor storage containers": 2, "amazoncom": 1, "outdoor": 3, "storage": 9, "storage containers": 6}, "description_wc": 319, "description_text": "Storage containers for your outdoor areas should be rugged and able to stand up to the weather. Specially designed tubs, trunks, and boxes made from weatherproof materials will keep the wind and rain out season after season, so you don\u2019t have to worry about unnecessary wear to your lawn and garden equipment. At Amazon.com, we offer storage containers in a range of sizes and materials. Plastic boxes and bins are lightweight and easy to assemble, which makes them a convenient solution for porch and patio storage. Many have helpful features like spring loaded lids, and secondary accessory trays to maximize utility. There\u2019s a plastic storage container to fit every porch and patio, from just a few cubic feet, to over 150 gallon capacity. The larger units are perfect for storing lawn and garden tools like shovels, rakes, and string trimmers, in order to protect them from moisture and sun exposure. Wooden storage containers are perfect for creating useful space on your deck. You can eliminate clutter and keep items like chair cushions, lights, and grilling equipment dry and secure overnight and during the off season. Our convenient product filters can help you find a wooden storage container that matches your deck or patio. Simply choose the materials, colors, and styles you\u2019re interested in, and we\u2019ll display products that meet your criteria. Many outdoor storage containers also double as comfortable, stylish seating. You can keep all your property safe and secure, while providing extra room to sit and be comfortable. We also offer smaller, portable storage containers with wheels and handles which are perfect for gardening and yard work. Store all the tools you need in a weather tight container, and bring it along with you wherever you need to go. Outdoor storage containers will keep your tools, cushions, and pool accessories safe and dry all year round, so you can relax and enjoy your yard.", "parent_text": "Patio, Lawn & Garden", "parent_catid": 109, "keyword_density": {"outdoor": "0.9", "amazoncom": "0.3", "outdoor storage containers": "1.9", "storage": "2.8", "storage containers": "3.8"}, "department_id": 10},
