he bank. Many graphic novels for kids are available in several different formats so you can choose what works best for your kids. Whether they love flipping through paperback and hardcover stories or using their Kindle for reading more, we offer physical, digital, and audio versions of all their favorites to make reading fun again. We also carry graphic novels and stories in different languages perfect for encouraging or reinforcing a second language at home. Help foster your kids\u2019 love of reading with graphic novels for kids from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Children's Books", "parent_catid": 70, "keyword_density": {"graphic novels for kids from amazoncom": "3.8", "graphic novels for kids": "5.1", "graphic": "3.2", "graphic novels": "4.5", "kids": "3.5"}, "department_id": 7},
