{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 50, "catid": 852, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_599858_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A599858%2Cn%3A%21599872%2Cn%3A16014521&bbn=599872&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=599872", "text": "Antiques & Collectibles", "description_title": "Save When You Subscribe to", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/magazines/b/ref=sd_allcat_magazines/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=599858", "keyword_count": {"subscribe": 1}, "description_wc": 54, "description_text": "A fascinating picture of the ever-changing U.S. and global art scene is what you'll find in the pages of Art in America . Covering everything from contemporary to classical, Art in America features paintings, sculptures, photography, and offers critiques of new talents and books. \u2022 Subscribe to Art in America for $71.00 $34.95", "parent_text": "Magazines", "parent_catid": 72, "keyword_density": {"subscribe": "1.9"}, "department_id": 7},
{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 288, "catid": 853, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_599858_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A599858%2Cn%3A%21599872%2Cn%3A602314&bbn=599872&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=599872", "text": "Arts & Photography", "description_title": "Art and Photography Magazines from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/magazines/b/ref=sd_allcat_magazines/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=599858", "keyword_count": {"art": 15, "photography magazines": 8, "photography": 11, "art and photography magazines": 6, "amazoncom": 4, "art and photography magazines from amazoncom": 1, "magazines": 11, "art and photography": 7}, "description_wc": 335, "description_text": "If you\u2019re looking for perfect coffee table books full of colorful and striking images, or you\u2019re trying to bolster your art education, the art and photography magazines from Amazon.com can make a great addition to your favorite reading materials. Amazon.com offers a wide variety of art and photography magazines for you to choose from. If you\u2019re looking for an inside look into the ever-changing world of contemporary art to keep track of new artists or to inspire yourself with cutting-edge sculptures and paintings, magazines such as Art Ltd. , Art in America , and New American Paintings could be great choices for you. We also carry a selection of art and photography magazines featuring eye-popping graphic designs and other computer-generated imagery to inspire and thrill readers. They can also feature tips and trick for making the most out of popular photo manipulation software and tools. If you\u2019re looking strictly for photography, we have the art and photography magazines for you. Popular Photography , Digital Photo , Lenswork , and other professional photography magazines can give you tips on using the best tools available for photographers today. To study source material, you can flip through our performance art and fashion photography magazines for high-energy and beautifully structured photographs from some of the top photographers in their fields. History buffs and fans of art with major cultural significance will love our art history magazines that can refresh your knowledge on the fundamentals. Flip through oversized, full-color featuring some of the world\u2019s most remarkable paintings, sculptures, and more. They make great magazines for guests to pick up and look through while you talk about your favorite pieces. To help you keep track of your art and photography magazines, Amazon.com makes it easy to manage all of your subscriptions in one place. You can even order gift subscriptions to inspire friends and family with fantastic art and photography. You can find vibrant art and photography magazines at Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Magazines", "parent_catid": 72, "keyword_density": {"art": "4.5", "art and photography magazines": "7.3", "photography": "3.3", "photography magazines": "4.8", "amazoncom": "1.2", "art and photography magazines from amazoncom": "1.8", "magazines": "3.3", "art and photography": "6.4"}, "department_id": 7},
{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 123, "catid": 854, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_599858_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A599858%2Cn%3A%21599872%2Cn%3A602316&bbn=599872&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=599872", "text": "Automotive", "description_title": "Save When You Subscribe to", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/magazines/b/ref=sd_allcat_magazines/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=599858", "keyword_count": {"subscribe": 1}, "description_wc": 44, "description_text": "A magazine for automobile enthusiasts, Car and Driver is for those interested in both the engine and the race track. Each issue contains international coverage of racing events, technical reports, personality profiles, product reviews and more. \u2022 Subscribe to Car and Driver for $59.88 $10.00", "parent_text": "Magazines", "parent_catid": 72, "keyword_density": {"subscribe": "2.3"}, "department_id": 7},
