se from a selection of different types of business magazines, including banking, marketing, or personal finance, then select the price range you\u2019re looking for, and we\u2019ll create a list of products that meet your criteria. Business magazines offer perspectives from top minds in the field, so you can better understand a wide variety of topics. Investment tips, market analysis, new trends across different industries, and profiles of rising stars in the business world are just a few of the countless features you\u2019ll have access to. You can give a business magazine subscription to a friend or family member as a gift that lasts all year. Simply enter the recipient\u2019s address as the delivery location, and they\u2019ll start receiving new issues straight to their door. Business magazines from Amazon.com can give you an insider\u2019s perspective into finance and economics, so you can stay at the top of your game.", "parent_text": "Magazines", "parent_catid": 72, "keyword_density": {"business magazines": "4.4", "amazoncom": "0.8", "business magazines from amazoncom": "1.1", "magazines": "3.0", "business": "3.0"}, "department_id": 7},
