{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 64, "catid": 858, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_599858_nr_n_6?rh=n%3A599858%2Cn%3A%21599872%2Cn%3A602324&bbn=599872&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=599872", "text": "Computers & Internet", "description_title": "Technology Magazines from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/magazines/b/ref=sd_allcat_magazines/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=599858", "keyword_count": {"technology": 10, "amazoncom": 2, "magazines": 12, "technology magazines": 8}, "description_wc": 345, "description_text": "Technology magazines are your source for the latest news and information from dozens of high-tech fields like computer science, graphic design, electronics and hardware, and more. From highly technical industry publications to general interest magazines, you\u2019ll find a wide variety of technology magazines well suited to every interest level. At Amazon.com, we offer many technology magazines focused on software development and computer science. From OS specific industry magazines to more conceptual publications covering the latest developments in programming, there\u2019s something to suit every developer and software engineer. You can view and control all your magazines with our subscription manager. We put everything you need in one convenient place, so you can update delivery and billing addresses, renew subscriptions, and check delivery dates for all your subscriptions. You can even add magazines to your subscription manager that you didn\u2019t purchase from Amazon.com, and renew at the same price you initially paid. Most technology magazines are available on a yearly subscription basis, but many are also offered for two-year subscriptions at a discounted price. Technology magazines aren\u2019t limited to just computer science. You\u2019ll also find a variety of publications covering the latest info about digital music production, graphic design, and gaming technology. Bestselling favorites include Wired , Popular Mechanics , and MAKE: Magazine . These technology magazines offer news and information from around the world, detail technological achievements of all kinds, and even provide project ideas for technologically inclined readers. No matter how involved you are in the tech industry, there\u2019s a magazine that can help you learn more about the ever-changing word of technology, science, computers, and engineering. Technology magazines make great gifts for inquisitive friends and family. Simply add your chosen recipient\u2019s address to the delivery field, and they\u2019ll start receiving new issues right away. You can even send a personalized e-mail or printed note to let them know you\u2019re thinking of them. Technology magazines cover the world of cutting-edge science, from astronomy to nano-scale engineering, and everything in-between.", "parent_text": "Magazines", "parent_catid": 72, "keyword_density": {"magazines": "3.5", "amazoncom": "0.6", "technology": "2.9", "technology magazines": "4.7"}, "department_id": 7},
{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 91, "catid": 859, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_599858_nr_n_7?rh=n%3A599858%2Cn%3A%21599872%2Cn%3A602334&bbn=599872&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=599872", "text": "Cooking, Food & Wine", "description_title": "Cooking Magazines from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/magazines/b/ref=sd_allcat_magazines/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=599858", "keyword_count": {"cooking magazines": 8, "amazoncom": 4, "cooking": 10, "magazines": 10}, "description_wc": 345, "description_text": "Cooking magazines are a fantastic source for new recipes, summer grilling tips, Christmas baking ideas, exciting ethnic dishes, and countless other ways to enjoy food, wine, and good company. From general food and drink magazines, to specialized publications on baking, organic, and natural foods, and periodicals about the restaurant industry, there\u2019s a wide array of cooking magazines to choose from at Amazon.com. At Amazon.com, we make it easy to choose cooking magazines that you like. Our helpful product filters let you select different culinary specializations, so whether you\u2019re interested in healthy cooking, pastries, or even brewing, finding the right magazine is just a few clicks away. With our subscription manager, you can easily keep track of all the magazines you receive through Amazon.com. Quickly check when your last issue was delivered, when you need to renew, how much your subscriptions cost, and more. Our wide selection of cooking magazines includes popular favorites like Bon Appetit, Everyday with Rachel Ray, Food Network Magazine, Cook\u2019s Illustrated, Martha Stewart Living, and many more. If you already have a subscription to a particular cooking magazine, you can renew it with Amazon.com, or transfer the subscription to your subscription manager, which can be a helpful way to organize all of your magazine subscriptions in one convenient place. Finding new recipes can revitalize your energy in the kitchen. If you love to cook, but want to try something new, cooking magazines can give you fresh, exciting ideas every month when the new issue arrives. If you\u2019re trying out a new diet, you can browse our selection of cooking magazines that feature healthy and alternative recipes, including vegetarian, organic, and fitness-oriented ideas. Subscriptions to cooking magazines can make a great gift for the foodie in your life. All you need is the recipient\u2019s address, and you can send your friends or family a whole year worth of delicious recipes and kitchen ideas. For great new recipe ideas and tips for around the kitchen, look for cooking magazines focused on the tastes and styles you like best.", "parent_text": "Magazines", "parent_catid": 72, "keyword_density": {"cooking magazines": "4.6", "amazoncom": "1.2", "cooking": "2.9", "magazines": "2.9"}, "department_id": 7},
{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 162, "catid": 860, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_599858_nr_n_8?rh=n%3A599858%2Cn%3A%21599872%2Cn%3A769100&bbn=599872&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=599872", "text": "Crafts & Hobbies", "description_title": "Craft Magazines from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/magazines/b/ref=sd_allcat_magazines/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=599858", "keyword_count": {"magazines": 10, "amazoncom": 3, "craft": 10, "craft magazines": 6}, "description_wc": 313, "description_text": "Whether you\u2019re a quilting fanatic, love glass blowing, or are a professional puppeteer, craft magazines are a great way of staying up-to-date with the latest news, trends, and looks. From candle making and kids\u2019 crafts to fashion and woodworking, Amazon.com features a large selection of craft magazines to choose from. With well-known titles like Threads, Country Sampler, Crochet Today! , and Popular Woodworking available online, it\u2019s easy to find the magazines that best align with your own interests and hobbies. Featuring full articles, features, columns, photos, and home guides, you can get the knowledge you want delivered straight to your door. A great gift for hobbyist, professionals, and beginners alike, craft magazines range from framing, lapidary, and patchwork to cross-stitching, dollhouses, and scrapbooking. We offer a wide variety of popular magazines for crafting, and whether it\u2019s the feature articles, the included patterns, or the current trends, craft magazines are a monthly go-to for crafters looking for creative inspiration and motivation in their own work. Available in different prices and subscription lengths, magazines are delivered to any specified address and can be set for auto-renewal for continued deliveries after the expiration date. We also feature discount and low prices on new and renewal subscriptions. Our Craft Magazines Store has a variety of hobby related titles to inform and teach about your favorite pastimes. Receive monthly inspiration, innovation, and patterns for quilting, sewing, woodworking, and beadwork or read up on the latest radio operation, model trains, and metal work news. You can keep track of all your magazines with our Magazine Subscription Manager, available online. Easily report problems, change addresses, and send gift notifications for magazine subscriptions purchased through and outside of Amazon.com. For monthly inspiration and full-coverage interests, you can keep calm and craft on with Amazon.com\u2019s selection of hobby and craft magazines.", "parent_text": "Magazines", "parent_catid": 72, "keyword_density": {"craft magazines": "3.8", "amazoncom": "1.0", "craft": "3.2", "magazines": "3.2"}, "department_id": 7},
{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 398, "catid": 861, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_599858_nr_n_9?rh=n%3A599858%2Cn%3A%21599872%2Cn%3A252511011&bbn=599872&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=599872", "text": "Education", "description_title": "Education Magazines from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/magazines/b/ref=sd_allcat_magazines/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=599858", "keyword_count": {"magazines": 7, "amazoncom": 2, "education": 9, "education magazines": 6}, "description_wc": 318, "description_text": "Whether you\u2019re looking for new enrichment materials to introduce to your little ones or are in charge of a learning-positive classroom or preschool, education magazines are a great source of interesting, kid-friendly knowledge. No matter what age your kids are, learning about the world around them is important for growth, curiosity, and overall smarts. From grade level and easily digestible publications like Horn Book Magazine , Highlights , and Calliope , to more focused titles like Teacher\u2019s Helper , Bien Dire , and Home Education Magazine , get the education magazines, teaching materials, and aids you want from Amazon.com. Perfect for light afternoon reading, keeping kids busy at night, or as a general reference, education magazines targeted at kids often include relatable and comforting cartoons, creatures, and characters. In this format, the information is more accessible and interesting to children who want to learn about it. Many also include games, puzzles, and activities\u2014like crosswords, popular science quizzes, fun jokes, and educational submissions\u2014that further engage young minds while teaching. With education magazines for small children and teenagers alike, you can find the materials you want to keep your child or student learning through the summer, on breaks, and as a supplement to school curriculums. Simply browse for the magazines that fit your needs, or sort by \u2018new and