{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 66, "catid": 866, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_599858_nr_n_14?rh=n%3A599858%2Cn%3A%21599872%2Cn%3A602340&bbn=599872&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=599872", "text": "Health, Mind & Body", "description_title": "Health and Fitness Magazines from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/magazines/b/ref=sd_allcat_magazines/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=599858", "keyword_count": {"health and fitness magazines from amazoncom": 1, "amazoncom": 4, "health and fitness": 9, "magazines": 9, "fitness": 13, "health and fitness magazines": 6, "health": 15}, "description_wc": 342, "description_text": "From perfecting a headstand in yoga class to learning the tastiest vegetarian recipes and finding the best fitness routines for your needs, health and fitness magazines can help you explore, experiment, and exercise in new and exciting ways. No matter the subject you\u2019re looking for, subscriptions to health and fitness magazines can help you improve your techniques, and stay up-to-date on all the trends and changes in your preferred health and fitness zones. Whether you\u2019re looking for health and fitness magazines for men or for women, Amazon.com offers a wide range on a variety of topics. If you\u2019re interested in men\u2019s or women\u2019s health, you can choose from magazines like Men\u2019s Health, Women\u2019s Health, Shape, Muscle & Fitness , and more. If you\u2019re looking for nutrition or alternative medicine options, you can select everything from Vegetarian Times, EatingWell, Spirituality & Health , and more. We also offer a range of magazines about relationships, psychology, beauty and fashion, and weight loss as well. When you subscribe to health and fitness magazines, you can keep up-to-date on all your subscriptions by using the handy subscription manager Amazon.com offers. Plus, you can even give gift subscriptions, so whether your intended prefers to stay abreast on yoga changes or different diets, you can find magazines like Yoga Journal, Outside, Cooking Light , and more all right here. Simply include the name and address of your intended recipient, and Amazon.com will ensure they get the latest issues of their gift subscription on time. Our selection of health and fitness magazines can help you do everything from improve your fitness to explore alternative health and fitness styles, and more. With alternative selections like Qi: Journal of Traditional Eastern Health & Fitness , and contemporary favorites like Health , you can find all the news you need for your favorite health and fitness activities. With health and fitness magazines from Amazon.com, you can find all the articles you need to get your heart rate up and get your brain inspired.", "parent_text": "Magazines", "parent_catid": 72, "keyword_density": {"health and fitness magazines from amazoncom": "1.8", "amazoncom": "1.2", "health and fitness": "8.0", "magazines": "2.7", "fitness": "3.9", "health and fitness magazines": "7.1", "health": "4.5"}, "department_id": 7},
{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 491, "catid": 867, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_599858_nr_n_15?rh=n%3A599858%2Cn%3A%21599872%2Cn%3A602342&bbn=599872&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=599872", "text": "History", "description_title": "History Magazines from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/magazines/b/ref=sd_allcat_magazines/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=599858", "keyword_count": {"history magazines from amazoncom": 1, "magazines": 11, "amazoncom": 2, "history magazines": 7, "history": 15}, "description_wc": 321, "description_text": "Whether you\u2019re looking for an educational pastime or you can\u2019t get enough of learning about a specific time period or region\u2019s history, the history magazines from Amazon.com can provide you with what you\u2019re looking for. We have a wide variety of history magazines to choose from. If you\u2019re a military history buff who loves to hear new, uncovered facts and stories from World War II, or other military events, you\u2019ll love magazines like America in WWII , Military Heritage , and more. There are also a huge assortment of magazines about other great moments and historical events in the history of the United States. You can find history magazines dedicated to American genealogy, archeological finds of the Native American cultures, or events of cultural important in the early 20th century, and more. If you\u2019re looking for magazine subscriptions on a budget, you can try filtering your search by price to see some of the most affordable history magazines available. If you\u2019re a cosmopolitan history enthusiast, we also carry many history magazines focused on the history of Europe and other regions. You can read magazines that feature a new selection of highlighted historical subjects, such as Ancient Rome, Egypt\u2019s early civilization, and the Middle Ages and medieval history, as well as magazines dedicated to specific regions and topics. Scottish Life ,