{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 551, "catid": 868, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_599858_nr_n_16?rh=n%3A599858%2Cn%3A%21599872%2Cn%3A602344&bbn=599872&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=599872", "text": "Home & Garden", "description_title": "Home Magazines from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/magazines/b/ref=sd_allcat_magazines/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=599858", "keyword_count": {"home": 11, "amazoncom": 3, "magazines": 8, "home magazines": 6, "home magazines from amazoncom": 1}, "description_wc": 308, "description_text": "Whether you\u2019re interested in the latest interior design trends, rising architects in the industry, new tips and suggestions for your home garden, or entertaining innovations, make sure you\u2019re up-to-date with the latest news and features with Amazon.com\u2019s variety of home magazines. Covering everything from farming and horticulture to small home and cottage living and animal care and weddings, we feature a large selection of home magazines and subscriptions to choose from. With well-known titles like Country Living , Sunset , Better Homes and Gardens , and Dwell , you can get all the articles, features, pictures, and columns you\u2019re interested in delivered regularly. From top-rated and bestselling general topics to specific home magazines, you can enjoy our same low prices on both new and renewal subscriptions. The perfect gift for hobby craftsman, log home connoisseurs, tech fanatics, or anyone interested in home and garden, magazine subscriptions are an easy and instant gift idea that can span days, months, and years. Available in different prices, number of issues, subscription lengths, and more, you can easily personalize subscriptions to home magazines to your own tastes or to your giftee\u2019s preferences. Home magazines can be delivered to the address you choose, making it easy to have monthly inspiration on your doorstep with every issue. Sorted into convenient c