{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 22030, "catid": 872, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_599858_nr_n_20?rh=n%3A599858%2Cn%3A%21599872%2Cn%3A602348&bbn=599872&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=599872", "text": "Lifestyle & Cultures", "description_title": "Lifestyle Magazines from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/magazines/b/ref=sd_allcat_magazines/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=599858", "keyword_count": {"magazines": 8, "amazoncom": 2, "lifestyle magazines": 6, "lifestyle": 7}, "description_wc": 308, "description_text": "Whether you\u2019re an intense movie fan who wants the latest news on your doorstep every month or new parents looking for helpful family and parenting advice, cultural and lifestyle magazines deliver a wealth of news, tips, recommendations, features, and more with every issue. From celebrity news and health breakthroughs to men\u2019s interest and travel, Amazon.com offers a wide variety of lifestyle magazines to satisfy many diverse tastes and interests. Featuring well-known titles with everything from People , Vanity Fair , O: The Oprah Magazine , and Esquire , to Mental Floss and National Geographic Traveler , you can get the celebrity interviews, vacation tips, movie reviews, photo stories, features, and columns you\u2019re interested in delivered straight to your door through our various lifestyle magazines and subscriptions. A great gift for anyone interested in cultural and lifestyle topics, magazine subscriptions are a personal gift that keeps on giving for the remainder of the subscription. Covering subjects ranging from movies, television, and pop culture to international publications, religion, and kids and family, lifestyle magazines are a go-to for monthly entertainment, features, life tips, and recommendations. Available in different subscription lengths and prices, all magazines are delivered to the specified address, bringing innovation and inspiration to you. We also feature low prices on new and renewal subscriptions with various auto-renewal options. Keeping track of all your lifestyle magazines and subscriptions is a breeze when you use our Magazine Subscription Manager, available online. Easily change addresses, report problems, send gift notifications, and monitor expiration dates from one place, no matter how many magazines you subscribe to. You can also add outside magazine subscriptions, for complete control. Convenient, easy, informative; magazine subscriptions from Amazon.com brings you a wide range of lifestyle magazines to fit any interest you have, from psychology and relationships to international travel and golf.", "parent_text": "Magazines", "parent_catid": 72, "keyword_density": {"lifestyle": "2.3", "amazoncom": "0.7", "lifestyle magazines": "4.0", "magazines": "2.6"}, "department_id": 7},
{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 393, "catid": 873, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_599858_nr_n_21?rh=n%3A599858%2Cn%3A%21599872%2Cn%3A602350&bbn=599872&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=599872", "text": "Literary Magazines & Journals", "description_title": "Literary Magazines from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/magazines/b/ref=sd_allcat_magazines/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=599858", "keyword_count": {"literary magazines from amazoncom": 1, "amazoncom": 2, "magazines": 8, "literary magazines": 7}, "description_wc": 356, "description_text": "If your love for words is like the red, red rose that\u2019s newly sprung in June, literary magazines from Amazon.com could be a welcome boon. Discover some of the most engaging and enriching new poetry, fiction, and non-fiction that\u2019s available in some of our journals and publications. We have a wide variety of fantastic literary magazines for you to choose from. Choose by genre to find stories, poetry, and essays in the subject of your choice. Literature and fiction magazines such as the New Yorker , Missouri Review , Bookmarks , and more will keep your mind stimulated with some of the most intricate stories, well-crafted poetry, and cutting-edge non-fiction. Literary magazines focused on mystery and suspense, including The Strand and Ellery Queen\u2019s Mystery Magazine , will leave you nervous and thrilled to turn the next page. Plus, our science fiction and fantasy selections, like Analog , Asimov\u2019s , and Fantasy & Science Fiction , deliver a sense of wonder second to none. Fans of poetry will find many of our literary magazines dedicated to one of the most demanding forms of writing. Discover inspiring lines and mind-bending metaphors in some of the top poetry publications, including Poetry , American Poetry Review , and Spoon River Poetry Review . By flipping through the pages, reading short, sharp poems, you could be discovering the next Emily Dickinson, Dylan Thomas, or William Carlos Williams. Literary magazines like Poets & Writers are also great resources for budding poets who want news on upcoming writer\u2019s retreats, tips from writing professionals, and information on where to publish your own verse. Many of our literary magazines also tackle some of the biggest issues facing us today. The Atlantic , Harper\u2019s Magazine , Believer , and others include articles, stories and poetry about controversial issues and heated subject matter. It\u2019s a great way to read about what struggles the country is going through from some of the most sharp-tongued journalists and storytellers out there. You can find enough literary magazines to feed your craving for well-written stories and poetry at Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Magazines", "parent_catid": 72, "keyword_density": {"literary magazines from amazoncom": "1.2", "amazoncom": "0.6", "magazines": "2.3", "literary magazines": "4.1"}, "department_id": 7},
