{"department_text": "Movies, Music & Games", "nr_products": 6907, "catid": 893, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_2650363011_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A2625373011%2Cp_n_theme_browse-bin%3A2650363011%2Cn%3A%212625374011%2Cn%3A2649513011&bbn=2650363011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833387&rnid=2625374011", "text": "TV", "description_title": "TV Shows on DVD from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/movies-tv-dvd-bluray/b/ref=sd_allcat_mov/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=2625373011", "keyword_count": {"tv": 12, "amazoncom": 1, "tv shows": 10, "tv shows on dvd": 8, "shows": 17}, "description_wc": 367, "description_text": "You can catch up on all your favorite television whenever you\u2019re in the mood with TV shows on DVD and Blu-ray. From classic favorites like Cheers and M.A.S.H. to new releases of hit shows, there are thousands of fantastic titles to choose from. At Amazon.com, we offer a complete selection of TV shows on DVD, ranging from the early days of live broadcast to the latest seasons of current hit shows. You\u2019ll find collections of classic shows like I Love Lucy , the original Star Trek series and Star Trek: The Next Generation , The Andy Griffith Show , and other beloved programs from the 50s and 60s. Many of these great old TV shows have been re-mastered for HDTV, and look better than ever. If you\u2019re interested in great TV shows on DVD from the 1970s and 80s, you can find complete collections of hilarious comedies, exciting crime dramas, and dozens of other genres. To find TV shows on DVD that you\u2019re interested in, you can use our helpful product filters. Choose the decades, networks, and genres you like, and we\u2019ll create a list of products that meet your criteria. Whether you\u2019re a fan of ABC sitcoms from the 1990s, cutting edge premium cable shows, or reality TV, we make it quick and easy to find the shows you want to watch. Since many TV shows on DVD and Blu-ray are eligible for free delivery, you can get your favorite programs sent straight to your door at no additional cost. Watching suspenseful and exciting TV shows on DVD makes the weekly cliffhangers a lot easier to deal with -- just press play on the next episode and start watching. If you can\u2019t get enough of your favorite shows, browse our selection of boxed sets of TV shows on DVD to enjoy every episode a show has to offer. You\u2019ll only have to stop watching when it\u2019s time to make more popcorn. TV shows on DVD are a convenient way to enjoy thousands of fantastic TV shows from many different eras of television, including all-time favorites, brand new releases, and hard to find independent shows.", "parent_text": "Movies & TV", "parent_catid": 77, "keyword_density": {"tv": "3.3", "amazoncom": "0.3", "tv shows": "5.5", "tv shows on dvd": "8.8", "shows": "4.7"}, "department_id": 8},
