{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 11271, "catid": 905, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_468642_nr_n_11?rh=n%3A468642%2Cn%3A%2111846801%2Cn%3A11075221&bbn=11846801&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833356&rnid=11846801", "text": "Sony PSP", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Popcap Store", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/computer-video-games-hardware-accessories/b/ref=sd_allcat_cvg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=468642", "keyword_count": {"store": 1}, "description_wc": 4, "description_text": "See all Brand Stores", "parent_text": "Video Games", "parent_catid": 91, "keyword_density": {"store": "25.0"}, "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 36587, "catid": 906, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_468642_nr_n_12?rh=n%3A468642%2Cn%3A%2111846801%2Cn%3A294940&bbn=11846801&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833356&rnid=11846801", "text": "More Systems", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Retro Games from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/computer-video-games-hardware-accessories/b/ref=sd_allcat_cvg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=468642", "keyword_count": {"retro games": 7, "amazoncom": 2, "retro": 8}, "description_wc": 334, "description_text": "If you\u2019re the kind of gamer who thinks the industry was at its best before motion-sensing controls and other bells and whistles, browse the retro games at Amazon.com to rediscover your favorite titles from a simpler time. You\u2019ll find a wide selection of retro games for legendary consoles. You can relive the golden age of the home arcade with classic titles for Atari, including Q*Bert, Pac-Man, Frogger, and more. Spurred on the by the popularity of early Atari systems, one of the most successful game consoles of all time was the original Nintendo Entertainment System, originally released in 1985. The cutting edge 8-bit graphics and sound wowed gamers, and titles like Super Mario Brothers, The Legend of Zelda, Castlevania and Final Fantasy are still producing sequels today. You can experience the roots of video game culture with retro games for these and other classic systems. In the \u201890s, televisions got bigger, and gaming consoles got more powerful. Nintendo and Sega fought for the top spot with the Super Nintendo Entertainment System, and the Sega Genesis, respectively. You\u2019ll find all the retro games for SNES and Genesis you loved back in the day in one convenient spot. From Golden Axe to Mega Man X, all your favorite 16-bit titles are available at the Amazon.com Retro games store. Nintendo 64 and PlayStation ushered in a new era of gaming. Polygons replaced pixels, and 3D rendering entered into the gaming vocabulary. Retro gaming hits like Crash Bandicoot, Mario Kart 64, and 007: Goldeneye pushed the limits of technology, and created the most realistic virtual environments seen up to that point. We also have some retro games for systems that might not feel as old as they are, including PlayStation 2, Nintendo GameCube, and the original Xbox. From the moment you get your sword in the Legend of Zelda, to doing a barrel roll in Star Fox 64, now you can relive classic scenes from all your favorite retro games.", "parent_text": "Video Games", "parent_catid": 91, "keyword_density": {"retro games": "4.2", "amazoncom": "0.6", "retro": "2.4"}, "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 7147, "catid": 907, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_468642_nr_n_13?rh=n%3A468642%2Cn%3A%2111846801%2Cn%3A979455011&bbn=11846801&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833356&rnid=11846801", "text": "Digital Games", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Want to see your game on Amazon?", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/computer-video-games-hardware-accessories/b/ref=sd_allcat_cvg/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=468642", "keyword_count": {"game on amazon": 1, "game": 2}, "description_wc": 19, "description_text": "Do you make games? Are you interested in selling your game on Amazon? Get started here . \u203a Learn more", "parent_text": "Video Games", "parent_catid": 91, "keyword_density": {"game on amazon": "16.7", "game": "11.1"}, "department_id": 9},
{"nr_products": 277098, "catid": 908, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172630_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A172623%2Cn%3A172630%2Cn%3A290438&bbn=172630&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833356&rnid=172630", "text": "MP3 Player Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_wc": 0, "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/MP3-Players-Audio-Video/b/ref=sd_allcat_mp3/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=172630", "parent_text": "MP3 Players & Portable Speakers", "parent_catid": 92, "department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 5044, "catid": 909, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_11091801_nr_n_3?rh=n%3A11091801%2Cn%3A%2111965861%2Cn%3A11969981&bbn=11965861&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833355&rnid=11965861", "text": "Keyboards", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Keyboards from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/musical-instruments-accessories-sound-recording/b/ref=sd_allcat_mi/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=11091801", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 1, "keyboards": 6}, "description_wc": 349, "description_text": "For musicians who want a more versatile tonal palette than an acoustic piano can provide, or who need to quickly and easily pack up their instrument and head out, portable keyboards are the ultimate in convenience and tone. Find all the keyboards, digital pianos, and synthesizers to keep making music away from a traditional piano in the Keyboard Store at Amazon.com. Digital pianos are keyboards designed to look and play more like acoustic pianos than their portable counterparts. They\u2019re often finished in wood grain, and feature premium conveniences like 88-key fingerboards, and built-in sustain pedals. For keyboard players who want a robust weighted action, digital pianos closely resemble acoustic instruments. Digital pianos are ideal for musicians who want to play quietly. Simply plug a pair of quality headphones in, and enjoy the full effect of a grand piano all to yourself. If you need a keyboard that\u2019s easy to pack up and bring to every rehearsal and gig, we offer a variety of convenient portable keyboards. Lightweight models from Yamaha and Casio combine the versatility of a full-featured keyboard with incredible portability, so you can pack up and go at a moment\u2019s notice. Whether you\u2019re plugging into a PA system, or using the keyboard\u2019s internal speakers, the convenience of a truly portable keyboard will allow you to play anywhere and everywhere you want. If you\u2019re more into Tiesto than Tchaikovsky, browse our selection of keyboard synthesizers from Novation, Roland, Korg, and more. You\u2019ll find electro-classics like the microKorg, complete with a built-in vocoder, and the UltraNova, featuring wavetable synthesis. Unlike digital pianos and other keyboards, synthesizers don\u2019t playback prerecorded sounds when you play--their specially designed circuitry actually generates a wave form, which you can customize and manipulate heavily to tailor your sound. You don\u2019t have to be the next Mozart to enjoy playing piano. For beginners and lifelong players alike, the convenience, portability, and versatility of keyboards and digital pianos make it easy and fun to play music at home or on the go.", "parent_text": "Musical Instruments", "parent_catid": 94, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.3", "keyboards": "1.7"}, "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 15855, "catid": 910, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_11091801_nr_n_4?rh=n%3A11091801%2Cn%3A%2111965861%2Cn%3A405758011&bbn=11965861&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833355&rnid=11965861", "text": "Band & Orchestra", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Band & Orchestra Instruments from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/musical-instruments-accessories-sound-recording/b/ref=sd_allcat_mi/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=11091801", "keyword_count": {"instruments": 9, "orchestra": 11, "band orchestra": 1, "band": 11, "amazoncom": 1, "orchestra instruments": 3}, "description_wc": 439, "description_text": "One of the great pleasures of life is the beautiful sound made by the harmony, cooperation, and synchronization of many instruments in unison. Playing music in a band or orchestra--from classical chamber music ensembles to peppy marching band performances\u2014is one of the most beloved forms of making music together with other people. Whether it\u2019s the drama of a crescendo in the orchestra or the toe-tapping rhythms of a big band performance, playing an instrument with others is a great way to add music to your life. In celebration of students of music everywhere, Amazon.com offers quality band and orchestra instruments and accessories to fully equip our customers with some of the best musical equipment on the market. In our Band & Orchestra store, you can find the instruments and accessories you\u2019re looking for--from woodwinds and brass to orchestral strings--instruments that are great for both students and masters of the musical craft. Browse our string instrument selection for a variety of cellos, violins, and violas from some of the most popular names in orchestra instruments, including Mendini, Yahama, and Cecilio. Our instrument accessories, such as resin for your bows and replacement strings, can keep you fiddling and pizzicato-ing to your heart\u2019s content. Our selection of brass instruments and woodwinds is unparalleled. Because they\u2019re lightweight and versatile, brass and woodwinds are great starting instruments for younger band and orchestra students. French horns, baritones, bugles, sousaphones, trumpets, cornets, and euphoniums come in a variety of finishes and metal plating, so you can choose the right equipment recommended by the music teacher. You can even find colored trombones for maximum pep and school spirit. For the woodwind players in your life, you can find the rich and warm sounds of a wide selection of woodwind instruments, from bassoons, clarinets, English horns, and oboes, to flutes, piccolos, recorders, and saxophones. You\u2019ll also find the accessories and parts to keep your instrument clean and to protect your sound quality and investment. Band and orchestra percussionists will appreciate how easy it is to find the right snares, basses, sticks, mallets, and accessories. For marching bands, we offer carriers and slings that drum lines need to hold up their drums. They\u2019re strong and reliable, freeing your hands to rap out intricate beats and drum rolls. Band and orchestra cymbals are ideal for pieces that require their colorful and dramatic splashes of sound. Add the beauty of band and orchestra music to your life. From the budding violinist, to the master of jazz saxophone, you\u2019ll find quality band and orchestra instruments for all your musical endeavors.", "parent_text": "Musical Instruments", "parent_catid": 94, "keyword_density": {"instruments": "2.1", "orchestra": "2.5", "band orchestra": "0.5", "band": "2.5", "amazoncom": "0.2", "orchestra instruments": "1.4"}, "department_id": 9},
{"nr_products": 27657, "catid": 911, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_11091801_nr_n_5?rh=n%3A11091801%2Cn%3A%2111965861%2Cn%3A11972411&bbn=11965861&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833355&rnid=11965861", "text": "Folk & World Instruments", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_wc": 0, "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/musical-instruments-accessories-sound-recording/b/ref=sd_allcat_mi/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=11091801", "parent_text": "Musical Instruments", "parent_catid": 94, "department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 232914, "catid": 912, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_11091801_nr_n_6?rh=n%3A11091801%2Cn%3A%2111965861%2Cn%3A11965871&bbn=11965861&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833355&rnid=11965861", "text": "Instrument Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Instrument Accessories from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/musical-instruments-accessories-sound-recording/b/ref=sd_allcat_mi/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=11091801", "keyword_count": {"instrument": 15, "amazoncom": 2, "accessories": 7, "instrument accessories": 5}, "description_wc": 359, "description_text": "Whether you play jazz guitar for an old-fashioned speakeasy, or you rock the tuba for an experimental ska band, every musical instrument needs reliable accessories to keep its sound and quality the best it can be. Amazon.com offers a wide variety of musical instrument accessories so you can focus on your musical art, and not on maintenance. Before you play any instrument, you want to make sure your pitch and tune are perfect. Everything from guitars and ukuleles to drums and pianos need to be tuned to the right pitch or key, and we have specialized instrument accessories for a wide selection of instruments. Electric tuners will make sure you train your ear and sound great on stage or in your living room. We also have a wide variety of capos to swiftly and easily switch keys on any stringed instrument. For musicians on the go, whether you\u2019re heading out to rock a concert hall or you\u2019re going down the road to your music lessons, having a trustworthy bag or case is crucial. Since every bump has the potential to change the sound of your instrument, it\u2019s important to keep them safely stored and protected in these instrument accessories. Our instrument straps can also help you protect your neck and back as well, and will help you play your bass guitar, saxophone, or snare drum with added ease and correct technique. It\u2019s a common saying that a musician gets better as his or her instrument gets worse. That\u2019s only because the practice involved in learning a new musical craft puts a lot of stress on the instruments. When your strings, sticks, mouthpieces, or reeds need a quick replacement, we have the instrument accessories you need. We have replacement parts and accessories for just about any instrument, including power cords for electric keyboards and valve oil for brass instruments. Hours of browsing music stores for the right items can\u2019t make you a better musician--only practice can. Amazon.com makes it easy to find the right parts and instrument accessories so you can focus on making your music and sharing it with the world.", "parent_text": "Musical Instruments", "parent_catid": 94, "keyword_density": {"instrument": "4.2", "amazoncom": "0.6", "accessories": "1.9", "instrument accessories": "2.8"}, "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 8017, "catid": 913, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_11091801_nr_n_7?rh=n%3A11091801%2Cn%3A%2111965861%2Cn%3A11973881&bbn=11965861&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833355&rnid=11965861", "text": "DJ, Electronic Music & Karaoke", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "DJ Equipment from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/musical-instruments-accessories-sound-recording/b/ref=sd_allcat_mi/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=11091801", "keyword_count": {"equipment": 6, "amazoncom": 2, "dj": 10, "dj equipment": 4}, "description_wc": 328, "description_text": "Being a DJ is about spinning a mixture of music, lighting, and timing to create ambience and the perfect environment for guests to enjoy their night out. With the DJ equipment and synthesizers from Amazon.com in your booth, you can drop beats with the best of them. Our DJ mixers, controllers and other equipment can help you scratch, mix, loop and more with ease. Ditch the vinyl, now you can hook up electronic turn tables to your computer or MP3 player and mix your entire library. Many of our models are portable enough that you can always be ready to DJ at a moment\u2019s notice. If you need your DJ equipment fast, we have a variety of expedited shipping options, so you can get the party started on time. When the club or the party gets loud and rowdy, every DJ needs a reliable pair of headphones. You need to keep an ear for the musical cues, and make sure the levels are right to ensure a smooth, musical experience. Our DJ headphones block out ambient noise and keep your monitoring cues out of your microphones. Used with your own home computer, our drum machines, synthesizers, and other DJ equipment can even help you create original mixes, mash-ups, and tracks. Now that you have your music all set up, it\u2019s time to add a little light show. We carry a variety of DJ lighting and equipment, including laser lights, fog machines, mirrored disco balls, and more so you can set the mood. Our ribbons of LED lights are ideal for marking off dance floors, adding accent to the architecture of a venue, and decorating to your booth. Our strobes are ideal for when the beat picks up and you want to let the dancers get lost in a sensory experience. When you need an extra oomph to get your next party, reception, or school dance bumping, check out the selection of DJ equipment at Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Musical Instruments", "parent_catid": 94, "keyword_density": {"equipment": "1.8", "amazoncom": "0.6", "dj": "3.0", "dj equipment": "2.4"}, "department_id": 9},
{"nr_products": 39045, "catid": 914, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_11091801_nr_n_8?rh=n%3A11091801%2Cn%3A%2111965861%2Cn%3A405757011&bbn=11965861&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833355&rnid=11965861", "text": "Live Sound & Stage", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_wc": 0, "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/musical-instruments-accessories-sound-recording/b/ref=sd_allcat_mi/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=11091801", "parent_text": "Musical Instruments", "parent_catid": 94, "department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 113739, "catid": 915, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_11091801_nr_n_9?rh=n%3A11091801%2Cn%3A%2111965861%2Cn%3A11973111&bbn=11965861&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833355&rnid=11965861", "text": "Studio Recording Equipment", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Recording Equipment from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/musical-instruments-accessories-sound-recording/b/ref=sd_allcat_mi/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=11091801", "keyword_count": {"recording": 9, "recording equipment": 6, "amazoncom": 3}, "description_wc": 339, "description_text": "You don\u2019t need to wait for a major label to notice you before you start making your own records. Setting up a cutting-edge digital studio with professional, quality recording equipment is easier and more affordable than ever for the first timer, and experienced audio engineers have access to an enormous variety of outstanding mics, preamps, monitors, and other recording equipment. In the age of the digital audio workstation, the heart of most home recording equipment is a quality interface. At Amazon.com, we have a huge selection of home recording gear, whether you need a two-channel interface for recording podcasts and simple music projects, or a 32-channel board for full band recordings. A reliable, great sounding interface is the crucial link between the performance and your computer. All your other recording equipment will be routed through your interface, so it\u2019s important to choose the right model. Browse user reviews written by other musicians to find products with great real-life performance from top brands like Focusrite, M-Audio, and Tascam. From studio staples like the Shure SM57 to newer, trend-setting recording equipment like the Blue Blueberry, you\u2019ll find microphones for vocals, electric guitars, acoustic instruments, and more at Amazon.com. For live applications, dynamic cardioid mics are perfect for vocals, but in the controlled environment of the studio, a large diaphragm condenser mic will more accurately capture the depth and nuance of your performance. Choose from brands like AKG, Sennheiser, and Rode to find the perfect mic for your style and budget. Before you can get your tracks on the radio, they need to be mixed and mastered on accurate, transparent studio monitors. Home speakers equalize and color audio, and make it difficult to mix accurately. What sounds good on one set of home speakers might sound muddy on another, which is why professionals rely on recording equipment like quality monitors to solidify their mixes. From legendary Yamaha reference monitors, to affordable KRKs, there\u2019s a set of speakers for every studio at Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Musical Instruments", "parent_catid": 94, "keyword_density": {"recording": "2.7", "recording equipment": "3.5", "amazoncom": "0.9"}, "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 57, "catid": 916, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_599858_nr_n_23?rh=n%3A599858%2Cn%3A%21599872%2Cn%3A602352&bbn=599872&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=599872", "text": "Men's Interest", "description_title": "Save When You Subscribe to", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/magazines/b/ref=sd_allcat_magazines/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=599858", "keyword_count": {"subscribe": 1}, "description_wc": 58, "description_text": "Are you a successful, professional man who wants greater control over his physical, mental and emotional lives? Then Men\u2019s Health is for you, with in-depth reporting on everything from fashion and grooming to health and nutrition as well as cutting-edge gear, the latest in entertainment and more. \u2022 Subscribe to Men's Health for $49.90 $24.94", "parent_text": "Magazines", "parent_catid": 72, "keyword_density": {"subscribe": "1.7"}, "department_id": 7},
