{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 84, "catid": 918, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_599858_nr_n_25?rh=n%3A599858%2Cn%3A%21599872%2Cn%3A602358&bbn=599872&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=599872", "text": "News & Politics", "description_title": "Great Deals on Bestsellers:", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/magazines/b/ref=sd_allcat_magazines/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=599858", "keyword_count": {}, "description_wc": 47, "description_text": "Week after week, The New Yorker keeps its readers current. Don't miss the famous fiction and poetry from The New Yorker , along with in-depth reporting, notable cartoons, surprising opinions, sharp wit, and the best in prose. \u2022 Subscribe to The New Yorker for $114.77 $39.99", "parent_text": "Magazines", "parent_catid": 72, "keyword_density": {}, "department_id": 7},
