{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 810, "catid": 920, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_599858_nr_n_27?rh=n%3A599858%2Cn%3A%21599872%2Cn%3A1040160&bbn=599872&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=599872", "text": "Newspapers", "description_title": "Newspaper Subscriptions from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/magazines/b/ref=sd_allcat_magazines/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=599858", "keyword_count": {"newspaper": 9, "amazoncom": 3, "newspaper subscriptions": 6, "subscriptions": 7}, "description_wc": 352, "description_text": "Stay on top of the latest developments across the globe with newspaper subscriptions to your preferred daily and weekly papers. Domestic and international newspapers are available for delivery across the country, so even if you can\u2019t find a copy of the Jerusalem Post , New Pittsburgh Courier , or even the Mojave Times in your area, you can have it delivered straight to your door daily, weekly, or monthly, depending on circulation. At Amazon.com, we offer a wide variety of newspaper subscriptions to papers from across the country and around the world. Some international newspapers are available on a weekly basis, while others can be delivered daily, like the International Herald Tribune , the New York Times , and many more. When you purchase a newspaper subscription from Amazon.com, it\u2019s easy to manage delivery, payment, and other important details. Our subscription manager gives you a single convenient place to track all of your different subscriptions, so you can change your delivery address, make renewal payments, and find out how many issues are remaining. International newspaper subscriptions are a terrific way to maintain a broad perspective on global news and politics. Sources from Europe, Asia, and Africa offer a local perspective on many global issues, and since you can choose from dozens of international publications to be delivered straight to your door, it\u2019s easier than ever to broaden your horizons. To make it as easy as possible to manage your newspaper subscriptions, our subscription manager allows you to renew publications you\u2019re subscribed to, even if you didn\u2019t subscribe through Amazon.com. This way, you can get all your news and magazines organized in one place quickly and easily. Newspaper subscriptions make a great gift for friends and family who love to stay on top of the latest news and information from around the globe. Simply purchase a subscription, make the lucky recipient\u2019s address the delivery location, and they\u2019ll enjoy a year\u2019s worth of informative news and politics. Newspaper subscriptions are a fantastic way to stay informed and involved in local and global news, politics, and culture.", "parent_text": "Magazines", "parent_catid": 72, "keyword_density": {"newspaper": "2.6", "amazoncom": "0.9", "newspaper subscriptions": "3.4", "subscriptions": "2.0"}, "department_id": 7},
{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 133, "catid": 921, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_599858_nr_n_28?rh=n%3A599858%2Cn%3A%21599872%2Cn%3A253359011&bbn=599872&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=599872", "text": "Outdoors & Nature", "description_title": "Outdoor Magazines from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/magazines/b/ref=sd_allcat_magazines/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=599858", "keyword_count": {"outdoor magazines": 6, "magazines": 9, "amazoncom": 4, "outdoor": 14, "outdoor magazines from amazoncom": 1}, "description_wc": 325, "description_text": "It\u2019s time for a trip into the great outdoors. You might be an avid backpacker, a sports-enthusiast in training, or a devotee to birdwatching. No matter your interest, subscriptions to outdoor magazines can help you hone your outdoor skills, improve your performance in outdoor pursuits, and keep you up-to-date on all the trends and changes in your favorite outdoors area. Whether you\u2019re looking for outdoor magazines all about outdoor fitness or conservation, Amazon.com offers a wide range on a variety of topics. If you\u2019re a nature watcher, you can choose from our assortment of birdwatching, flora, fauna, environmental awareness, and nature writing magazines, including National Wildlife, Birds & Blooms , and more. If you\u2019re looking for sports options, you can pick outdoor activity magazines like Runner\u2019s World, Golf Digest , and more. If you\u2019re interested in survival skills or hunting and fishing, we offer a range of outdoor magazines on those options as well. When you subscribe to outdoor magazines, you can keep up-to-date on all your subscriptions by using the handy subscription manager Amazon.com offers. Plus, you can even give gift subscriptions, so whether your intended prefers leisure outdoor activities like boating or likes to rough it in the wild, you can find magazines like Houseboat, Backpacker, Outside, Trailer Life , and more all right here. Simply include the name and address of your intended recipient, and Amazon.com will ensure they get the latest issues of their gift subscription on time. Our selection of outdoor magazines can help you do everything from improve your garden, identify rare birds, and kayak around the world, and more. With selections like Organic Gardening, National Parks, Sea Kayaker , and more, you can find all the contemporary trends and news you need for your favorite outdoor activities. With outdoor magazines from Amazon.com, you can find all the articles you need to give you a breath of fresh air.", "parent_text": "Magazines", "parent_catid": 72, "keyword_density": {"outdoor magazines": "3.7", "outdoor magazines from amazoncom": "1.2", "amazoncom": "1.2", "outdoor": "4.4", "magazines": "2.8"}, "department_id": 7},
{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 348, "catid": 922, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_599858_nr_n_29?rh=n%3A599858%2Cn%3A%21599872%2Cn%3A602330&bbn=599872&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=599872", "text": "Parenting & Families", "description_title": "Parenting Magazines from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/magazines/b/ref=sd_allcat_magazines/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=599858", "keyword_count": {"parenting": 7, "parenting magazines from amazoncom": 2, "magazines": 9, "amazoncom": 5, "parenting magazines": 5}, "description_wc": 367, "description_text": "With topics for everything from temper tantrums to sleep routines to family fun, parenting magazines are a great resource to help you learn more about raising your little ones. No matter the age of your kids, there are always new trends, movements, and ideas available as a resource for parents. When you subscribe to parenting magazines from Amazon.com, you\u2019ll get all the latest news and ideas in the world of parenting, and can pick up new ways to nurture, educate, inspire, and have fun with your kiddos. Whether you\u2019re looking for magazines for yourself or your children, Amazon.com offers a wide range for both of you. If you\u2019re pregnant and preparing to bring a little one into this world, you can choose from our assortment of pregnancy and childbirth magazines. If you\u2019re looking for options to entertain your whole family and keep your kiddos sharp, you can find many educational and family activity magazines. Plus, we also offer children\u2019s magazines so you can give your kids reading material full of information on the environment, literature, and more. You can even subscribe to parenting magazines for yourself and keep up-to-date on all your subscriptions by using the handy subscription manager Amazon.com offers. Plus, you can also give gift subscriptions, so whether your kiddo wants the newest issues of National Geographic Kids , National Geographic Little Kids , Ranger Rick , Highlights , Jack and Jill , Zoobooks , or more, you can find it all here. Simply include the name and address of your intended recipient, and Amazon.com will ensure they get the latest issues of their gift subscription on time. Our selection of parenting magazines can help you stay on track whether you\u2019re looking for the best ways to work and care for your children, help them learn their A-B-Cs and 1-2-3s, and more. With selections like Parents, Working Mother, Scholastic, Parent and Child , and more, you can find all the contemporary tips you need to stay organized and abreast of parenting resources. With parenting magazines from Amazon.com, you and your kids can read up on all the topics that appeal to your interests.", "parent_text": "Magazines", "parent_catid": 72, "keyword_density": {"parenting": "1.9", "parenting magazines from amazoncom": "2.2", "magazines": "2.5", "amazoncom": "1.4", "parenting magazines": "2.8"}, "department_id": 7},
