{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 264, "catid": 926, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_599858_nr_n_33?rh=n%3A599858%2Cn%3A%21599872%2Cn%3A602362&bbn=599872&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=599872", "text": "Religion & Spirituality", "description_title": "Religious Magazines from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/magazines/b/ref=sd_allcat_magazines/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=599858", "keyword_count": {"religious": 9, "amazoncom": 4, "religious magazines": 7, "magazines": 9}, "description_wc": 319, "description_text": "No matter what faith or tradition you celebrate, there are a variety of religious magazines that can help you stay on top of the latest news, editorials, events, and information. From global news with a faith-based perspective to scholarly reviews of religious philosophy, religious magazines offer a wide range of content and perspective. At Amazon.com, you\u2019ll find religious magazines focused on many major faith traditions, including many Christian denominations, Judaism, Islam, new age and spiritual resources, and many others. You can browse many publications focused on religious lifestyles and culture, news and events, philosophy, and scholarship to find religious magazines that appeal to you. When you subscribe to a periodical through Amazon.com, it\u2019s easy to keep track of payment and renewal dates, delivery addresses, and other important details with our subscription manager. We\u2019ve created a single convenient place for you to review and track all of your current subscriptions, no matter what publisher or genres they\u2019re from. If you currently subscribe to any religious magazines or other periodicals, you can renew your subscriptions with Amazon.com and track them with our helpful subscription manager at the same price you currently pay, making it easier than ever to organize all of your print media in one place. When you browse for magazines, we\u2019ll show you the total subscription price, as well as the price per issue. Many magazines are published monthly, while others are quarterly or seasonal. You can give a friend or family member a gift subscription to their favorite religious magazines through Amazon.com. Simply enter the recipient\u2019s address as the delivery location, and they\u2019ll start receiving new issues quickly. We\u2019ll even let them know about your gift with an e-mail, a printed note, or both. Religious magazines offer a spiritual perspective on world news, culture, and events, specific to a wide variety of faith traditions from around the world.", "parent_text": "Magazines", "parent_catid": 72, "keyword_density": {"magazines": "2.8", "amazoncom": "1.3", "religious magazines": "4.4", "religious": "2.8"}, "department_id": 7},
{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 1167, "catid": 927, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_599858_nr_n_34?rh=n%3A599858%2Cn%3A%21599872%2Cn%3A602364&bbn=599872&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=599872", "text": "Science & Nature", "description_title": "Science Magazines from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/magazines/b/ref=sd_allcat_magazines/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=599858", "keyword_count": {"science": 11, "science magazines": 7, "magazines": 11, "amazoncom": 1}, "description_wc": 358, "description_text": "From cutting edge peer-reviewed journals to general interest publications, science magazines are available on a wide variety of topics, from archaeology to zoology. Whether you\u2019re a scientist yourself, or merely interested in understanding more about the world around you, there are science magazines tailored to readers of all kinds, including highly technical publications and more accessible magazines. At Amazon.com, you\u2019ll find a broad selection of science magazines covering dozens of specific topics, as well as many general publications. Stargazers will love our selection of astronomy magazines, including popular favorites like Sky & Telescope and Astronomy , where you\u2019ll find the latest news, equipment reviews, and observation charts. For the most up-to-date medical news, look for medical magazines from the US and around the world, including publications that cover administrative topics like marketing. No matter how many magazines you subscribe to, it\u2019s easy to keep track of all of them with our subscription manager. We\u2019ve created a single convenient place where you can review renewal dates, check when new issues are coming out, and change billing or delivery addresses. If you\u2019re looking for an informative source for science news and information, browse our selection of general interest science magazines that includes bestselling favorites like Popular Science , National Geographic , and Discover . You\u2019ll get the latest news and reports about cutting-edge discoveries and research across all fields of science, including earth science, biology, chemistry, aerospace, and more, complete with in-depth reporting, informative diagrams, and stunning photography. These award-winning science magazines and many others can bring the world of empirical investigation right to your doorstep every month. Science magazines make a terrific gift for friends and family members. You can purchase a subscription, add the recipient\u2019s address as the delivery location, and they\u2019ll start receiving new issues right away. You can notify them with an e-mail or a printed note, so they know who to pat on the back for a the great gift idea. Science magazines bring the natural world into focus and offer the latest news and information from dozens of fields.", "parent_text": "Magazines", "parent_catid": 72, "keyword_density": {"science": "3.1", "science magazines": "4.0", "magazines": "3.1", "amazoncom": "0.3"}, "department_id": 7},
