ness software designed to simplify record keeping and financial planning. Tax preparation is faster and easier when you have guided, automated tools to help you find deductions, calculate depreciation, and estimate returns. Digital storage means you can enter information all year long as it becomes available, and access it quickly when you need it. If your business relies on fast information exchange, consider business software to help make database access, file storage, and communications consistent across your network. Email, word processing, and office software are available in individual or group licenses, so you can get every employee and worksite operating on the same page. Business software from Amazon.com can help you streamline your office, and make day-to-day operations run more smoothly.", "parent_text": "Software", "parent_catid": 101, "keyword_density": {"business software from amazoncom": "1.2", "amazoncom": "0.6", "business software": "3.7", "business": "3.1", "software": "2.8"}, "department_id": 9},
