lters. Simply choose the developer, operating system, and server style you want, and we\u2019ll create a list of products that fit your criteria. Since most of our server software programs have detailed descriptions of their features and functionality, you\u2019ll be sure to choose a product that suits your IT infrastructure well. In addition to creating virtual desktop environments for remote users, server software makes it easy to set up reliable cloud storage for many users across the network. Collaborative work, important data backups, and daily reports can be aggregated, stored, and secured quickly and easily on a customizable schedule. Server software allows you to control and customize your network, so you can integrate the features and capabilities your users need to work efficiently and reliably.", "parent_text": "Software", "parent_catid": 101, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.3", "server software": "4.9", "server": "3.3", "software": "3.0"}, "department_id": 9},
