{"department_text": "Digital Games & Software", "nr_products": 549, "catid": 1009, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1233514011_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A229534%2Cn%3A%2144262011%2Cn%3A1233514011%2Cn%3A229535&bbn=1233514011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833427&rnid=491286", "text": "Business & Office", "description_title": "Business Software from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/pc-mac-software-downloads/b/ref=sd_allcat_dgs_sft/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=1233514011", "keyword_count": {"business software from amazoncom": 1, "amazoncom": 2, "business software": 6, "business": 10, "software": 9}, "description_wc": 321, "description_text": "Business software is available to help make common tasks like tax preparation, document management, marketing, and database management faster, easier, and more consistent. For small and big business alike, accurately tracking and storing important information is crucial to ongoing success. Digitizing records is an effective way to make sure you know exactly how and where to access your important information quickly and easily. At Amazon.com, we offer business software that is tailor-made for all aspects of business, from communications to finances. To make it easy to find the business software that you\u2019re looking for, you can browse for your software with our helpful product filters. Simply choose the type of software you need, such as reporting, spreadsheets, or word processing. Then, choose the operating system and brands that you prefer, and we\u2019ll automatically create a list of products that meet your needs. We feature top brands like Microsoft, Intuit, Nuance Communications Inc., and Corel, so you\u2019ll be sure to find programs that work well for your business. When the new year rolls around and it\u2019s time to start organizing your yearly taxes, one of the most helpful tools at your disposal is quality business software designed to simplify record keeping and financial planning. Tax preparation is faster and easier when you have guided, automated tools to help you find deductions, calculate depreciation, and estimate returns. Digital storage means you can enter information all year long as it becomes available, and access it quickly when you need it. If your business relies on fast information exchange, consider business software to help make database access, file storage, and communications consistent across your network. Email, word processing, and office software are available in individual or group licenses, so you can get every employee and worksite operating on the same page. Business software from Amazon.com can help you streamline your office, and make day-to-day operations run more smoothly.", "parent_text": "Digital Software", "parent_catid": 66, "keyword_density": {"business software from amazoncom": "1.2", "amazoncom": "0.6", "business software": "3.7", "business": "3.1", "software": "2.8"}, "department_id": 6},
{"nr_products": 1177, "catid": 1010, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1233514011_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A229534%2Cn%3A%2144262011%2Cn%3A1233514011%2Cn%3A229548&bbn=1233514011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833427&rnid=491286", "text": "Children's", "description_wc": 0, "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/pc-mac-software-downloads/b/ref=sd_allcat_dgs_sft/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=1233514011", "parent_text": "Digital Software", "parent_catid": 66, "department_text": "Digital Games & Software", "department_id": 6},
