{"department_text": "Digital Games & Software", "nr_products": 785, "catid": 1012, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1233514011_nr_n_4?rh=n%3A229534%2Cn%3A%2144262011%2Cn%3A1233514011%2Cn%3A229563&bbn=1233514011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833427&rnid=491286", "text": "Education & Reference", "description_title": "Educational Software from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/pc-mac-software-downloads/b/ref=sd_allcat_dgs_sft/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=1233514011", "keyword_count": {"educational software": 9, "amazoncom": 1, "software": 11}, "description_wc": 325, "description_text": "Educational software brings a world of knowledge to your personal computer. You can study art, foreign language, science, and even philosophy at home as part of a structured course, or simply for your own enjoyment. Interactive educational software can bring these subjects and many more to life with brilliant multimedia demonstrations, automated lessons, and age-specific content. At Amazon.com, you\u2019ll find a wide range of educational software designed to encourage kids and adults alike to explore a world of ideas. As a supplement to school work, educational software can be a fun and effective way to learn even more about dozens of subjects. You can bring history to life with detailed, informative software that covers important events from the past with pictures, video, maps, and interactive quizzes and games. Science students can benefit from 3D visualizations and models of many different concepts in anatomy, physics, astronomy, and more. From elementary school through a professional level, we offer educational software that can help students of all ages better understand a wide variety of topics. To find educational software that covers the topics you\u2019re interested in, you can use our helpful product filters. Simply choose the subjects, developers, operating system, and price range you want, and we\u2019ll create a list of products that meet your criteria. We feature top brands like Rosetta Stone, Topics Entertainment Software, Microsoft, and Encore, so you\u2019ll be sure to choose a program that can help you learn more about your preferred subject. We also offer educational software that\u2019s focused on practical skills like typing, test prep, and vocabulary. If you\u2019re looking to boost your average words per minute, or want to learn the perfect time to use \u201cloquacious\u201d in a sentence, you\u2019ll find a variety of educational software programs to help. You can broaden your horizons and have fun learning new information with educational software that makes a world of knowledge right on your computer.", "parent_text": "Digital Software", "parent_catid": 66, "keyword_density": {"educational software": "5.5", "amazoncom": "0.3", "software": "3.4"}, "department_id": 6},
