{"department_text": "Digital Games & Software", "nr_products": 1037, "catid": 1053, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1233514011_nr_n_7?rh=n%3A229534%2Cn%3A%2144262011%2Cn%3A1233514011%2Cn%3A229614&bbn=1233514011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833427&rnid=491286", "text": "Illustration & Design", "description_title": "Design Software from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/pc-mac-software-downloads/b/ref=sd_allcat_dgs_sft/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=1233514011", "keyword_count": {"design": 13, "design software": 11, "software": 12}, "description_wc": 342, "description_text": "You can create eye-catching, professional looking work with design software made for photo editing, layouts, illustrating, and even animation. Whether you\u2019re looking for a way to design your own materials for the first time, or you\u2019ve been a professional for years, you\u2019ll find design software for all types of projects and skill levels. At Amaozn.com, we offer a full range of design software from popular developers like Adobe, Corel, Techsmith, Showtime, Honestech, Roxio, and Encore. One of the most popular categories of design software is photo editing. Programs like Photoshop and Paint Shop Pro allow you to make changes to digital images, ranging from subtle adjustments to dramatic manipulations. New photographers and old pros alike can benefit from being able to perform color corrections, exposure compensations, artistic alterations, and dozens of other useful processes. You\u2019ll find design software for Mac computers as well as PCs, so no matter what OS you prefer, we offer programs you\u2019ll love to use. To find design software that has the features you\u2019re looking for and runs well on your computer, you can use our helpful product filters. Simply choose the software format, operating system, and product category you want, and we\u2019ll create a list of products that fit your criteria. Since most design software programs have detailed descriptions of their features and capabilities, you\u2019ll be sure to choose a product that meets your needs completely. From photo editing to publishing layouts to pure illustration, we offer design software to suit people of all kinds of levels of creative expertise. Illustrating with design software has some major convenience advantages. You can save your work in multiple file formats, in any size you want, and quickly share it with people all over the world. For artists who work in the design industry, quick, reliable communication is essential, and design software makes it easier than ever to share your work. Take advantage of the efficiency and accuracy that computers offer with design software tailored to casual users and professionals alike.", "parent_text": "Digital Software", "parent_catid": 66, "keyword_density": {"design": "3.8", "design software": "6.4", "software": "3.5"}, "department_id": 6},
{"department_text": "Digital Games & Software", "nr_products": 1088, "catid": 1054, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1233514011_nr_n_8?rh=n%3A229534%2Cn%3A%2144262011%2Cn%3A1233514011%2Cn%3A497026&bbn=1233514011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833427&rnid=491286", "text": "Language & Travel", "description_title": "Language Software from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/pc-mac-software-downloads/b/ref=sd_allcat_dgs_sft/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=1233514011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 1, "language software": 11, "language": 18, "software": 14}, "description_wc": 352, "description_text": "Specialized language software lets you learn a new language from the comfort of your home computer. From Arabic to Vietnamese and everything in-between, there\u2019s a language software program to help you starting learning the language of your choice available. One of the benefits of language software is its ability to combine the interactivity of the classroom with the flexibility of a text book. At Amazon.com, we offer a full range of language software from popular developers like Rosetta Stone and Topics Entertainment Software in languages from all across the globe. You\u2019ll find European, Asian, African, and Middle Eastern language software designed for both children and adult students of all skill levels. If you had a few years of Spanish in high school and want to brush up, you\u2019ll enjoy a browse of our selection of intermediate Spanish language software to get you started re-learning your skills. If you\u2019re curious about the basics of a new language, look for basic and beginner software that walks you through the elements of a new language. When it comes to learning a new alphabet, multimedia language software gives you an advantage over written lessons, because you can associate audio cues with written text. To find language software that meets your needs, you can use our helpful product filters. Simply choose the language you want to learn, the operating system your computer uses, and the particular developer you\u2019re interested in, and we\u2019ll create a list of products that fit your criteria. Since most of our language software programs have detailed descriptions of their features, you\u2019ll be sure to choose a product that suits your skill level and learning style. No matter what language you\u2019re interested in learning, you\u2019ll find language software to help you get started. Interactive software makes it easier and more efficient to learn proper pronunciation, expand your vocabulary, and string together important phrases. You\u2019ll have access to thousands of words and phrases, taught to you in full audio with visual and written examples with language software on your PC or Mac computer.", "parent_text": "Digital Software", "parent_catid": 66, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.3", "language software": "6.2", "language": "5.1", "software": "4.0"}, "department_id": 6},
{"department_text": "Digital Games & Software", "nr_products": 44, "catid": 1055, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1233514011_nr_n_9?rh=n%3A229534%2Cn%3A%2144262011%2Cn%3A1233514011%2Cn%3A229637&bbn=1233514011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833427&rnid=491286", "text": "Networking & Servers", "description_title": "Server Software from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/pc-mac-software-downloads/b/ref=sd_allcat_dgs_sft/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=1233514011", "keyword_count": {"software": 10, "amazoncom": 1, "server software": 8, "server": 11}, "description_wc": 329, "description_text": "Sever software allows you to build a functional and efficient network infrastructure that integrates data storage servers, user terminals, offsite computers, and mobile devices on a unified network, allowing for data synchronization, cloud storage, virtual machine access, and more. Choosing the right hardware is only the first step in setting up an effective server network. Server software gives you control over your hardware, so you can create a useful network for any number of users. At Amazon.com, we offer a range of server software programs from popular developers like Microsoft, Webroot, and Absolute Software, VMWare Inc., and BTH2. Depending on the size of your network, your storage needs, and the complexity of your database, you can choose basic server software, or more robust network control programs to achieve efficient control over your IT infrastructure. If your network is accessed by remote users, most server software will allow you to set up and monitor virtual desktop infrastructure, so users can access their terminals wherever and whenever they need to. Security settings are highly customizable, so you can maintain the level of access you prefer. To find server software that meets the needs of your network and users, you can use our helpful product filters. Simply choose the developer, operating system, and server style you want, and we\u2019ll create a list of products that fit your criteria. Since most of our server software programs have detailed descriptions of their features and functionality, you\u2019ll be sure to choose a product that suits your IT infrastructure well. In addition to creating virtual desktop environments for remote users, server software makes it easy to set up reliable cloud storage for many users across the network. Collaborative work, important data backups, and daily reports can be aggregated, stored, and secured quickly and easily on a customizable schedule. Server software allows you to control and customize your network, so you can integrate the features and capabilities your users need to work efficiently and reliably.", "parent_text": "Digital Software", "parent_catid": 66, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.3", "server software": "4.9", "server": "3.3", "software": "3.0"}, "department_id": 6},
