{"department_text": "Digital Games & Software", "nr_products": 75, "catid": 1059, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1233514011_nr_n_13?rh=n%3A229534%2Cn%3A%2144262011%2Cn%3A1233514011%2Cn%3A229545&bbn=1233514011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833427&rnid=491286", "text": "Tax Preparation", "description_title": "Tax preparation software from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/pc-mac-software-downloads/b/ref=sd_allcat_dgs_sft/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=1233514011", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 1, "software": 9, "tax": 14, "tax preparation software": 8}, "description_wc": 325, "description_text": "Helpful tax preparation software makes it easier to get your receipts, tax write-offs, and deductions organized and ready for that April 15th tax return day. Whether you\u2019re filing as an individual, family, or small business, automated features and tracking forms track your income and expenses, so you can be sure to file an accurate return the first time. At Amazon.com, we offer popular tax preparation software from Intuit, H & R Block, TurboTax, Quicken, and more. For individual tax returns, you\u2019ll find several basic software programs with quick and easy to use return management tools. You\u2019ll be able to input and store W-2 tax forms, 10-99 EZs, and other common records digitally for fast access. Most tax preparation software can even accurately predict the value of your return based on your income and withholdings, so you\u2019ll know well before your check arrives in the mail what you can expect. For small business owners, we offer robust tax preparation software that can help you find possible deductions, determine what depreciation methods will yield the biggest savings, and even which vehicle deduction plan is best for you. Simply follow the guided entry process, and the program will perform all calculations and comparisons automatically. Some tax preparation software even offer accuracy guarantees, so you can be sure you\u2019re getting the biggest refund possible. To find tax preparation software that has the features and capabilities you need, you can use our helpful product filters. Simply enter the brands, features, and return types you need, and we\u2019ll show you programs that meet your criteria. Since most tax preparation software has a detailed description what types of returns can be filed, automated features, and other benefits, it\u2019s easy to find the right product for you or your business. Filing your tax return can be simpler and more accurate than ever before when you use tax preparation software designed to streamline the process.", "parent_text": "Digital Software", "parent_catid": 66, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.3", "tax preparation software": "7.4", "tax": "4.3", "software": "2.8"}, "department_id": 6},
