{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 931156, "catid": 1062, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_283155_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A283155%2Cn%3A%211000%2Cn%3A1&bbn=1000&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=1000", "text": "Arts & Photography", "description_title": "Arts & Photography Books", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/books-used-books-textbooks/b/ref=sd_allcat_bo/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=283155", "keyword_count": {"arts": 5, "books": 2, "photography": 6, "photography books": 1, "arts photography": 1}, "description_wc": 165, "description_text": "Throughout human history, our engagement with the arts has propelled us forward and connected us to our past. The arts help us express our wonder at ourselves and the world around us, and give us tools with which to question and challenge. But it is almost as difficult to define art as it would be to define ourselves without it. Acknowledging the enormous variety of methods and purposes in the arts, Amazon.com has worked to present readers with the best selection possible of art books and photography books . Amateur and professional photographers alike who may be interested in fashion photography , portrait photography , or atmospheric black and white photography will find sections of our store devoted to their interests. From readers studying art history and art criticism or photography history , to people interested in the performing arts or just finding a good drawing book to help them work on proportions, Amazon.com's selection of titles in Arts & Photography has something for everyone.", "parent_text": "Books", "parent_catid": 68, "keyword_density": {"arts": "3.1", "books": "1.2", "photography": "3.7", "photography books": "1.2", "arts photography": "1.2"}, "department_id": 7},
{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 684442, "catid": 1063, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_283155_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A283155%2Cn%3A%211000%2Cn%3A2&bbn=1000&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=1000", "text": "Biographies & Memoirs", "description_title": "Biographies from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/books-used-books-textbooks/b/ref=sd_allcat_bo/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=283155", "keyword_count": {"biographies": 7, "biographies from amazoncom": 1, "amazoncom": 2}, "description_wc": 376, "description_text": "Whether you\u2019re intrigued by the founding fathers and the birth of the nation, or you want to know what led up to some of the biggest cultural and scientific discoveries, the biographies from Amazon.com can be a personal, involving way to experience history through the stories of fascinating and inspiring history-makers. We have a great variety of biographies to choose from in a variety of formats, from paperbacks and hardcovers to audiobooks and ebooks. You can find riveting portraits of some of our nation\u2019s most influential leaders and political figures like previous presidents, civil rights pioneers, and others. If you want a deeper look into the politics and history of the United States, Canada, the United Kingdom, or other countries, we carry great historical biographies for you. Or if you\u2019re drawn to big events like the Vietnam War or World War II, you can find real-life accounts of what it was like to live through the most globe-changing battles in history. Artists and cultural figures of all sorts have also played a major role in shaping our world and the way we communicate, and with the Art & Literature biographies and memoirs of professionals, academics and scientists, you can get an inside look on all the events and effort that went into changing the world for the better. Books about Steve Jobs, J.D. Salinger, Johnny Carson, and other leaders of their field can also make great gifts for friends and family who love technology, comedy, literature, music, and more. And with free shipping on eligible items, you can conveniently and affordably enjoy the delight of getting books delivered straight to your door. You can also find a variety of biographies that cover a great selection of special interests. Sports memoirs from athletes and coaches can inspire more than just die-hard fans with intense stories of effort, practice, and undying motivation. Biographies of top scientists like Richard Feynman, Albert Einstein, Nikola Tesla, and others are ideal for getting a view into the creativity, genius--and sometimes the touch of madness--that went into modern innovations and inventions. Increase your understanding of history, the music scene, artistic movements, technology, fascinating people, and more, with the in-depth biographies and memoirs from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Books", "parent_catid": 68, "keyword_density": {"biographies": "1.9", "biographies from amazoncom": "0.8", "amazoncom": "0.5"}, "department_id": 7},
{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 1960714, "catid": 1064, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_283155_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A283155%2Cn%3A%211000%2Cn%3A3&bbn=1000&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=1000", "text": "Business & Money", "description_title": "More About Business & Money", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/books-used-books-textbooks/b/ref=sd_allcat_bo/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=283155", "keyword_count": {"money": 3, "business money": 1, "business": 4}, "description_wc": 125, "description_text": "Amazon.com has books and guides to address nearly every business and money topic. For entrepreneurs, find books and guides on writing a business plan, marketing a company, and taking a venture from startup to thriving business. Investment professionals can access a wealth of resources on the global markets, investment trends, and much more. Managers will find books to enhance their leadership skills and success at coordinating teams. In personal finance, explore books on managing money for a comfortable retirement and saving for major purchases, among other topics. From books on interview skills to job guides, check out career management resources. Also, learn about the shifts in the ever-changing economy and read books on economic history. Visit Amazon.com frequently for the latest Business & Money books.", "parent_text": "Books", "parent_catid": 68, "keyword_density": {"money": "2.4", "business money": "1.6", "business": "3.2"}, "department_id": 7},
