{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 407981, "catid": 1068, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_283155_nr_n_6?rh=n%3A283155%2Cn%3A%211000%2Cn%3A4366&bbn=1000&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=1000", "text": "Comics & Graphic Novels", "description_title": "Comics from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/books-used-books-textbooks/b/ref=sd_allcat_bo/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=283155", "keyword_count": {"comics": 6, "amazoncom": 2}, "description_wc": 307, "description_text": "From rich, alternate universes with vibrant characters to beautifully drawn panels of classic novels and stories, comics and graphic novels have grown in popularity with both adults and kids for their intriguing plot lines, interesting characters, artistic value, and easy to read formats. Whether you\u2019ve been a comic book fan since you were a kid or are just starting to dive into the fantastical world of graphic novels and manga, Amazon.com carries a wide selection of comics for you to read and love for years to come. Spanning a wide range of topics from fiction to nonfiction, comics and graphic novels explore ideas, themes, and stories from history, fantasy, science fiction, childhood, modern media, romance, the everyday, and more in a visually compelling way. Looking for the most recent releases and bestsellers? We feature a wide selection of new and notable titles from popular publishers like Marvel and DC, as well as from independent authors. You can also sort our Comics and Graphic Novels Store by new and popular or average customer rating for customer-recommended and highly-rated reads. Or look for original prints and books featuring Wonder Woman, Batman, The Green Lantern, Superman, and other great superheroes and supervillains for classic graphics and storytelling. If you have a favorite author, illustrator, or series, you can filter by author and book series or simply do a search to find all your favorites quickly and easily. From apocalyptic settings with undead menaces and outer space adventures to graphically presented biographies and comprehensive comic compendiums, it\u2019s easier than ever to have all the comics you love delivered straight to your door with FREE Super Saver Shipping and other convenient shipping options available on eligible items. With Amazon.com\u2019s large collection of comics, you can find old favorites and explore new, exciting titles all in one place.", "parent_text": "Books", "parent_catid": 68, "keyword_density": {"comics": "2.0", "amazoncom": "0.7"}, "department_id": 7},
{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 487068, "catid": 1069, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_283155_nr_n_7?rh=n%3A283155%2Cn%3A%211000%2Cn%3A5&bbn=1000&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=1000", "text": "Computers & Technology", "description_title": "Computer Books, Internet Guides, Technology Manuals & More", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/books-used-books-textbooks/b/ref=sd_allcat_bo/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=283155", "keyword_count": {"books": 7, "technology": 6, "computer books": 2, "computer": 5, "guides": 4}, "description_wc": 168, "description_text": "The Computer & Technology books category at Amazon.com strives to provide the best selection of computer books, technology guides, programming references, strategy and gaming guides, online marketing, and social media books for our customers. Browse the Computer & Technology books category page to get a sneak peek at what\u2019s \u201cNew & Notable\u201d, \u201cComing Soon\u201d or view the monthly selection of books that focus on everything from home computing to a specific programming language to the newest certification guides . From the main page, explore subcategories that features bestselling titles on the latest technology, programming languages, social media, computer hardware and software. Amazon carries a wide-range of computer books for everyone from the beginning user interested in how-to guides for Microsoft Office 2010 or Windows 7 to developers looking for books on building mobile apps for the iPhone, iPad, or Android. We also stock titles on all the latest technology trends from the biggest technology publishers like O\u2019Reilly, Pearson, Wiley, Elsevier, Random House, McGraw Hill, and more.", "parent_text": "Books", "parent_catid": 68, "keyword_density": {"books": "4.2", "technology": "3.6", "guides": "2.4", "computer books": "2.4", "computer": "3.0"}, "department_id": 7},
{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 185043, "catid": 1070, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_283155_nr_n_8?rh=n%3A283155%2Cn%3A%211000%2Cn%3A6&bbn=1000&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=1000", "text": "Cookbooks, Food & Wine", "description_title": "Cookbooks, Food & Wine", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/books-used-books-textbooks/b/ref=sd_allcat_bo/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=283155", "keyword_count": {"food": 3, "cookbooks": 7, "cookbooks food wine": 1, "wine": 2}, "description_wc": 221, "description_text": "Amazon.com has the world's largest collection of cookbooks, including regional and international cookbooks, baking books, entertaining guides, wine resources, and quick and easy cookbooks. Find inspiration for your next meal, explore foodie favorites and chef memoirs, plan a dinner party for a dozen guests, or look for essential reference guides for your kitchen. Browse best sellers , hot new releases for favorite cookbook authors, recipes from popular restaurants, books by celebrity cooks, and tips from master chefs. Spice up your meals with our selection of classic and modern Italian favorites, authentic Mexican cookbooks, techniques of French cuisine, or find hundreds of recipes for pasta, pizza, and other easy recipes for breakfast, lunch, dinner, and snacks. Plus, learn how to bake and barbecue like the professionals. Amazon.com also offers a wide selection of books for special diet cooking, including vegan and vegetarian, gluten-free, Paleo, juicing, and diabetic cookbooks. Visit the Best of the Month: Cookbooks, Food & Wine page for monthly picks by our editors, along with Best of the Year So Far and Best of the Year selections. Eating will never go out of style. Whether you're an experienced chef, a certified foodie, a first-time home cook, or anywhere in between, you will always be able to find classic cookbooks and new favorites of all kinds on Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Books", "parent_catid": 68, "keyword_density": {"food": "1.4", "cookbooks": "3.2", "cookbooks food wine": "1.4", "wine": "0.9"}, "department_id": 7},
{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 427741, "catid": 1071, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_283155_nr_n_9?rh=n%3A283155%2Cn%3A%211000%2Cn%3A48&bbn=1000&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=1000", "text": "Crafts, Hobbies & Home", "description_title": "Crafts, Hobbies & Home", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/books-used-books-textbooks/b/ref=sd_allcat_bo/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=283155", "keyword_count": {"home": 4, "crafts hobbies home": 1, "crafts": 3}, "description_wc": 98, "description_text": "Amazon.com has the world's largest selection of crafts books on sewing, knitting, and crocheting, along with titles about gardening, pet care, home improvement, interior decorating, entertaining, and gardening. Visit the Best of the Month: Crafts, Hobbies & Home page for monthly picks by our editors, along with Best of the Year So Far and Best of the Year selections. Whether you're taking on a minor home renovation project, learning to knit, planning your vegetable garden, redecorating your living room, or taking care of a new cat or dog, Amazon.com has books for home, garden, and crafts activities.", "parent_text": "Books", "parent_catid": 68, "keyword_density": {"home": "4.1", "crafts hobbies home": "3.1", "crafts": "3.1"}, "department_id": 7},
{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 4492148, "catid": 1072, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_283155_nr_n_10?rh=n%3A283155%2Cn%3A%211000%2Cn%3A21&bbn=1000&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=1000", "text": "Education & Reference", "description_title": "Education & Reference Books", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/books-used-books-textbooks/b/ref=sd_allcat_bo/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=283155", "keyword_count": {"education reference books": 2, "books": 4, "reference": 4}, "description_wc": 230, "description_text": "Amazon Education & Reference Books encompasses a phenomenally broad range of resources: dictionaries and thesauruses, atlases and maps, foreign language guides, test prep, writing resources, and medical and legal references, to name a few. We carry references from all the top publishing imprints, including Barrons, For Dummies, Merriam-Webster, Rand McNally, and Oxford University Press. The Education & Reference Books page is not just for those looking for a dictionary or encyclopedia. Our broad range of test prep resources include study guides for the SAT, AP, GRE, LSAT, ACT, GMAT, and TOEFL, from trusted publishers like Kaplan, The Princeton Review, Barrons, and The College Board itself. We offer an extensive selection of college and grad school guides, to help you choose the right school for you. If you are trying to pick up a new language or brush up on an old one, look no further. We feature foreign language instruction guides for Spanish, French, and many more languages. There\u2019s everything from coursebooks and foreign language dictionaries to phrase books and vocabulary lists to get you started. We also have writing style guides and manuals for every type of writer. From an academic style guide like the Publication Manual of the American Psychological Association to the more general Elements of Style , we\u2019ve got you covered--whether you\u2019re looking to complete that research paper or just writing a letter.", "parent_text": "Books", "parent_catid": 68, "keyword_density": {"education reference books": "2.6", "books": "1.7", "reference": "1.7"}, "department_id": 7},
