{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 448578, "catid": 1077, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_283155_nr_n_15?rh=n%3A283155%2Cn%3A%211000%2Cn%3A86&bbn=1000&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=1000", "text": "Humor & Entertainment", "description_title": "Entertainment Books from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/books-used-books-textbooks/b/ref=sd_allcat_bo/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=283155", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "books": 11, "entertainment books": 6}, "description_wc": 316, "description_text": "It\u2019s been said that laughter is the best medicine. From hilarious narratives written by comedic geniuses to deeply involved fiction novels, humor and entertainment books are a great choice for those times when you just want to sit back, relax, and read something interesting and intriguing--and maybe even laugh out loud. Whether you\u2019re looking for a comedian\u2019s sarcastic take on what\u2019s wrong with the world today, or a classic humorist\u2019s biography, Amazon.com carries a wide selection of entertainment books to keep you well entertained. From audiobooks to take in the car or ebooks to read on your laptop on the plane to the time-honored paperback and hardcovers for the beach or cozy armchair, we offer a variety of book formats so you can choose the ones that best fit your reading preferences and lifestyle. Available in many different languages, our collection of entertainment books also spans multiple genres, including humor, movies, television, puzzles & games, and more, from popular authors like Si Robertson, Pay Bradbury, George Orwell, and Russell Baker. We also feature a large number of nonfiction books for that taste of reality you need every so often. Easily find all the entertainment books you want with our handy shopping filters, located on the left side of the page. Simply choose the format, author, book series, language, shipping option, and condition you want and we\u2019ll show you the books and literature that best match your preferences. You can also sort by new and popular, average customer rating, and most reviews for notable, customer-recommended entertainment books. And with FREE Super Saver Shipping and other convenient shipping options available on eligible items, it\u2019s more affordable than ever to stock up on the good books that you\u2019ve been meaning to check out. Treat yourself to a break with fun and inspiring reads from the entertainment books at Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Books", "parent_catid": 68, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.6", "books": "3.5", "entertainment books": "3.8"}, "department_id": 7},
{"department_text": "Books & Audible", "nr_products": 562376, "catid": 1078, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_283155_nr_n_16?rh=n%3A283155%2Cn%3A%211000%2Cn%3A10777&bbn=1000&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833386&rnid=1000", "text": "Law", "description_title": "Law Books at Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/books-used-books-textbooks/b/ref=sd_allcat_bo/178-6146972-2884157?ie=UTF8&node=283155", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 1, "books": 4, "law": 11, "law books": 1}, "description_wc": 120, "description_text": "Amazon.com's Law bookstore contains a variety of resources for anyone interested in, studying, or practicing law. For the law student or aspiring law student we carry a variety of LSAT preparation books, case studies, legal histories, legal theory books, legal writing guides and dictionaries, and bar exam study guides. For the practicing lawyer or legal professional we carry books from a broad range of specialties such as criminology, constitutional law, business law, estate planning, family law, international law, intellectual property, medical law, and law practice. For the interested layperson, we also carry titles on understanding your constitutional and legal rights, the details of legal procedures, and advice on how to secure a patent for your original ideas and inventions.", "parent_text": "Books", "parent_catid": 68, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.8", "books": "3.3", "law": "9.2", "law books": "1.7"}, "department_id": 7},
