te your home entertainment system such as receivers, amplifiers, CD players, CD recorders, turntables, and more. If you're building a movie theater in your own home, you'll want to be sure you have the proper components to replicate the theater experience: projectors, surround speaker systems, receivers, and amplifiers. You can also find everything you need to listen on-the-go in our store. We carry boomboxes, portable radios, clock radios, and compact stereos that make it easy to take audio anywhere. Need help finding the right home audio and theater products? Our featured home audio and theater categories make it easy to find the perfect addition to your home entertainment system.", "parent_text": "Electronics & Computers", "parent_catid": 9, "keyword_density": {"home audio": "1.9", "home theater": "0.6", "audio": "1.9", "theater": "1.9", "home": "3.8"}, "department_id": 9},
