{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 169, "catid": 1139, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_3?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A2811119011%2Cn%3A2407750011&bbn=2811119011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833529&rnid=2811119011", "text": "Mobile Broadband", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Mobile WiFi from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A2811119011&bbn=493964&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=493964", "keyword_count": {"mobile": 12, "mobile wifi": 11, "amazoncom": 2}, "description_wc": 327, "description_text": "Access the internet on all your devices, wherever you go with a mobile WiFi hotspot. You won\u2019t have to spend time running in and out of coffee shops searching for wireless internet when you have your very own hotspot with you, ready to go whenever you are. At Amazon.com, we offer mobile WiFi solutions from top carriers like AT & T, Verizon, and T-Mobile, so you can often keep your mobile WiFi and cell service organized on the same bill. Depending on network availability in your area, you\u2019ll have access to 4G LTE mobile WiFi that\u2019s fast enough to stream music and movies to your computer or tablet wherever you go. Many mobile WiFi modems are dual band, so they\u2019ll automatically switch between 4G and 3G, depending on coverage. If you don\u2019t want to commit to a contract with a particular provider, browse our selection of prepaid mobile WiFi products. You\u2019ll get all the bandwidth you need, without the added obligation of a service contract. For international travelers, prepaid mobile WiFi is a convenient way to make sure you stay connected overseas, without paying expensive roaming charges, or signing up for an international data plan. Most products have detailed descriptions of their features and specifications, so you can be sure the mobile WiFi product you\u2019re interested in meets your needs perfectly. The convenience of being able to connect to the internet on your smartphone, tablet, or laptop wherever you go makes it easier than ever to work and play on your own schedule. Catch up on your e-mail from your sunny back yard, or connect with friends while you wait for your flight to take off. With a mobile WiFi connection, the sky is the limit. Stay connected on the go with a mobile WiFi hotspot. Bring your work or fun with you on vacation, to the park, and all over town with the mobile WiFi solutions from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Cell Phones & Accessories", "parent_catid": 1121, "keyword_density": {"mobile": "3.7", "mobile wifi": "6.7", "amazoncom": "0.6"}, "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 8925862, "catid": 1140, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_4?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A2811119011%2Cn%3A2407755011&bbn=2811119011&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833529&rnid=2811119011", "text": "Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Phone Accessories from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A2811119011&bbn=493964&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=493964", "keyword_count": {"phone": 22, "amazoncom": 2, "phone accessories": 7, "accessories": 8}, "description_wc": 340, "description_text": "Protect your phone or give it useful new features with decorative and functional phone accessories. At Amazon.com, you\u2019ll find phone accessories to help protect your investment. Cases and covers will prevent scratches and dings, and help protect your phone from damage if you accidentally drop it. Some sturdy cases can even protect your phone from water damage. You can also find protective phone cases in a variety of fun and stylish designs. Set yourself and your phone apart with phone accessories that reflect your personality. We offer cases and covers in almost any color and material you can imagine, from basic monochrome plastic, to brushed aluminum. Your imagination is the only limit when it comes to customizing the look of your phone with fun and functional accessories. Make sure your cell phone battery never dies at an inopportune moment by carrying an extra charger or battery with you. Chargers are a simple and affordable phone accessory that you can keep in your car or purse. We offer car chargers, wall chargers, and portable chargers for practically every phone on the market. Many chargers have universal adapter kits, so you can keep one charger for all the different cell phones in the house. Most of us rely on our phones a lot, and one of the most helpful phone accessories available is an extension battery. Smartphones can drain a lot of battery over the course of a day, so make sure you\u2019ve got enough juice with an extension battery built into a protective case. For drivers, we offer hands free phone accessories to help you stay safe on the road. Keep both hands on the wheel and your eyes on the road by using a headset to make calls while you\u2019re driving. Bluetooth wireless phone accessories allow you to make calls with your phone safely in your pocket, while wired units plug conveniently into the headphone jack. Let Amazon.com help you give your phone a boost with stylish and functional phone accessories for good looks, protection, and usability.", "parent_text": "Cell Phones & Accessories", "parent_catid": 1121, "keyword_density": {"phone": "6.5", "amazoncom": "0.6", "phone accessories": "4.1", "accessories": "2.4"}, "department_id": 9},
