{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 372, "catid": 1162, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_524136_nr_n_4?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A524136%2Cn%3A7161093011&bbn=524136&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833454&rnid=524136", "text": "Remote Home Monitoring Systems", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Remote Home Security from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_10?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A524136&bbn=493964&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=493964", "keyword_count": {"home": 8, "amazoncom": 2, "remote": 5, "security": 5, "remote home security": 4}, "description_wc": 296, "description_text": "Remote home security systems from Amazon.com can offer you unparalleled security and peace of mind, allowing you to keep an eye on your belongings, pets, and property wherever you go. Convenient and compatible with a wide range of devices, you can easily keep track of your home or yard through video and receive instant movement alerts via email and text messages. Get peace of mind any time of day by checking live streaming video on handheld tablets and Smartphones, as well as your primary desktop or laptop. We offer a wide variety of remote home security cameras to choose from. Many of our cameras are very discreet, and can be hung up on walls and ceilings or placed on shelves so you can get the best angle to keep an eye out on your home or office. Some also come with remote pan and tilt options, so you can move the lens from wherever you are if you want to scan the room. Some are especially built to be put up outside and withstand the weather, while others have nighttime recording capabilities for 24/7 surveillance. To ensure that you get full coverage of your home, we carry bundles of up to three or four cameras. They\u2019re great for keeping an eye on your garage and workplaces when you want to ensure that your projects are secure, or as nanny-cams to ensure that your kids are comfortable and happy when you\u2019re not home. Pet owners can also benefit from remote home security cameras to see how Fido keeps getting out of the yard or how the cat managed to build a nest on top of the refrigerator. You can find all of the cameras and remote home security equipment you need at Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Security & Surveillance", "parent_catid": 1129, "keyword_density": {"home": "2.7", "amazoncom": "0.7", "remote": "1.7", "security": "1.7", "remote home security": "4.1"}, "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 20757, "catid": 1163, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A16285901%2Cn%3A16285851&bbn=16285901&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833454&rnid=16285901", "text": "Computers & Add-Ons", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Computer Services from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_11?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A16285901&bbn=493964&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=493964", "keyword_count": {"services": 6, "amazoncom": 5, "computer": 12, "computer services": 5}, "description_wc": 275, "description_text": "You can protect your investment and make sure you\u2019re covered for damage and deterioration with various computer services offered by Amazon.com. At Amazon.com, we offer numerous computer services to insure your computer equipment, and you can find protection for everything from accidental water damage to hardware failures. Easily filter through various services by brand, certification, price, and more to narrow down the perfect protection plan, accident protection plan, or warranty for your new computer. As an add-on item to your Amazon.com computer purchase, or as a standalone warranty for your current equipment, it\u2019s smart to make sure you\u2019re covered and avoid the risk of losing your data. Our computer equipment warranties and protection plan will cover a wide variety of computer services available for most all laptops, computers, models, and brands. From accidental damage care to full replacements, Amazon.com offers warranties from well-known brands like Apple, SquareTrade, and Brother. Some warranties are for specific products, but eligible protection plans can be used with broader categories like tablets, PCs, and office. With many different computer services options available, you can protect just a single piece of computer equipment or a broad range of desktop computers, basic electronics, or entire office systems. Protect your investments up to thousands of dollars, or just a few hundred\u2013it\u2019s your call with plenty of options to choose your amount of coverage. You can also read customer reviews right on the page to see how others believe the protection plans stack up. When you insure your equipment with warranties, computer services, and support packages from Amazon.com, you can ensure yourself a good night\u2019s rest.", "parent_text": "Service & Replacement Plans", "parent_catid": 1130, "keyword_density": {"services": "2.2", "amazoncom": "1.8", "computer": "4.4", "computer services": "3.6"}, "department_id": 9},
