{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 23479, "catid": 1178, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_3610841_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A3610841%2Cn%3A2422430011&bbn=3610841&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833456&rnid=3610841", "text": "Baskets & Bins", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Storage Bins from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_11?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A3610841&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 3, "storage": 12, "bins": 8, "storage bins": 6}, "description_wc": 320, "description_text": "Give yourself peace of mind with a well-ordered home. Take care of your everyday storage needs while keeping your home organized with functional storage bins of all shapes and sizes that you won\u2019t mind having around. Whether it\u2019s time to pack away your winter clothes or finally clean up the back closet, Amazon.com offers a large selection of storage bins. Finding the perfect basket, bucket, container, or box to fit your needs and organizing at home is easy with our handy search filters. Browse by brand, type, color, and even price to narrow it down for whatever shape, size, and design you\u2019re looking for\u2014stacking boxes, pull-out drawers, lidded baskets, dry food containers. We all have that one space that requires some extra storage love\u2014it\u2019s okay to admit it. Give yourself extra motivation to clean it up with sturdy and spacious storage bins from top brands like Sterilite, Storage Dynamics, Richards Homewares, Seville Classics, and others. Cleaning out the garage or putting away toys doesn\u2019t have to be a chore\u2014make it easy with a diversity of storage accessories like extra lids, organizers, vacuum-sealed bags, and labels, so you can keep track of all you\u2019ve packed. At Amazon.com, storage bins aren\u2019t just generic white plastic bins with a lid anymore. Add a personal touch to your d\u00e9cor with unique storage options\u2014use an open wicker basket to store patterned blankets in the living room, or try colored, foldable fabric bins for extra shoes in the entry way. From a small wooden box to a large vintage steamer trunk, storage bins can be a beautiful and functional accent to any room. Think outside of the box and choose storage bins that not only fit the bill, but your style too. With a wide variety of sizes, materials, and designs, rely on Amazon.com for all your storage and organization needs.", "parent_text": "Storage & Organization", "parent_catid": 1119, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.9", "storage": "3.8", "bins": "2.5", "storage bins": "3.8"}, "department_id": 10},
