{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 24051, "catid": 1187, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_3610841_nr_n_9?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A3610841%2Cn%3A2422453011&bbn=3610841&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833456&rnid=3610841", "text": "Trash & Recycling", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Trash and Recycling from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_11?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A3610841&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"trash and recycling": 7, "amazoncom": 2, "recycling": 10, "trash": 11}, "description_wc": 333, "description_text": "With the level of environmental awareness increasing, you may be inspired to do a little extra work to help out our planet. If your trash and recycling bins look identical, it can make your job a lot harder to do your part. Luckily, Amazon.com has attractive trash and recycling bins so you can differentiate and organize your garbage appropriately. We have a wide variety of indoor trash and recycling bins for you to choose from. Black wire mesh cans are ideal for dry refuse, like office papers, used post-its, wrapping paper and old shipping materials. Plastic bins are better suited for kitchens and bathrooms. We carry blue plastic recycling bins that can serve as a great reminder to put your bottles and cans in the right place. They can help kids learn where the right garbage goes easily. Our step cans are great for when you constantly have your hands full. They\u2019re especially useful when you\u2019re sweeping and you have one hand holding a broom, and the other holding your dust pan. If you have pets, the automatically closing lids can help keep them from making a mess out of your garbage. Many of our step trash and recycling cans are eligible for Free Shipping, saving you time and money on your delivery choices. Our outdoor trash and recycling containers come in just as many styles and varieties. Our Rubbermaid rolling trash bins can make garbage day a breeze. Simply roll your garbage down your driveway instead of lugging heavy cans or bags. Our clearly-marked recycling containers will illuminate confusion among kids and trash collector who frequently get your trash and recycling receptacles mixed up. We even carry ingenious trash \u201chideaways,\u201d so you can tuck your garbage away behind an attractive fa\u00e7ade during the rest of the week. Do your best for the planet by sorting out the papers and the trash. You can get going on your recycling campaign with the trash and recycling bins from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Storage & Organization", "parent_catid": 1119, "keyword_density": {"trash and recycling": "6.3", "amazoncom": "0.6", "recycling": "3.0", "trash": "3.3"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 18686, "catid": 1188, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_3610841_nr_n_10?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A3610841%2Cn%3A1069182&bbn=3610841&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833456&rnid=3610841", "text": "Storage Cabinets", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Storage Cabinets from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_11?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A3610841&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"storage cabinets": 5, "cabinets": 6, "storage": 7, "storage cabinets from amazoncom": 2}, "description_wc": 326, "description_text": "When you\u2019re beginning any venture\u2014business or otherwise\u2014one of the most important skills to learn is organization. It can save you money and time trying to find the right supplies, paperwork, tools and other necessities to get your job done. Thankfully, the storage cabinets from Amazon.com can help you sort and sift through your things quickly and store them securely when they\u2019re not in use. We have a wide variety of storage cabinets to choose from. Our utility cabinets are ideal for offices and garages. They can be used to store a variety of cleaning supplies for the custodial staff, or to keep all of your printing-room paper, toner, and other supplies neat and tidy. Now, with our filtering features, you can organize your search for a storage cabinet by average customer rating, so you know the models and units you order have worked well for others with similar needs. For optimal organization of smaller parts like screws, nails, fuses, electrical components, fasteners, paperclips, tacks, pins, needles and any other small, easily lost items, we have a variety of storage cabinets compartmentalized with many drawers. They\u2019re also ideal for the craft tables at home. You can put tubes of paint, brushes, quills, bottles of ink, gum erasers and so much more in them for your drawing or craft tables. Locked storage cabinets secure your sensitive and extremely important documents and items away so you won\u2019t have to worry about someone getting into them when you\u2019re not around. It\u2019s also a great way to lock away special drinks or snacks that you don\u2019t want your coworkers snitching. If you need a locking storage cabinet soon, Ammazon.com offers a variety of expedited shipping options for you to choose from so you can get it right when you need it. Work smarter, not harder. With the storage cabinets from Amazon.com, you\u2019ll see that organization is the key to productivity.", "parent_text": "Storage & Organization", "parent_catid": 1119, "keyword_density": {"storage cabinets": "3.1", "cabinets": "1.8", "storage": "2.1", "storage cabinets from amazoncom": "2.5"}, "department_id": 10},
