{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 5334, "catid": 1190, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_10802561_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A10802561%2Cn%3A15356181&bbn=10802561&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833455&rnid=10802561", "text": "Dusting", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Dusting Supplies from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_12?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A10802561&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"dusting": 9, "dusting supplies": 7, "dusting supplies from amazoncom": 2}, "description_wc": 341, "description_text": "It's easy to remember to vacuum every once in a while, and to take out the garbage when it gets full, but dusting your home in often forgotten, and can make a difference in the brightness and air quality of a room. Give any room a satisfying dust; we make it a little easier with the dusting supplies from Amazon.com. We have a wide variety of dusting supplies to choose from. Extendable dusters can make it a breeze to reach areas that are usually extremely difficult to get to. With extendable dusting supplies from such popular brands as OXO, Swiffer, NorPro, Mantta, and more, you can sweep up the dust from the tops of bookcases, ceiling fan blades, and crown molding on high ceilings with little or no difficulty. If you already know how useful extendable dusters are because you use one to finish your chores, you may be interested in our replacement heads. No matter what brand you use, you can find a replacement cleaning head from trusted brands like Swiffer, Norpro, and Shark for your cleaning tools and dusting supplies. Many models use static and special fibers to attract and cling to dust, so there's no need to spray or wipe up excess moisture. For tougher jobs and when you're cleaning area that you want to make spotless, the disinfectant wipes from Lysol and Clorox are a quick and simple solution. We also have a collection of other dusting supplies and accessories to choose from. Microfiber cloths and chamois cloths are great accessories to dust off and clean larger areas like countertops, big kitchen appliances, and even cars. Dusting slippers are a fun way to pick up dirt from tile floors while keeping your feet and socks from collecting the particles themselves. If you're looking for dusting supplies on a budget, try filtering your search by price to see some of the most affordable options. The dusting supplies from Amazon.com make cleaning so easy, you can get any member of the family to pitch in.", "parent_text": "Cleaning Supplies", "parent_catid": 1120, "keyword_density": {"dusting": "2.6", "dusting supplies": "4.1", "dusting supplies from amazoncom": "2.3"}, "department_id": 10},
