{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 8925876, "catid": 1301, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A281407%2Cn%3A2407755011&bbn=281407&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833530&rnid=281407", "text": "Cell Phone Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Phone Accessories from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A281407&bbn=493964&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=493964", "keyword_count": {"phone": 22, "amazoncom": 2, "phone accessories": 7, "accessories": 8}, "description_wc": 340, "description_text": "Protect your phone or give it useful new features with decorative and functional phone accessories. At Amazon.com, you\u2019ll find phone accessories to help protect your investment. Cases and covers will prevent scratches and dings, and help protect your phone from damage if you accidentally drop it. Some sturdy cases can even protect your phone from water damage. You can also find protective phone cases in a variety of fun and stylish designs. Set yourself and your phone apart with phone accessories that reflect your personality. We offer cases and covers in almost any color and material you can imagine, from basic monochrome plastic, to brushed aluminum. Your imagination is the only limit when it comes to customizing the look of your phone with fun and functional accessories. Make sure your cell phone battery never dies at an inopportune moment by carrying an extra charger or battery with you. Chargers are a simple and affordable phone accessory that you can keep in your car or purse. We offer car chargers, wall chargers, and portable chargers for practically every phone on the market. Many chargers have universal adapter kits, so you can keep one charger for all the different cell phones in the house. Most of us rely on our phones a lot, and one of the most helpful phone accessories available is an extension battery. Smartphones can drain a lot of battery over the course of a day, so make sure you\u2019ve got enough juice with an extension battery built into a protective case. For drivers, we offer hands free phone accessories to help you stay safe on the road. Keep both hands on the wheel and your eyes on the road by using a headset to make calls while you\u2019re driving. Bluetooth wireless phone accessories allow you to make calls with your phone safely in your pocket, while wired units plug conveniently into the headphone jack. Let Amazon.com help you give your phone a boost with stylish and functional phone accessories for good looks, protection, and usability.", "parent_text": "Accessories & Supplies", "parent_catid": 1098, "keyword_density": {"phone": "6.5", "amazoncom": "0.6", "phone accessories": "4.1", "accessories": "2.4"}, "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 1832883, "catid": 1302, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_3?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A281407%2Cn%3A172456&bbn=281407&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833530&rnid=281407", "text": "Computer Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Computer Accessories at Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A281407&bbn=493964&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=493964", "keyword_count": {"computer": 6, "accessories": 7, "computer accessories": 4}, "description_wc": 241, "description_text": "Looking for an external hard drive to expand your storage, a router to set up your own network, or just a more comfortable keyboard and mouse? Amazon\u2019s Computer Accessories Store has all these and more. You\u2019re sure to find what you need in our broad selection of computer accessories and peripherals, including flash memory cards and USB drives, wired and wireless PC headsets, cables, and laptop bags, batteries, and cases. Check out our best sellers, top-rated computer accessories, and helpful customer reviews. We have accessories for every need and every computer, Mac or PC, from compact, high-speed SDHC and microSD flash memory cards to full-featured peripherals like wired and wireless keyboards, mice, headsets, and microphones designed for business, gaming, and home computing. If you\u2019re tough on your devices, don\u2019t miss our selection of rugged and spill-resistant accessories. Does your home or office network need a boost? Take a look at our selection of AC and N Wi-Fi routers. If it\u2019s deals you want, look no further. We have big discounts on every kind of computer accessory. Or maybe you just need more cables for all your gadgets. We\u2019ll keep you connected and in sync with USB, Ethernet, SATA, Lightning cables and more. If you\u2019re always on the go, protect and power your laptop and accessories with our bags, cases, batteries, and chargers--all in Amazon\u2019s Computer Accessories Store.", "parent_text": "Accessories & Supplies", "parent_catid": 1098, "keyword_density": {"computer": "2.5", "accessories": "2.9", "computer accessories": "3.3"}, "department_id": 9},
