{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 262874, "catid": 1307, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_8?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A281407%2Cn%3A173541&bbn=281407&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833530&rnid=281407", "text": "Batteries, Chargers & Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Battery Chargers from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A281407&bbn=493964&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=493964", "keyword_count": {"battery": 9, "chargers": 3, "amazoncom": 2, "battery chargers": 1}, "description_wc": 318, "description_text": "Getting the most out of your handheld devices often means making sure you are fully stocked with batteries. Keep more money in your pocket by using a battery charger to juice up rechargeable batteries and create a near endless supply of portable power. Not only will you save money, but you'll be doing the Earth a favor by reducing the number of batteries that end up in landfills. At Amazon.com, we have a battery charger that fits every need and lifestyle from well-known manufacturers like Schumacher, Sanyo, Sony, Duracel, and Energizer. Find chargers that handle battery types such as nickel metal hydride, alkaline, lithium, nickel cadmium, and more. You can find battery chargers that handle as few as two batteries or as many as eight or 12 batteries of differing sizes and types. These larger chargers can be quite handy around the holidays when portable electronics get the most use. Use the battery charger accessories available on the site to maximize the product's usefulness. We have organizers for keeping batteries in order and testers that can show you instantly whether a battery is good or not. No more wasting time putting batteries in an electronic device to see if it works. We also sell rechargeable batteries in all sizes, AC adapters, power converters, and other items that make owning a battery charger a very smart investment. Whether you are looking to go green or have a family that goes through batteries like there's no tomorrow, a battery charger can help you manage your power supply. Our low prices means you can buy as many as you need and still have money to buy the electronics you'll need batteries for. Front door shipping means you don't even have to leave your house to get exactly what you need. Amazon.com makes it easy to get a battery charger and accessories at prices you love.", "parent_text": "Accessories & Supplies", "parent_catid": 1098, "keyword_density": {"battery": "2.8", "chargers": "0.9", "amazoncom": "0.6", "battery chargers": "0.6"}, "department_id": 9},
