{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 28924, "catid": 1310, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_11?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A281407%2Cn%3A281408&bbn=281407&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833530&rnid=281407", "text": "Blank Media", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "LightScribe from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A281407&bbn=493964&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=493964", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 3, "lightscribe": 9}, "description_wc": 338, "description_text": "Fumbling around for permanent markers or sticky labels to help you mark a CD or DVD can lead to disorganization and hassle in the recording process. Copy your favorite images or sounds onto a blank CD quickly with a LightScribe disc instead. Laser-friendly graphene coats the surface of each LightScribe disc, creating a smooth surface that you can customize with images, designs, or text with easy-to-use computer software. We carry many trusted brands of LightScribe DVD-R and CD-R discs, including Philips, HP, and Verbatim, allowing you to choose a blank DVD or CD that pairs well with your current recording device. Amazon.com also carries a wide selection of external drives and disc writers that are compatible with LightScribe discs. Paper sleeves make it simple to deliver a disc to a friend or colleague, while a plastic spindle keeps recordings organized on your desk. You can also shop for binders designed to keep a large amount of discs safe from debris and scratches. If you copy things on a regular basis, you'll appreciate the packs of 50 or 100 discs, while a 10-pack works well for people who just like to transfer the occasional image or song. You aren't limited to traditional means of recording media when it comes to LightScribe, and Amazon.com has several different pens and notebooks that capture your handwritten notes and sounds when you're on the go. Ensure that you don't miss a single word during your next business meeting or class lecture by taking notes with a LightScribe pen. Sharing family photos or your band's new single is easy when you copy the data on a LightScribe disc. Each dependable disc holds a generous amount of data, allowing you to finish simple recording jobs without the need for multiple pieces of blank media. Ensure that your favorite moments are not forgotten, or capture important information for work or school, with a pack of high-quality LightScribe discs and a LightScribe pen from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Accessories & Supplies", "parent_catid": 1098, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.9", "lightscribe": "2.7"}, "department_id": 9},
