{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 49777, "catid": 1314, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_15?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A281407%2Cn%3A11974521&bbn=281407&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833530&rnid=281407", "text": "Microphones", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Microphones from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A281407&bbn=493964&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=493964", "keyword_count": {"microphones": 6, "amazoncom": 2}, "description_wc": 305, "description_text": "Whether you're singing Karaoke or recording a new vocal artist, using good reliable equipment can help you capture the best audio. If you are looking for microphones that will pick up every note from an electric guitar or the soft, whispery tones of a shy singer, then you've come to the right place. From making demo tapes to providing entertainment at a birthday party, Amazon.com has an excellent selection of studio recording equipment including microphones and related accessories that are perfect for all your audio recording needs. On our site, you will find a wide variety of microphones including condenser, dynamic, ribbon, and wireless from preeminent manufacturers such as Nady, Blue Microphones, Audio-Technica, and Olympus. To improve the quality of your recording, we also sell preamps for controlling and maintaining a good signal, and windscreens and pop filters that protect the mic while preventing plosives from ruining all of your hard work. Phantom power supplies ensure your condenser microphones have a constant, reliable source of electricity so they always work when you need them to. Our catalog contains an assortment of microphone stands, clips, and mounts like handheld boom poles and tripods that make it easy to capture recordings. Microphone bags and wheeled storage cases protect your equipment whether you store it in a closet or take it with you on the road. We also sell cables, tools, and replacement parts for connecting your recording equipment and keeping it in great shape. Whether you're making videos at home, setting up in a professional recording studio, or on stage in front of thousands of your greatest fans, Amazon.com has the microphones and accessories you need to record high-quality audio. Our low prices fit any budget and our fast shipping ensures you get the equipment you require exactly when you need it.", "parent_text": "Accessories & Supplies", "parent_catid": 1098, "keyword_density": {"microphones": "2.0", "amazoncom": "0.7"}, "department_id": 9},
