{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 62381, "catid": 1322, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_502394_nr_n_7?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A502394%2Cn%3A7161086011&bbn=502394&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833529&rnid=502394", "text": "Lighting & Studio", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Photo Studio Lighting from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A502394&bbn=493964&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=493964", "keyword_count": {"photo studio lighting": 5, "photo": 13, "photo studio": 6, "amazoncom": 2, "studio": 8, "lighting": 7}, "description_wc": 320, "description_text": "Great photos and portraits aren\u2019t just usually taken on a whim--they take time, effort, and forethought to convey the photographer\u2019s idea. Thinking about the quality of light you want to have in your composition is a great part of the creative process and at Amazon.com, we want to help you find the best photo studio lighting options that will help you bring your vision to life. There\u2019s no definitive rule to how many reflectors, umbrellas, or photo studio lighting accessories you should use--it heavily depends on the type of photo shoot you\u2019re conducting and where. Whatever your vision for the light in your photos, we can help you make sure you have what you need whether you\u2019re shooting indoors or out. From strobe lights, flash tubes, and continuous output lighting, to barn doors, booms, and stands, you\u2019ll quickly learn how to create your own lighting schemes and ideas. You\u2019ll also want to check out our selection of light meters, color calibration charts, and other accessories to complete your photo studio lighting kits. We also carry a wide selection of other photo and video studio equipment that can help give your photography a professional feel and look from more than just photo studio lighting. From studio backdrops, clamps, and gaffers tape, to presentation materials like leather portfolios, digital picture frames, and matte backing, you can find everything you need to turn your study, living room, or den into a working photo studio. Or if you\u2019re more interested in video, we also have teleprompters and video monitors to keep track of all the action. And with free shipping and free returns on eligible items, we make it affordable and convenient to have all your photography equipment, supplies, and accessories right to your door. When you shop for photo studio lighting supplies from Amazon.com, you\u2019ll never be left in the dark again.", "parent_text": "Camera & Photo", "parent_catid": 1099, "keyword_density": {"photo studio lighting": "4.7", "photo": "4.1", "photo studio": "3.8", "amazoncom": "0.6", "lighting": "2.2", "studio": "2.5"}, "department_id": 9},
{"department_text": "Electronics & Computers", "nr_products": 192972, "catid": 1323, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_502394_nr_n_8?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A502394%2Cn%3A7161073011&bbn=502394&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833529&rnid=502394", "text": "Video", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_172659_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A172282&bbn=172282&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338741", "description_title": "Video Camera Equipment from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=sr_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A172282%2Cn%3A%21493964%2Cn%3A502394&bbn=493964&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=493964", "keyword_count": {"video camera equipment": 5, "equipment": 7, "amazoncom": 2, "camera": 9, "video": 14, "video camera": 8, "equipment from amazoncom": 1}, "description_wc": 328, "description_text": "Creating videos and movies may seem as easy as taking a video camera out with you and pressing \u201crecord.\u201d However, to really make the most of all your video projects, you\u2019ll need a variety of other accessories and video camera equipment to protect, connect, and enhance your videos for higher quality and greater control. Whether you\u2019re working out of the unused den or study at home, at a rented creative space, or on location in Canada, having the right video camera equipment lets you focus on what\u2019s going on in front of the camera instead of behind. If you need new equipment fast, you can choose from several affordable and convenient shipping options to have it all delivered in time for your next big shoot. At Amazon.com, you\u2019ll find a large selection of video cameras to document your life, from sports and action types to camcorders and professional models. Featuring top brands like GoPro, Sony, Panasonic, and Canon, we bring together trusted, quality, and customer-recommended options for you to shop from the comfort of home. We also carry a variety of video camera equipment and accessories to further enhance your video camera and work. Make sure you have al