{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 3799, "catid": 1371, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_3736081_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A3736081%2Cn%3A13340241&bbn=3736081&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833495&rnid=3736081", "text": "Drawings", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Drawings from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_6?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A3736081&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "drawings": 9, "drawings from amazoncom": 1}, "description_wc": 322, "description_text": "Every room gives off a feeling, whether it\u2019s fresh, open, and clean or rich, warm, and cozy. With the fine drawings from Amazon.com, you can make sure your home sends the right message to your guests. Adorning your walls with original artwork will let friends and family know you care about creating a welcoming environment. We have a large variety of pencil drawings to add texture and taste to bare walls. We even carry a wide variety of westerns drawings from the self-taught, Canadian artist Bernie Brown. Cowboys, kids in five-gallon hats, cattle, horses and scenes from the everyday life of a farmer are his specialties. They\u2019re ideal for giving any room in the house a rustic and rural feel. Our variety of shipping options ensures you can get your new pencil drawings as quickly as you need them. If your taste in art runs to another hemisphere, we also have ink drawings from the Far East. Our reproductions of traditional Chinese calligraphy add a level of sophistication to offices and dens. We have the names of the different Chinese zodiac animals written in calligraphy; these drawings make great, personal gifts. You can even find pre-framed artworks to save you the time and money of having to hunt down the right frames. You can always check back in our Drawings Store to see new artworks we get in. Since we carry many one-of-a-kind new pieces, our collection keeps growing. Whether you\u2019re looking for a moody charcoal drawing, a brightly-color ink illustration, or a light crayon sketch, you can find what you\u2019re looking for. Our filter-by-price option even allows you to browse the most affordable drawings and illustrations we offer. Give your home the gift of ambience. No matter what mood you\u2019re trying to set in your office, living room or bedroom, Amazon.com offers drawings to suit any atmosphere.", "parent_text": "Artwork", "parent_catid": 1114, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.6", "drawings": "2.8", "drawings from amazoncom": "0.9"}, "department_id": 10},
