{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 130772, "catid": 1374, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_3736081_nr_n_3?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A3736081%2Cn%3A13337971&bbn=3736081&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833495&rnid=3736081", "text": "Photographs", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Photographs from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_6?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A3736081&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"photographs": 5, "amazoncom": 2}, "description_wc": 351, "description_text": "Do you want to refresh your eyes and mind at home after a busy work day or make a conversation connection with a co-worker or friend? A photograph hung on an office wall or placed on a mantel at home can visually inspire, delight, or connect you to the larger world. You can pay homage to your favorite U.S. president with our historical photographs printed on quality photography stock. It doesn\u2019t matter which Roosevelt you love the most, the wide selection at Amazon.com means you\u2019re sure to find what you\u2019re looking for. Our photographs --from the Apollo 12 mission to end of WW II celebrations to John Muir\u2019s stay in Yosemite--will help you commemorate the most inspiring moments in American history. If you\u2019re looking for photographs from classic moments in sports history, we have those too. What could be a better photo to get you inspired for the day ahead than the famous photo of Muhammad Ali\u2019s first-round knockout of Sonny Liston, or our 1980 Olympic hockey team celebration? Before you go to your next NBA, NFL, NHL or MLB game, check to see if we have your favorite player\u2019s portrait. Eligible items can ship at no cost with our Free Shipping and you can be sure to count on our reliable shipping to receive your photograph in time for the big game. If you get it autographed, it could become a life-long keepsake or valuable memorabilia for trading. We have plenty of artistic photographs if you\u2019re looking for something to liven up your office or mantelpiece. Black and white travel shots of the Eiffel Tower or the Brooklyn Bridge placed at the corner of a desk can spark fond travel memories. The colorful splashes of floral photography can also be used as subtle accents to your interior decoration. Whether you\u2019re looking to connect with others over a photo of a favorite sports hero or celebrity, or you want to quietly refresh your eyes with a beautiful natural vista, you\u2019ll find the photographs you want at Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Artwork", "parent_catid": 1114, "keyword_density": {"photographs": "1.4", "amazoncom": "0.6"}, "department_id": 10},
