{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 538130, "catid": 1382, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1063278_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A1063278%2Cn%3A1063298&bbn=1063278&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833498&rnid=1063278", "text": "Area Rugs & Pads", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Rugs from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_5?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A1063278&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "rugs": 13, "rugs from amazoncom": 1}, "description_wc": 426, "description_text": "Even if your gaze is primarily towards the stars or the horizon, the laws of gravity compel us to keep our feet firmly on the ground. Throughout history, from the plush beauty of traditional Persian-style rugs to the clean, natural elegance of a bamboo or sea grass mat, we humans have been making the ground under our feet beautiful with rugs, carpets, and runners. Rugs can make wonderful accent pieces to tie in the colors of a room, and they can make even the floor a welcoming and comfortable place to live, relax, and dream. At Amazon.com, you can find a huge selection of rugs in a wide variety of styles and materials. You\u2019ll find everything from braided runners to add a textured look to your hallway, to the clean and modern style of sculptured area rugs. Rugs with handmade tassels can also add a rustic and worldly feeling to any lounge or living room. Choose from a vast selection of silk, sea grass, leather, cotton, wool, acrylic, or chenille pieces. Now you can filter your search by price to see the most budget-friendly products first, and save time and money on your hunt for the right carpets, rugs, and accessories. We also have rugs in a variety of sizes, for a variety of areas and uses. Runners can add color and depth to hallways and breezeways and circular rugs are great for living rooms and under dining tables. We have all sorts of rug accessories, like under pads and carpet grippers, and you can even find fireproof rugs to make your hearth a cozy place while protecting your flooring from flying sparks. Many of our items come with Free Shipping, so you don\u2019t have to worry about extra delivery charges when you\u2019re shopping for accent pieces. Themed rugs are a fun way to express your individual style and unique hobbies. Our sports-themed items are great for the sports lovers in the family. You can find rugs with your favorite football, baseball, basketball, or hockey team logo printed on it to create your own Fan Zone in your family room. We also have many animal-themed pieces, such as elephants, zebra stripes, or birds. A faux-fur bearskin rug makes a great addition to a man cave or a lodge-themed room. Whether you need an accent rug to cozy up a bedroom, or you want a comfortable place to rest your feet on the hearth, make the ground under your feet beautiful and comfortable with the rugs from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Home D\u00e9cor", "parent_catid": 1113, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.5", "rugs": "3.1", "rugs from amazoncom": "0.7"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 42024, "catid": 1383, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1063278_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A1063278%2Cn%3A14087321&bbn=1063278&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833498&rnid=1063278", "text": "Artificial Flora", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Silk Flowers from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_5?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A1063278&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "silk": 8, "flowers": 8, "silk flowers": 5}, "description_wc": 322, "description_text": "If you miss the colorful array of flowers that bloom in April and May, or you simply want some low-maintenance floral decorations, silk flowers can give your space a burst of color and texture. You don\u2019t need a green thumb to enjoy these flowers, as they won\u2019t wilt or shrivel up from lack of water or sun. Silk flowers make perfect decorations for offices and rooms without much natural lighting. At Amazon.com, you can find your favorite silk flowers in a variety of styles and types. You\u2019ll find bouquets of red roses that will never wilt to give a lasting token to the ones you love. We also offer daisies, chrysanthemums, geraniums, daffodils, and many other flowers to make it feel like spring all year long. We even have silk orchids to bring delicate color and texture to your office desk or your kitchen windowsill. Flower petals are the perfect accessory to set the mood for a special evening. Sprinkle silk rose petals over your dining room table before you light your candles for a romantic dinner. They\u2019re also ideal for weddings, anniversaries, and sprinkling on the edge of your bathtub or hot tub. Filter your search by price to see the most affordable silk flower options first. It could save you time and money in your hunt for the perfect wedding or party decorations. Not every d\u00e9cor needs to evoke a romantic getaway. Add fresh green and a peaceful ambiance of the outdoors with artificial trees and shrubs. You can find fun shapes of topiary to create a whimsical atmosphere for garden parties. We also have a number of hanging silk flowers in pots, like purple wisteria, when floor space is scarce or you want to accent archways and other architectural features. Enjoy the long-lasting beauty of silk flowers and add a touch of nature to your home or office with help from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Home D\u00e9cor", "parent_catid": 1113, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.6", "silk": "2.5", "flowers": "2.5", "silk flowers": "3.1"}, "department_id": 10},
