{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 31667, "catid": 1391, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1063278_nr_n_9?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A1063278%2Cn%3A1063284&bbn=1063278&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833498&rnid=1063278", "text": "Fireplaces & Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Fireplaces from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_5?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A1063278&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"fireplaces": 7, "fireplaces from amazoncom": 1}, "description_wc": 335, "description_text": "It was on one fateful New Year\u2019s Eve in England that bassist Noel Redding invited American guitar legend Jimi Hendrix to his mother\u2019s house. The night was so cold, and the fire so warm, it inspired Jimi to write his hit \u201cFire\u201d. Let the fireplaces from Amazon.com inspire you on the coldest nights. Classic wood burning fireplaces give your home a traditional feeling and a wonderful smell. Our fireplace surrounds make sure you can tailor the look of your fireplace to fit your home\u2019s d\u00e9cor, whether you want to add a rustic cabin-style atmosphere, or one of luxury and grace. Our gas fireplaces look authentic, but since they do not make ash or cinders, they can be a cleaner and safer alternative to traditional fireplaces. We make it easy for you to search fireplaces by letting you filter by price, so you can easily stay within your budget. Our outdoor and portable fireplaces make it easy to stay toasty even outside. If you are hosting a barbeque, a pool party or just having a few friends over for a drink on the patio, do not let the conversation freeze up. You will be glad you have these sturdy outdoor units to keep you warm while the beautiful exterior keeps your guests talking. We have a variety of shipping options, so if you need your order quickly to ensure your guests are not left out in the cold, we have you covered. It can be tough to remember all the fireplace accessories you need when you go out shopping. That\u2019s why we also offer kindling, Zippos, logs, and more to light your fire and keep it burning strong. Our magnesium fire starters fit great on key chains, and come in handy when camping or just lighting up a log. We have only one burning desire: to offer you the best and most affordable fireplaces possible. Once you write your legendary musical hit, just remember who helped light your fire.", "parent_text": "Home D\u00e9cor", "parent_catid": 1113, "keyword_density": {"fireplaces from amazoncom": "0.9", "fireplaces": "2.1"}, "department_id": 10},
