{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 74096, "catid": 1394, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1063278_nr_n_12?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A1063278%2Cn%3A3734741&bbn=1063278&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833498&rnid=1063278", "text": "Home Fragrance", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Home Fragrances from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_5?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A1063278&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"home": 7, "home fragrances": 4, "fragrances": 5, "amazoncom": 3, "home fragrances from amazoncom": 2}, "description_wc": 360, "description_text": "Experts say that out of all of our senses, smell has the closest ties with memory. Make sure your guests remember you positively with home fragrances from Amazon.com. Make your home smell wonderful to create a warming and comforting environment that welcomes friends and families. We offer a wide variety of home fragrances in many mediums, including room sprays. Room sprays are a quick and efficient way to freshen up a musty or stale room. We have a variety of spray fragrances, including vanilla, pumpkin, white cotton and much more. With so many choices available it could be difficult to choose the right one for you. Amazon\u2019s filters allow you to quickly narrow your searches find just the right fragrance for your needs. Aromatherapists know how different smells can alter your mood, make you more focused, or even soothe headaches and tension. According to some home fragrances like eucalyptus have antibacterial and pain-easing properties, jasmine can enhance your mood, and cypress or peppermint can help you focus. At Amazon.com, we carry a variety of fragrant oils to add to diffusers, or to dilute and dab on your wrists and behind your ears for a quick pick-me-up. But don\u2019t take our word for it, experiment to see which scents fits your mood and keep your creativity and imagination going. We also have a wide variety of decorative home fragrance solutions, including incense, sachets and potpourri. Sachets can add a spot of color to your bathroom and make it smell as fresh as a field of lavender or as earthy as sandalwood. Our incense comes in sticks, cones, or resin, and we have a wide variety of intricate incense burners that look as good as your incense smells. Light bulb rings are an interesting way of diffusing fragrant oils, simply fill the ring with your fragrance, and screw a light bulb into its socket through the ring. The warmth of your lights will also breathe the smell of flowers and linens through your house. Our rich aromas will make coming to your home a rich and memorable event. Make memories with the fresh home fragrances from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Home D\u00e9cor", "parent_catid": 1113, "keyword_density": {"home": "1.9", "home fragrances": "2.2", "fragrances": "1.4", "amazoncom": "0.8", "home fragrances from amazoncom": "2.2"}, "department_id": 10},
