{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 326583, "catid": 1406, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1063278_nr_n_24?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A1063278%2Cn%3A1063302&bbn=1063278&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833498&rnid=1063278", "text": "Window Treatments", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Window Treatments from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_5?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A1063278&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"window treatments": 5, "window treatments from amazoncom": 2, "window": 14}, "description_wc": 354, "description_text": "If you\u2019re redoing your living room, bedroom or kitchen and you feel like something\u2019s missing, we have just the thing to add color, depth, and atmosphere to your room. They say that eyes are the windows of the soul, but we say the windows are the soul of the home. The window treatments from Amazon.com are the perfect finishing touches to your redecorating project. Nothing provides a more regal and opulent atmosphere than a lush set of curtains. Our curtains come in a variety of materials, colors, and styles so you can choose what goes best with your existing interior design scheme. Heavy curtains can also help you insulate your home from chilly or warm weather, keeping the climate in your home more comfortable. If you love to let in the light and weather, we have sheer curtains that filter light through rich colors, giving your home a fresh, airy ambience. Blinds and shades are great window treatment options for smaller window areas, for offices, or for those shopping on a budget. Our blinds and shades come in just as many colors and styles, so you don\u2019t have to sacrifice beauty for functionality. Blinds are easier to retract and let down whenever you want; there are no hooks, ties or stubborn curtain rings to deal with, only a simple draw string. In terms of window treatments, they\u2019re also much lighter, making them easier to install or store away. Once you have your blinds or curtains up, it\u2019s time to start thinking about treatment for the window panes themselves. Browse our collection of window films to give your transom, bathroom windows, or kitchen windows a splash of color. We have many stained glass designs that can give your living room a cathedral-like grandeur, and elegant frosted glass window treatments to add a bit of privacy. Now you can even filter your search by price, so you can see the most affordable window treatments first. If windows are the soul of your home, you can add light and comfort to your life with all the fresh window treatments from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Home D\u00e9cor", "parent_catid": 1113, "keyword_density": {"window treatments": "2.8", "window": "4.0", "window treatments from amazoncom": "2.3"}, "department_id": 10},
