{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 4980337, "catid": 1409, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_3736081_nr_n_4?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A3736081%2Cn%3A381142011&bbn=3736081&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833495&rnid=3736081", "text": "Posters & Prints", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Posters from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_6?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A3736081&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"posters": 10, "amazoncom": 3}, "description_wc": 301, "description_text": "On a decorating budget, or limited for space in your home, dorm room or apartment? For affordable, space-saving decorations, there\u2019s nothing better than posters. You\u2019ll find everything you want in the wide selection of posters at Amazon.com, whether you want a touch of classic art to refresh your eyes, or something to express your unique personality and individuality. At Amazon.com, you can find posters of works by classic masters such as Dali, Van Gogh, Renoir, and more. We have everything from a timeless classic like Van Gogh\u2019s \u201cStarry Night\u201d to posters of the work of Ralph Steadman, whose iconic illustrations from the book Fear and Loathing in Las Vegas helped create a lasting aesthetic. Many of our posters are eligible for Free Shipping, so you don\u2019t have to worry about added delivery costs. We also carry posters of your favorite movies, TV shows, sports heroes, and actors. You can find posters of iconic movie stars like James Dean and Marilyn Monroe or movie posters for just about any movie you can think of, from Star Wars, The Big Lebowski, and James Bond, to Indiana Jones and The Walking Dead. If music is a big part of your life, you can find all the posters with the musicians and bands that influenced you and made you who you are musically. Led Zeppelin, Jimi Hendrix and Kurt Cobain, Bob Dylan, and Bob Marley can help you express your style and taste and start conversations. Now you can filter your search by price to see the most affordable items first. It could save you time and money. Whether you\u2019re trying to add a little atmosphere to your home or dorm room, or want to express your own unique style, the posters at Amazon.com could be the perfect solution.", "parent_text": "Artwork", "parent_catid": 1114, "keyword_density": {"posters": "3.3", "amazoncom": "1.0"}, "department_id": 10},
