{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 141, "catid": 1431, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_510240_nr_n_5?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A510240%2Cn%3A3737861&bbn=510240&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833456&rnid=510240", "text": "Garment Steamer Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Steamer Accessories from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_9?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A510240&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 3, "steamer accessories": 5, "accessories": 6, "steamer": 9}, "description_wc": 310, "description_text": "Don\u2019t look like you rolled out of bed with your clothes on\u2014look fresh and wrinkle-free everyday with simple garment steamer accessories. At Amazon.com, you can find all the accessories for steaming, cleaning, and pressing your clothes. Browse our selection for everything you could need to look your best from start to finish. With Free Shipping, get the items you need straight to your door, whether that\u2019s a steam press stand, garment brush, or different head attachment. Garment steamers can be extremely dangerous if used without the proper steamer accessories. Use protective hand mitts so you don\u2019t burn yourself doing a quick steam, and be sure to maintain and clean your steamer regularly with liquid cleaner to remove hard buildup. Many steamers also feature interchangeable heads so you can use the appropriate attachment for different types of clothing, drapes, and fabrics. For those on-the-go or special-care items, Amazon.com carries a wide range of specialty steamer accessories for you to find what you need. Get the fresh-pressed look at your next business conference with portable, handheld steamers that easily fit into carry-on luggage. Use a hanging steamboard to create a convenient workplace to steam without damaging nearby furniture. You can also try a scented steam spray right before the steam; it will leave your clothes and fabrics smelling clean and fresh. Once you\u2019ve finished steaming, don\u2019t forget the steamer accessories that add the finishing touches. One quick sweep with a lint brush or roller easily removes leftover lint, hair, and dust. Then get rid of fuzz on napped, woven, and knitted fabrics with a fabric comb to have a spotless and sharp look every time. With Amazon.com\u2019s wide selection of garment steamer accessories, you won\u2019t be hard-pressed to look and feel good. It\u2019ll just come naturally.", "parent_text": "Irons & Steamers", "parent_catid": 1117, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "1.0", "steamer accessories": "3.2", "accessories": "1.9", "steamer": "2.9"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 671, "catid": 1432, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_510240_nr_n_6?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A510240%2Cn%3A510248&bbn=510240&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833456&rnid=510240", "text": "Garment Steamers", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Steamers from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_9?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A510240&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"steamers from amazoncom": 1, "amazoncom": 3, "steamers": 7}, "description_wc": 360, "description_text": "When you want to get some deep cleaning done, but don\u2019t want to scrub and scrap for hours, try using a machine like a steamer to get that deep, satisfying clean with less effort and chemicals. Steamers are easy to use and require little energy to melt dirt and stains away. All you have to do is fill the steamer with water as if you were filling an kettle to make tea, and the steamer provides a stream of pure steam to clean your surfaces with ease. Find the selection of steamers and cleaners you\u2019re looking for at Amazon.com. You can find standing steamers which are great for heavy-duty jobs or everyday use. Many come with a number of attachments for carpets, upholstery and more, so if you have a stubborn stain on a couch cushion that you can\u2019t run through the washer, our steamers can make short work of it. You can even disinfect cutting surfaces in the kitchen with a thorough steam wash. Like waving a magic wand, you\u2019ll make stains and grime disappear in an instant. Our handheld steamers are so effective and easy to use, you\u2019ll walk around your home like a cowboy wondering what else to aim your six-shooter at. Blast the gunk from bathroom tile grout, lift away stains from your favorite armchair, and steam press wrinkles out of your clothes without lugging around heavy equipment. Speaking of lugging things around, Amazon.com offers a wide variety of shipping options, including Free Shipping for eligible items so you can avoid added delivery costs. A very popular benefit of steamers and steam-cleaning is that you can achieve a deep clean without using chemicals. Pure steam is a very efficient cleaner and can blast away dirt and grime without bleach, ammonia, or soap. If you want to limit your exposure to household chemicals, a steamer can be indispensable. Cleaning your kitchen, bathroom, sofa, and clothing is as easy as filling a kettle. Enjoy more freedom to sit down and savor an actual cup of tea, as you make your cleaning jobs a pleasant experience with the steamers from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Irons & Steamers", "parent_catid": 1117, "keyword_density": {"steamers from amazoncom": "0.8", "amazoncom": "0.8", "steamers": "1.9"}, "department_id": 10},
