{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 18138, "catid": 1435, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_510106_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A510106%2Cn%3A3743521&bbn=510106&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833456&rnid=510106", "text": "Vacuums", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Vacuums from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_10?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A510106&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "vacuums": 5}, "description_wc": 341, "description_text": "There\u2019s nothing quite like walking barefoot on clean, freshly vacuumed carpet, or sliding in your socks across a sleek, wood floor. You can enjoy keeping your carpets squishy and walkable and keep your hard flooring surfaces smooth and clean with the right type of vacuum cleaner. Bagged or bagless, upright or canister, the variety of sizes and styles available at Amazon.com means you\u2019ll find the perfect vacuum for you--and your toes. New vacuums are more powerful and easier to use than ever before. You can find popular brands like Dyson, Hoover, and Eureka--brands that are making innovative new vacuums with handy features like retractable cords, bagless canisters, and integrated extension tools to target hard to reach places. Most newer vacuums are just as effective on hardwood floors as they are on carpets, and some even have integrated wet carpet cleaning, so you can do the work of two machines with a single vacuum. There are a number of vacuum models specifically designed for pet owners. Hair and dander can be notoriously difficult to extract from carpet and upholstery, so many vacuum manufacturers have developed deep cleaning brushes and attachments to gather up everything your pet leaves behind. Some models are equipped with HEPA filters, so you can be sure all the dust you\u2019re collecting stays in the bag or canister, and doesn\u2019t end up recirculating. For quick cleanups, reach for a handheld vacuum. Cordless and rechargeable models are perfect for spot cleaning accidental messes, or nimbly getting around cluttered areas like desks and workbenches. Powerful lithium ion batteries maintain powerful suction for longer than older designs, so you won\u2019t have to worry about running out of juice in the middle of cleaning up. Some handhelds can be mounted to an extension handle, so you can use them like lightweight upright vacuums for larger messes. Your vacuum should help you get done cleaning quickly and easily. Choose a full-featured model from the selection of vacuums at Amazon.com, and start enjoying clean and walkable floors.", "parent_text": "Vacuums & Floor Care", "parent_catid": 1118, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.6", "vacuums": "1.5"}, "department_id": 10},
