{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 868, "catid": 1441, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_510106_nr_n_6?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A510106%2Cn%3A3303860011&bbn=510106&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833456&rnid=510106", "text": "Steam Cleaners & Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Steam Cleaners from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_10?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A510106&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 1, "steam": 13, "steam cleaners": 6}, "description_wc": 320, "description_text": "Keeping your home clean and fresh doesn\u2019t have to involve harsh cleaning chemicals and laborious scrubbing. Steam cleaners are a popular new way to clean and sanitize many surfaces around your home. If you\u2019re eager to get rid of the old mop and bucket, consider a steam cleaner designed for floors. Sealed wood floors, concrete, laminate, or any other hard, impermeable surfaces can be cleaned and sanitized quickly and easily. Unlike traditional mops, a steam cleaner can sanitize your floors without any chemicals or harmful fumes. The clean surface dries quickly, so you won\u2019t have to wait long to walk on it. We offer lightweight, easy to use steam mops, as well as heavier duty models for more frequent use. Hand steam cleaners are fantastic for kitchen and bathroom fixtures, glass, and a range of other household applications. Just like steam mops, handheld steam cleaners will quickly sanitize the surface you\u2019re cleaning, eliminating odors and making clean up a breeze. Many customers use handheld steam cleaners to freshen and sanitize hard to wash items like dog beds and cat litter boxes. Most come with handy attachments like wire brushes and angled nozzles to help clean hard to reach places and stubborn messes. At Amazon.com, you\u2019ll find a variety of steam cleaners and accessories from top brands like Bissel, Shark, and Haan. Extra cleaning pads and attachments are easy to find with our powerful product search. Simply enter the brand and style of steam cleaner you own, and we\u2019ll show you compatible products. Whether you\u2019re looking for microfiber, cotton, or disposable pads and cloths, we make it easy to get the supplies you need delivered straight to your door. With steam cleaners, you can clean nearly any room in your home quickly and free of chemicals. Powerful sanitizing steam will replace many cleaning products, and help your new steam cleaner to pay for itself.", "parent_text": "Vacuums & Floor Care", "parent_catid": 1118, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.3", "steam": "4.1", "steam cleaners": "3.8"}, "department_id": 10},
