{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 44118, "catid": 1446, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1063306_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A1063306%2Cn%3A3733781&bbn=1063306&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833495&rnid=1063306", "text": "Dining Room Furniture", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Dining Room Sets from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_4?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A1063306&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"dining": 10, "dining room sets": 5, "dining room": 9, "room": 12}, "description_wc": 338, "description_text": "Whether you\u2019re entertaining guests, or simply enjoying a meal at the table with your family, the furniture you enjoy can help set the mood, and create a comfortable atmosphere. Dining room sets are a prominent aspect of the overall d\u00e9cor of a room, and styles vary from casual and comfortable, to traditional and embellished. No matter what style reflects your personal taste, you\u2019ll appreciate how a coordinated dining room set can help tie a room together. Since dining room sets come in such a wide variety of styles, we\u2019ve made it easy to browse furniture you\u2019re interested in. You can filter products by keyword, style, construction material, and more. Do you need a square, oak table with matching chairs? Simply enter your criteria and peruse the items that match. If you have broader ideas about what you want your room d\u00e9cor to look like, you can browse style categories like casual, contemporary, and traditional. Some dining room sets include cabinetry and other storage furniture. A buffet or china hutch that matches your dining room furniture creates a wonderful, cohesive look. It can also be helpful when entertaining to have access to serving or storage areas in the same area as the rest of your dining room set, to cut back on running back and forth from the kitchen. The practically endless variety of styles, functions, and sizes in dining room sets means you can create the dining and entertaining space you\u2019ve always wanted, and with Free Shipping on many products, you won\u2019t have to dip into the dinner fund to do it. Of course, if you\u2019ve got an important party coming up and simply can\u2019t live without a new dining room set, we can expedite your order at additional cost. Either way, your new furniture will arrive on your doorstep, and you\u2019ll be ready to start entertaining. Coordinated dining room sets are a great way to create a cohesive and welcoming atmosphere for your family and guests. >", "parent_text": "Furniture", "parent_catid": 1112, "keyword_density": {"dining": "3.0", "dining room sets": "4.4", "dining room": "5.3", "room": "3.6"}, "department_id": 10},
