{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 157052, "catid": 1456, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_nr_n_0?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A284507%2Cn%3A289668&bbn=284507&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833495&rnid=284507", "text": "Bakeware", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Kitchen Bakeware from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A284507&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"bakeware": 6, "kitchen bakeware": 4, "kitchen bakeware from amazoncom": 1}, "description_wc": 275, "description_text": "Nothing shows your love like freshly baked goods, and high-quality kitchen bakeware from Amazon.com can help you create delectable desserts and savory snacks for your whole family to enjoy. From baking sheets to mixing bowls, we pride ourselves on offering everything you need to get all of your baking done as efficiently as possible. Looking for kitchen bakeware sets to help you make the most of your oven? Choose bakeware sets that include loaf pans, cake pans, muffin tins, and cookie sheets to give yourself plenty of options when you're ready to bake. Glass bakeware from Pyrex and CorningWare let you store and serve your baked goods in the same pieces you cooked them in, and nonstick pieces from Rachael Ray and Nordic Ware make cleanup a breeze. You can also find specialty pieces, such as ramekins and bundt pans, to help you branch out into more complex baking projects. In addition to the basic pieces of kitchen bakeware, we also carry all of the accessories you need to make your baking endeavors successful. Cake-decorating kits from Wilton help your cakes, cupcakes, and cookies look even better. Cute cookie cutters from Fred & Friends give your desserts a fun new look. Mixing bowls in a variety of sizes from Trudeau and OXO help you with the preparation so you can start off your baking marathon right. Everyone loves dessert, and when you stock up on kitchen bakeware, you'll be ready to make homemade treats whenever you like. Whether you prefer cakes or pies, cookies or scones, these pieces can make your favorite desserts look like they were made by a professional baker.", "parent_text": "Kitchen & Dining", "parent_catid": 1109, "keyword_density": {"bakeware": "2.2", "kitchen bakeware": "2.9", "kitchen bakeware from amazoncom": "1.5"}, "department_id": 10},
