{"nr_products": 165077, "catid": 1458, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A284507%2Cn%3A915194&bbn=284507&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833495&rnid=284507", "text": "Coffee, Tea & Espresso", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_wc": 0, "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A284507&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "parent_text": "Kitchen & Dining", "parent_catid": 1109, "department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 65133, "catid": 1459, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_nr_n_3?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A284507%2Cn%3A289814&bbn=284507&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833495&rnid=284507", "text": "Cookware", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Kitchen Cookware", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A284507&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"cookware": 11, "kitchen": 3}, "description_wc": 424, "description_text": "One of life's truest pleasures, cooking at home is the supreme act of love toward family, friends, and guests. Believe it or not, it can actually be one of life's simplest pleasures, too--provided you're stocked with the right pots and pans for the job. You know from experience that pasta expands when cooked, that tomato sauce spatters something terrible if overheated, and that the right tea kettle can fill your home with the most comforting whistle when the soul-warming brew's ready. That's why it's so important to augment, rethink, and occasionally replace your pots and pans to ensure that your kitchen's ready for each task at hand. For example, Amazon.com offers a full line of individual pots and pans--such as a large stockpot with a sieve inset to make draining those spaghetti noodles a breeze, or a tightly lidded saucepan that keeps the stovetop and surrounding range free from messy splatters. You'll also find entire cookware collections including cast-iron cookware, stainless-steel cookware, copper cookware, and hard-anodized-aluminum cookware--pieces designed to not only perform flawlessly under a variety of applications, but also to look beautiful for effortless kitchen-to-table use. For the professional (or simply adventurous) chef, Amazon.com provides a full range of specialty pots and pans--pieces such as oversized woks for authentic Asian cooking, risotto pans that create perfect versions of the Italian delicacy, and double boilers for melting fine chocolate, cooking European custards, and whipping up homemade fondues, frostings, or fudge. When you know what you need to round out your current cookware--or even if you're just getting started on your cookware collection--you can sort by a number of different criteria in order to narrow in on the right pots and pans for the job. For example, search cookware by ethnicity to find a range of cookware tailored to those spicy Indian dishes or exotic Spanish sides you've been wanting to try. Or, search for cookware by brand or price (or both), and use the customer reviews to help you decide between Rachael Ray's and Wolfgang Puck's lines of non-stick frying pans. Adding just one or two new cookware options can reinvigorate your entire kitchen and redouble your resolve to try that new recipe, which can in turn provide the impetus to invite that couple over for drinks and appetizers--or try your hand at hosting the family Thanksgiving this year. And that's how memories are made.", "parent_text": "Kitchen & Dining", "parent_catid": 1109, "keyword_density": {"cookware": "2.6", "kitchen": "0.7"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 44256, "catid": 1460, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_nr_n_4?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A284507%2Cn%3A3733781&bbn=284507&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833495&rnid=284507", "text": "Dining Room Furniture", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Dining Room Sets from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A284507&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"dining": 10, "dining room sets": 5, "dining room": 9, "room": 12}, "description_wc": 338, "description_text": "Whether you\u2019re entertaining guests, or simply enjoying a meal at the table with your family, the furniture you enjoy can help set the mood, and create a comfortable atmosphere. Dining room sets are a prominent aspect of the overall d\u00e9cor of a room, and styles vary from casual and comfortable, to traditional and embellished. No matter what style reflects your personal taste, you\u2019ll appreciate how a coordinated dining room set can help tie a room together. Since dining room sets come in such a wide variety of styles, we\u2019ve made it easy to browse furniture you\u2019re interested in. You can filter products by keyword, style, construction material, and more. Do you need a square, oak table with matching chairs? Simply enter your criteria and peruse the items that match. If you have broader ideas about what you want your room d\u00e9cor to look like, you can browse style categories like casual, contemporary, and traditional. Some dining room sets include cabinetry and other storage furniture. A buffet or china hutch that matches your dining room furniture creates a wonderful, cohesive look. It can also be helpful when entertaining to have access to serving or storage areas in the same area as the rest of your dining room set, to cut back on running back and forth from the kitchen. The practically endless variety of styles, functions, and sizes in dining room sets means you can create the dining and entertaining space you\u2019ve always wanted, and with Free Shipping on many products, you won\u2019t have to dip into the dinner fund to do it. Of course, if you\u2019ve got an important party coming up and simply can\u2019t live without a new dining room set, we can expedite your order at additional cost. Either way, your new furniture will arrive on your doorstep, and you\u2019ll be ready to start entertaining. Coordinated dining room sets are a great way to create a cohesive and welcoming atmosphere for your family and guests. >", "parent_text": "Kitchen & Dining", "parent_catid": 1109, "keyword_density": {"dining": "3.0", "dining room sets": "4.4", "dining room": "5.3", "room": "3.6"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 90613, "catid": 1461, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_nr_n_5?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A284507%2Cn%3A6054382011&bbn=284507&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833495&rnid=284507", "text": "Food Service Equipment & Supplies", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Food Service & Restaurant Supplies", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A284507&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"food": 7, "restaurant supplies": 3, "food service": 2, "supplies": 9, "restaurant": 17}, "description_wc": 230, "description_text": "Restaurant supplies and equipment include a wide variety of restaurant supply products that are used in commercial and residential kitchens, and carried by restaurant supply stores. Essential kitchen supply products commonly include kitchen utensils, commercial cookware, and commercial bakeware. Restaurant equipment is used to prepare and transport food and dishes used in restaurant supply environments. Restaurant equipment and kitchen supplies include janitorial equipment, racks and shelving, and bulk food storage products, used to store food. Kitchen supplies also include food serving items. Tabletop restaurant supply products, such as restaurant dining room supplies, are used to set tables, and serve and display food. Food service disposables are used to replenish kitchen supplies for everyday serving. Kitchen supplies consist of commercial bakeware, such as racks, baking sheets, and braising torches, which are common products in a restaurant supply business. Commercial stovetops, sinks, dishwashers, pizza ovens, and refrigeration products are a central component of restaurant supplies. Specific restaurant equipment, such as bar equipment and supply, or concession and vending restaurant supply products, may also be used. Restaurant supply products include food service disposables, such as gloves, plates, and utensils, and items used to support cleaning and maintaining kitchens, restaurants, and other facilities that use restaurant supplies. Restaurant equipment can include other types of specific restaurant supply equipment, such as bar equipment and other kitchen supply accessories, such as coffee and espresso kitchen supplies.", "parent_text": "Kitchen & Dining", "parent_catid": 1109, "keyword_density": {"food": "3.0", "restaurant supplies": "2.6", "restaurant": "7.4", "supplies": "3.9", "food service": "1.7"}, "department_id": 10},
