{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 17903, "catid": 1465, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_nr_n_9?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A284507%2Cn%3A1063316&bbn=284507&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833495&rnid=284507", "text": "Kitchen Furniture", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Kitchen Furniture from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A284507&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 3, "kitchen furniture": 6, "furniture": 7, "kitchen": 13}, "description_wc": 320, "description_text": "The kitchen, which is the place where you prepare food in your home, can make or break your living experience or your guests' comfort. Shopping from our selection of kitchen furniture ensures that your kitchen is as comfortable and efficient as it can be, so you can prepare tasty meals and entertain guests with minimal hassle. Do you need new kitchen furniture to remodel the room or to make things easier to find? The Kitchen Furniture Store on Amazon.com has everything you need to store food, spices, and condiments and to accommodate a room full of people. Our products include bakers' racks, kitchen chairs, tables, serving carts, storage carts, and tables. We pride ourselves on delivering all the furnishings you need for your kitchen. Bakers' racks give you a space to organize your spices and baking materials or to place finished confections. The Whitmor supreme baker's rack, a simple chrome-and-wood design, can go well with any kitchen's decor. The SEI Celtic metal baker's rack stands tall in the corner of your room and gives you plenty of space to work. Our selection of serving and storage carts gives you places to put food items you use frequently, such as canned goods or condiments. Buying carts instead of fixed containers lets you rearrange your kitchen or move where you're working without heavy lifting. Browse the Kitchen Furniture Store to find cheap prices on furniture. Our wide selection of chairs and tables ensures that you can seat your family, friends, or guests comfortably. The Kitchen Furniture Store on Amazon.com offers prep tables, folding tables, and dining tables. If you need chairs, you can choose from a wide variety of models and designs. The kitchen is one of the focal points of your home. Why not use Amazon.com's Kitchen Furniture Store to equip it? You're sure to find reasonable prices on any product you need.", "parent_text": "Kitchen & Dining", "parent_catid": 1109, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.9", "furniture": "2.2", "kitchen": "4.1", "kitchen furniture": "3.8"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 56255, "catid": 1466, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_nr_n_10?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A284507%2Cn%3A289851&bbn=284507&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833495&rnid=284507", "text": "Kitchen Knives & Cutlery Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Kitchen Knives from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A284507&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"knives": 9, "amazoncom": 2, "kitchen knives": 4, "kitchen": 7}, "description_wc": 277, "description_text": "Preparing food is much easier when you have a good set of kitchen knives to tackle the chopping, slicing, and dicing. From sushi to steaks, each food has a particular knife that it works best with. Whether you are looking for a complete set of knives to handle all of your food prep needs or a specialty knife, such as a Santoku knife, to help you focus on perfecting a particular style of cuisine, you can find all your cutlery at Amazon.com. Looking for a set of kitchen knives that includes a chef knife, bread knife, and more? We pride ourselves on offering plenty of knife sets from manufacturers such as Chicago Cutlery, Wusthof, and Ginsu. Each set comes with a wood, plastic, or metal knife block that keeps your knives safe and organized. In addition to kitchen knives, you can find plenty of kitchen accessories that help you keep your knives in good shape, so they continue to work as well as the first day you bought them. Knife sharpeners from manufacturers such as Presto and Fiskars can keep your blades keen and ready for action. Magnetic knife bars from MIU France and Norpro help you keep your knives close at hand, and no kitchen is complete without a set of cutting boards from OXO, Totally Bamboo, or Farberware to chop, cut