{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 75015, "catid": 1469, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_nr_n_13?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A284507%2Cn%3A289913&bbn=284507&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833495&rnid=284507", "text": "Small Appliances", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Kitchen Appliances from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A284507&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"kitchen appliances": 3, "appliances": 6}, "description_wc": 278, "description_text": "Having the right kitchen appliances, whether they are large or small, helps you make the meals that fill your family's bellies and gives you a reason to gather around the table to talk about your day. There are kitchen appliances to fill every cooking need you may have. Looking for a way to prepare your ingredients? These products will help you mix, chop, and dice. Our preparation appliances include mixers, food processors, and toasters, and we carry a wide range of small kitchen appliances to help you turn raw ingredients into dish-ready concoctions. Looking for a way to cook your main dish? These products will help you fully cook your main dish, so it is hot and ready at dinner time. Our cooking appliances include contact grills, slow cookers, ovens, and microwaves. We carry a selection of items that will make your dinner a success.Looking for a way to satisfy your sweet tooth? These products will help you make a delectable dessert that the whole family will enjoy. Our appliances include ice cream machines and blenders that will transform you into a sweets connoisseur and help you whip up everyone's favorite course: dessert. Looking for a pick-me-up in the morning? These products will help you make everything from coffee to smoothies. Our products include coffeemakers, juicers, electric kettles, and espresso machines. We carry everything you need to make the special beverage that gets you up and moving. The more specific an appliance is to your needs, the easier it will be to prepare the meals that your children will remember even after they are grown and possibly make for their own children someday.", "parent_text": "Kitchen & Dining", "parent_catid": 1109, "keyword_density": {"appliances": "2.2", "kitchen appliances": "2.2"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 181769, "catid": 1470, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_nr_n_14?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A284507%2Cn%3A510136&bbn=284507&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833495&rnid=284507", "text": "Storage & Organization", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Kitchen Storage from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A284507&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "kitchen storage": 6, "kitchen": 11}, "description_wc": 339, "description_text": "The kitchen is often considered to be the heart of the home, a place where warmth, nourishment, and connection flourish. Would you like to make your kitchen a light, clean, and healthy heart of the home? The kitchen storage solutions from Amazon.com can keep the flow going by helping you put everything in its rightful place and banishing the chaos of clutter in your kitchen. We have a wide variety of kitchen storage containers in different shapes and sizes. Snap the lids over left-overs or lunches to keep them fresh and tasty. Our cabinet organizers are great for those with limited pantry and cabinet space. These simple kitchen storage solutions easily hold your spices and baking materials.. Our utensil organizers will keep your forks, knives, and spoons handy and spotless while you\u2019re not using them. Bottles and jars offer useful kitchen storage solutions for a variety of food and condiments. Here\u2019s a great idea: mix a fresh basil pesto with light mayonnaise and keep it in one of our convenient squeeze bottles for a delicious and quick sandwich topping. We also carry a selection of cookie jars, candy trays and other treat canisters. Our cookie jars come in fun designs like colorful teddy bears, owls with scarves, bright cupcakes, Tardis from Dr. Who, and even Darth Vader. Browsing our kitchen storage items with our price filter on lets you find the most affordable products easier. For those on the go, our lunch boxes provide your meals a safe journey. Our vintage-style, tin lunch boxes come with a huge variety of characters from cartoons, movies, and classic TV shows. Choose from Batman, Star Trek, My Little Pony, Snoopy, The Wizard of Oz, and many others. You can buy one for your kids to take to school. There, that\u2019s the perfect excuse to use when you buy yourself a Wonder Woman lunch box. Make your kitchen a place of warmth, nourishment, and harmony. Keep your kitchen free of clutter with the kitchen storage supplies from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Kitchen & Dining", "parent_catid": 1109, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.6", "kitchen storage": "3.5", "kitchen": "3.2"}, "department_id": 10},
