{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 29796, "catid": 1475, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1063252_nr_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A1063252%2Cn%3A2224405011&bbn=1063252&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833496&rnid=1063252", "text": "Comforters & Sets", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Comforters at Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A1063252&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"comforters": 4, "amazoncom": 1}, "description_wc": 324, "description_text": "Are you the kind of person who likes to feel like you\u2019re sleeping in an enormous, snuggly cloud? Or do you prefer to slumber under slimmer and more weightless bedding? No matter what your preference, choosing the right comforter can help you achieve the perfect night\u2019s sleep. Comforters are made from a variety of soft fabrics and fillings, so it\u2019s important to determine which combination suits you best. For years, the preferred material for comforters has been goose down. The soft, insulating feathers effectively keep warmth in, and provide a pleasant weight on your body. More modern synthetic materials have also become popular due to their low cost, and easy maintenance. Many are also hypoallergenic, which is crucial for people sensitive to natural fibers. Synthetic fillers are often machine-washable, which makes caring for your comforter a breeze. Some comforters feature cells stitched into the structure of the fabric which help hold filler material in place, which means no more waking up to an empty comforter with all the down balled up in the end. You can choose from different cell sizes, depending on your preferences. You can use our search filters to narrow what products are displayed to make it easier to find the right comforter for you. You can even sort by thread count to make sure your new comforter matches the sheets you\u2019ve already got at home. When it comes to comforters, knowing as much as you can about a product before you make a decision is important. Our customer reviews let you hear feedback from other people who have purchased the exact item you\u2019re interested in, taking some of the guesswork out of shopping for bedding. With Free Shipping on many items, you won\u2019t have to wait long until your new bedding is delivered right to your door. Compliment your favorite sheets and pillows and get cozy with a wonderful new comforter from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Bedding", "parent_catid": 1110, "keyword_density": {"comforters": "1.2", "amazoncom": "0.3"}, "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 234895, "catid": 1476, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1063252_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A1063252%2Cn%3A2224404011&bbn=1063252&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833496&rnid=1063252", "text": "Duvet Covers & Sets", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Duvet Covers from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A1063252&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"covers": 6, "amazoncom": 2, "duvet covers from amazoncom": 1, "duvet covers": 5, "duvet": 8}, "description_wc": 312, "description_text": "According to the National Health Institute, lack of sleep can result in sluggish thoughts and an increased risk of certain conditions, including obesity. If keeping your mind sharp and waist-line down aren\u2019t great excuses for a midday nap, I don\u2019t know what is. The duvet covers at Amazon.com will help lull you into a healthful sleep by keeping you warm and comfortable. We have duvet covers in every standard bed size you could need. Twin, full, queen, king and even Californian king sized covers are here in a variety of style and materials. Choose from smooth Egyptian cotton, velvet, satin and silk, or sturdier fabrics such as flannel, denim and polyester blends. Our selection of shipping options means you can save money with Free Shipping on certain items, or expedited two-day and next-day shipping for speedy delivery. We know you don\u2019t want a duvet cover that will disrupt your bedroom\u2019s jungle feel, pastel color scheme, or other theme. That\u2019s why we carry such a huge selection of colored and patterned items. Our chocolate-brown duvet covers will make you feel like you\u2019re sleeping in a warm pile of fresh brownies. Bold lines and colors will add a modern edge to your room. You can filter our products by price or by discount, so you can browse the most affordable items first. Our full duvet sets ensure that your whole bed will get the same make-over that your duvet does. Mismatched pillow-cases, sheets and blankets can make your room look haphazard and messy even when the bed is made. Now you can make your bedroom look consistent and neat with our duvet covers. Loss of focus or weight gain can mean you\u2019re not getting enough sleep. Tuck yourself in with the duvet covers from Amazon.com for a good night\u2019s sleep.", "parent_text": "Bedding", "parent_catid": 1110, "keyword_density": {"duvet covers": "3.2", "amazoncom": "0.6", "duvet covers from amazoncom": "1.3", "covers": "1.9", "duvet": "2.6"}, "department_id": 10},
