{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 5142, "catid": 1480, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1063252_nr_n_6?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A1063252%2Cn%3A3732131&bbn=1063252&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833496&rnid=1063252", "text": "Bedding Collections", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Bedding Sets from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A1063252&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"bedding": 7, "bedding sets": 5, "amazoncom": 4}, "description_wc": 340, "description_text": "At the end of a long day, you want to crawl into a warm, perfectly soft bed that melts away your stress and is a comfortable place to rest and recharge. Choosing the right bedding set will help you create the ideal place to lay your head. If you like your bed fuzzy and warm, try set of flannel sheets for extra coziness. If you\u2019re more comfortable in smooth, luscious fabrics, a set of satin or silk sheets might suit you better. There are dozens of styles in every material at Amazon.com, so take your time and find the bedding sets that are just right for you. Standing in a store staring at a wall packed with endless colors and materials can be overwhelming. At Amazon.com, our convenient product filters make it easy for you to browse the colors and materials you\u2019re looking for, without having to sift through the ones you don\u2019t. No more searching through enormous bins hunting for the correct size--simply filter your results to only show bedding sets in the size you need. When it comes to items you use every day like bedding, it\u2019s important that they meet your expectations. At Amazon.com, you can read reviews written by other people who have bought the exact items you\u2019re interested in to find out if they were satisfied. You can even choose to browse through all of the items that have been positively reviewed by other customers. Wondering if those German flannel bedding sets is going to end up pilling? Simply check the reviews to see what other buyers say. There\u2019s no need to be an expert on bedding sets when you shop at Amazon.com. We provide detailed information for most products that include specific sizes, materials and thread counts, making it easy to compare similar products. Your bed can be the most comfortable place in your home, and a wonderfully restful place to relax. Find your favorite among our large selection of bedding sets and created your ultimate retreat.", "parent_text": "Bedding", "parent_catid": 1110, "keyword_density": {"bedding": "2.1", "bedding sets": "2.9", "amazoncom": "1.2"}, "department_id": 10},
{"nr_products": 13473, "catid": 1481, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1063252_nr_n_7?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A1063252%2Cn%3A1063254&bbn=1063252&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833496&rnid=1063252", "text": "Bed in a Bag", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_wc": 0, "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A1063252&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "parent_text": "Bedding", "parent_catid": 1110, "department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "department_id": 10},
{"department_text": "Home, Garden & Tools", "nr_products": 86302, "catid": 1482, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1063252_nr_n_8?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A1063252%2Cn%3A1063272&bbn=1063252&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833496&rnid=1063252", "text": "Shams, Bed Skirts & Bed Frame Draperies", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_284507_ex_n_1?rh=n%3A1055398&bbn=1055398&ie=UTF8&qid=1393338782", "description_title": "Shams from Amazon.com", "parent_url": "http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=lp_1055398_nr_n_2?rh=n%3A1055398%2Cn%3A%211063498%2Cn%3A1063252&bbn=1063498&ie=UTF8&qid=1395833450&rnid=1063498", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 3, "shams": 10}, "description_wc": 381, "description_text": "Your bedroom is your sanctuary and the place where we spend a third of our lives in rest and sleep. If you\u2019re looking to create a restful, peaceful space or you want to add a flourish to your bedroom d\u00e9cor, try adding the softness and warmth of fabric accents. With pillow shams, bed skirts, and bedframe drapes from Amazon.com, you can create a personal oasis of comfort in your bedroom. Pillow shams give shape, texture, and color to ordinary pillows. Our large selection of patterns, materials, and colors at Amazon.com mean you\u2019ll be able find the perfect sham to go with your current bedspread or bedroom d\u00e9cor. We have everything from elegant, classic designs like eyelet or satin shams to pillow shams with rockets, Harley Davidson fireballs, and kids\u2019 themes. Shams are also incredibly easy to put on and remove for cleaning. Pillows fit into their shams through a simple envelope in the back. You can even find varieties of shams that don\u2019t use buttons or zippers, so you can keep your bed smooth, catch-free, and snag-free. To go with your new pillow shams, we have bed skirts to add softness to your bedframe. Our ruffled and lacey bed skirts will add gentle lines to your interior decorating scheme. Used in conjunction with the bed risers, you can create extra storage space under your bed while hiding all of your boxes and bags behind our decorative bed skirts. Many of our bed skirts, pillow shams, and other bedding supplies are eligible for Free Shipping, so you won\u2019t get surprised by unexpected delivery costs. Bedframe drapes and canopies were originally designed to keep cold out of drafty bedrooms, but now can add a rich, luxurious feeling to any bedroom instantly. Much the same as Georgian four poster beds, these bedframe drapes add a rich colorful canopy over your bed to make you feel like royalty. Our light-weight, Moroccan style drapes are ideal when you want to dress up your bedroom in warmer weather. We even have mosquito netting to add a charming mood while sleeping bug free. Make your bedroom an oasis of comfort and rest, when you add the softness and warmth of pillow shams, bed skirts, and bedframe drapes from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Bedding", "parent_catid": 1110, "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.8", "shams": "2.6"}, "department_id": 10},
